\id PSA - Yawa NT 
\h MASMUR 
\toc1 Masmur 
\toc2 Masmur 
\toc3 Mzm 
\mt1 MASMUR 
\is1 AYAO MANASYIN 
\ip Bukugo Masmur somamo Ayao Amisy ama nake inta mije, wemirati ransyeran muno sambaya no rai. Arono manasyin dave ratoe irati ayao Ibrani rai. Tume pakoe rave omirati Masmur umaso ratoe anyi: manasyin dave Musa po inta ratoe, umba mansanan ava Daud po inta ratoe, umba nto ava kawasae Yahudi wuje Babel raora ti wakata no Israel weamo wo Masmur inta ratoe tavon. Bukuge somamo vatano makarikuga mbaro ransyerane rai wo ratantona ti wo ratoe muno ukiny daive. Umba ransyeran muno sambaya umaso, vatano Israel wo ranunugambe akato muno wo ratoe indamu ukiny dai no arono wo sambaya rave, weti umba ratoe tavon no Ayao Amisye rai. 
\ip Ransyerane kotaro ratoe umaso ama kotare manui, maisyare so: inta mamo ransyerano kangkaman, muno ransyerano mbeaje Amisy Ai. Inta mamo sambaya Amisy anajo indamu aemeno nai, inta mamo Amisy anajo indamu darino naora muno Po napaya ana nsosobe rai. Inta mamo sambaya Amisy anajo inda Po ayao kakai rapaya muno inta mamo ransyerano kove raura seo Amisye Ai weye Apa kove nde nai. Inta mamo sambaya Amisy anajo indamu Po mangke raude marova mai. Ransyerane umaso inta mainyamo mo vatane apa anaundi no anuga rave raura, yara kaije inta mainyamo mo anugano Amisye awa ubekedaije muno manaundije raura. 
\ip Tamo Amisy ratoe ayao Yawa rai no taiso: ‘‘AMISY’’ ratoe urupijo akokoe rai tenambe som, no ayao Ibrani rai mare \it YHWH\it* (bacave raijamo \it Yahweh.\it*) Muno ‘‘Amisy’’ ratoe urupijo akoe no manasyine obo rai som, no ayao Ibrani rai mare \it Elohim.\it* Amisye Apa tame jirume umaso mbe mobe no buku Masmur so rai. 
\ip Masmur umaso ama ayao mamo Yesus Po inta raura nakato. Muno vatano wo Urairi Wanyine ratoe nawamo wo Masmur ama ayao inta ratoe akato tavon. Anugano Kristen manasyin dave maija ndea naiso manayanambe tenambe wo Masmur raugavo sambaya rai. 
\iot ETET RAOSO DAI: 
\io1 Masmur umaso ama mote 150, raosor akato ama etet radani, maisyare so: 
\io2 Etet Manasyin: moto 1–41 
\io2 Etet Jirum: moto 42–72 
\io2 Etet Mandeij: moto 73–89 
\io2 Etet Mambisy: moto 90–106 
\io2 Etet Radani: moto 107–150 
\c 1  
\ms1 ETET 1 
\ms1 MASMUR 1-41 
\s1 Vatano kov muno vatano mamun aya unanui 
\q1  
\v 1 Kove ngkov irati vatano are pirati ponae beto vatano mamune\f + \fr 1:1,4,6 \fq vatano mamun \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Ai muno Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.\f* awa ananyao raiji, 
\q2 muno ponae tavondi vatano wo ayao kakai rave awa unanui raiji, 
\q2 muno ponae tuna vatano wo Amisye aura tantunawi matavoni. 
\q1  
\v 2 Yara apa bekere mamo ananyao AMISY, 
\q2 muno siman naman po ananyao AMISY\f + \fr 1:2 \fq AMISY: \ft Ayao Ibrani mo \ft \+it YHWH\+it* ratoe, bacave taiso maisy: ‘‘Yahweh.’’ Omamo Amisye taune Apa tam dave mije, ama ine mare ‘‘RISY irati RISY.’’ Tame so tavonamo ama ine mare ‘‘Risyamo sasye ramu nai unumeso ntoa nuge nuganui,’’ raura tavona ‘‘RISYAMO no pitawabe.’’ \f* obo ratantona tutir. 
\q1  
\v 3 Indati anakere kotar po raijare mamo ama ine raen, 
\q2 raurata inyo moto nte no mana tuga 
\q2 ama wao mayone ramu, 
\q2 arono anamuke ama muki nande, weamo man dave. 
\q1  
\v 4 Yara vatano mamune usasye, 
\q2 onawamo maurata kapume rai, 
\q2 ovare damawisyamo nsaonto ti rakanive. 
\q1  
\v 5 Maisyare omaiti, onawamo usayae kakai no AMISY amun, 
\q2 arono Po mangke rapatimu, 
\q2 weye ayao kakai no mai ti usisa vatano kove\f + \fr 1:5,6 \fq vatano kove \ft onawamo vatano ubeta Amisye Apa ananyao rai.\f* mai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weye vatano kove nawamo AMISY Po mansayaranande, 
\q2 yara vatano mamune nawamo wo unanuijo kakai raronto kobe. 
\c 2  
\s1 Vatano Amisye taune Po aijaseo akarijo titi rai 
\q1  
\v 1 \f + \fr 2:1 \ft Anemo 1 muno 2 ratoe akato no Arakov. 4:25-26.\f*Wakoe! Veanimaibe susyo wanave Amisye Ai jewene ubesea mangkakeraive? 
\q2 Veanimaibe susye kotare manatantonave ana ngkakai rai? 
\q2 Weramu indati ubea marudija! 
\q1  
\v 2 Akari titi mine so wanatatayaube tenambe, 
\q2 muno akari akokoe wanunugambe wanyinyaube, 
\q2 indamu umarovave AMISY Ai, muno Apa akari titi Po aijaseo\f + \fr 2:2 \ft No koano Israel raijamo vatano wo apatimu indamu be akari titive opamo manino saitun rauvaro akari rai.\f* ai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Akari akokoe umaso wo raura ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Wade! Wampapaya irati aya ibe akarive wansai rai,\f + \fr 2:3 \ft Munijo una no Israel makijani nawamo wonae akari titi Israel be akarive maiji, weti ware umarovave ai.\f* 
\q2 muno wamo aya vambunino mo wansaokaisye radaut.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Akoe tuna no Apa kursijo titi rai no Manunggara 
\q2 pugoeno mai muno Po maura tantunawi. 
\q1  
\v 5 Umba soowato mai Apa parijo mangke rai, 
\q2 muno Po mapapabe irati Apa parijo mpanyoane rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Amisy Po raura pare: ‘‘Nai Sion, Sya unato ndandinit, 
\q2 Syo akari syatayao aijaseo akari titi rai to!’’ 
\q1  
\v 7 Ribeker syare syo AMISY Apa ayao Po raura aje rinai ravov, 
\q2 Po raura pare: ‘‘Winyamo Sya arikainye pi winy!\f + \fr 2:7 \ft Ayao so ratoe tavon no Arakov. 13:33; Ibr. 1:5, 5:5.\f* 
\q2 Masyoto unumeso Syo naijaseo akari rai, Syo nawainamo Sya arikainye pi winy. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare nyo Rinanajo indamu Syo susye kotare maunande ti nya ura mai tawan, 
\q2 muno muni tename som ti nto no ama marane rai, omamo syo raunande indamu wimbe akarive rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wenawamo indati winyo manepati nya isyo besije rai, 
\q2 muno nyo makupi vintabo, maisyare kavine inta ravari ti ngkukupi vintabo wemaisy.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Maisyare omaiti, akarijo titi weap, syare wapo rakarae kobe! 
\q2 Inya, akari akokoe mine so weap, wapo ananyao raraniv kobe! 
\q1  
\v 11 Wabeaje wapanapatambe AMISY Ai muno wapo asyaniv, 
\q2 wabeaje watutar no Amun. 
\q1  
\v 12 Indamu vemo Amisye parijo wasai mo wapuenen papabe inya, 
\q2 weye Apa parijo mangke mamo nde papabe rave. 
\b  
\q1 Kove ngkov irati vatano ugaugambe Amisye Aije mai. 
\c 3  
\s1 Ransyeran rikiny dai no awatan ngkov arono marova umarovave rinai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe, arono sarar ti to, weye apa kavo Absalom pare be marovave ai.\f + \fr 3:1 \ft 2Sam. 15:13-17:22\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, wakoe! Sya marova wanui rave! 
\q2 Vatano ubesea ti umarovave rinai wanui rave! 
\q1  
\v 3 Vatane wanui wo inaura ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Amisye pamo indati Po apaya irati marova mai ramu.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Weramu sya AMISY, Winyirati ndarino rinaora, 
\q2 maisyare naite apa vakano po raijaro aora ramaisy, 
\q1 Winyirati Nyo anasineko raunande rinai, 
\q2 muno Nyo inanuga so raveti mbambunin. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syo AMISY winanonae inanamoto manakoeve rai, 
\q2 muno nai Sion, unato ndandinit terave taune ntuna rai, 
\q2 Winyo sya ana idanonae raveti mamaisyo rinai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Arono naman ribeaje niki muno rinikito mariraave, 
\q2 muno awatan ngkov ribeseo akato weye AMISY Winyo rinayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 7 Vatano wo rinawariki ra umarovave rinai awa wanui mamo ratore kakai, 
\q2 weramu risyamo syo masyanive ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY, mbeseo!\f + \fr 3:8 \fq mbeseo: \ft Maisyare muno Pemasmur po apa marova maeno \ft \+it ubesea\+it* ti umarovave ai no anemo 1 rai, weti soamo po Amisye awain indamu \+it beseo ra\+it* Po apaya irati mai.\f* 
\q2 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo rinapaya irati kakai rai! 
\q1 Tugae, Winyi Nyo mangke raude sya marova mai tenambe, 
\q2 Winyi Nyo vatano mamune umaso awa vambunine radaut.\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Tugae, Winyi Nyo sya marova matamo tenambe mawamona rai. Winyi Nyo vatano mamun awa matomokane radaut bintabo.’’ Ama ine mamo maisyare ratoe no aneme so rai wemaisy.\f* 
\q1  
\v 9 AMISY, Winyirati Nyo reansapaya irati reama marova mai, 
\q2 syare Nyo Nya kove raugaje Nya kawasae reansai. 
\c 4  
\s1 Amisye anajo, no arono naman 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukinyo rai, wo itari\f + \fr 4:1 \fq Itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* raeyan dai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, Winyirati Nyo marimbe irati rinai, 
\q2 ranivara syo nawain syare Nyo rinaraniv. 
\q1 Arono rino irati anakotaro nsosobe rai, Winyirati Nyo rinapaya irati rai to. 
\q2 Syare naemen irati rinai, muno Nyo sya ana danajo ore raraniv! 
\q1  
\v 3 Inya, vatane weap, wapo inaura tantunawi ma ntoa nandui rati umba nsopija? 
\q1 Wabekero ayao ama ine mewen dai bo rai 
\q2 muno wasanuga no aarurijate rai mamo, ntoa nandui rati umba nsopija? 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare wadaen: tugae, AMISY Opamo Po vatano atawandi tavondi Ai atayao terave amarom to. 
\q2 AMISY Po rinaraniv arono risyo anonae. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ranivara nyare mpari, weramu vemo nyo ayao kakai rave nora, 
\q2 yara nyo ratantona vayave no nanuga muno manin dautan no niki ri arono naman.\f + \fr 4:5 \ft Matius 5:23-24; Epesus 4:26\f* 
\q1  
\v 6 Syare wapo anakotare rameseo AMISY Ai mamaisyo Apa anaparatote rai, 
\q2 muno wapanave irati Ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7-8 Vatano wanui wo raura ware: ‘‘Koveamo reana kovo ana mawese obo rai jakato rema!’’ 
\q2 Vatane umaso manayanambe awa nawaisye ama ino manui wo raugabe rai. 
\q1 Abo! Sya AMISY, reamare Nya kove mbaro reansai! 
\q2 Weye anayanambe Winyo raugaje ntami inanuga so rai mamo mo awa rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weti umba risyaje niki ti, riniki mariraave, 
\q2 weye sya AMISY, Wibuiny irati Nyo rinayaranande ti rino kovo saumane rai! 
\c 5  
\s1 Sambaya Amisye anajo indamu tuna inautan 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukiny dai, wo suline ramawisyo rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, syare namarikoame rasakinade sya ana danajo ore so rai, 
\q2 sya anonae mamo syare Nyo ranaun. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sya Amisy, Winyirati sya Akari Titi, 
\q2 syare Nyo sya anonae raraniv muno Nyo rinaeno rai, 
\q2 weye Wibuiny irati sya sambaya so raura ore Nai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya AMISY, arono akane ntipu, Winyi Nyo sya ana daura ore Nai ranaun. 
\q2 Arono awatan ngkov, sya ana idanajo ratodi nanentabove ore Winai,\f + \fr 5:4 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware ayao Ibrani ama ine maisyare so: ‘‘arono akane ntipu, syo anakotare ratayao indamu syo rameseo Nai.’’\f* 
\q2 muno syo Nya ana ndaura akare rinaije ranyut. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Weye Winyamo Amisyo nyonae irati ana ngkakainoanive rai, 
\q2 vatano mamune nawamo nyonae ude umararai Winaiji. 
\q1  
\v 6 Vatano mararine nawamo umamaisyo usayae no namune ramu, 
\q2 muno Winyamo nanuga mamuno vatano awa ana udave mamune mai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Vatano wo aarurijate rakedije nawamo, Winyo maupaeta vintabo, 
\q2 vatano maneme nijam muno wo anapamponae rave nawamo, AMISY winanuga mamuno mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Yara risyamo syore siso no Nya Yavar, 
\q2 weye Winyamo Nya muinyo no tawane manakoe rave. 
\q1 Rinamumbeto no tanoano ndandinit, 
\q2 ribeaje irati Nai inanuga mpayaje rai, weye syo nasyaniv. 
\q1  
\v 9 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo inaugavo Nya mbekere raron, mamaisyo Nya ananyao rai, 
\q2 weye sya marova wanui rave. 
\q1 Syare Nyo Nya unanuijo nsarokire ratayao da syanya rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Sya marova awa ana udaura mamo ayao mamaisye ma jewen, 
\q2 mansanuga mamo ntairijo ana ngkakainoanive rai. 
\q1 Awa ayao muje no mansanuga rai mamo ngkakainoanive, 
\q2 maisyare vatane anasino kopa mandami ti mbaug no aipapo wemaisy. 
\q2 Aarurijate ntairi mansawa rai.\f + \fr 5:10 \ft Aneme so ama ayao inta ratoe akato no Roma 3:13.\f* 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya AMISY, awa ayao kakai mamo koveamo Nyo ama mangke raude mai ra wo ranawan, 
\q2 koveamo awa ana wo ratantona ti ngkakai so raugakare ra mo taune makep asyo. 
\q1 Syare Nyo mavakano marambe, weye awa ayao kakai manui rave, 
\q2 muno wonae ubeta Winaiji. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Yara koveamo vatan tenambe ugaugambe Nai nawamo mansananibe, 
\q2 syare ukinyo manamoto manakoe rai, umananibea ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1 Syare Winyi no mansaora kijani, 
\q2 indamu vatano umuinyo Nai mananibe weye Nya ura mai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weye AMISY, Nyo kove raude irati vatano ubeta Nya ananyao rai mai, 
\q2 Winyi ndarino maora irati Nya muinye rai, 
\q2 maisyare naite apa vakano no aora wemaisy. 
\c 6  
\s1 Ransyeran weotor Amisye anonae arono no irati wanene rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukiny dai wo itari\f + \fr 6:1 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai. Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it sheminith\+it* ama ine mba kobe jewen, weramu kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware ama ine mare ‘‘itari ama waije kaumandeij.’’\f* ama wai kaumandeije raeyan dai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, syare vemo Nyo Nya pari mangke raugaje rinai nora, 
\q2 vemo Nyo Nya pari mpanyoane veano inanepat inya. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sya AMISY, syare naemeno rinai weye sya vambunine meweno rinai to. 
\q2 AMISY, syare Nyo saumane raude rinai weye inanasine tename so mayondi rave, 
\q1  
\v 4 muno inanuga so ntanamanine jewen. 
\q2 Sya AMISY, winakirive rinaija ntoa nanduija?! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY, syare namumbe de rinai, 
\q2 Nyo rinapaya irati kakai rai mamaisyo Nya muinyo no tawane rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weye ranivara syasyo no wene ama uga rai, weamo rinanimari Winai, 
\q2 rikangkamambe Nya tame rai akato no amani jewen. 
\q1  
\v 7 Rimarerembe rave weye syanonae tutir, 
\q2 namane anteter inami ngkaru nsoyan no sya vasyoto niki ri, 
\q2 inami ngkaru nsopato sya anukane rai ti mbaubu. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syoyov tutir ti inami tuga mbambanai weye inanimaumbe rave, 
\q2 sya marova wo inansewabe ti syoyova inami ndadiri. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Inya, vatano mamune weap, wata ra wasaumandita, 
\q2 weye AMISY Po sya oyove ranaun to. 
\q1  
\v 10 AMISY Po sya sambaya syo awaine ranaun to, 
\q2 muno sya ana danajo mamo AMISY Po raveti mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 11 Indati sya marova nao tenambe upaparo mai ti usamane, 
\q2 ti kavuratawe wansuk akiri muno usamane ti unanajibe. 
\c 7  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po patimu moyare raugaje 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano weotor, kinyo raijo AMISY Ai, weye Kus vatano susyo Benyamin po awatan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY, Winyirati sya Amisy, Winyirati inamamavube Nai; 
\q2 syare Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 muno vatan tenambe nanawirati wo rinawatane mai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Vemo naneme mpaya rinai jinya, indamu vemo sya marova wo rinarisyi nora, 
\q2 maisyare make sivuiny\f + \fr 7:3 \fq make sivuiny \ft ranigwano ‘‘singa’’ rai.\f* aroyaro rinai, po rinararambe ti to, yara vatane inta wo rinapaya ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4-5 AMISY, Winyirati sya Amisy, ranivara syo ana inta raveti ngkakaija ava, 
\q2 ranivara syo ana inta raveti ngkakaijo sya arakova aija ava! 
\q1 Indako ranivara rinaroyaro sya marova aijo ana mamaisye jewene raija ava! 
\q2 Weti ranivara sya ana dave ngkakai tugae tai somaisy, 
\q1  
\v 6 weamo sya marova wo rinawatan kai indamu wo rinaijar, 
\q2 muno wo rinatakare, wo rinauvabe no kopa, 
\q2 muno wo rinaubaisy ti wo sya koke ramauta ntami vayave no kopa von. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Sya AMISY, syare nseo naugananave Nya pari rautan, 
\q2 syare mbeseo ra naroyaro vatano upari ti umarovave rinai mai. 
\q1 Sya AMISY, syare mbeseo ra Nyo inasopan, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Nyo patimu mamaisye raude vatane mai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Amisy, syare koveamo susye kotare wangkuire tenambe ra una nakijani, 
\q2 muno wintuna no Manunggara indamu mbe akarive mansai vintabo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 AMISY, syare Nyo patimu raugaje susye kotare mai tenambe mamaisyo awa ana udave rarijati. 
\q2 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo patimu moyare raugaje rinai weye ana mamaisye mi syo rave, 
\q2 muno ana ngkakai ma syo inta rave ramu. 
\q1  
\v 10 Sya Amisy, Winyirati moyar, 
\q2 syare vatano mamune awa ana udave ti mamune mamo Nyo ransopi, 
\q1 yara vatano ubeta Naije nawamo Nyo mavera usayae tindimuve tawan, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Nyo vatane awa ana udatantona muno manuga rayasir tenambe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Amisye Opirati sya vakano no rinaora, 
\q2 Wepirati Po vatano manuga nsarokire mapaya marova aneme rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Amisye Opirati akari Po patimu moyare raugaje, 
\q2 masyote anteteramo pari mangkebe vatano mamune mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Tugae, ranivara vatane usakinavo awa ana udave rai jewen, 
\q2 weamo Amisye Po Apa omake rawan ti nsansinao dave, 
\q2 Po Apa apae raivit Po atoe rantiki rai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Po anaiyu mo wene raugavere ratayao, 
\q2 muno Po Apa ato mbadurur dave ratayao. 
\q1  
\v 15 Tugae rave, vatano mamune man dave irati ana ratantona ngkakaije rautan, 
\q2 opamo po ana ngkakaije raugavo vatane mai muno po maponae tutir. 
\q1  
\v 16 Po ateme rawae vatano kaije mai 
\q2 weramu taune pirati pakato temasyo rai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Ana ngkakai panatantonave raijo vatano kaije mai omamo makare ti mo taune anepat, 
\q2 muno ivuinyo bekero rai omamo makare ti mo taune aron. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 Yara risyamo syo kove raura seo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weye Opamo moyar. 
\q1 Muno rikinyo ransyeran kangkamane rai, 
\q2 syo AMISY Titi Rave Apa tame rararimbe. 
\c 8  
\s1 Vatane wamamo AMISY Po wansatantona rave 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Mamaisyo ransyeran ‘‘Gitit’’\f + \fr 8:1 \ft Ayao ‘‘Gitit’’ ama ine raene ramu. Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware ama ine mare ransyerano munijo Gat, weramu kuruno kaijinta ware omamo ransyerano vatano Israel ukiny dai arono wo anggur ama mane rakugan no mampiriare rai, weye ayao Gat ama ine mare ‘‘mampiriaro anggur.’’\f* rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Tugae AMISY, Winyirati reama Akoe, 
\q2 wakoe, Nya tame ntiti rave no mine tename so! 
\q2 Nya kovo ntiti mo naume rakivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 3 Nde no arikainy tuvan muno arikainyo wisyisyo ukame rai mansai wo nararimbe. 
\q1 Weye Nyo Nya vambunine ratonamo mansai to,\f + \fr 8:3 \ft Matius 21:15-16 mamo Yesus Po aneme so ama ine raura kakavimbe pare Amisye pamo Po arikainye manyao indamu wo ararimbe.\f* 
\q2 ti mo Nya marova mapamo muno vatano uparijo Naive mapamo tavon. 
\q1  
\v 4 Wakoe! Syo naume warae ranyanyube, 
\q2 windanari naneme rai–embae, tume, Winyo ratonami, 
\q1  
\v 5 umba veanimaibe Nyo vatan bayave mansatantona rave? 
\q2 Muno veanimaibe Nyo arikainyo vatane mayaranande rave tavon? 
\q1  
\v 6 Weramu Winyo manari to kavintare umba wo Nya naito titi\f + \fr 8:6 \ft Ayao Ibrani naiso mare \ft \+it elohim,\+it* ama ino manasyine mamo ‘‘Amisye,’’ yara ama ino jirum mamo ‘‘naito Amisy muno anakotaro ntuna no munijo ntiti.’’ Aneme so ratoe akato no Ibrani 2:7, ama ine no naije mare ‘‘naito Amisy.’’\f* mansamaisy. 
\q2 Winyo mansainyave kovo ntiti rai muno Nyo tamo manakoe raugaje mai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Winyo vambunine raunanto mai ti ube akarive anakotaro ndanari rai vintabo. 
\q2 Nyo raveaje ntuna no majo ate rai: 
\q1  
\v 8 kambine, domba muno sapi 
\q2 muno maere kotar nsyisyaube ntuna no anoko ayamuga; 
\q1  
\v 9 insani kotar muno jiane kotar 
\q2 muno anakotar tenambe ntovabe no nawanan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Tugae, AMISY, Winyirati reama Akoe, 
\q2 wakoe, Nya tame ntiti rave no mine tename so! 
\c 9  
\s1 Amisye Po patimu moyare raugaje mine so rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Mamaisyo ransyeran ‘‘Mut-Laben’’ rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 \f + \fr 9:2 \ft Arono Masmur 9 muno 10 ratoe no wusyinoe, omamo masmur mbe intabove. Masmur umaso omamo ransyerano Ibrani \ft \+it akrostik\+it* inta mije, weye ntavondi urupijo Ibrani ama ntetebeaje rai. Weramu ayao Yawa ntavondi urupije so rai jewen.\f*Syare syo kove raura seo AMISY Winai, inanuga ntenami rautan, 
\q2 muno syare syo Nya anakotaro ndaveti mbe anaanibe rariri. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare inananibe muno inanayanambe weye Winya ana ndave mbewar, 
\q2 sya Amisy Winyi Ntiti Rave, syare rikiny syo Nya tame rararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye wimarovave sya marova mai ti wansuk muno unanajibe, 
\q2 onawamo utaopon muno ugwenen. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye Winyirati Nyo marimbe rinai, 
\q2 muno Winyirati Akari Nyo moyare rapatimu rinai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Winyo mangke rapatimu susyo wanave Nai jewene mai to, 
\q2 muno Nyo vatano mamune maupaeta ti makanive, 
\q2 muno awa tame mamo Nyo raupaisy ti rakanive ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 7 Reama marova nawamo maupaeta ti makanive to, 
\q2 awa muni mainyamo Nyo rakupi ti ntuna, 
\q2 weti vatane inta mansaemendi akato mai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 8 Weramu AMISY Winyirati mbe akarive ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 wintuna no kursijo titi rai indamu Nyo mangke rapatimu mine so rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Winyirati Nyo patimu moyare raugaje vatan tenambe mine so mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo ayao mamaisye rapatimu susye kotare mai. 
\q1  
\v 10 AMISY Winyirati yano oram ntiti no irati vatano matawanto maora, 
\q2 Winyirati ndarino maora arono una irati ana nsosobe rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya AMISY, vatano wo naen tugaive no manuga rai nawamo mansanaveano winamen, 
\q2 weye vatano ude ubeaje Nai nawamo winaneme mpaya mai jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Wakiny! AMISY ararin, Wepirati be akarive no Sion! 
\q2 Wapo Apa ana dave ravovo susye kotare mai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weye Opirati Po mangke rasakinavo vatano maneme nijame mai, 
\q2 yara aemeno vatano matawanto mai, muno animari wanonae rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 14 Sya AMISY, syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 Nyo rinaen, sya marova wo rinansewabe ti risiuri rave, 
\q2 syare Nyo inapaya irati weno mare mo inaunto so rai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Indamu Nya ana ndave ti mamai dave mamo 
\q2 syo rararimbe no vatano Israel mansamun no nai unsanda akoe sisa no Yerusalem. 
\q2 Muno rinanayanambe weye Winyirati Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Susyo wanave Nai jewene nawamo utatayasyo atemo taune wo rawae rai, 
\q2 wakata usawa taune awa isyeano wo ratugare rai. 
\q1  
\v 17 AMISY Po taune aroron kakavimbe, 
\q2 pare taune Pirati Po patimu moyare raugaje. 
\q2 Vatano mamune awa ana udave mo taune maokaisy. Higayon.\f + \fr 9:17 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it higayon\+it* ama ine mare: nsopi vavai indamu ransyerano Masmur Israel ukiny dai umaso ama ine ratantona no nanuga.\f* 
\q1  
\v 18 Vatano mamune nawamo indati muenen ti wasya no amani, 
\q2 onawamo susyo wanave Amisye Ai jewene nao tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 19 Weramu vatano awa ana jajewembe mai nawamo Amisy Opamo parandeno mai jewen, 
\q2 muno vatano una siuri rai nawamo awa anave mpatimu jewen ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 20 AMISY, syare mbeseo, Nyo mangke raugaje susyo wanave Nai jewene mai. 
\q2 Vemo Nyo vatan bayave umaso manyanyut bayave inya, 
\q2 weye umararin wo ratantona ware awa vambunine mi mo Winya rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 21 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo mavera ujaniv dave, 
\q2 wirati susyo wanave Nai jewene wo taune mansaen dirive ware tugae, onawamo vatan bayave nanawa. 
\c 10  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po wansapaya irati vatano mamune mai 
\q1  
\v 1 Sya AMISY, mbe animaibe winggwaravainyo reansai? 
\q2 Muno Nyo reansaene jewen arono reana ana nsosobe rai? 
\q1  
\v 2 Weye vatano mamun mararine wo vatano matawanto mawatan tutir, 
\q2 weti koveamo awa ana wo ratantona ti mamuno reansai mo taune makep. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye vatano mamune umararino awa ubekere obo rai, 
\q2 vatano utantunaube wo AMISY aura tantunawi muno wo kakai ratoro Ai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Vatano mamune umaso nawamo mansamuno mararine obo raen dirive mai, 
\q2 weti wo Amisye akani jewen. 
\q2 Wo ratantona ware Amisye pamo no ramu. 
\q1  
\v 5 Vatano mamune umaso awa anakotaro wo raijare mamo ama ine raen kobe. 
\q2 Amisy Nya patimu moyare mamo ntiti rave, weramu onawamo unanta rai jewen. 
\q2 Wo vatano matawanto umaso\f + \fr 10:5 \fq vatano matawanto umaso: \ft ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘awa marova.’’ Vatano matawanto so nawirati vatano mamune awa marova nanawije.\f* matantona daradambe vayave. 
\q1  
\v 6 Wo raura no manuga, ware: ‘‘Risyamo inanto ana nsosobe inta rai ramu. 
\q2 Ana ngkakai mamo inta nande rinai jewen ntoa nuge nuganui.’’ 
\q1  
\v 7 Mawa mamo ntairi anaamatane,\f + \fr 10:7 \ft Roma 3:14\f* anapamponae, muno ukantetoaro ayao rai, 
\q2 manatantonave kakai rai me, ubekero wo vatane mave pabe obo mi wayao dai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 8 Ukaokaibe no kampo rai janyi indamu maroyaro vatane mai, 
\q2 no varoro maninimbe ukaokaibe ri we, wo vatano ayao kakai meweno mai maubaisy bayave. 
\q2 Wo vatano umayondi manyanyuti tutir. 
\q1  
\v 9 Onawamo maisyare make sivuinye\f + \fr 10:9 \fq make sivuinye \ft ranigwano ‘‘singa’’ rai.\f* wemaisy, 
\q2 ukaokaibe no insumai uga indamu wo vatane mansaman. 
\q1 Wo mansaman indamu wo vatano umayondi maijar,\f + \fr 10:9 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘aijar no ename rai.’’ Weti ama ananeneae maisyare jiane raugav no ename rai muno ugeye aijar no aviri rai. \f* 
\q2 wo vatano mayondi maijar muno wo mansararambe ti uta. 
\q1  
\v 10 Maisyare make akiri mona ntararai ti pare pirak da po natao wemaisy, 
\q2 onawamo ubambunin dave, ti wo vatano mayondi mataopon muno wo marisyi. 
\q1  
\v 11 Vatano mamune umaso wo ratantona no manuga, ware: ‘‘Amisye pamo animari wama ana wandave rai to! 
\q2 Somaisyamo amije ntatuvi ti merere nto mamo, Po wansaeno rai ramu.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 AMISY, sya Amisy, syare mbeseo ra Nyo mangke raugaje vatano mamune mai, 
\q2 yara naemeno vatano matawanto mai! 
\q1  
\v 13 Mbe animaibe vatano mamune wo Amisye aura tantunawi tutir, 
\q2 muno wo raura no manuga ware Amisye pamo Po makewabe awa ana udave rai ramu! 
\q1  
\v 14 Weramu Winyo raen to, weye Winyirati vatano umayondi wakare usaroro Nai, 
\q2 muno Winyirati Nyo arikainyo wawate mansayaranande. 
\q1 Winyo awa siuri muno mansanuga njorame raen to, 
\q2 indamu winanembe mai jakato. 
\q1  
\v 15 Nyo vatano mamune nawe, vatano awa ana udave ngkakainoanive awa vambunine radaut, 
\q2 Nyo mansakewabe awa udave ti ngkakai rai vintabo muno Nyo mansopi rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 AMISY Wepi be Akari titive tutira ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q2 Susyo wanave Ai jewene nawamo indati Po maupaeta irati Apa munije rai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Sya AMISY, Winyirati Nyo vatano matawanto awa ana udanajo raraniv, 
\q2 muno namarikoame rasakinavo mai muno Nyo mansanuga raijaseo ra mbambunin. 
\q1  
\v 18 Nyo patimu moyare raugaje arikainyo wawate muno vatano matakarasyo mai, 
\q2 indamu vemo vatano mine so inta seo po vatano umayondi mave yanibe akato inya. 
\c 11  
\s1 AMISY Wepi darino wansaora 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1 Risyamo rigaugambe AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weti mbe animaibe nyo inaura dea nyare: 
\q2 ‘‘Winyare mpaya kakai rai, weamo nyo pepake ratonami 
\q2 indamu nto nanto nte no unate warae!’’ 
\q1  
\v 2 Weye vatano mamune\f + \fr 11:2,5,6 \fq vatano mamun \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai tenambe.\f* po apae raivit, 
\q2 po atoe rantiki te no kaumudi rai, 
\q2 indamu po vatano beto Amisye Ai atapo. 
\q1  
\v 3 Ranivara ananyao mo kawasae wansaokaisye rataka doyadi, 
\q2 weamo vatano ubeta AMISY Ai ubeta ri mamaundi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY no no Apa Yavaro ndandinite rai, 
\q2 AMISY tuna no Apa kursijo ntiti rai no Manunggara. 
\q1 Ami ntamijo vatano mine so mai tenambe, 
\q2 Po vatane mayasiro mavabe muno Po matauno awa ana udave rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY Po vatano beto Ai pe vatano mamune pe 
\q2 yanuga rayasir tenambe. 
\q2 Opamo pari jirati vatano bekero ivuinye rai ai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Po mangke tanamo nsundive 
\q2 muno tanamo ama kijao ranavane ngkakai rasui vatano mamune mai,\f + \fr 11:6 \ft Mangke somamo ratoe tavon no Yesaya 30:33, 34:9; Yeheskiel 38:22; Wahyu 14:10, 19:20, 20:10, 21:8.\f* 
\q2 muno Po ovaro mamoane ratutiro mai ti mo manen; 
\q1 omirati mangke Po ratayao mansamarom. 
\q1  
\v 7 Weye AMISY Apa ana be muno Apa ana dave mamai dave, 
\q2 muno muiny irati vatano ubeta Apa ananyao raije mai, 
\q2 wenawamo indati wo amune raen. 
\c 12  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po wansapaya irati vatano angkarije mai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Kinyo rai itari ama wai kaumandeije raeyan dai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, syare nde Nyo sopambe rinai, 
\q2 weye vatane inta ubeta Winai jakato ramu to,\f + \fr 12:2 \ft Vatano Pemasmur po maura so onawamo taune apa arakovo Israel nao.\f* 
\q2 vatano matawandi ti utavondi Winai nawamo mansaumandi vintabo to. 
\q1  
\v 3 Vatan tenambe wayarurijabe taune mai vambinibe, 
\q2 maunane mamo mansak ti wo vatane maponae ayao manavane rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY, syare Nyo vatano wo ayao manavane ratore mansopi tenambe, 
\q2 muno Nyo vatano mawa mbaubu mawa rakuvu vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 5 Onawamo wo raura ware: ‘‘Reama ayao reandatore mirati vatane utaopono rai! 
\q2 Ana rui vayave reamare reamo raura mamo reandaura kai, 
\q2 muno vatane inta umamaisyo wo reansansopi rai kakai!’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Weramu AMISY Po raura pare: ‘‘Syo raen, wo vatano awa ana jajewembe matawanto, 
\q2 weti Syo raura syare: 
\q2 naije kobeamo Syo kovo sauman, namirati mansanaveano ramene, raunanto mai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 7 AMISY Apa urairi mamo mamaisyo anave rai, 
\q2 muno kakui maisyare peraki kakui ramaisy, 
\q2 namirati raugasya rauno taname rai susye kaururum indamu mbe peraki kakuive.\f + \fr 12:7 \ft Mamaisyo vatano Israel awa ana udatantona rai, kaururum omamo vari mamai dave. Ananeneae peraki omamo maisyare vatane wo angkaji rauno mavabe ra ndu rave indamu ama manino ngkov dave obo raen. Anakero peraki rauno taname rai raura kakavimbe no 1Petrus 1:7 ama catatan kaki rai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY, Winyirati ndarino reansaora, 
\q2 ndarino reansaora irati vatano mamun susyo naiso mai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye vatano mamune ntuna mandayano sota sore, 
\q2 muno awa ana udave ti ngkakainoanive mamo vatan tenambe ukangkamambe rai. 
\c 13  
\s1 Vatano matawanto awa ana udanajo AMISY Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Abo! Sya AMISY, ntoa nugoenta to winanimari rinai tutir bayave kobea e? 
\q2 Ntoa nugoenta to winakirive rinaija e? 
\q1  
\v 3 Ntoa nugoenta to inanuga mamaun, 
\q2 muno rinanuga ranimaumbe masyote yanteter. 
\q2 Ntoa nugoenta to sya marova wo inatawanto tutir kobea e? 
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY, sya Amisy, syare namumbe de rinai, Nyo sya ana danajo ravera mamaisy. 
\q2 Nyo vambunine raugakare rinai, muno vemo Nyo rinapayamo kakai nora. 
\q1  
\v 5 Vemo sya marova wo raura ware wo rinapinde to inya. 
\q2 Muno vemo umararin ware wo rinangkuku to inya. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weramu risyamo syanave irati Nya muinyo no tawano rinai rai, 
\q2 rinananibe weye Nyo rinapaya sya marova aneme rai to. 
\q1 Syare rikinyo ransyerane raijo AMISY Nai, 
\q2 weye Winyamo mbekobe irati rinai to. 
\c 14  
\s1 Vatane awa ana udave ngkakainoanive 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1 Vatano wantatukambe wo raura no manuga ware: ‘‘Amisye Pa inta no ramu.’’ 
\q2 Awa ana udave mamo mamun muno ngkakainoanive, 
\q2 vatan inta po ana ngkove rave ramu. 
\q1  
\v 2 No munijo Manunggara AMISY tuna Po vatan tenambe mansanyanyut, 
\q2 indamu Po mansaen vatane inta apa ana datantona ntiti no aija rako, 
\q2 muno beaje Aija nene rako. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weramu vatan tenambe makirive Ai, 
\q2 wenao tenambe awa ana udave ngkakainoanive. 
\q1 Vatan inta po ana ngkove rave ramu, 
\q2 vatan inta mamaisye jewen bayave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY pare: ‘‘Vatano awa ana udave mamun umaso nanawamo 
\q2 awa ana udatantona no maija rako, jewena e? 
\q1 Wenanawamo wo Sya kawasae Syo matayao mave tatugadi, 
\q2 muno wonae usambayambe Rinaiji.’’ 
\q1  
\v 5 Indati vatano mamune umaso ujaniv dave, 
\q2 weye Amisye Po vatano ubeto Aije mansayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 6 Vatano mamune ware wo vatano awa ananuge jajewembe mai mansosobe, 
\q2 weramu AMISY darino mansaora. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Syare koveamo Amisy Wepi no no Sion de Po Israel mapaya vatano mamune mai! 
\q2 Arono rui AMISY Po kovo ngko dave raugav akare Apa kawasae mai, 
\q2 weamo indati Yakop apa susyo Israel mansananibe. 
\c 15  
\s1 Vatano mamaisyo de no AMISY Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY, are pirati Nyo amayaro de siso no Nya randumo sambaya\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Randumo sambaya somamo mo wama randumo no no naiso ramaisye ramu. Yara Israel awa randumo no no ratuije mamo wo maero domba muno kambine awa kea wemi wo rave randumbe, omamo Akari Titi Daud wepi po ransano vayave ra usambayambe rai ma. 2Sam. 6:12-17\f* rai? 
\q2 Umba are pirati Nyo amayaro no natavon no Nya unato ndandinit\f + \fr 15:1 \fq Nya unato ndandinit \ft omamo unato Sion no no Yerusalem, Yavaro Amisye ntuna rije.\f* rai? 
\q1  
\v 2 Wepamo vatano ana ngkakaije inta raeno ai jewen,\f + \fr 15:2 \ft Apa ana dave tai maisy weti vatane wanaikebe ai kakai.\f* 
\q2 muno po ana mamai dave obo rave,\f + \fr 15:2 \ft Mamai dave weye mamaisyo Amisye Apa ananyao rai.\f* 
\q2 muno po ayao tugae obo raura anuga kakui rautan. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wepamo po apa vatane maura tantunawi jewen, 
\q2 muno panakakaive irati apa arakove mai jewen 
\q2 muno po yavaruga kaije maura tatugadi jewen tavon. 
\q1  
\v 4 Wepamo po vatano AMISY ponae mansai, matantona titive jewen, 
\q2 yara po vatano ubeta AMISY Ai matantona titive. 
\q1 Muno vatane so teto apa urairi rai tawan kobe. 
\q2 Ranivara nanto ana nsosobe inta rai weamo akirive apa urairi umaso raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wepamo apa arakove inta po doije inta augavo arijat, 
\q2 pare ranijan akare mamaisyo po raugave bo rai, 
\q2 yara ama nako nseo raija datavone mamo pare jewen kai. 
\q1 Muno wepamo vatano po doijo yanyano rawatambe 
\q2 indamu vemo ama mangke makare vatano mamaisye po ranawan inya. 
\b  
\q1 Vatano apa ana dave mamai tenambe maisyare so, 
\q2 wepamo indati teto tindimuve tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 16  
\s1 Amisye obo Pi aijaro usye rai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Masmur po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo inayaranande, 
\q2 weye Winyirati syakaore gaugambe Nai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Syayao to irati AMISY Ai, syare: ‘‘AMISY Winyirati sya Akoe Pi Winy, 
\q2 sya anakotar tenambe ngkovo rinai mamo Winyirati ndaunande rinai!’’ 
\q1  
\v 3 \f + \fr 16:3 \ft Anemo 3-4 no ayao Ibrani raijamo ama ine mbare ramu.\f*Vatano ubeta Amisy Winai una no muni so nao, 
\q2 onawirati mamaisyo maijaseo vombe, 
\q2 muno rimayaro no matavon. 
\q1  
\v 4 Vatano wo anawayo kotare masyanive nanawamo, awa anakotaro nsosobe mai mamo manakoe rave kobe. 
\q2 Wo maere mavu rameseo anawayo kotare mai mamo syonaeyo tavondi raiji, 
\q2 muno syonae inawa mpaato anawayo kotare awa tame rai no sya sambaya raiji. 
\q1  
\v 5 Sya AMISY, Wibuiny irati ribekero Nai, 
\q2 Winyirati Nyo sya anakotaro ibekedai raunande, 
\q2 muno sya tumo merere nto mamo no no winanem uga rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Tugae, maisyare tauno wai rapayaje mino minsine rai rinamarome wemaisy, 
\q2 kovo Nyo raosoro inamarome mamo mo anayanambe raugavo inanuga so rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Syo AMISY ararimbe, weye Opirati Po ananyao raugaje rinai, 
\q2 tugae, arono naman Apa ananyao ntairi inanuga rai weti mo inanyao unanui ngkove rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 \f + \fr 16:8 \ft Anemo 8-11 raen tavon no Arakov. 2:25-28.\f*Syo AMISY aijaro sya usye rai tutir, 
\q2 Opamo no inautan\f + \fr 16:8 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Opamo no no rinaneme ngkove rai,’’ ama ine mare Opamo no inautan.\f* weti riteto tindimuve tawan. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wemi mbewar inanuga so rananibe muno sya jugara anayanambe, 
\q2 muno inanasine tename so no mariraave kovo saumane rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Risyamo Nya vatano atawandi tavondi Nai pi risy, 
\q2 indati Nyo inapaya ti rituna tawan no wene ama uga raije ramu, 
\q2 muno Nyo inapaya ti inanasine so ntami mauge ramu.\f + \fr 16:10 \ft Arakov. 13:35 \f* 
\q1  
\v 11 Winyirati Nyo unanuijo nto no kovo nuge nuganuije rarorono rinai; 
\q2 Wintuna rinautan weti rinanayanambe, 
\q2 muno rino Winatavon weamo rinananibe tutir ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 17  
\s1 Sambaya Amisye anajo arono marova wo nawatan 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa sambaya. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo sya anonae so raraniv muno Nyo moyare raugaje rinai, 
\q2 namarikoame rasakinav de sya ana danajo inanuga tugae raije so rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Syare Nyo patimu moyare raugaje rinai indamu mbe rarorombe risya ana dave mamo musyo marambe jewen, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Nyo ana mamaisye raen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Ranivara Winyo inanuga so rayasiro mavabe, 
\q2 Nyo rayasiro mavabe no arono naman, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinakani mavabe rai, 
\q1 indati Nyo inaen risyamo ayao kakai meweno rinai, 
\q2 sya ana idaura musyo marambe jewen. 
\q1  
\v 4 Vatano wanui awa ana udave nsasye risya rai, 
\q2 yara risyamo sya ana dave mamaisyo Nya ayao rai. 
\q1 Risyamo syo inanasine so rayaranande ti itavobombe vatano wo ivuinye rave awa unanui raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 5 Risyamo itavondi Nya unanui obo rai, 
\q2 muno risyusyo akirive rai ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Sya Amisy, syo winanonae, 
\q2 weye Winyirati indati Nyo sya ana danajo raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 syare namarikoame rasakinav de rinai muno Nyo sya ana idaura so raraniv. 
\q1  
\v 7 Syare Nya muinyo no tawan mbe anainambe rarorono rinai. 
\q2 Weye Winyirati Nyo vatano mansamamavube Nai mapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 nanemo mbambunine omirati mo mavijuri awa marova mai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare Nyo rinayaranande maisyare risyamo Nya nanuga rave pi risy, 
\q2 Nyo inangkokaibe no nanem ate rai, maisyare mangkuere mo ama pepake veano tuvane rarau wemaisy, 
\q1  
\v 9 no inaora irati vatano mamun ware wo inaupaeta mai. 
\q2 Sya marova ware wo inaubaisye wo rinawariki, 
\q1  
\v 10 onawamo mansaemeno vatano kaije mai ramu, 
\q2 muno mansararino ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Ude umarovave rinai ti wo rinakijaniri, 
\q2 mansami ntetero rinai indamu wo rinakupisen muno wo rinangkukuv asyo tami no kopa. 
\q1  
\v 12 Onawamo maisyare singa kokaibe no varoro maninimbe ti po rinamane wemaisy, 
\q2 maisyare singa kamuram pare pirak indamu po rinatao wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Sya AMISY, mbeseo ra naroyaro sya marova mai, 
\q2 indamu Nyo mataopon, 
\q1 Nya omake veano rinapaya irati vatano mamune mai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Sya AMISY, syare nanemo vambunine veano rinapaya 
\q2 irati vatano ubekero ananugo mine so obo rai mai. 
\q1 Syare mangke ndatayao mai mamo, 
\q2 ndaugaje ra ratutumbe mai indamu mangke mai, 
\q1 muno mangke so merere masyo awa arikainye, ajavije mansai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 15 Yara risyamo indati syore te no Winamun, 
\q2 weye ibeto Nya ananyao rai muno syusyo akirive Nya ayao rai ramu. 
\q1 Muno arono rinikija ibeseo weamo inananibe, 
\q2 weye taune winarorono rinai. 
\c 18  
\s1 Kove raura seo Amisye Ai weye Po inapaya sya marova mai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud, wepirati vatano panapatambe AMISY Ai, po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane somamo Daud kinyo raijo AMISY Ai, arono AMISY Po apaya marova mai tenambe, muno akarijo Saul anem uga rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, rimuinyo Nai, 
\q2 Winyirati sya vambunine nsawa Nai. 
\q1  
\v 3 AMISY Opirati sya unato oram muno yano no inaora, Opirati Po rinapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q2 Sya Amisye Opirati sya unato oram inamamavube Ai. 
\q1 Opamo maisyare vakano no rinaora, muno Opamo bambunin\f + \fr 18:3 \fq bambunin: \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ine mare ‘‘korodowai’’ weye no koano Israel raijamo maero sapi apa korodowai mbe rarorombe vambunine rai.\f* Po rinapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q2 Opirati sya yano oram ntiti rinino aowan. 
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY Opirati mamaisyo aura titive; 
\q2 syo awain umba Po rinapaya irati marova mai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Risyamo waijo wene mo inapaka to, 
\q2 muno wene mo inaunto maisyare manayame nsepadi rinai to wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Waijo amani mo rinapapakai to, 
\q2 muno wene mo inaman maisyare aviri ratugar ti mo inaman no sya usye wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Arono rino ana nsosobe ama uga rai, syo AMISY awain, 
\q2 syanonaeto Amisye Ai indamu Po sopambe rinai. 
\q1 No no Apa yavaro tuna ri\f + \fr 18:7 \ft Apa yavaro tuna ri so no no munijo Manunggara.\f* Po inanamote ranaun, 
\q2 muno Po risya ana syo ranonae seo Aije raraniv muno Po rinasopan. 
\q1  
\v 8 Umba mine tename so mangkiki muno raunuve, 
\q2 muno unate mantaun masyo no ama ate waraya muno ntutar, 
\q2 weye Amisye Apa pari mangke mbadurur. 
\q1  
\v 9 Apa pari umaso maisyare kijao ntutupo atumateme raide, 
\q2 tanamo mbadurure muje no awa rai, 
\q2 muno neno nsundive muje rai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 10 Po naume raporar ti paje kobe, 
\q2 paje te no andoramo naaman dave ama vone rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Seo tuna naito Amisy kerub\f + \fr 18:11 \fq kerub \ft onawamo ana akokoe maisyare naito Amisy mansamaisy, una Amisy akijani no Manunggara. Yesaya 37:16; Yeheskiel 1:5-6, 10:20-21\f* ai weti badirir de, 
\q2 ovare po amawisy ti pavave de maisyare insani apa pepako mbadiriro autane wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 12 Po nugo naamane raijaro aora, 
\q2 andorame muno maruge wenairati maisyare randumo no aora wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weramu nai taune amunamo vare ntami, 
\q2 muno andorame muje raijo marugo esije me tanamo nsundive me rautan. 
\q1  
\v 14 Umba AMISY anamote ravari no naume warae; 
\q2 AMISY Titi Rave anamote ngkinde ti ranaun. 
\q1  
\v 15 Wepi Po ato veano marova maivuiny weti mpusyek tatugadi, 
\q2 omamo ivako Po ratatukande ti rantebai tutiro mai ti mo maungkananive. 
\q1  
\v 16 Naije mayane mamo eravo anawadi to no ate waraya, 
\q2 mine so ama ajijo mo ratugare raeno kakavimbe. 
\q1 Weye sya AMISY, Winyo sya marova mansaneneno soowabe, 
\q2 muno nanawayo parije veano mapuar. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Amisy Wepi tuna no Manunggara, aneme rareande Po inaijaseo, 
\q2 Po inakarimu sen no ana mo inatawanto, 
\q2 maisyare manayam akoe inta ama vambunine ramaisye rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Wepi Po inapaya irati sya marova ubambunin dave mai, 
\q2 muno vatano manuga mamuno rinaije mai, 
\q2 weye wenawamo awa vambuninen mo inakivan. 
\q1  
\v 19 Onawamo maroyaro rinai arono ana nsosobe mo inakep, 
\q2 weramu AMISY Po sopambe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Opirati Po inapaato no varoro ntanenae\f + \fr 18:20 \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ine mare ‘‘varoro ntanenae,’’ weye arono Pemasmur no irati ana nsosobe ama uga rai, omamo maisyare no no varoro nandi rai wemaisy.\f* rai, 
\q2 muno Po inapaya irati ana ngkakai rai weye Opamo anayanambe rinai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 AMISY Po kove rasakinavo rinai mamaisyo sya ana daveti ngkove rai, 
\q2 muno Po kove raugaje rinai weye syo ana inta ravera ngkakai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 22 Weye risyamo ritavondi tutiro AMISY Apa unanuije rai, 
\q2 muno rinakirive Aije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 23 Weye risyamo ibeto Apa anaparatote rai tenambe, 
\q2 muno Apa ananyao mamo idapaya ra ntami ramu. 
\q1  
\v 24 Risyamo syo ana inta ravera nggwambe no Amune rai ramu, 
\q2 muno inanasine so raisyisyi ana ngkakainoanive rai. 
\q1  
\v 25 Weti AMISY Po kove rasakinavo rinai mamaisyo sya ana daveti ngkove rai, 
\q2 muno Po kove raugaje rinai weye syo ana inta ravera ngkakai no Amune rai ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 26 Sya Amisy, nde irati vatano matawandi utavondi Nya ananyao raije mai, winteto Nya urairi raijo mai; 
\q2 muno nde irati vatano manuga nsarokire mai, Winyamo nanuga nsarokire rarorono mai. 
\q1  
\v 27 Nde irati vatano manuga ndandinite mai, Winyo Nya nanuga ndandinite rarorono mai, 
\q2 yara nde irati vatano wo kakai ratantona mai, Winyo namuno nsansinao rarorono mai. 
\q1  
\v 28 Susyo matawanto nawamo Winyo mapaya irati rai, 
\q2 yara vatano umararine nawamo Nyo maveaje. 
\q1  
\v 29 AMISY, Winyirati Nyo vare raugaje rinai maisyare yawainyo mbaro rinai wemaisy, 
\q2 sya Amisy, wimbaro kaumudi no rinakijani so rai. 
\q1  
\v 30 Weye Winyirati Nyo vambunine raugaje rinai ti inaroyaro marova mai, 
\q2 muno sya Amisy Nya vambunino mo inasopane mirati syo sya marova maukir ti risiso no awa munije rai.\f + \fr 18:30 \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ine mare ‘‘syo yane raiseo,’’ mbe rarorombe yano oram ntiti namirati mo munije rakijani indamu no raora rai.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 31 Amisye Apa ana dave mamo mamai dave, 
\q2 Amisye Apa urairi mamo mamai dave ti anave rai, 
\q2 Opirati vakano darino vatan tenambe ude mansamamavube Aije maora. 
\q1  
\v 32 Weye AMISY obo Pirati wama Amisye Pije, 
\q2 Amisy obo Pirati wama unato oram wansamamavube Ai pije. 
\q1  
\v 33 Wepirati Amisy, Po vambunine raunande wansai, 
\q2 muno Po inaugavo unanui syanya raije raito kovo saumane rautan. 
\q1  
\v 34 Wepi Po inajo raveti ndaradam, maisyare rusa ajo ndaradam ti po raansandi wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Po inapaato no mariraave no unato ntiti rai, weti marova wo inaubaisye jewen. 
\q1  
\v 35 Wepi Po inanyao irati marova rave rai, 
\q2 weti ribambunin syo apae moto tembaga mpanyoane raivit. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 36 Sya Amisy, Winyi Nyo rinapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 maisyare Nyo vakane raunande indamu no irati rinaora wemaisy. 
\q1 Nanem ngkov vambunine wemi mo inasopan, 
\q2 muno wimbekobe rinai weti umba syo anasineko. 
\q1  
\v 37 Winyi Nyo varoro maneka ratayao rinai no marova ama uga rai, 
\q2 weti ritet tawan ti rimarovave tutir, yara ritende jewen. 
\q1  
\v 38 Syo sya marova mawatan ti syo maijar, 
\q2 muno syo maotada mewen dainyamo syansop akare ramu. 
\q1  
\v 39 Syo kaipate ko mai ti wakaeyove akato kakai, 
\q2 wenawamo ntarurandi ti ntuna no inajo ate rai. 
\q1  
\v 40 Weye Winyirati Nyo vambunine raunande rinai indamu risiso marova rai, 
\q2 weti sya marova nawamo Nyo mataopon bintabo no inanem ate rai. 
\q1  
\v 41 Winyi mbewaramo syo anasineko sya marova mai, ti wansuk unanajibe, 
\q2 muno vatano manuga mamuno rinai umaso nawamo syo mao bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 42 Ugwain wanonae, weramu vatane inta ude wo sopambe mai ramu, 
\q2 wenawamo wanonaeto AMISY Ai, weramu Po maranive ramu. 
\q1  
\v 43 Syo maakoyandija ngkupi ti ntuna maisyare kapumo ovare damawisyamo nsaone wemaisy, 
\q2 muno syo kamumu tawano mai ti mparakami maisyare kopa mparadakambe no unanui wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 44 Winyi Nyo inapaya irati sya kawasaeyo wonae ubeta rinai mai, 
\q2 muno Winyo inaijaseo ti ibe akariveo susyo mato siso Israel mai jewene mai tavon, 
\q2 weti soamo syo vatano syantukambe maije mave anakebe no inanem ate rai. 
\q1  
\v 45 Vatano marane umaso ubeaje irati rinai, 
\q2 muno sya ayao idaugaje mamo wo ranaun ubeta rai kobe. 
\q1  
\v 46 Vatano marane umaso awa mangkakeraive raumandi mai to, 
\q2 wenawamo ututar wuje irati awa varoro ukaokaibe raije raora. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 47 Tugae! AMISY Opamo jayaisy tutir! 
\q2 Opirati sya unato oram inamamavube Ai, ti syo ararimbe. 
\q2 Kangkamambe Amisye Ai, Wepirati Po inapaya kakai rai! 
\q1  
\v 48 Amisye Pi Po kakai rasakinavo sya marova mai, 
\q2 Wepi Po susye kotare maveaje ntuna no inanem ate rai. 
\q1  
\v 49 Amisy, Winyi Nyo inapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 muno Winyi Nyo anasineko raunande rinai irati vatano umarovave rinai mai, 
\q2 Winyi Nyo inapaya irati vatano usivuiny dave mai. 
\q1  
\v 50 Maisyare omaiti, sya AMISY, syare syo kove raura seo Nai no susye kotare so awa yasyin, 
\q2 muno rikiny kangkamambe Nya tame rai. 
\q1  
\v 51 Winyo vambunine raunande akari titi Nyo aijaseo ai, weti po anasineko. 
\q2 Muno Nyo Nya muinyo no tawane rarorono vatano Nyo atayao terave indamu be akarive umaso ai, 
\q2 opamo Daud muno apa susyo merere nto maija ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 19  
\s1 AMISY Apa kovo ntiti raeno anakotaro danari rai muno raeno Apa ananyao rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po anugano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Naume muno ama anakotaro no no ama uga rai mo Amisye Apa kovo ntiti raroron, 
\q2 muno mandepe mo Apa anakero daijaro aneme rai raura. 
\q1  
\v 3 Masyote mo Apa kovo ntiti ravovo tutiro masyoto miridi nto rai, 
\q2 muno namane mo rariri tutiro namano miridi nto rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Naume ma mayaode intai jewen, mayao jewen bayave, 
\q2 ama ranamote mamo vatane wandanaune ramu. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weramu ama kine manonon nto no munije rai tenambe, 
\q2 ama ana mo raura mamo muija nto no munije ama mamaran rai vintabo.\f + \fr 19:4-5 \ft Aneme so ama ntunato raije mare naume mayao ramu, weramu mo Amisye Apa kovo ntiti raroron kakavimbe.\f* 
\q1 Nai naumo warae Amisye Po uma apa randume ratayao to. 
\q1  
\v 6 Uma umaso tipu seo kai rave, maisyare anya kamuram puje no apa tanoano vauname rai kai rave. 
\q2 Uma umaso puje, maisyare anaanivo bambunin pansanan irati apa unanuijo ratayao aije raito anayanambe rautan. 
\q1  
\v 7 Nai ranijo wanamuram uma tipu seo rai, 
\q2 pansanana to pasyo no varet, 
\q2 apa varo mamoane meweno vatane inta maije ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY Apa anaparatot wemi mamai dave, 
\q2 mo vambunine raugav akare vatane awa jugara mai jakato. 
\q1 Ananyao AMISY wemi ntindimu ti anave rai, 
\q2 mo ana ratantona ntiti raudeo vatano unanta rai jewene mai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Anaparatot AMISY wemamo ananyao nsarokir, 
\q2 mo anayanambe raugavo vatane manuga rai. 
\q1 Ananyao AMISY mamo kakui rave mije, 
\q2 mo vatane manyao ti makari mbaro Apa bekere rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Wamo AMISY asyaniv, wemi mamai no Amune rai, 
\q2 wamanya rai tutira ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1 Patimugo AMISY omamo ayao tugae, 
\q2 muno moyar tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 11 Wambekero ananyao AMISY rai mo wama mbekero emasije rai rakivan, 
\q2 tugae mo emasi kakui manui rave rakivan. 
\q1 Muno Apa ananyao mo anyauene ama mana manavane rakivan, 
\q2 tugae mo anyaune ama poko muje rave kobe no ama nenete rai rakivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 12 Tugae, ananyao umaso raugaje vatano panapatambe AMISY Aije ai indamu mo aorai; 
\q2 vatano po raijaro matuve opamo kovo manakoe ratayao amarom. 
\q1  
\v 13 Are pirati po taune apa ana dave ti ngkakai namirati pantatukambe raije raen? 
\q2 Amisy, syare Nyo sya ayao kakai syantatukambe rai namije rapaya rinai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Muno Winyo inansopo marambe ayao kakai syo raen to weramu inakari kapan dai so rai, 
\q2 inda vemo ama vambunine mo inatatuv asyo inya. 
\q1 Wirati indamu vemo ana ngkakaije inta raeno rinai jinya, 
\q2 yara ripaya irati sya ayao kakai mare ntapekano rinai rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 Sya AMISY, ribeker syare sya ayao daura ore som muno sya ana datantona som mamaisyo winanuga rai. 
\q2 Winyirati sya unato oram inamamavube Nai muno Nyo rinapaya sya marova mai. 
\c 20  
\s1 Sambaya Amisye anajo indamu Po anasineko raunande akari titi ai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po anugano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Reama akari titi winy, koveamo AMISY Po winaraniv muno Po napaya irati anakotaro mo nansosobe rai, 
\q2 reamare Amisy Opirati darino aneno Yakop aora be yambe naora! 
\q1  
\v 3 Reamare Amisy no no Apa Yavaro ndandinit, aneme rareande Po nasopan, 
\q2 muno nai Sion, Opamo de, Po vambunine raugaje winai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Reamare nya anakotaro ndameseo Ai mamo aemeno rai, 
\q2 muno maero ndameseo Ai mamo mo aveti ananibe rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Reamare nya anakotaro mbekedai mamo Po raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 muno anakotaro nyo ratantona tavone mamo Po raveti ama ine no rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Indati reansananibe reanggwain weye reama akari titi winyo anasineko wama marova mai. 
\q2 Muno reamo nyovara wao njayaibe rangki, omamo mbe rarorombe Amisy Apa vambunine raijaseo titive. 
\q2 Reamare AMISY Po nya ana ndanajo ravera mamaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Soamo umba syo raen tugae: AMISY Po anasineko raunande akarijo titi Po atayao terave\f + \fr 20:7 \ft No koano Israel raijamo vatano wo apatimu indamu be akari titive opamo manino saitun rauvaro akari rai.\f* ai to. 
\q2 Nai munijo Manunggara ndandinit AMISY Po raude ti mamaisyo ai, 
\q2 AMISY anem ngkov mbambunine mirati mo anasineko raunande akari titi ai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Vatane inta nawamo manaveano awa kereta marova obo ramen, 
\q2 inta manaveano awa kuda obo mansamen no marova rai. 
\q1 Yara wamamo wansanaveano AMISY, Opirati wama Amisy, 
\q2 Apa vambunine obo ramen. 
\q1  
\v 9 Vatano manaveano kereta muno kuda obo mansamene nawamo utataopon, 
\q2 yara wamamo wansayae tindimuve muno wamo anasineko. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 AMISY, reamare Nyo anasineko raude irati reama akari titi ai! 
\q2 Arono reamo winanonae, reamare Nyo reama ana ndanajo ravera mamaisy! 
\c 21  
\s1 Akari titi apa ransyeran kangkaman weye po anasineko marova rai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY, Nya vambunine mirati mbewaramo akari titi ananibe; 
\q2 opamo anayanambe rave, weye Amisye Winyo anasineko raunande ai! 
\q1  
\v 3 Apa bekere mamo Nyo raunande ti mamaisyo ai, 
\q2 muno apa ana danajo mamo Nyo rawatambe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye Winyo aovambe irati Nya kove rai ti manakoe ai, 
\q2 muno Winyo kakion\f + \fr 21:4 \fq kakion: \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ine mare ‘‘mahkota.’’\f* emasi kakui raugasya akari rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Po kove ranajo Winai ra Nyo raude ai indamu opamo jayaisy tutir, 
\q2 muno Nyo apa tume raveti nggwaravainy merere nto tutir. 
\q1  
\v 6 Apa tame ntiti weye Amisy Winyo anasineko raunande ai no marova rai, 
\q2 Winyi Nyo aijaseo titive muno Nyo aveti apa tame manakoe. 
\q1  
\v 7 Tugae, Nyo kovo manakoe raugaje ai ti merere nto tutir, 
\q2 opamo ananibe muno anayanambe weye Amisye wintuna autan. 
\q1  
\v 8 Weye akari titije umaso anaveano AMISY obo amen, 
\q2 muno Amisy Titi Rave Apa muinyo no tawane mo akom weti tindimu tutir.\f + \fr 21:8 \fq tindimu tutir: \ft ayao so ama ine mare akari titi so apinde jewen, yara be akarive tutir.\f* 
\q1  
\v 9 \f + \fr 21:9 \ft Ayao Ibrani anemo 9-10a muno 11-13 mbar kobe jewen, weti kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware aneme so mo akari titi aura, yara kuruno kaijinta wo ratantona ware mo Amisye aura. \f*Indati apa marova inta nin da to jewen, 
\q2 muno po vatano manuga mamuno ai mawatan ti po maijar. 
\q1  
\v 10 Arono apa marova maugav ude no amun, 
\q2 indati po mansamero tanamo mbadurure rai. 
\q1 Indati AMISY Apa pari mamoane mo maubaisy, 
\q2 muno taname mo mansanen ti mangkur bintabo ti mewen. 
\q1  
\v 11 Awa arikainye, ajavije nawamo indati akari titi po maotar ti makanive no mine vone so, 
\q2 awa susyo wo mampame umaso nawamo makanive tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ranivara apa marova manatantonave kakai raijo ai, 
\q2 weramu awa ana wo ratantona ti mamuno ai somamo mamaisye jewen bayave. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weye po ato veano maivuiny, 
\q2 weti usakinav muno unanajibe. 
\q1  
\v 14 Reama AMISY, reamare mbeseo ra Nyo Nya vambunine raroron! 
\q2 Reamare reangkinyo ransyerane rai, reamo Nya vambunine rangkakivambe! 
\c 22  
\s1 Sya Amisy, mbeanimaibe irati winakirive inai? 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Rusa seo no awatan ngkov.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, sya Amisy, mbeanimaibe irati winakirive inai?\f + \fr 22:2 \ft Mat. 27:46; Mrk. 15:34\f* 
\q2 Syanonae syo winawain, weramu winggwaravainyo rinai rave kobe, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinapaya irati ana nsosobe rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sya Amisy, arono masyot syo winawain, 
\q2 weramu Winyo rinaranivi vayave. 
\q1 Muno arono naman syo winanajoa marudi, 
\q2 weti inanuga so ntanamanine jewen. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weramu tugae mamo Winyirati Akari Titi ndandinit, 
\q2 mamaisyo Israel ukangkamambe Nai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Winyirati reama aneno sinane mansanaveano namen, 
\q2 mansanaveano namen, muno Winyo mapaya irati siuri rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Winyirati wo nanonae, weti Nyo mapaya irati awa marova mai, 
\q2 Winyirati mansanaveano namen, muno usamane jewen weye winaneme mpaya mai ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Weramu risyamo maisyare kurume we, muno inaura vatan be ramu, 
\q2 vatano wanuije wo inaura tantunawi muno wo inaura tatugadi. 
\q1  
\v 8 Vatan tenambe wo inaene nawamo wo inakekebe, 
\q2 mawakea vivibe muno makari rangkiki rinai.\f + \fr 22:8 \ft Mat. 27:39,43; Mrk. 15:29; Luk. 23:35\f* 
\q1  
\v 9 Wo inakekebe, ware: ‘‘Ranivara nanaveano AMISY obo amen, 
\q2 mbe animaibe Po napaya kakai rai jewen? 
\q1 Ranivara AMISY anuga no nai, 
\q2 wea mbe animaibe Po napaya rai ramu?’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Weramu sya Amisy, Winyirati Nyo inauguje no sya ingkoa ranobon, 
\q2 muno Nyo inaveti ino mariraave no ingkoa ama ukame rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Arono rinano aje kobe we ndea naiso, rino no winanem uga rai. 
\q2 Arono ta ino no ingkoa ranobone we ndea naiso, Winyirati sya Amisy Nyo rinayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 12 Vemo nggwaravainyo rinai jinya, 
\q2 weye sya marova wo ana nsosobe raugav ndea mangkepano rinai to, 
\q2 muno arepi indati po sopambe rinai? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Marova wanui wo inakijaniri, maisyare sapi anya wanui wemaisy. 
\q2 Wo inawariki, maisyare maero banten usivuiny dave una no munijo Basan\f + \fr 22:13 \fq munijo Basan \ft ntami no mana Yordan ama ranijo wanamuram. Basan ama maero banten onawamo usivuiny dave.\f* wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 14 Sya marova usivuiny dave, weti ware wo inaubaisy, 
\q2 maisyare singa karirimbe, awa rayak ti pare po maere arisyi wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 Sya vambunine meweno inai, maisyare mana ngkanene wemaisy. 
\q2 Muno risiuri rave, maisyare sya pae mare mpapaya ama kabume rai wemaisy. 
\q2 Inanuga so mandamisyi rave, maisyare inunijo nsooyandi wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 16 Sya vambunine meweno rinai, maisyare kavinonamo nturi ti ngkupi wemaisy, 
\q2 inaunane ngkanen ti nseo noka inatumam ate rai. 
\q1 Amisy, Winyo inapaya ti ritami no kopa rai maisyare vatano kakai to wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Maisyare make sivuinye wo inakijaniri wemaisy, 
\q2 vatano mamune wo inawariki, 
\q2 wo inajo muno inaneme ratukam ti nsukir.\f + \fr 22:17 \fq inajo muno inaneme ratukam: \ft Yoh. 19:37, 20:20,25,27\f* 
\q1  
\v 18 Inanasine so ndupan ti eranande sya pae bo raen, 
\q2 muno sya marova mansami ntami tawano rinai rave kobe. 
\q1  
\v 19 Wo aikarae rapatino sya ansune rai, 
\q2 indamu arepi apa ura ansune umaso rai.\f + \fr 22:19 \ft Mat. 27:35; Mrk. 15:24; Luk. 23:34; Yoh. 19:23-24\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Weramu AMISY, syare vemo nggwaravainyo rinai jinya! 
\q2 Nyavave ra nde Nyo sopambe rinai, weye Winyirati sya vambunine nsawa Nai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Syare Nyo inapaya irati sya marova awa anaiyu rai. 
\q2 Onawamo maisyare make sivuinye amaisy, 
\q2 weti syare Nyo sya kove so rapaya irati awa vambunine rai. 
\q1  
\v 22 Syare Nyo inapaya marova awa vambunine rai, maisyare ripaya singa mansawa rai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare ripaya bantene awa korodowai rai wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Amisy, Nya ana ndave mamo indati syo rariri sya arakovo Israel mai, 
\q2 rikangkamambe Nai no anugane ama yasyin.\f + \fr 22:23 \ft Ibr. 2:12\f* 
\q1  
\v 24 Inya, vatano wapo AMISY asyanive weap, wapo ararimbe! 
\q2 Inya, Yakop apa susye weap, wapo aijaseo titive! 
\q2 Muno kawasae Israel weap, watarurandi no Amisy Amun muno wabeaje Ai! 
\q1  
\v 25 Weye vatano matawanto ti una siuri rai nawamo, 
\q2 Amisy Po mave tatugadi ramu muno Po mansamumuibe ramu. 
\q1 Muno Opamo akirive mai ramu, 
\q2 yara Po mansaraniv arono wo anonae. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 26 No anugan akoe awa yasyin, Winyirati rikangkamambe Nai, 
\q2 no vatano wo Amisye winasyanive mansamun, syo maere rameseo Nai mamaisyo sya urairi idaokae nande Nai to rai. 
\q1  
\v 27 Vatano manuga mpayaje nawamo indati wo maere umaso inta raisya uman dave, 
\q2 vatano ubeker ware ude mararai AMISY Ai onawamo indati wo ararimbe. 
\q2 Syare kovo ana mawese ntamijo wasaija ntoa nuge nuganui! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 28 Vatan tenambe una no mine so, indati wo AMISY atantona akato, 
\q2 muno usakinav wakare irati Ai. 
\q1 Muno susye kotare ude wo vukane ranteter, 
\q2 indamu ubeaje no Amun. 
\q1  
\v 29 Weye AMISY Obo Pirati Akari Titi, 
\q2 be akarive susye kotare mai vintabo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 30 Tugae, vatan tenambe taune mararin no mine so nawamo indati ude beaje Ai, 
\q2 vatan tenambe nanawirati indati wakasya no kopa nawamo awa vukane ranteter ti ubeaje Ai. 
\q1  
\v 31 Susyo indati wakasea akato nao, ukangkamambe Akoe Ai, 
\q2 muno wo ariri akato irati susyo merere nto mai. 
\q1  
\v 32 Amisye Apa moyare mamo indati wo raririjo susyo mansavaki akato mansai, 
\q2 ware Amisy Opirati Po Apa kawasae mapaya irati kakai rai to. 
\c 23  
\s1 AMISY Wepi Po rinayaranande ngko dave 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY Po rinayaranande maisyare vatano po maero domba makum, 
\q2 weti anakotare inta meweno rinai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 2 Po inaugav asyo tuna no anoko insumai njayaibe rai, 
\q2 Po inaugave to no mana ami ntanamanine rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wepi Po vambunine raugav akare rinai jakato, 
\q2 muno Po rinaugavo unanuijo nsarokire raito, 
\q2 indamu Apa tame raijaseo titive. 
\q1  
\v 4 Arono syanya kaivo wen akoe no rai raito, 
\q2 syo ama ngkakai rasyanive ramu, 
\q1 weye wintuna rinautan. 
\q2 Nya kaijije me isyo me nanairati yo inayaranande,\f + \fr 23:4 \ft Kaijije muno isyo omamo veano domba mansayaranande. Kaijije veano domba manepat indamu wanya sarokibe, muno veano makeo sivuinye manepat tavon indamu vemo wo domba maubai nora. Umba isyo mamo ama kume ngkariwae indamu rave wusyawave inda veano domba awa nyovaravao, nyoamane wo raisye rauvade, muno domba temasyo no ateme pamo ransawa ai ti auvasen. \f* 
\q2 weti ino kovo saumane rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Winyi Nyo anaisye ratayao ti maweso rinai, 
\q2 no sya marova mansamune rai. 
\q1 Winyi Nyo manino mbovove rauvaro inakari rai,\f + \fr 23:5 \fq manino mbovove rauvaro inakari rai: \ft koano manine somamo Israel wo rave vatano wo aovambe ai. \f* 
\q2 muno Nyo sya kapijo syo mana ramanam daije raveti ntairi tutir. 
\q1  
\v 6 Syo raen, tugae, AMISY Nya mbekobe muno Nya muinye manakoe rinai no arono ta rikove so; 
\q2 muno indati rituna no AMISY Nya Yavare rai tawan tutir. 
\c 24  
\s1 AMISY Wepi Akari Titi, de no Apa Yavar rai no Yerusalem 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY Wepirati peyave irati mine so rai muno ama anakotaro ntuna rai rautan, 
\q2 muno vatano ntuna rai mautan tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 2 Weye Wepi Po muni so rauseo nte no mana ntuna no kopa mate\f + \fr 24:2 \fq mana ntuna no kopa mate \ft muno \fq mana masyo rave \ft omamo mamaisyo vatano Israel awa ana udaene rai. Mana so maisyare mayane ramaisy muno ntento rave ntuna no kopa mate so. Raen no Kej. 7:11; Maz. 136:6.\f* so ama vone rai. 
\q2 Po raveti ntindimu no mana masyo rave ama vone rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 ‘‘Are pirati indati mamaisyo seo no unato AMISY\f + \fr 24:3 \fq unato AMISY \ft mare Sion, omamo Yavaro Amisy ama ntuna rije.\f* we rai? 
\q2 Are pirati indati mamaisyo de siso no AMISY Nya Yavar, indamu beaje irati Nai?’’ 
\q1  
\v 4 ‘‘Vatano anuga ngkakavin, muno apa ana dave ngkov, 
\q2 paarurijabe jewen arono po urairije raokaisy, 
\q2 muno beaje yare rai jewenep. 
\q1  
\v 5 Vatano napije, indati AMISY Po kove raugaje ai. 
\q2 Amisye, Opi Po apaya kakai rai, pare vatane sopamo ayao kakai meweno ai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Maisyare wemaisy vatano nanawirati ude no Amisye Winui, 
\q2 onawirati ude indamu ubeaje irati Amisye Winai, Winyirati aneno Yakop beaje Nai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Inya, unsanda akokoe\f + \fr 24:7 \ft Somamo unsanda akokoe nsiso no Yavaro Amisye rai. \f* no no wusyin to, nsaneka! 
\q2 Nsaneka ra ntanenae, 
\q2 indamu Akari Titi, Apa kove ntiti, de siso. 
\q1  
\v 8 Akari Titi so, Apa kove ntiti, opamo are pije? 
\q2 Opamo AMISY, anaaniv muno bambunin dave, 
\q2 AMISY bambunin Po anasine ugav no marova rai! 
\q1  
\v 9 Inya, unsanda akokoe no no wusyin to, nsaneka! 
\q2 Nsaneka ra ntanenae, 
\q2 indamu Akari titi, Apa kove ntiti, de siso. 
\q1  
\v 10 Akari titi, Apa kove ntiti, opamo are pije? 
\q2 Opamo AMISY Wepi be akarive naito munijo ntiti mansai, 
\q2 Opirati Akari Titi, Apa kove ntiti rave! 
\c 25  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po wama ayao kakaije rapaya muno Po wansayaranande 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe.\f + \fr 25:1 \ft Masmur somamo ransyerano Ibrani \ft \+it akrostik\+it* inta mije, weye ntavondi urupijo Ibrani ama ntetebeaje rai. Weramu ayao Yawa ntavondi urupije so rai jewen.\f* 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, Winyirati inanuga so raijaseo Nai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, Winyirati rinanaveano namen; 
\q2 syare vemo winaneme mpaya rinai mo risamane inya; 
\q2 muno vemo sya marova umananibe anakotaro nsosobe rinai rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 3 Tugae, vatano mansanaveano winamene nawamo indati usamane jewen, 
\q2 yara usamane nawamo vatano nanawirati wangkarive vayave ti wo ana ngkakai rave nao. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo Nya unanui mamaisyo ritavondi rai rarorono rinai, 
\q2 syare Nyo rinanyao Nya unanui rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syare Nyo rinanyao muno Nyo rinaugavo Nya unanui mamaisye rai, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Amisy Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 masyote tename omainyamo Winyirati inanaveano namen. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya AMISY, syare naemeno reansaijo Nya mbekobe rai muno Nya muinyo no tawane rai, 
\q2 weye omamo Nyo rarorono reansai no arono wusyinoe to. 
\q1  
\v 7 Sya AMISY, sya ayao kakaije muno sya ana dave ti ngkakai, 
\q2 no arono ta rikamurame wemamo, syare vemo windatantona akareve inya. 
\q1 Yara syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 weye Winyamo ngkov dave muno Nya muinye no tawano rinai. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY, Opamo kov dave muno moyar, 
\q2 weti Po Apa unanui mamaisye raroron irati vatano wusya marambe mai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Po vatano mansanuga mpayaje maugav indamu utavondi ana mamaisye rai, 
\q2 muno Po mansanyao irati Apa bekere rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 AMISY Opamo Apa muinye no tawan muno teto Apa urairije rai,\f + \fr 25:10 \ft Amisye Apa urairijo Po raokaisyo kawasae Israel mansai ama ayao ratoe no Kel. 24:3-8.\f* 
\q2 omamo nde irati vatano nanawirati ubeta Apa urairije muno Apa ananyao raije mai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo sya ayao kakai rapaya irati rinai, weye sya ayao kakai manakoe rave, 
\q2 wirati indamu syo Nya tame raijaseo titive. 
\q1  
\v 12 Vatano po AMISY asyanive pamo, 
\q2 Amisye Po Apa unanui kov mamaisyo Apa bekere rai rarorono ai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Vatano napijep opamo no irati kovo ngko dave Amisye Po raugaje ai rai tawan, 
\q2 muno apa arikainye, apa ajavije nawamo utantuna irati awa muni tawane rai tawan. 
\q1  
\v 14 AMISY de pangkepan dave irati vatano wo asyanive mai, 
\q2 muno Apa urairije mamo Po raveano mansanyao indamu unanta rai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Risyamo, AMISY Opirati inanaveano amen tutir, 
\q2 weye Opirati Po inapaya irati ana ngkakai mo rinamane rai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Syare namumbe de rinai muno naemeno rinai, 
\q2 weye risyamo siuri rave muno vatane inta po inasopan akatoe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 17 Syare Nyo inapaya irati inanimaumbe manakoe nseo masyove tutir no inanuga so rai, 
\q2 muno Nyo inaugav uje irati ana mo inatawan asyo so raora. 
\q1  
\v 18 Syare Nyo rinaeno sya siuri muno ana mo inakepe so rai, 
\q2 muno sya ayao kakaije mamo syare Nyo rapaya tenambe irati rinai. 
\q1  
\v 19 Wakoe! Nyo rinaen sya marova wanui rave, 
\q2 onawamo manuga mamuno rinai rave muno usoowato rinai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Syare Nyo rinayaranande muno Nyo inapaya, 
\q2 inda vemo wo anasineko rinai mo risamane inya, 
\q2 weye Wibuiny irati rigaugambe Nai. 
\q1  
\v 21 AMISY, Wibuiny irati inanaveano namen, weti syare ndarino rinaora, 
\q2 weye risyamo syo ana mamaisye obo rave muno inanuga nsarokir. 
\q1  
\v 22 Sya Amisy, syare Winyo Nya kawasae Israel mapaya 
\q2 irati ana nsosobe maije rai tenambe. 
\c 26  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po patimu mamaisye raugaje rinai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY, syare Nyo patimu moyare raugaje rinai, 
\q2 weye risyamo rikov irati rinanuga nsarokire rai. 
\q1 Muno rinanaveano AMISY winamene mamo syo inta rantotobe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY, syare Winyo rinayasiro mavabe muno Nyo rinatauno sya ana dave rai, 
\q2 Nyo rinanuga muno sya ana datantona rayasir mavabe indamu Nyo raen ayao kakaije inta no rinaija rako? 
\q1  
\v 3 Risyamo inaemendi tutiro Nya muinyo no tawane\f + \fr 26:3 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it hesed\+it* ama ine ratoe tumaimbe naiso mare: ‘‘muinyo no tawan.’’ Ama ino manakoe mare: ‘‘Amisye Apa muinye muno Apa anakotaro Po raurairive ti no tawan tutiro Apa kawasae Israel mansai mamo Po raveti mamaisy.’’\f* rai, 
\q2 muno risyamo inatawandi itavondi Winai.\f + \fr 26:3 \ft Ama ino kaijinta mare: ‘‘muno risyamo syanya mamaisyo Nya ayao tugae rai.’’\f* 
\q1  
\v 4 Vatano aarurijate ntubai maije nanawamo syonae rituna matavon ija, 
\q2 muno vatano awa angkarije ntapekane nawamo syonae tavondi maiji. 
\q1  
\v 5 Risyamo syonae daveo vatano wo ana ngkakai rave nao reangkavave ija, 
\q2 muno risyamo syonae rituna vatano mamune\f + \fr 26:5 \fq vatano mamun \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.\f* matavon ija. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya AMISY, risyamo rinaneme rarondom indamu mbe rarorombe mare sya ayao kakaije meweno rinai. 
\q2 Umba syanya Nya tewa orame rakijani, 
\q1  
\v 7 muno rikinyo ransyerane rai syo kove raura seo Amisye Winai, 
\q2 muno syo Nya anakotar tenambe ndave ti mbe anainambe rariri. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY, rinanuga ntove rave Nya Yavaro ntuna rije rai rave, 
\q2 muno ribekero Nya norije rai wemirati Nya kovo ntiti raeno rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Syare vemo Nyo rinaubaisyo vatano ayao kakaije no mai matavon inya, 
\q2 muno vatano maneme nijame matavon inya. 
\q1  
\v 10 Wenawamo wo ana kakaije obo raijar tutir, 
\q2 muno awa ube akarive mamo wavakananta doijo veano mawa rakuvu rai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 11 Risya maisyare wemaisye ramu, yara risyamo rinanuga nsarokir dave, 
\q2 weti syare naemeno rinai, Nyo rinapaya irati ana nsosobe rinaije so rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Risyamo rite no unanuijo ngkove rai, 
\q2 weti risyo AMISY winararimbe no Nya kawasae Israel awa yasyin. 
\c 27  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu darino wansaora 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY, Winyirati mbaro sya unanui rai muno Nyo inapaya kakai rai, 
\q2 weamo indati are pirati syo asyaniv akato? 
\q1 AMISY, wibuiny irati sya yano oram ndarino inaora, 
\q2 weti rijanive ramu. 
\q1  
\v 2 Ranivara vatano mamune maroyaro rinai, 
\q2 ware wo rinaubaisy, 
\q1 wea indati sya marova umaso taune nawirati 
\q2 majo rantukam, ti utaopon. 
\q1  
\v 3 Ranivara naito wanui wo rinawariki kai, 
\q2 weramu rijanive ramu. 
\q1 Ranivara marova ntipu ti mo rinaron kai, 
\q2 weramu sya anave mamo no tawano Amisy Ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Ana ibekero rai ti syo ranajo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 omamo intabom dave: 
\q1 syare rituna no AMISY Apa yavar 
\q2 arono ta rikove so, 
\q1 indamu syo AMISY Apa kove raen, 
\q2 muno syo anajo irati Apa bekere rai no Apa Yavar. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye Opirati indati darino rinaora, 
\q2 arono ana ngkakai mare nde rinai; 
\q1 Po inangkokaibe no Apa yavar, 
\q2 muno no rinaora, maisyare Po rinapaato no no unato orame rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Umba soamo syo anasineko sya marova wo inakijaniri mai, 
\q2 weti indati syo maere rameseo no Yavaro Amisy, rigwain inananibe rautan, 
\q2 muno rikinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo AMISY Ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo rinaranivo sya ana dawain ore rai, 
\q2 naemeno rinai muno Nyo sya ana danajo ravera mamaisy! 
\q1  
\v 8 Syo ranaun no inanuga Winyo raura nyare: ‘‘Nde ramu mbeaje Rinai.’’ 
\q2 Weti AMISY, syore beaje Winai kobe. 
\q1  
\v 9 Vemo winamune rangkokaibe rinai nora. 
\q1 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, muno Winyirati Nyo inayaranande, 
\q1 weti vemo wimpari rinai muno nakirive rinai nora. 
\q2 Sya Amisy, Winyirati Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 weti vemo Nyo inavakano marambe inya, muno naneme mpaya rinai inya. 
\q1  
\v 10 Ranivara sya injaya pe ingkoa me yaneme mpaya rinai rave kai, 
\q2 weramu AMISY Winyamo Nyo rinakum. 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya AMISY, syare Nya unanuijo kove rarorono rinai, 
\q2 muno Nyo inaugavo unanuijo nsarokire raito, 
\q2 weye sya marova wanui rave. 
\q1  
\v 12 Vemo Nyo rinaunanto sya marova maneme uga rai jinya, 
\q2 weye usea wo ayao angkarije rangkivano rinai, 
\q2 muno ware wo ivuinye veano rinave. 
\q1  
\v 13 Tugae, syanave indati syo AMISY Apa kove raen, 
\q2 no arono ta rikov no mine so. 
\q1  
\v 14 Syare wansanaveano AMISY amen, 
\q2 wansanuga raveramu mbambunin muno ntindimu Ai. 
\q2 Tugae, syare wansanaveano AMISY amen! 
\c 28  
\s1 AMISY Opirati darino rinaora 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, Winyirati syo nawain, 
\q2 Winyirati sya unato oram inamamavube rai, 
\q2 syare vemo Nyo rinaranivi vayave inya. 
\q1 Weye ranivara Winyo rinaranivi vayave, 
\q2 weamo risyamo indati maisyare vatano syasyo no aipapo amani ate rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 2 Syare Nyo sya ana danajo raraniv, 
\q2 arono rui inamumbe to no Nya Yavaro ndandinit,\f + \fr 28:2 \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ine mare Tanoano Ndandini Dave namirati ntami no Yavaro Amisye ama uga.\f* 
\q1 muno inaneme raijaseo syo winawain 
\q2 indamu Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Vemo Nyo inararambe usya vatano mamune matavon inya, 
\q2 indamu vemo Nyo mangke raugaje rinai jirati 
\q2 vatano awa ana udave ngkakainoanive umaso mautan inya. 
\q1 Onawamo awa ayao nsaumano awa arakove mai, 
\q2 weramu manatantonave mamune raijo mai vayave. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare Nyo mangke raugaje mai awa ana udave rai, 
\q2 mamaisyo awa ana udave ti ngkakainoanive rarijati. 
\q1 Syare Nyo mangke raugaje mai mamaisyo awa ana udave rai, 
\q2 Nyo mangke rasakinavo mai indamu mamaisyo mai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye AMISY Apa ana dave me, anakotaro danari aneme rai me, 
\q2 omainyamo wo ama kove ratantona kobe ramu. 
\q1 Weti indati Po mataopon, 
\q2 muno Po maijaseo akato jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Kangkamambe AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weye Opirati Po sya ana danajo raraniv to. 
\q1  
\v 7 AMISY Opirati sya vambunine nsawa Ai muno darino rinaora, 
\q2 maisyare naite apa vakano po raijaro aora ramaisy; 
\q2 Opirati syanave ntindimu Ai. 
\q1 Po sopambe rinai weti inanuga so rananibe, 
\q2 weti rikinyo ransyerane rai syo kove raura seo Ai. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY Opirati Po vambunine raunande Apa kawasae mai, 
\q2 muno be yambe irati akari titi napirati Po atayao ti manino mbovove rauvaro akari raije ai.\f + \fr 28:8 \ft Vatane sopamo Daud, opirati be akari titive Israel mai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 9 Syare Nyo Nya kawasae mapaya irati marova mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo kove raugaje irati vatano Nyo matayao terave indamu Nya ura maije mai. 
\q1 Syare Nyo mansayaranande maisyare vatano po maero domba makume wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Nyo makepano naneme rai ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 29  
\s1 Vambunin AMISY raen no repe rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\q1 Kangkamambe AMISY Ai! 
\q1 Inya, kotaro wana no munijo Manunggara, 
\q2 wakangkamambe Apa kovo ntiti rai muno Apa vambunine rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Wakangkamambe AMISY Apa tamo ntitije rai, 
\q2 weye AMISY Opamo dandinit weti wabeaje Ai. 
\q1  
\v 3 AMISY anamote ngkin no mayane von, 
\q2 Amisy titi anamote ravari maisyare katitir, 
\q2 AMISY anamote ranauni ntamijo nawanane vone rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY anamote ngkin, Apa vambunine ntairi rai, 
\q2 AMISY anamote ngkin, Apa kovo ntitije ntairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY anamote mbambunin, mo inyo arase radaut, 
\q2 muno mo inyo aras no no munijo Libanon rabibiti. 
\q1  
\v 6 Wepi Po unato no no munijo Libanon raveti nsasopati 
\q2 maisyare lembu tuvane sasopati wemaisy. 
\q2 Muno unato Siryon nsotove maisyare bantene tuvane sotove wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 AMISY anamote ngkin, ivake muje rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY anamote mbambunin, mo anoko ngkanembe rambayar, 
\q2 muno mo anoko kanen Kades rambayar tavon. 
\q1  
\v 9 AMISY anamote mbambunin, mbewar inyo ngkakiwae ngkomati,\f + \fr 29:9 \ft Aneme so ama ine mbe jirumbe wemi ratayao mamaisyo ayao Ibrani rarijati. Ayao Amisy TB mo ratoe taiso: AMISY anamote mbewar ti rusa wanya mbaki rainye mbaki.\f* 
\q2 umba anamote mo inyo wao raveti mpopan. 
\q1 Weramu nai Yavaro Amisy Yerusalem, anugano Amisye wo raura seo ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Tugae, AMISY ararin!’’ 
\q1  
\v 10 AMISY Apa vambunine obom ntiti rave 
\q2 ti be akarive manayam akoe rai. 
\q1 Wepirati bambunin dave 
\q2 be akarive ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 11 Syare AMISY Po vambunine raunande taune Apa kawasae mansai, 
\q2 muno Po kovo saumane raugaje mansanuga rai. 
\c 30  
\s1 Ransyeran kangkaman weye mpaya irati kakai rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Ransyerane somamo vatano Israel ukiny dai no arono usisa Yavaro Amisy ama one rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, syare syo naijaseo titive, 
\q2 weye Winyi Nyo rinapaya irati waneno mangke dave rinaije rai, 
\q2 muno sya marova nawamo Nyo mansamayaro umananibe sya wanene rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 3 AMISY, sya Amisy, Winyirati syo nawain syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 umba Nyo saumane raude rinai to. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya AMISY, Winyirati Nyo inapaya irati munijo wen akoe rai, 
\q2 Winyo kove raude rinai ti syasyo no aipapo amanija ama ate waraya rai jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Inya, kawasae wasatawandi watavondi AMISY Ai weap, 
\q2 wakinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo Ai, 
\q2 Opirati dandinit dave, ti wapo kove raura seo Ai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weye Amisye pamo Apa parije ma ntora nugoenta ramu, 
\q2 yara anuga ngkovo wansai mi no tawan no arono ta wangkove so. 
\q1 Nai namano waravainyoe mamo wamoyov, 
\q2 weramu arono akane ntipu, wansanayanambe akato. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Arono risya kovo syanya rai mamo rino anayanambe obo rai, syo raura syare: 
\q2 ‘‘Risyamo inanto ana nsosobe inta rai jakatoe ramu ntoa nuge nuganui!’’ 
\q1  
\v 8 Weye AMISY, wimbekobe irati rinai, 
\q2 Winyo rinaveti ritindimu maisyare unato ntindimuge wemaisy. 
\q2 Weramu arono winakirive rinai, weamo rijaniv dave.\f + \fr 30:8 \ft Arono Pemasmur nanto waneno mangke rai, weamo po rakarae pare Amisye akirive ai to.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Sya AMISY, Winyirati syo nawain indamu naemeno rinai; 
\q2 sya Akoe, Winyirati syo nanajo indamu Nyo sopambe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Syo raura syare: ‘‘Ranivara rikakai ti to tami no atemo amanijamo, 
\q2 ama kovo animaisye mi makaore Winai? 
\q1 Muno vatano kakai to apa kopa mamo indati makaseo mo nararimbe 
\q2 muno mo winteto Nya urairije rai ravov akatoe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo rinaraniv muno naemeno rinai. 
\q2 AMISY, syare Winyirati Nyo sopambe rinai!’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Sya oyove mamo Nyo ranigwan akato anayanambe rai ti risarer, 
\q2 rinanimaumbe mamo Nyo rapaya rinai muno Nyo ranigwano ananibe rai.\f + \fr 30:12 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘sya ansuno ridave no arono rinanimaumbe rai mamo Nyo ranigwano ansuno wanyino syo rave no arono rinanibe rai jakato.’’ No koano Israel raijamo wo iije vasye karisya veano maakuvi arono manimaumbe rave.\f* 
\q1  
\v 13 Weti anamainitu rinai ramu, yara inanuga ntenami rikinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo Winai, 
\q2 AMISY, sya Amisy, syo kove raura seo Naijao ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 31  
\s1 Nanaveano Amisye amen 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, Wibuiny irati syakaore gaugambe Nai, 
\q2 vemo Nyo rinapayamo sya marova wo rinave samaneve inya. 
\q2 Amisye Winyamo moyar, weti syare Nyo rinapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare namarikoame rasakinavo sya ana danajo ore rai, 
\q2 muno Nyavave ra Nyo rinapaya irati sya marova aneme rai. 
\q1 Syare Winyirati maisyare unato oram inamamavube Nai, 
\q2 muno yano oram ntindimu no inaora indamu ipaya irati kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Tugae, Winyirati maisyare sya unato oram muno sya yano oram ntindimu. 
\q2 Syare Nyo rinaugav mavabe, wirati indamu Nya tame raijaseo titive. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syare Nyo rinapaya irati sya marova awa aviri wo ratugar ti mo rinamane rai, 
\q2 weye Winyirati syakaore gaugambe irati Nai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Syo inanawayoe augav ore no Amisy winanem uga rai.\f + \fr 31:6 \ft Luk. 23:46\f* 
\q2 Winyirati Nyo rinapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 weye AMISY, Winyirati Amisy nteto Nya urairije rai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 7 AMISY Winyamo nanuga mamuno vatano ubeaje yaro mamaisye jewene rai mansai, 
\q2 weramu risyamo syanave irati Winai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Indati inananibe muno inanayanambe rave weye Winyo Nya muinyo no tawane raveti mamaisyo rinai, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Nyo rinaeno sya siuri rai, 
\q2 muno winanto sya ana nsosobe rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 9 Muno Winyo rinaunanto sya marova maneme uga rai jewen, 
\q2 yara Nyo rinapaya irati ana mo kakai raugave rai.\f + \fr 31:9 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Nyo inaveti ritet no varoro ntanenae rai,’’ ama ine maisyare ratoe no aneme so ama varoro jirume so rai wemaisy.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Sya AMISY, syare naemen irati rinai, weye anakotare mo inakikipi. 
\q2 Inami tuga so mbambanai weye inanuga so ranimaumbe, 
\q2 inanasine so me sya jugara pe siuri rave. 
\q1  
\v 11 Rimayondi rave, weye arono ta rikove soamo rinanimaumbe tutir, 
\q2 sya tumo rino no mine vone somamo syanonae tutir. 
\q1 Sya vambunine ntende, weye sya ayao kakai mbewar, 
\q2 weti inanasine tename so mayondi. 
\q1  
\v 12 Sya marova wo rinaura tantunawi, 
\q2 muno sya arakovo reama yavare ntuna nande tenambe wonae daveo rinai. 
\q1 Sya arakove upaparo mai arono wo sya siurije raen, 
\q2 muno unande rinai no unanuijamo unaji ti uta rinaora. 
\q1  
\v 13 Vatane manimari rinai to, maisyare rikakai to wemaisy, 
\q1 Wo inatantona ware risya sya ana intai jewen, 
\q2 maisyare kavino kopa nturi to ti ramauta vayave wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 14 Weye syo ranaun vatane wanui usaumugadi wayao rinai, 
\q2 muno nai rui ruijamo wo rinawariki ti rijaniv. 
\q1 Wenawamo manatantonave kakai raijo rinai, 
\q2 muno wanyinyaube ware wo rinaubaisy. 
\q1  
\v 15 Weramu AMISY, Wibuiny irati rinanaveano namen, 
\q2 weye sya Amisye Pi Winy. 
\q1  
\v 16 Risya masyoto rikovo rai mamo no no winanem uga rai, 
\q2 syare Nyo rinapaya sya marova wo rinawatan tutire maneme rai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, syare Nya kove mbaro rinai, 
\q2 syare Nyo rinapaya kakaije rai mamaisyo Nya muinyo no tawane rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Sya AMISY, vemo winaneme mpaya rinai mo risamane inya, 
\q2 weye rigwain ore Winai. 
\q1 Syare koveamo Nyo vatano mamune mapinde indamu usamane, 
\q2 muno koveamo wasyo no amani, indamu anamainitu mai. 
\q1  
\v 19 Syare Nyo vatano waarurijabe umaso mawa rakuvu, 
\q2 weye umararin wo vatano ubeto irati Amisy Winai makaajian, 
\q2 muno wo maura tantunawi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Tugae, Amisye Winya kove mamo manakoe rave, 
\q2 namirati Nyo ratayao ti ntuna vatano wo nasyanive mansamarom, 
\q2 namirati Nyo raunanto vatano ugaugambe irati Nai mai, 
\q2 no vatan tenambe mansamun. 
\q1  
\v 21 Winyo mangkaokaibe no nanem ate rai indamu no mansaora 
\q2 irati vatano manatantonave mamune rai mai. 
\q1 Winy ndarino mansaora 
\q2 irati vatano ware wanaikebe irati mansaije mai. 
\q1  
\v 22 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Weye Po Apa muinyo no tawane rarorono rinai, omamo mbe anainambe, 
\q2 arono marova wo sya munije rawariki\f + \fr 31:22 \fq wo sya munije rawariki: \ft ananeneae so ama ine mare Pemasmur no irati ana nsosobe ama uga rai.\f* indamu umarovave rinai. 
\q1  
\v 23 Syananepabe vayave, ti syo ratantona syarevo: 
\q2 ‘‘AMISY Po rinawatano marambe no Amune rai to.’’ 
\q1 Weramu jewena, arono risyo awain indamu aemeno rinai, 
\q2 Opamo Po sya ana danajo Ai raraniv. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 24 Inya, kawasae AMISY Apa ura wasai weap, syare wasanuga no irati Ai! 
\q2 Vatano matawandi utavondi AMISY Aije nanawamo Po mansayaranande. 
\q1 Yara vatano wo taune mararine nanawamo mangke Po raugaje mai mamo Po rantotobe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 25 Inya, vatan tenambe wasanaveano AMISY amene weap, 
\q2 syare wasanuga mbambunin muno ntindimu irati Ai. 
\c 32  
\s1 Ayao kakaije raura kakavimbe no Amisye Amun 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano ananyao. 
\b  
\q1 \f + \fr 32:1-2 \ft Ayao so ratoe akato no Roma 4:7-8.\f*Vatano are nawirati awa ana udaveti ngkakai mamo Amisye Po rapaya mai, 
\q2 muno awa ayao kakaije mamo Po raupae ti rakanive mai, onawamo manayanambe! 
\q1  
\v 2 Vatano are nawirati awa ana udaveti ngkakai mamo Amisye Po ratore ramu, 
\q2 muno mansaunane mansake jewene nawamo manayanambe! 
\q1  
\v 3 Arono syo sya ayao kakaije raura kakavimbe rainy, weamo inanasine tename so mayondi, 
\q2 weye masyote tename omainyamo syanonae tutir. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye namane rinit winaneme mo rinatawanto mangkebe, 
\q2 ti sya vambunine meweno rinai maisyare uma po rinanen ti rimayondi wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weti umba risya ayao kakaije mamo syo raura kakavimbe Nai, 
\q2 muno sya ana daveti ngkakai mamo syo rangkokaibe Nai ramu. 
\q1 Syo rapatimu indamu sya ana daveti ngkakai mamo idaura kakavimbe no AMISY Winamun, 
\q2 umba Winyo inapaya irati sya ayao kakaije so rai tenambe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Maisyare omaiti, koveamo vatane nanentabo matawandi ti utavondi Amisye Winai nawamo usambayambe ore Nai, 
\q2 arono unanta irati ana nsosobe rai weamo wore no Winui. 
\q1 Ranivara mansansowave ana nsosobe rai, maisyare manayamo akoe inta mo mansarone wemaisy, 
\q2 weamo mo maugave jewen. 
\q1  
\v 7 Winyirati varoro syakaore kokaibe Nai, 
\q2 ana nsosobe mamo Winyirati no rinaora irati rai. 
\q1 Winyo inapaya rai to, ti rikiny inananibe, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Nyo inakom. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Amisy Po raura pare: ‘‘Syare Syo nanyao ana ratantona ngkove rai, 
\q2 muno Syo naroron irati nya unanuijo nyo raito rai, 
\q2 syare Syo ananyao raugaje nai muno Syo nayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 9 Mbemo maisyare kuda amai nora, 
\q2 weye ana ratantona meweno ai, 
\q1 weti ranivara nyo waije ransawa ai jewen, 
\q2 weamo tavono nya mbekere rai ramu.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Vatano mamune nawamo unanta irati siuri manui rai, 
\q2 yara vatano mansanaveano AMISY amene nawamo, 
\q2 Apa muinyo no tawane mo mansakom ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 11 Inya, vatano wabeta AMISY Ai weap, wasananibe muno wasanayanambe Apa ana dave rai! 
\q2 Inya, vatano watavondi Amisye Apa bekere rai weap, wagwain wasananibe! 
\c 33  
\s1 Kangkaman raura seo irati Amisye Ai 
\q1  
\v 1 Inya, vatano wabeta AMISY Ai weap, 
\q2 wasanamote raijaseo wasanuga rananibe rautan! 
\q2 Weye vatano utavondi AMISY Apa bekere rai wo ararimbe omamo mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 2 Kove raura seo AMISY Ai, wapo itarijo mamaune\f + \fr 33:2 \fq Itarijo mamaun \ft muno \fq itari anakoe \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ muno ‘‘gambus’’ rai.\f* raeyan dai, 
\q2 wakinyo ransyerane raijo Ai, wapo itari anakoe ama wai abusyine raeyan dai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wakinyo ransyeran wanyine raijo Ai, 
\q2 wapo itarije raeyan da ngko dave rai muno wasanamote raijaseo manakoeve wasananibe rautan. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye AMISY Apa ayao mamo tugae, 
\q2 Apa anakotar tenambe Po rave mamo mamaisyo Apa urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Opamo anuga no irati ana mamaisye\f + \fr 33:5 \fq ana mamaisy: \ft ama ine mare anakotaro mamaisyo Amisye Apa ananyao rai. \f* muno moyare rai, 
\q2 mine so ntairi jirati AMISY Apa muinyo no tawane rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY Po raura awa obo rai, weamo naume no, 
\q2 muno anamote obom, weamo naume ama anakotaro ntuna rai\f + \fr 33:6 \fq naume ama anakotaro ntuna rai: \ft ama ine mare uma, embae, tum, naito Amisy, muno anakotaro kaijo ntuna raije ntavon.\f* no tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 7 Po mana mayane ransop ti ntuna varore intai, 
\q2 Po nawanane raugaje ntami ama ntento rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Koveamo vatano munije tename so wo AMISY asyaniv, 
\q2 koveamo vatano mine tename so ntarurandi no Amun muno ubeaje Ai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye Po raura awa obo rai, weamo anakotare no tenambe, 
\q2 muno Po Apa ayao raugaje, weamo anakotare no tindimuve kobe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 AMISY Po susyo wanave Ai jewene awa anakotaro wo ratantona ransopi vintabo, 
\q2 Wepi Po susye kotare awa anakotaro manatantonave raije raorai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Yara AMISY taune Apa anakotaro Po ratantona mamo no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno Apa bekero Po ratantona no anuga rai mamo manya tutiro nugo merere nto rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Kove ngkov irati susyo are nawirati wo AMISY aura ware Opamo awa Amisye Pije, 
\q2 onawamo Apa kawasae Po matayao terave indamu Apa ura maija ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 13 No munijo Manunggara, AMISY ami ntami munije tename so rai, 
\q2 Po vatan tenambe mine tename so mansanyanyut. 
\q1  
\v 14 Nai Apa tuna ri rai, 
\q2 ami ntetero vatan tenambe ntuna no mine so mai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Wepirati Po vatane mansanuga ranari tenambe, 
\q2 muno Po awa anakotaro udave raen tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 16 Akari titi inta apa naite wanui rave kai, weramu wemi mo anasineko raunande ai ramu. 
\q2 Naito anaaniv kakui inta dave kai, weramu apa vambunine mamo mo apaya marova aneme raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 17 Kuda marova pamo umba ta mamaisye jewen kobe anaveano amen indamu po anasineko raunande aiji, 
\q2 opamo bambunin dave kai, weramu mamaisyo po apaya marova aneme raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 18 Tugae rave, AMISY opamo Po vatano wo asyanive mansayaranande tutir, 
\q2 onawamo vatano manaveano Apa muinyo no tawane ramen. 
\q1  
\v 19 Indamu Po awa jugara apaya irati wene rai, 
\q2 muno Po mansakum arono marore tami. 
\q1  
\v 20 Weti wamo AMISY anyut weye wamanave tugaeve Ai, 
\q2 Wepi Po wansayaranande muno darino wansaora.\f + \fr 33:20 \fq darino wansaora: \ft maisyare naite apa vakano po raijaro aora ramaisy.\f* 
\q1  
\v 21 Wansananibe Amisye Ai weye Po anakotare raveti ngkovo wansai, 
\q2 muno Apa tamo ndandinite mirati wansanaveano ramen. 
\q1  
\v 22 AMISY, syare Nya muinyo no tawane mamo ntavono reansai tutir, 
\q2 weye Wibuiny irati reansanaveano namen. 
\c 34  
\s1 Kove raura AMISY Ai Apa kove rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe, arono be ponaibe maisyare vatano anaivi wemaisy no Abimelek amun, weti Abimelek po awatan ti pusyo.\f + \fr 34:1 \ft 1Sam. 21:10-22:1, weramu mo akari titi apa tame rawainamo ‘‘Akis,’’ yara Pemasmur po apa tame rawainamo ‘‘Abimelek.’’\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 \f + \fr 34:2 \ft Masmur somamo ransyerano Ibrani \ft \+it akrostik\+it* inta mije, weye ntavondi urupijo Ibrani ama ntetebeaje rai. Weramu ayao Yawa ntavondi urupije so rai jewen.\f*Syare rikangkamambe AMISY Ai masyote anteter, 
\q2 rikangkamambe Aije mamo mpaya inawa rai intai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syo AMISY ararimbe weye apa ana dave mbewar, 
\q2 koveamo vatano matawanto wo ranaun muno manayanambe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare wade, wantenambe wamo AMISY aijaseo titive, 
\q2 wade tenambe wamo Apa tame raijaseo titive. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syo AMISY anajo, muno Po sya ana danajo raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 muno Po inapaya irati anakotaro idasyanive so rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Vatano usaroro AMISY obo Ai nawamo indati manayanambe, 
\q2 muno usamane akatoe ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Risyamo vatano inatawanto, arono syanonae AMISY Po rinaraniv, 
\q2 ti Po inapaya irati ana nsosobe inaije rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Vatano wo AMISY asyanive nawamo Apa naite wo mansayan kijani, wo mansayaranande, 
\q2 indamu po mapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wade ra wapo ranaun muno wapo raen tavon: AMISY Opamo kov dave! 
\q2 Kove ngkov irati vatano mansamamavube Aije mai! 
\q1  
\v 10 Inya, vatano wasatayao terave AMISY Ai weap, syare wapo asyaniv, 
\q2 weye vatano wo asyanive nawamo indati una irati ana jajewembe rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Make sivuinye\f + \fr 34:11 \fq make sivuinye \ft ranigwano ‘‘singa’’ rai.\f* pamo maror weye apa anaisye meweno ai, 
\q2 yara vatano ubekero AMISY Ai nawamo indati anakotaro kove meweno mai jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Inya, arikainye weap, wapo inaranide, 
\q2 risyo wasanyao indamu wapo AMISY asyaniv. 
\q1  
\v 13 \f + \fr 34:13 \ft Anemo 13-17a ama ayao ratoe akato no 1Petrus 3:10-12.\f*Are nyirati mbeker nya tume nggwaravainy arono ntuna no mine so, 
\q2 muno mbeker nyo ama kove raen, 
\q1  
\v 14 weamo syare nyo taune nawa rayaranande indamu vemo nyo ana ngkakai inta raura inya, 
\q2 muno nyo aarurijate inta raker inya. 
\q1  
\v 15 Syare nakirive ana ngkakai rai, yara nyo ana ngkove obo rave tutir, 
\q2 muno mbekero panyoambe indamu nanuga nsaumano vatan tenambe mansai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 AMISY ami ntetero vatano ubeta Aije mai, 
\q2 Po mansayaranande muno Po awa sambaya wo awaine raraniv. 
\q1  
\v 17 Yara vatano awa ana udave ngkakainoanive nawamo, AMISY be marovave mai, 
\q2 ranivara ugwenen to, weamo Po awa tame raupaisy ti vatano mine so inta mansaemen akato mai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 18 Ranivara vatano ubeta AMISY Ai wo awain, weamo Po maraniv, 
\q2 muno Po mapaya irati ana nsosobe maije rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 19 AMISY pararai irati vatano manuga mpatimu mai, 
\q2 muno vatano siurije mo mansakupi nawamo Po mapaya rai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Vatano ubeto AMISY Ai nawamo, indati unanta irati siuri manui rai tavon, 
\q2 weramu awa siuri wem AMISY Po rapaya tenambe mai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Wepi Po mansayaranande vintabo. 
\q2 Tugae! Awa pae mamo inta daute ramu.\f + \fr 34:21 \ft Yoh. 19:36\f* 
\q1  
\v 22 Vatano mamune nao ugweneno taune awa ana udave ti ngkakai rai, 
\q2 muno are nawirati manuga mamuno vatano kove mai indati mangke makare mai. 
\q1  
\v 23 AMISY Po Apa vatano wanapatambe Ai mapaya kakaije rai, 
\q2 muno vatano mansamamavube AMISY Ai nao, Po mangke raugaje mai jewen. 
\c 35  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu no wansaora irati marova mai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\q2 Sya AMISY, syare winaroyaro vatano maroyaro rinai so mai, 
\q2 wimarovave irati vatano umarovave rinaije mai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Syare Nyo Nya vakano mamaune me anakoe me yaijaro tindimuve, 
\q2 muno nseo ra nde Nyo sopambe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Winyo weame muno tama raijaseo, 
\q2 indamu naroyaro vatano wo inangkarimuge so mai. 
\q1 Syare Amisye Winyo raurade rinai, nyare: 
\q2 ‘‘Risyirati AMISY, Syo napaya irati kakaije rai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 4 Koveamo vatano ware wo rinaubaisye nawamo, 
\q2 indati usamane muno awa tame ngkakai. 
\q1 Koveamo vatano wo kakai ratantona rinai 
\q2 wansuk akiri muno wananepabe. 
\q1  
\v 5 Koveamo onawamo maisyare kapumo ovare po ransaonto wemaisy, 
\q2 muno naito AMISY Po mansamayo rijat. 
\q1  
\v 6 Koveamo wo unanuijo nsaremo ngkaumudi raronto wemaisy, 
\q2 muno naito AMISY Po mangkarimu rijat. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Weye ana inta mbe ayaobe rinai ramu, weramu wo isyeane ratugar ti mo rinaman, 
\q2 umba wo ateme rawae ti mo rinaman. 
\q1  
\v 8 Koveamo wene nde mai papabe vayave, 
\q2 koveamo taune usawa awa isyeano wo ratugare rai, 
\q2 muno utatayasyo atemo wo rawae rai weti ugwenen dai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Weti rinanayanambe weye AMISY Nya vambunine raroron, 
\q2 muno rinananibe weye Winyo rinapaya irati kakai umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Inanuga ntenami syo raura, syare: ‘‘AMISY, Winyamo inta po namaisye ramu! 
\q2 Winyirati Nyo vatano mayondi apaya irati vatano bambunine ai. 
\q2 Muno Nyo vatano atawanto muno apa ana jajewembe ai apaya irati vatano wo ananuge raowenta mai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Vatano mamune ubeseo, wangkarive ware wo ana ngkakai inta raeno rinai, 
\q2 wo rinantutibe ana idaene jewene rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Sya ana daveti ngkove mamo wo rasakinavo kakai rai, 
\q2 weti rinanimaumbe mo inatatuv asyo. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weramu arono wenawa ujajoram, 
\q2 risyamo rinanimaumbe mai, weti inatawandi marore rai, 
\q1 muno syo mana raijame jewen yara syo ansuno wusyine obo rave.\f + \fr 35:13 \fq ansuno wusyine obo rave: \ft no koano Israel raijamo wo iije vasye karisya veano maakuvi arono manimaumbe rave.\f* 
\q2 Umba inami ratu syo sya sambaya raura seo Amisye Ai, 
\q1  
\v 14 maisyare risambayambe sya arakovo taun dave ai rako, 
\q2 sya arakovo ingkavave inta ai wemaisy. 
\q1 Risyoyovo mansai 
\q2 maisyare inanimaumbe sya ingkoa rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 15 Weramu arono rino ana nsosobe ama uga rai, 
\q2 onawamo manayanambe muno wanugan tenambe umarovave rinai. 
\q1 Vatano syantatukambe mai nao, 
\q2 wo kaipate ko rinai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 16 Vatano ubeta Amisye Ai jewene umaso wo inaura tantunawi tutir, 
\q2 matomokane ntitiki nande rinai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Sya Akoe Winy, Winyo rinanyanyut bayavea ntoa nanduija? 
\q2 Syare Nyo inapaya vatano maroyaro rinai ti ware wo inakupi so mai, 
\q2 syare Nyo rinapaya sya marova maisyare make sivuiny\f + \fr 35:17 \fq make sivuiny \ft ranigwano ‘‘singa’’ rai.\f* dave so mai! 
\q1  
\v 18 Wea indati syo kove raura seo Nai no anugan akoe awa yasyin, 
\q2 syo winararimbe no vatano wanui mansamun. 
\q1  
\v 19 Vemo winaneme mpaya rinai mo sya marova wo rinambaone umananibe inya, 
\q2 syo ana inta ravera ngkakai jewen, weramu onawamo umarovave rinai vayave. 
\q1 Vemo nakirive rinai mo vatane umaso wugoeno rinai jinya, 
\q2 sya ana dave inta ngkakai jewen, weramu onawamo manuga mamuno rinai vayave.\f + \fr 35:19 \ft Maz. 69:5; Yoh. 15:25\f* 
\q1  
\v 20 Weye awa ayao mamo nsaumane jewen, 
\q2 yara ubeker ware wo vatano una kovo saumane rai no munije so mansapamponae. 
\q1  
\v 21 Ugwain wo rinakekebe ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Ko dave, ko dave, umba reamo nya ana ndave raeno reansami rai ije.’’ 
\q1  
\v 22 Weramu AMISY, Winyo raen to, 
\q2 weti vemo manin bayave inya; 
\q1 sya Akoe Winy, vemo Winy nggwaravainyo rinai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 23 Wimbeseo ra Nyo marimbe rinai! 
\q2 Amisy, sya Akoe Winy, syare Nyo sopambe rinai weye wo ayao rangkivano rinai. 
\q1  
\v 24 AMISY, Winyirati sya Amisy, 
\q2 syare Nyo patimu moyare raude rinai, 
\q2 indamu vemo sya marova woaro rinai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 25 Vemo wo rinaura no manuga ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Ko dave! Reama mbekere mamai to, 
\q2 reamo anasineko ai to!’’ wemai nora. 
\q1  
\v 26 Koveamo vatano manayanambe sya siuri so rai nawamo, 
\q2 wananepabe muno usamane. 
\q1 Koveamo vatano umararino rinai nawamo, 
\q2 vatano kaije wo mavororobe indamu usamane. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 27 Syare koveamo vatano ubekero wo rinaeno patimu moyare raugaje rinaije, 
\q2 umananibe muno ugwain manayanambe. 
\q1 Koveamo wo raura tutir ware: ‘‘AMISY ararimbe! Opirati titi rave! 
\q2 Wepi anayanambe Po kovo saumane raude irati Apa vatano panapatambe Aije ai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 28 Weamo indati risyo Nya moyare ravov, 
\q2 muno rikangkamambe Winai namane rinit. 
\c 36  
\s1 Vatano mamune awa ana udave muno Amisye Apa muinye 
\p  
\v 1 Daud wepi vatano panapatambe AMISY Ai, po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Vatano mamune opamo ayao kakaije obo mirati ntubai anuga rai, 
\q2 Po Amisye asyanive mamo meweno ai.\f + \fr 36:2 \ft Roma 3:18\f* 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye opamo po taune ararin dave, 
\q2 weti aemendi apa ayao kakaije rai jewen muno ponae rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Awa mamo ntairijo ayao kakaije obo rai muno anapamponae rai, 
\q2 ana ratantona ntiti ngkove mamo po rapaya ti ntami muno ponae po ana ngkove ravei. 
\q1  
\v 5 Arono naman panatantonave kakaije obo rai tutir no apa niki ri, 
\q2 po anasine raugavo unanuijo kakaije raito, 
\q2 apa ana dave mamune mamo po rapaya ra ntami ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Sya AMISY, Nya muinyo no tawane mamo ntitito no naume warae, 
\q2 muno winteto Nya urairi rai mamo nto rave no kamure rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Nya moyare ntitito rave maisyare unato titi ntindimu no tawan, 
\q2 Nya ana ndapatimuge mamaisy ngkambito rave rarope kakai maisyare mayano tento ramaisy. 
\q2 Sya AMISY, Winyi Nyo vatane muno maere kotare rakum tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Wakoe, sya Amisy, Nya muinyo no tawane mamo ama ngkove manakoeyo reansai! 
\q2 Vatan tenambe ugaugambe Nai maisyare mangkuere tuvane gaugambe irati akoe ama pepak ate rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Anaisyo mawes Nyo ratayao ti ntuna mansamarom no Nya yavare rai mamo wenao tenambe wisyisyo rai. 
\q2 Winyo mana raunande ti wo ramanam, omamo mana nori rati Nya mana ami mo anayanambe raugave rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weye Winyirati anakotar tenambe njayaisyo Nai, 
\q2 Taune Nya vare wemirati reangkovo rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Ribeker syare Nyo Nya muinyo no tawane raugaje vatano wo naen tugaive mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo ana ngkove rave irati vatano manuga nsarokire mai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Syare vemo vatano mararine wo rinatakar asyo nora, 
\q2 muno vatano mamune wo inawatambe syusyo inya. 
\q1  
\v 13 Wapo raen! Vatano maneme mamumbe utataopon to, 
\q2 wenawamo Amisye Po maugaje mavari, weti usea sayae akatoe kakai. 
\c 37  
\s1 Vatano kove\f + \fr 37:0 \ft \+it vatano kove:\+it*\ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it lassadiq\+it*\ft ama ine ratoe tumaimbe mare: ‘‘vatano kove.’’ Ama ino manakoe mare: ‘‘vatano ubeta Amisye Apa ananyao rai.’’ Ayao so ratoe manui no Masmur so rai.\f* pe vatano mamune\f + \fr 37:0 \ft \+it vatano mamune:\+it*\ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it rasha‎\+it* ama ine ratoe tumaimbe mare: ‘‘vatano mamun.’’ Ama ino manakoe mare: ‘‘vatano wonae Amisye Ai muno Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.’’ Ayao so ratoe manui no Masmur so rai.\f* pe aya ana nande yai no maran 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 \f + \fr 37:1 \ft Masmur somamo ransyerano Ibrani \ft \+it akrostik\+it* inta mije, weye ntavondi urupijo Ibrani ama ntetebeaje rai. Weramu ayao Yawa ntavondi urupije so rai jewen.\f*Vemo winy mparijo vatano mamune mai jinya, 
\q2 vemo winyamo nanuga mparijo vatano awa ana udave ngkakainoanive mai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 2 Weye wenawamo makaniveta vayave kobe, maisyare insumaijo ngkanene wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare anare njayaibe mayone wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare nyanave AMISY obo Ai muno nyo ana ngkove obo raijar. 
\q2 Indati wino kovo nsaumane rautan no muni so. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare winy nananibe AMISY atavon, 
\q2 indati Wepi Po nya ana mbekedai ti no no nanuga raveti mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syare nyo taune naunanto AMISY Ai, 
\q2 muno nanaveano amen; Wepirati indati Po naugavo kove rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Wepirati indati Po winya mbeto Apa ananyao rai raroron kakavimbe ti vatane wo raen no nai maisyare wo uma apa vare raen wemaisy. 
\q2 Muno nya mamaisye raen kakavimbe maisyare uma moyar no masyote yasyine wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Syare nanuga ntanamanin nyo AMISY anyut, 
\q2 natawandi nyo atunao Apa betoije rai. 
\q1 Vemo mparijo vatano wo ana mawese rako mai jinya, 
\q2 weye wenawamo vatano wo aarurijate raker muno wo ana kakaije obo ratantona. 
\q1  
\v 8 Parije mamo nsopi muno nanuga mamoane mamo rapaya ra ntami, 
\q2 vemo mpari nora, weye parije mamo mo anakotaro ngkakainoanive obo raugav. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye vatano awa ana udave ngkakainoanive nanawamo maotar ti makanive irati munije so rai, 
\q2 yara vatano manaveano AMISY amen, awa ura irati munije we rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Masyote inta ai jakato, vatano mamune opamo aumandi to; 
\q2 ranivara akani ta no apa norije rai, wepamo aen akatoe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Yara vatano manuga mpaaje nanawamo awa ura irati munije we rai, 
\q2 muno mananibe una irati anakotaro mawese ama uga obo rai.\f + \fr 37:11 \ft Ino kaijinta no taiso: ‘‘mananibe una no kovo saumane ama uga rai.’’\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Vatano mamune wo kakaije ratantona nanto irati vatano kove mai, 
\q2 manuga mamuno mai ti matomokane ntitiki mai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weramu Akoe pamo pugoeno vatano mamune mai, 
\q2 weye Po raen pare Apa masyoto Po mangke raugaje maije ndea mangkepan kobe. 
\q1  
\v 14 Vatano mamune wo awa omake rapatino ama kokome rai, muno wo apae raivit, 
\q2 indamu wo vatano ana jajewembe nawe vatano siurije nawe maubaisy, 
\q2 muno vatano utavondi Amisye Apa bekere rai maotadi. 
\q1  
\v 15 Weramu onawamo awa omake nsakinav akare mo taune maotar akato, 
\q2 muno awa apae mamo rakupi ti ntuna. 
\q1  
\v 16 Vatano kove apa ananuge kavinta vayave 
\q2 omamo ngkov akato irati vatano mamune apa ananuge mawese ai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Weye vatano mamun awa vambunine mamo AMISY Po radaut, 
\q2 yara Po sopambe irati vatano kove mai. 
\q1  
\v 18 AMISY Po vatano ana ngkakaije inta raeno mai jewene mayaranande mavabe masyote anteter, 
\q2 muno wenawamo indati awa ura muni Amisye Po raunande mai raija ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 19 Arono una irati nsosobe ama uga rai, wenawamo unanta irati siurije rai ramu, 
\q2 arono marore tami, wenawamo una irati mane obo rai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Yara tugae, vatano mamun indati ukakai; 
\q2 muno vatano ube marovave AMISY Ai indati ugwenen kobe. 
\q1 Maisyare kavasasi ama ugo mpopan raumandi ramaisy, 
\q2 wenao mansaumandi maisyare kijao nsaonto ti rakanive. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 Vatano mamun po romane ranajo po raugav, weramu po ravae akare ramu, 
\q2 yara vatano kove bekobe, weti po romane raugaje manui, mamaisyo anuga muinye rai. 
\q1  
\v 22 Weye vatano AMISY Po kove raugaje mai, wenawirati awa ura munije so rai, 
\q2 yara vatano AMISY panaamatambe mai onanawamo Po maotar ti makanive. 
\q1  
\v 23 AMISY Po vatano utavono Aije maugavo awa unanuijo wanya raije rai, 
\q2 Wepi Po masopan tindimuve weye anayanambe awa ana wo rave rai. 
\q1  
\v 24 Arono utemasyo, wenawamo unanta pare manakoe rai jewen, 
\q2 weye AMISY taune Pi Po maneme raijar. 
\q1  
\v 25 Arono ta rikamuramoe ndea be vatan anuive so, 
\q2 weramu syo vatano kove inta aeno Amisye aneme mpaya aije ramu, 
\q2 muno apa arikainye, apa ajavije inta wanatambe anaisye raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 26 Vatano napijep bekobe ti po apa ananuge rapapaya vayave irati vatano wo ranajo mai, 
\q2 muno apa arikainye muno ajavi nanawamo kovo manakoe no mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 27 Syare ana ngkakaije rapaya ra ntami yara ana ngkove obo raijar, 
\q2 weamo nya susyo merere nto utantuna irati munijo we raija ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 28 Weye AMISY anuga no irati ana mamaisye muno moyare obo rai. 
\q2 Opamo Po vatano matawandi utavondi Aije mapaya ra una marambe ramu. 
\q1 Onawamo Po makum mavabe ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 yara vatano mamun onawamo indati awa susye maotar ti makanive. 
\q1  
\v 29 Vatano kove nanawamo indati awa ura irati munije we rai, 
\q2 muno utantuna raija ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 30 Vatano kove pamo indati po ayao ana ratantona ntitije raura, 
\q2 muno apa ana dapatimuge mamo moyar. 
\q1  
\v 31 Weye Amisye Apa anaparatote obo mirati no anuga rai tugaive, 
\q2 weti tavondijo rai mavabe muno po rakivandije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 32 Vatano kove pamo, vatano mamune po anyanyuti, 
\q2 po varore rakanijo ai indamu po aubaisy. 
\q1  
\v 33 Weramu AMISY Po vatano kove apaya ra no vatano mamune aneme raije ramu, 
\q2 muno Po apaya ra mangke raugaje ai jewen arono patimu marane raugaje ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 34 Syare AMISY obo Pirati wasanave amen muno watavondijo Apa ananyao rai. 
\q2 Wea indati Po wasaijaseo indamu weapa ura munije we rai tawan tutir, 
\q2 muno wapo raen Po vatano mamune maotar ti makanive rai. 
\q1  
\v 35 Risyamo syo vatano mamune inta aen to, opamo sivuin dave muno po vatane matekar asyo, 
\q2 opamo bambunin dave maisyare inyowo ntiti rave wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 36 Weramu arono rikivandeto opamo aen akatoe jewen, 
\q2 syo akanijamo rinanto aije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 37 Syare winyo vatano anuga nsarokir muno tavondi Amisye Apa bekere rai anyanyut, 
\q2 weye vatano bekero saumane rai, wepamo indati masyoto makareye umu apa susye merere nto. 
\q1  
\v 38 Yara vatano umarovave Amisye Ai nanawamo indati Wepi Po maubai bintabo, 
\q2 muno vatano mamune nanawamo awa susyo merere nto rapamo ti mewen. 
\q1  
\v 39 AMISY Po vatano kove mapaya irati vatano mamune mai, 
\q2 muno Po makom arono una irati ana nsosobe ama uga rai. 
\q1  
\v 40 AMISY Opirati Po maijaseo muno Po maugavuje vatano mamune manem uga raora, 
\q2 Po maugavuje muno Po mapaya irati awa vambunine rai, 
\q2 weye Amisy Obo pirati wakata gaugambe Ai. 
\c 38  
\s1 Amisye anonae arono no irati wanene rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe, arono po anakotare rameseo Amisye Ai indamu Amisye aemeno ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY, syare vemo Nyo Nya pari mangke raugaje rinai nora, 
\q2 vemo Nyo Nya pari mpanyoane veano inanepat inya. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye Nya pari mangke mo rinaron maisyare atoe inta nteto rinai to wemaisy, 
\q2 winaneme mo mangke veano inatawan asyo. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ti rigwaneno mangkebe rave kobe weye wimpari rinai, 
\q2 inanasine so njoram tenambe weye sya ayao kakai mbewar. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye taune sya ana dave ti ngkakai manakoe rave, ti mo inatatuv asyo, 
\q2 sya ayao kakaije umaso mangke dave kobe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya pare mamo anane ntuna rai janyi ti ranavane mbaug, 
\q2 weye taune risyananepabe. 
\q1  
\v 7 Sya wanene mangke dave weti riseo tete kakai, 
\q2 masyote tename wemamo risyoyov maisyare rino memene rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 8 Weye wanene ama mamoane mansanano inanasine rai vintabo, 
\q2 inanasine somamo inta nsaumane ramu. 
\q1  
\v 9 Sya vambunine meweno rinai muno inanasine mbanonom to, 
\q2 syanonae weye inanuga ntanamanine jewen. 
\q1  
\v 10 Akoe Winy, Winyi Nyo sya bekere raen tenambe, 
\q2 muno sya ana idanonae mamo ngkokaibe no winamune rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya okami pirabe rave, sya vambunine raumandi rinai, 
\q2 muno sya wanene mo rinaveti inamije ndadiri. 
\q1  
\v 12 Waneno nande rinai mbewar ti sya arakove muno sya manivuvi wo rinamumuibe, 
\q2 muno sya arakovo yavaruga ugwaravainyo rinai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Vatano ware ubekero wo rinaubaisye nawamo wo isyeane ratugar ti mo inaman. 
\q2 Vatano manatantonave rinai nawamo ware wo rinaubai da inaumandi. 
\q2 Masyote tename weamo anapamponae obo mirati wanyinyaube raijo rinai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Weramu risyamo maisyare vatano amarikoame mpapaki weti syo awa ayao ranaune ramu, 
\q2 maisyare vatano awa ngkao weti syayao kakai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Tugae, risyamo maisyare vatano po ana inta ranaune jewen, 
\q2 weti syo ayao inta rasakinavo mai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 16 Weramu sya AMISY, rinanave namen, 
\q2 Amisy, sya Akoe Winy, sya ana danajo mamo indati Nyo ravera mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 17 Weye syo nanajo to, syare: ‘‘Ranivara ritemaje, weamo vemo sya marova umararin nora, 
\q2 vemo Nyo rinapayamo vatano wo rinambaone mansananibe inya.’’ 
\q1  
\v 18 Weye risyamo kavintare wo rinapinde, 
\q2 muno rinanuga so njoram tutiro sya siurije rai. 
\q1  
\v 19 Risyo taune sya ana daveti ngkakai raura kakavimbe, 
\q2 rinanuga so ranimaumbe rave weye syo sya ayao kakai ratantonave. 
\q1  
\v 20 Vatano umarovave rinai vayave ayao mamaisye jewene rai nawamo wanui, 
\q2 sya ana inta mbe ayaobe jewen, weramu vatano manuga mamuno rinai nawamo wanui. 
\q1  
\v 21 Sya ana daveti ngkove mamo wo rasakinavo ana mamune obo rai, 
\q2 syo ana ngkove obo rave, weramu onawamo umarovave rinai vayave. 
\q1  
\v 22 AMISY, vemo Nyo rinapaya nora, 
\q2 sya Amisy, vemo nggwaravainyo rinai nora. 
\q1  
\v 23 Syare nyavave ra nde Nyo sopambe rinai, 
\q2 sya Akoe Winyi Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai. 
\c 39  
\s1 Wansanave Amisye amen weye wama matame mamo ntumainy bayave 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Nto irati Yedutun ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Syo ratantona no inanuga, syare: syo taune rinayaranande sya ana dave rai, 
\q2 indamu vemo inaunane so mo ayao kakaije ratande rinai jinya. 
\q1 Syo inawa so rakuvu indamu syayao inya, 
\q2 arono vatano mamune ta una mararaive rinaiji. 
\q1  
\v 3 Anamainitu rinai ti, syo ayao inta raura jewen, 
\q2 syo ayao kove inta raura tavone jewen, rinawa ntapumi vayave, 
\q2 weramu sya siuri mamo mangkeo rinai rave kobe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Rinanuga raraniva ngkantebe rave, 
\q2 syo ratantona akoevea inanuga so mamaun dave, 
\q2 weti syo raura syare: 
\q1  
\v 5 ‘‘Sya AMISY, syare Winyo sya matam akari raura rinai, 
\q2 inda syo raen risyamo kov ti ino somamo ntumainy dave ti mavave nde nto. 
\q1  
\v 6 Tugae, sya tumo windapatimu syanya rai omamo ta no no ire maran karisya. 
\q2 Risya kov ti rino somamo ntumainy dave, ramuinyo Winai. 
\q2 Vatane reamamo maisyare anawayo ta ramawita wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Reama reangkove mamo maisyare ugara deto vayave ti aumandi wemaisy. 
\q2 Reansamun nsariraeve anakere rai omamo reambea marudi. 
\q1 Reamo ana ngkenav no mine so ratayao ti reamo ratutumbe, 
\q2 weramu reamantukambe indati arepi apa ura rai jakato? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Sya Akoe Winy, umba animaisye mi ridanyube akato? Jewena! 
\q2 Wibuiny irati inanaveano namen! 
\q1  
\v 9 Syare Nyo inapaya irati sya ayao kakai rai tenambe, 
\q2 vemo winaneme mpaya rinai mo vatano wananepabe wo rinambaon inya. 
\q1  
\v 10 Anamainitu rinai, syonae syayaobei, 
\q2 weye mangke somamo Winyi Nyo raude rinai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Syare Nya mangke nde rinaije raveto marambe rinai, 
\q2 weye kavintare rikakai irati Nya mangke umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Winyo mangke raude vatane nanentabo mai mamo indamu Nyo manyao, 
\q2 weye awa ana udave ngkove jewen. 
\q1 Muno Winyo awa anakotaro ngkenav no mine so rawaumbe, 
\q2 maisyare puso nsanambe ana kov dave rai wemaisy. 
\q1 Tugae, vatane awa ukove mamo maisyare nanawayo ta ramawito vayave wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 13 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo sya ana danajo raraniv, 
\q2 muno namarikoame rasakinavo sya anonae so rai, 
\q2 vemo Nyo sya oyove so raraniv bayave inya! 
\q1 Maisyare sya aneno sinane una tawane jewen no mine vone so rai mansamaisy, 
\q2 risyamo vatano wanisen ta ride no vavai no Nya muni so rai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Syare vemo Nyo pari raude rinai tutir inya, 
\q2 indamu rinanayanambe vavai rati, 
\q2 nai arono risyana kakai rainy muno inaumandi rainye so.’’ 
\c 40  
\s1 Sambaya kove raura Amisye Ai muno nya mbekere ranajo 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Rinatawandi syo AMISY atunao, 
\q2 weti umba Po rinaen muno Po sya anonae raraniv. 
\q1  
\v 3 Po rinapaya irati atemo wene rai, 
\q2 omamo maisyare Po inakarimu sen no kanuga nsararane rai wemaisy. 
\q1 Po rinapaato te no unato orame von, 
\q2 Po rinaveti inawanto tindimuve muno ino kovo saumane rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Wama Amisy Po ransyerano wanyine raunande ti rikinyo rai, 
\q2 indamu syo veano ararimbe. 
\q1 Indati vatane wanui wo AMISY Apa ana dave raen, 
\q2 ti wo asyaniv umba wanave Ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Kove ngkov irati vatano wanave AMISY obo Aije mai, 
\q2 onawamo umamanaive nanto vatano mararine mai jewen, 
\q2 muno manaveano vatano wangkarive mansamene ramu!\f + \fr 40:5 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware ayao Ibrani ama ine maisyare so: ‘‘muno mansanaveano yare mansamene ramu.’’\f* 
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY, Winyirati sya Amisy, Nya anakotaro ndave mamo manui rave, 
\q2 Nya mbekero Nyo ratantona reansai mamo mbe anainambe rave irati reansai. 
\q1 Winyamo inta po namaisye ramu! 
\q2 Syare syo Nya anakotaro ndave ravovo muno syo raura, 
\q2 weramu ama manui mamo nseo rave ti ratore kakai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 \f + \fr 40:7 \ft Aneme 7-9 ratoe akato no Ibrani 10:5-7.\f*Winyamo nanuga no irati maero raotar 
\q2 muno anaisyo raugavere rameseo Nai raije ramu. 
\q2 Maere rameseo Nai muno ama mavu raunanto indamu veano ayao kakai rapaya mamo 
\q2 Winyamo ntuvako rai ramu, 
\q2 yara nyare ibeto Nya ayao rai wemi mbewar Winyo ana ranaune ngkove raude rinai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Umba syo raura syare: ‘‘Tugae, risyi so, 
\q2 syare syo rave maisyare Nya bukuge mo inaurairive wusyimbe, no ama ayao mo ratoe rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 Sya Amisy, inananibe ibeto Nya mbekere rai, 
\q2 Nya anaparatote mamo syo raugasyo ntami sya wanyatije rai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Sya AMISY, Winyamo Nyo raen tenambe to, 
\q2 Nya ayao mamaisye mamo syo ravovo Nya kawasae wanui so mansamun, 
\q2 omamo mpaya inawa so rai jewen, yara syo raura tutir. 
\q1  
\v 11 Nya ayao mamaisye mamo ritanamanino rautan no inanuga so jewen, 
\q2 winteto Nya urairi rai me, Nyo reansapaya irati ana ngkakai rai me nayamo syo ravov tutir. 
\q1 Winteto Nya urairi rai me, Nya muinyo no tawane me nayamo rimanino rautane ramu, 
\q2 yara syo raura kakavimbe no Nya kawasae wanui so mansamun. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 AMISY, syare naemeno rinai tutir muno windarino rinaora, 
\q2 weye Nya muinyo no tawane me, winteto Nya urairi rai omirati ntavono rinai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weye ana nsosobe mo rinawariki mamo manui rave, ti ratore kakai, 
\q2 muno taune sya ayao kakai mo rinawatan ti syantukambe to rije rai. 
\q1 Sya ayao kakai manui rave ti mo inakarivuinye so rakivan, 
\q2 mo inaveti inanuga mamaun. 
\q1  
\v 14 AMISY, syare naemeno rinai indamu Nyo inapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 sya AMISY, syare nyavave nde Nyo rinasopan! 
\q1  
\v 15 Syare koveamo vatano ware wo rinaubaisye nawamo, 
\q2 Nyo mapinde ti usamane muno mpusyek tatugadi. 
\q1 Syare koveamo vatano ubekero siurije nande rinai nawamo, 
\q2 Nyo matamo ra wansuk akiri muno awa tame ngkakai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Vatano wugoeno rinai useambe rinai ware: ‘‘Ko dave, ko dave...!’’, 
\q2 syare koveamo onawamo usamane dave. 
\q1  
\v 17 Yara vatan tenambe nanawirati ude ubeaje Amisye Winai nawamo 
\q2 koveamo umananibe muno manayanambe irati Nya ana ndave rai. 
\q1 Vatano mansanuga no Winai weye Nyo mapaya kakai rai nawamo 
\q2 koveamo wo raura tutir ware: ‘‘Tugae, AMISY Opirati panakoeve rave!’’ 
\q1  
\v 18 Weramu risyamo vatano inatawanto muno sya ana jajewembe rinai; 
\q2 syare sya Akoe winaemeno rinai. 
\q1 Weye Winyirati Nyo sopambe rinai muno Nyo inapaya irati anakotaro ngkakai rai, 
\q2 weti sya Amisy, syare vemo maneai nora! 
\c 41  
\s1 Amisye anajo ra Po saumane raude nai no arono nggwanen 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Kove ngkov irati vatano are pirati aemeno vatano awa ana jajewembe mai ai, 
\q2 opamo arono ana nsosobe nande ai indati AMISY Po apaya rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Vatano napije pamo AMISY darino aora, muno Po ayaranande indamu jayaisy tutir. 
\q2 Weti vatane wo aura ware opirati vatano no anayanambe rai no munijo Israel pijep, 
\q2 muno Winyo aunanto apa marova manem uga rai jewen! 
\q1  
\v 4 Arono niki doyabe apa wanene rautan, AMISY Winyo ayaranande, 
\q2 muno Nyo saumane raude ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Yara risyamo syo raura, syare: ‘‘Sya AMISY, rigwambe ayao kakai rai no winamune rai to, 
\q2 weramu syare naemeno rinai, Nyo saumane raude rinai!’’ 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya marova wo mamune ratantona rinai, 
\q2 ubeker dave indamu rikakai muno rinakaniveto. 
\q1  
\v 7 Vatano ude wo rinapane nawamo wayao angkarive, 
\q2 ude indamu wo rinakani ayao mamaisye jewene rai, 
\q2 umba wusya wo rinampami no nuge we raito. 
\q1  
\v 8 Vatan tenambe nanawirati manuga mamuno rinai usaamugadi wo rinaura tantunawi, 
\q2 ubeker ware ana ngkakai nande rinai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wo rinaura ware: ‘‘Apa wanene mangke dave kobe ai kai, 
\q2 indamu opamo vemo beseove akato inya.’’ 
\q1  
\v 10 Muno sya arakovo ingkavave muno syanave ai rave, 
\q2 ririmisyisye mamai dave, sakinav akare ti po rinangkukuv.\f + \fr 41:10 \ft Mat. 26:23; Mrk. 14:18; Luk. 22:21; Yoh. 13:18,26\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Weramu sya AMISY, syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 Nyo vambunine raugav akare rinai indamu syo ana ngkakaijo wo rave rinaije rasakinav akananto mansai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ranivara marova wo anasineko rinai akatoe ramu, 
\q2 weamo syo raen Winyamo nanayanambe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Risyamo Winyo sopambe rinai, weye rinanuga so nsarokir, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinaugav ti rituna winatavon ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 AMISY ararimbe! Opirati Amisy vatano Israel wambeaje Ai pije, 
\q2 no nugo pitawarowe ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q2 Tugae, syare tugae! 
\c 42  
\ms1 ETET 2 
\ms1 MASMUR 42-72 
\s1 Wambekero wamakata Amisye Ai no Apa Yavar 
\p  
\v 1 Susyo Kora awa ransyerano ananyao. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Maisyare rusa awa ngkamandi, weti bekero mana njayaisye rai, 
\q2 maisyare omai tavon, sya jugara so bekero sya Amisye Winai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Amisy Winyi njayaisy, sya jugara so bekero de mararai Winaiji, 
\q2 nanduija umba syakaore beaje Nai no Nya yavar? 
\q1  
\v 4 Siman, naman inami ngkaru nsoyan, 
\q2 syonae syo anaisye raisyi.\f + \fr 42:4 \fq syonae syo anaisye raisyi: \ft ayao Ibrani mo ratoe maisyare so: ‘‘inami ngkaru mbe anaibe syo raisy.’’ \f* 
\q1 Masyote anteter sya marova wo inakekebe ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Nya Amisye Pi ro, yara aemeno nai ramu ge?’’ 
\q1  
\v 5 Inanuga so ranimaumbe, arono rui inaemen akato wusyine rai, 
\q2 arono ono masyoto akokoe\f + \fr 42:5 \fq ono masyoto akokoe: \ft Kel. 23:14-19; Maz. 118:27\f* rai, rito no Yavaro AMISY, 
\q1 itavono vatano wanui mai, iteto usye rai, 
\q2 reambovambe, reansananibe nggwagwaimbe, kinyo ransyeran kangkamane rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Mbe animaibe inanuga so mamaun? 
\q2 Mbe animaibe rinanimaumbe no inanuga so rai? 
\q1 Koveamo inanaveano Amisye obo amen, 
\q2 weye Opirati sya Amisy, Po inapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 weti indati syo kove raura seo Ai jakato. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Inanuga so mamaun, weti inaemen akaore Amisye Winai, 
\q2 nai varoro mana Yordan, muno unato Hermon, nai unato Misar. 
\q1  
\v 8 Amisy, Nyo anakotaro nsosobe raude rinai tutir ti mo inatawanto, 
\q2 ama vambunine maisyare mana vuko mpanyoan nsopato pene rai wemaisy. 
\q1 Inanimaumbe mo inapinto, 
\q2 maisyare manayam akoe Nyo raugaje ti mo inapinto wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 AMISY Po Apa muinyo no tawane rarorono rinai, no sansimane rai, 
\q2 weti arono naman rikinyo ransyerane raijo Ai, 
\q2 omamo sya sambaya idaura to Amisye Ai, Wepirati rijayaisyo Ai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Amisy Wepirati sya unato oram inamamavube Ai, syo raura to Ai, syare: 
\q2 ‘‘Mbe animaibe winakirive inai? 
\q1 Mbe animaibe sya marova wo rinatawanto, 
\q2 weti rinanimaumbe tutir?’’ 
\q1  
\v 11 Inanuga\f + \fr 42:11 \fq inanuga: \ft no ayao Ibrani raijamo mo ‘‘pae’’ ratoe.\f* so ngkupi rawaumbe rave, 
\q2 weye sya marova wo inaura tantunawi. 
\q1 Masyote anteter wo inakekebe ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Nya Amisye Pi ro, yara aemeno nai ramu ge?’’ 
\q1  
\v 12 Mbe animaibe inanuga so mamaun? 
\q2 Mbe animaibe rinanimaumbe no inanuga so rai? 
\q1 Koveamo inanaveano Amisye obo amen, 
\q2 weye Opirati sya Amisy, Po inapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 weti indati syo kove raura seo Ai jakato. 
\c 43  
\s1 Israel awa ana udanajo Amisye Ai arono una no munijo aroo\f + \fr 43:0 \ft Masmur 43 mamo arono wusyinoeamo mbe intabove Masmur 42 rai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 1 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo patimugo moyare raugaje irati rinai, 
\q2 syare Nyo marimbe rinai no susyo umarovave Winai so mai. 
\q2 Syare Nyo inapaya irati vatano aarurijate muno mamune maneme rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Weye Amisy Winyirati rinino naowan. 
\q2 Mbeanimaibe irati winaneme mpaya rinai? 
\q1 Mbeanimaibe sya marova wo rinatawanto, 
\q2 weti rinanimaumbe tutir? 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare Nyo Nya vare muno Nya ayao tugae raude rinai, 
\q2 indamu mo inajum, muno mo inaugav syakaore no Nya Yavaro ntuna ri, 
\q2 no Sion unato ndandinit.\f + \fr 43:3 \fq unato ndandinit: \ft unate so ndandinit weye omamo unato terave AMISY tuna rai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 4 Wea indati syore no Amisy Nya tewa orame rai, 
\q2 syore te no Amisye Winamun, Winyirati sya inananibe muno inanayanambe no rave Nai. 
\q1 Indati rikiny kangkamambe Winai, syo itari mamaune raeyan dai. 
\q2 Amisy, Winyirati sya Amisy! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Mbe animaibe inanuga so mamaun? 
\q2 Mbe animaibe rinanimaumbe no inanuga so rai? 
\q1 Koveamo inanaveano Amisye obo amen, 
\q2 weye Opirati sya Amisy, Po inapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 weti indati syo kove raura seo Ai jakato. 
\c 44  
\s1 Susyo matawanto awa anonae 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano ananyao susyo Kora wo ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Tugae Amisy, anainamo ndarorono reama aneno sinane mai, 
\q2 no arono wusyinoe, 
\q1 omamo wo rarire reansai ti, 
\q2 taune reamo ranauno reansamarikoame rai to. 
\q1  
\v 3 Taune Nya nanemo vambunine mirati Nyo veano susyo wanave Nai jewene mawatano kopa so rai, 
\q2 indamu Nya kawasae wakasisa utantuna rai. 
\q1 Susye kotaro kaije nawamo Nyo kakai raugaje mai, 
\q2 yara Nya kawasae nawamo Nyo maveti ubambunin. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye Nya kawasae awa omake mirati mbewar, wo kopa so raugavo mansamaroma jewen, 
\q2 muno taune awa vambunine mirati mo anasine ugavo maija jewen tavon. 
\q1 Yara Winya vambunine mi no mai muno Nya kove mbaro mai omirati mbewar utantuna rai, 
\q2 weye winanuga no irati mai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Winyirati sya Amisy muno sya Akari Titi, 
\q2 anasineko mamo Winyirati Nyo rapatimu Yakop apa susye mai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Nya vambunine mirati reamo veano marova maroyar ti makanive, 
\q2 muno Nya tame mirati mbewar reamo vatano umarovave reansai mataka doyadi. 
\q1  
\v 7 Weye sya apae, atoe mirati sya vambunine nsawa raija jewen, 
\q2 muno sya omake mamo mo anasine ugavo rinai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 8 Yara Winyirati Nyo reansapaya irati reama marova mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo vatano manuga mamuno reansai maveti usamane. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weti masyote anteter reamo Amisye winararimbe, 
\q2 muno Nya tame mi reangkangkamambe raija ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Weramu soamo winaijaro reama naite matavon da wata marova rai akatoe ramu, 
\q2 yara winakirive reansai muno naneme mpaya reansai ti reansamane. 
\q1  
\v 11 Winaneme mpaya reansai ti marova wo reansakupire ti reamansuk akiri, 
\q2 muno vatano manuga mamuno reansai wo reama ananu raowen ti mewen. 
\q1  
\v 12 Winyo reansapaya ti marova wo reansaubaisy, maisyare domba maotare wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Nyo reansampusyek ti reanta na no susye kotaro wanave jewene awa yasyin. 
\q1  
\v 13 Winyo Nya kawasae reansamavunta mawebe vayave, 
\q2 muno ama kove inta makare Nai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 14 Winaneme mpaya reansai ti susyo una reansakijani wo reansampami, 
\q2 wugoeno reansai muno wo reansaura tantunawi. 
\q1  
\v 15 Winaneme mpaya reansai ti susye kotaro wanave Amisye Ai jewene wugoeno reansai; 
\q2 onawamo mansakari rangkiki reansai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Masyote tename omamo wo reansave samaneve, 
\q2 weti reansamane dave tutir. 
\q1  
\v 17 Weye reamo ranaun, vatano mansanuga mamuno reansai muno umarovave reansai 
\q2 wo reansaura tantunawi muno wo reansakaajian. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 Anakotare so nande reansai, 
\q2 weramu reamamo reansanimari Winai ramu, 
\q2 muno Nya urairi ndaokae nande reansai mamo reandakanyoandi ramu. 
\q1  
\v 19-20 Winyo reansakupi ti soamo reama kopa mamo maisyare nugo maninimbe maero sivuinye obo una rai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Nyo reansaugavo weno ngkakai\f + \fr 44:19-20 \fq weno ngkakai: \ft No ayao Ibrani mo ratoe mare ‘‘ananaman,’’ mbe rarorombe wene rai.\f* raronto kobe. 
\q1 Weramu reansanuga mamo reamo namamarave ramu, 
\q2 muno reamanya marambe Nya unanui rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 21 Ranivara reambeaje reama Amisye Winai akato jewen, 
\q2 yara reamakata mbeaje vatano marane awa anawayo kotare mai ratire, 
\q1  
\v 22 wea indati Winyo raena mo? 
\q2 Weye Winyamo Nyo ana ngkokaibe no reansanuga rai raen to! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Vatane manuga mamuno reansai weye reantavondi Amisy Winai, 
\q2 namane rinit ubeker wo reansaubaisy, 
\q2 reamaisyare maero domba auga da apa isyisye raotare amaisy.\f + \fr 44:23 \ft Ayao so ratoe akato no Roma 8:36.\f* 
\q1  
\v 24 Akoe Winy, mbeseo! Mbeanimaibe Nyo reansaene jewen? Winikija e? 
\q2 Mbeseo ra Nyo reansaen! Vemo nyonae reansai tutir bayave kobe inya. 
\q1  
\v 25 Mbe animaibe winamune rangkokaibe reansai? 
\q2 Muno nanimarijo reansai reama siuri muno reansansewabe so raija e? 
\q1  
\v 26 Weye reama marova wo reansataopon, 
\q2 ti reantatayaje ntavainy no kopa rai. 
\q1  
\v 27 Weti mbeseo ra Nyo sopambe reansai, 
\q2 Nyo reansapaya anakotare so rai weye Nya muinye mamo no tawano reansai. 
\c 45  
\s1 Ransyerano kiny dai no arono akari titi apa ono vauname rai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano ananyao susyo Kora wo ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerano muiny, ukiny dai arono ono akari titi apa vauname rai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramaisy tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Aepare ama ug.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Inanuga so mbekero mo ayao ngkov dave rauguje, 
\q2 sya ransyerane somamo syo veano akari titi angkakivambe. 
\q1 Maisyare vatano aneme nsiridi po pena veano ayao ngkov dave ratoe amaisy, 
\q2 rinaunane sopamo maweso po ayao ngkov dave raura. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Akari titi winamune mamo ngkov daveo anya kaije makivan, 
\q2 nawa mamo ntairi ayao ngkov dave rai. 
\q1 Maisyare omaiti, wandaen Amisye Po kove raugaje nai, 
\q2 ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 4 Inya, akari titi baribuai winy, nyo nya omako marova ransawa no nateriri, 
\q2 winyirati anaaniv kakui muno nya kovo ntiti mo namuman! 
\q1  
\v 5 Nyusyo irati nya vambunino anaanive rautan indamu nyo anasineko marova rai, 
\q2 wirati indamu nyo marimbe vatano mayondi mai muno winteto ayao tugae rai muno moyare rai. 
\q2 Syare nya nanem ngkov vambunine mo anasineko mbe anaanibe ratande nai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Nya ato nsasiu dave mamo, syare mo nya marova awa okami raukidi, 
\q2 susye kotare nawamo nyo mataopon aje ntuna no najo ate rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 \f + \fr 45:7 \ft Anemo 7-8 ratoe akato no Ibr. 1:8-9.\f*Amisye Pi Po vambunine raugaje nai ti, 
\q2 winya mbe akarive mamo indati ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 nya mbe akari titive mamo ana mamaisye obo mirati ndapatimugo vatane mai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Winyamo nanuga no irati ana ngkove obo rai, yara ana ngkakainoanive mamo nanuga mamuno rai tenambe. 
\q2 Wemi mbewar Amisy, Opirati Amisy wimbeaje Ai, Po napatimu indamu Po naijaseo akari titi rai,\f + \fr 45:8 \ft Ayao Ibrani mo ratoe maisyare so: ‘‘Amisye Po manino mbovove rauvaro nakari rai.’’\f* 
\q2 muno Po naveti nanayanambe rave mo akari titi kaije makivan. 
\q1  
\v 9 Nya ansuno manawadi mamo manino mbovove muno inyo mbovove ama ranavane ntami rai. 
\q2 Wintuna no nya yavaro akari titi namirati korodowai popere\f + \fr 45:9 \fq korodowai popere \ft omamo gaja apa korodowai raugav ti raotadi indamu veano yavaro akari titi rainyave.\f* rave rainyave rai. 
\q2 Muno itari ama kine mo nanuga raveti ranayanambe. 
\q1  
\v 10 Akari titi kaije awa wanya arikainye inta nawamo ude 
\q2 utavondi wanya wanapatambe nai mansai. 
\q1 Yara nai taune nya nanem ngkove omamo wanya nyare ndaovane nteto narijat no we, 
\q2 omamo rainyave emasijo kakui rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Inya, wanya winy, syare ndanide muno ndaen kobe, 
\q2 syare vemo ndatantona makato nya susye mai muno nya yavaruga mai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 12 Koveamo akari titi anuga ntento nai weye winamune ngkov dave, 
\q2 weti mbeaje ai, weye opirati vatano akoe be akarive nai pije. 
\q1  
\v 13 Indati kawasae Tirus ude wo romane raveaje namarom, 
\q2 vatano awa ananuge manui ubeker ware wo nanuga raugabe indamu nyo kove rarorono mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Wanya rangkaivovambe akari titije ai rainyave ti nsamorive, raugave nsiso no apa tanoano tuna ri, 
\q2 ansuno mo rave mamo ama vararauno emasije nsaawa rai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Raasaro ansuno nsev dave rai raugaveta akari titije ai, 
\q2 ama arakovo wanya mansae utavondi udijat uta no akari titi ai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Onawamo mananibe muno manayanambe rave, 
\q2 arono maugaveta usisa no akari titije umaso apa yavar. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Akari titi winy, nya arikainyo anya nao indati wakaseo wo awa anene manigwan utantuna akari titi rai, 
\q2 onawamo nyo maijaseo ube akari titive no mine tename so rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Syo ransyerane so veano nya tame raijaseo titive, 
\q2 indamu susyo mbakipambe mansaemeno nai tutir; 
\q2 maisyare omaiti, susye kotare wo nangkakivambe ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 46  
\s1 Amisye Tuna Wansautan muno Po wansayaranande 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur vatano susyo Kora wo ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny, maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Mamaisyo ransyeran ‘‘Alamot’’ \f + \fr 46:1 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it Alamot\+it* ama ine raene ramu. Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware \+it Alamot\+it* omamo ransyerane kotar inta mije, yara kuruno kaijinta ware ama ine mare wanya mansae onawirati ukiny dai.\f* rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Amisye Pi darino wansaora, muno Wepi Po vambunine raunande wansai no marova rai, 
\q2 muno Opamo Po wansaijaseo arono rui wana nsosobe ama uga rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Maisyare omaiti, vemo wanjaniv inya, arono rui muni so ntutar, 
\q2 muno unate mangkiki ti ntaopon ntundumu asyo no mayan ate waraya. 
\q1  
\v 4 Muno aneae mpanyoane mpapoambe, ama rareno kavavugai manakokoe, 
\q2 ti ama vambunino mpanyoane mo unate raveti mangkiki. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Munijo Yerusalem omamo munijo terave Amisy Titi Rave Apa tuna rai mije. 
\q2 Mana ami njayaisye njamo rai, mo anayanambe raugavo vatano una no munijo we mai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Amisye taune Pi tuna munije we rai, weti mandamisye kakai, 
\q2 Wepi pavaveo\f + \fr 46:6 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘arono akane ntipu,’’ omamo mbe rarorombe Amisye pavave Po rave. \f* Po rayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 7 Amisye anamote ravari, weamo mine tename so mandamisyi, 
\q2 susye kotaro wanave jewene ntavae wanonae, 
\q2 muno akarijo titi awa ube akarive raije mandamisy. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY Wepi be akarive naito munijo ntiti mansai, tuna wansautan, 
\q2 Wepirati Amisy aneno Yakopa beaje Ai, Wepi be yambe wansaora irati wama marova mai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wade, wapo AMISY Apa ana dave raen: 
\q2 Po anakotaro mine so inta rapamo anyi ti rakanive ta. 
\q1  
\v 10 Wepi bambunin Po marova ntami no mine tename so ransopi, 
\q2 muno wepi Po apae, atoe, weyame rakomati, 
\q2 muno Po anaiyu marova ramero taname rai! 
\q1  
\v 11 Po raura pare: ‘‘Syare wapo marova ravea nsopi 
\q2 muno wapo raen Risyirati Amisy! 
\q1 Risyirati titi rave susye kotare mai vintabo 
\q2 muno titi rave no muni tename so!’’ 
\q1  
\v 12 AMISY Wepi be akarive naito munijo ntiti mansai, tuna wansautan, 
\q2 Wepirati Amisy aneno Yakopa beaje Ai, Wepi be yambe wansaora irati wama marova mai. 
\c 47  
\s1 Amisy Akari Titi mine tename so 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur vatano susyo Kora wo ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Inya, vatan tenambe weap, wasaneme rapoam, wasananibe! 
\q2 Wapo Amisye aovambe, wasanamote raijasea manakoeve! 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye AMISY Titi Rave, Opamo anaaniv, 
\q2 Akari Titi panakoeve mine so rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Wepirati Po susye kotaro ntuna no wama munijo Israel so rakijani mapinde. 
\q1 Po vambunine raunande wansai ti 
\q2 wama marova utataaje no wansanem ate rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wepi Po wama kopa no tawan ratayao wansai, 
\q2 weye muinyo Yakop apa susye\f + \fr 47:5 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Yakop apa susye,’’ ama ine mare kawasae Israel.\f* wansai, 
\q2 kopa wansanuga manakoeve rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Amisye seo tuna Apa kursijo titi rai to, 
\q2 ti vatane mananibe ugwain Amisye aijaseo titive.\f + \fr 47:6 \ft Arono rui vatano Israel wo Kasyamo Urairi Amisye rauga siso no Yavaro Amisye rai, onawamo mananibe weye omamo raurata irati Amisye seo tuna no Apa kursijo titi rai.\f* 
\q2 AMISY seo to ti tavuna ama kine veano aovambe. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wakiny, wakiny, Amisy ararin, 
\q2 Wakiny, wakiny, wama Akari Titi ararin! 
\q1  
\v 8 Weye Amisy Wepirati Akari Titi mine tename so pije. 
\q2 Wakiny, wakiny ransyeran ama kine ngko dave rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Amisye tuna no Apa kursijo titi ndandinite rai, 
\q2 be akarive vatano susyo mine so mansai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Akarijo titi susyo mine so wangkuire, Amisye Apa kawasae matavon, 
\q2 no Amisyo napirati Abraham panave Aije Amune rai. 
\q1 Weye Amisye Opamo titi rave, 
\q2 Opirati Akari Titi be akarive akari titi mine so mansai tenambe. 
\c 48  
\s1 Sion omamo Amisy Apa muni mije 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran. Masmur vatano susyo Kora wo ratoe.\f + \fr 48:1 \ft Vatano susyo Kora so nanawamo vatano ukinyo ransyerane rai no Yavaro Amisy.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY Wepi panakoeve rave, weti mamaisyo aura titive 
\q2 no wama Amisy Apa munijo ntuna no unato ndandinit rai.\f + \fr 48:2 \ft Unate so ndandinit weye omamo unato terave AMISY tuna rai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 3 Unate ratuije ranyanyutamo ngkov dave, 
\q2 munije ratuije mo vatano mine tename so manuga raveti ranayanambe. 
\q1 Unato Sion\f + \fr 48:3 \fq Sion \ft omamo Yerusalem ama tamo wusyine mije.\f* no no Yerusalem ama ranijo wanansai, 
\q2 omamo AMISY Akarijo Titi panakoeve Apa norije. 
\q1  
\v 4 Amisye Opamo maisyare no no yano orame ama soero ramane rai, 
\q2 indamu Po Yerusalem raman. 
\q1  
\v 5 Waperata akari titi ude awa naite mautan, 
\q2 wanugan ware maroyaro mansai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weramu arono werananta wo Sion ama vambunine raen upaparo mai, 
\q2 naije ujaniv bintabo ti unanajibe tatugadi. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wenawamo ujaniv muno ututar no ratuije, 
\q2 wenawamo kikuaji yorame rai maisyare wanya njanjorami arikainye ai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY Po marova mandamisy maisyare Po ovaro repe augaje ti po nyoman akokoe Tarsis\f + \fr 48:8 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy wo ratantona ware munijo Tarsis mamaisyo munijo Spanyol rai.\f* randujai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 Maisyare muno wandanaumbe no wusyinoe, soamo wandaeno wansami rai to, 
\q2 nai Yerusalem, AMISY Wepi Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti\f + \fr 48:9 \ft Ayao Ibrani mare \ft \+it Yahweh Sabaot,\+it* ama ine mare ‘‘AMISY Wepi Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti.’’\f* Apa munije. 
\q1 No wama Amisy Apa muni so, 
\q2 Po raugasya nteto tindimuve muno Po rayaranande ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Reama Amisy, reansaemeno Nya muinyo no tawano reansai rai, 
\q2 arono reande mbeaje nai no Nya Yavare ama uga. 
\q1  
\v 11 Amisy Nya tame mamo vatane wo ranaun no mine tename so, 
\q2 muno wo nararimbe tenambe. 
\q1 Winyamo Akarijo Titi mbambunin dave,\f + \fr 48:11 \fq mbambunin dave: \ft ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘anem ngkove,’’ ama ine mare Amisye Apa vambuninem.\f* 
\q2 patimu Nyo raugaje mamo mamaisyo Nya moyare rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Syare kawasae Sion mananibe, 
\q2 syare arikainyo wanya Israel ugwain manayanambe, 
\q2 weye AMISY Nya ana ndapatimu mamaisy irati Nya ananyao rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Kawasae Israel weap, syare wasarirae Sion rakiani, 
\q2 wapo ama soere rator, 
\q1  
\v 14 wapo ama yano orame ranyanyuto mavabe. 
\q2 Wapanya wapo ama soero ramane rayasiro mavabe, 
\q2 indamu wapo rariri akato irati wapa susyo miridi nto mai, 
\q1  
\v 15 wapare: ‘‘Tugae rave Opirati Amisye pije, 
\q2 wama Amisy, wambeaje Aija ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 Wepirati Po wansaugav tutira ntoa pitawar.’’ 
\c 49  
\s1 Vatano manaveano ananuge ramen marane mamo wene mo maugav 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur vatano susyo Kora wo ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Inya, susyo mine tename wadanide! 
\q2 Inya, vatano mine tename weap, wasamarikoame rasakinav de! 
\q1  
\v 3 Inya, weapirati vatano wapa tame ntiti weap 
\q2 muno weapi vatano wapa tame ntiti jewen weap. 
\q1 Weapirati vatano ananuge jajewembe wasai weap, 
\q2 muno vatano watantuna ananuge vone rai weap. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare syo ananyao mo vatane manyao irati ana ratantona ntitije rai raura, 
\q2 muno inanuga so mo ananyao kakai, kove ratantonave. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syare syo ayao vari mbe ananyaobe\f + \fr 49:5 \fq ayao vari mbe ananyaobe \ft omamo maisyare Amsal.\f* raraniv mavabe, 
\q2 syare syo itarije\f + \fr 49:5 \fq itarije \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* raeyan muno syo ayao vari nsosobe rave raura kakavimbe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Risyamo janive ramu arono ino no anakotaro nsosobe ama uga rai, 
\q2 muno arono marova mamune wo rinawariki. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wenawirati wo awa romane obo raijaseo vombe, 
\q2 muno mararin irati awa ananugo mine so rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Tugae, vatane nanawamo inta mamaisyo po romane veano apa jayaisy ti no no mine so ravae indamu anasine rapaya wene rai ramu. 
\q2 Muno inta mamaisyo po romane ravae nanto Amisye Ai indamu veano apa jayaisy ti no no mine so ranigwane ramu. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye romane mamo inta mamaisyo veano vatane apa kove ravae ramu, 
\q2 muno romane ama manuije mamo inta mamaisyo veano ravae jewen tavon, ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q1  
\v 10 indamu vatane nanto wene rai jinya, 
\q2 yara jayaisy ti piridi to kobe. 
\q1  
\v 11 Tugae, ana wamo raene mamo vatano wantatukambe nawe vatano wananepabe nawe ugwenen, 
\q2 muno vatano ukov nanawirati awa ana udatantona ntiti nanawamo ugwenen tavon, 
\q2 muno awa ananugo mine somamo wo rapaya ti ntuna vatano kaije mansamarom. 
\q1  
\v 12 Wusyinoeamo vatano awa romane mawese weyave kopa manakoe rai, 
\q2 weramu indati mantuna no kopa aipapo ti utantavainy raija ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 omirati awa una rai tawan tutire mijem. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weti vatane inta tuna tawano apa ananugo maweso aije rautane ramu. 
\q2 Yara ugwenen tavon maisyare maere kotare muenen ti makanive wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Maisyare omaisy wene wemi indati vatano wantatukambe awa marane mije, 
\q2 muno vatano utavondi awa ayaowe rai, wenawamo awa marane nanto wene rai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 15 Onawamo Amisye Po mapatimu indamu ugwenen, maisyare maero domba mansamaisy, 
\q2 indati wen akoe be akarive mai po maugav no wene ama uga rai. 
\q1 Wavave wanawadi wasya no aipapo ama uga rai, 
\q2 manasino kopa mamo parakam, 
\q2 muno amani wemirati munijo una tawan dai kobe mijem. 
\q1  
\v 16 Yara risyamo Amisye Wepi Po inavae patimuve to 
\q2 indamu Po rinapaya irati wene ama vambunine rai, 
\q2 weye Wepi Po rinaugav akare taune Ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Ranivara vatane inta apa ananuge manui rave, 
\q2 muno apa romano yavaruga ama manui miridi nseo, 
\q2 weamo vemo nanuga njoramo ai nora. 
\q1  
\v 18 Weye arono wene nde ai, po inta rauga da to rautane ramu, 
\q2 muno apa romane omamo no autan da pasyo no aipapo raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 19 Arono ta kove weamo pare opamo no kovo ananuge manui rai rave to, 
\q2 muno vatano kaije ukangkamambe ai weye apa anakere ama ine manui. 
\q1  
\v 20 Weramu opamo indati po apa aneno sinane mansarijato tavon no aipapo rai, 
\q2 indati utantavainy no kaumure obo rai tutir kobea ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 21 Maisyare maere kotare muenene wemaisy, 
\q2 vatane nanao tavon indati inta kov indamu no tawano apa ananugo maweso aije rautane ramu. 
\c 50  
\s1 Wade wambeaje Amisye Ai tugaive 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY, Wepirati Amisy Apa vambunine ntiti rave, payao aje no mine so rai, 
\q2 Po vatano mine tename so mansawainde 
\q2 no ranijo wanamuram mansanan nto nanto no varet. 
\q1  
\v 2 Amisy no no Unato Sion, munijo ngkov dave kaije rakivan bintabo rai, 
\q2 Apa vare mujeamo mba dave maisyare uma apa vare wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wama Amisye de muno anamainitu Ai ramu yara payao. 
\q2 Taname muisyeve Ai, mo nuge ranen ti mangkudi panyoambe, 
\q2 muno ovaro rep panyoan nande no akijani. 
\q1  
\v 4 Amisye Po naume warae me mine so me yawainde, 
\q2 indamu Po ana mamaisye rapatimu irati Apa kawasae maija yo raen. 
\q1  
\v 5 Po raura pare: ‘‘Syare vatano sya ura mai nanawamo mansanugande muno maugavere no Rinui, 
\q2 wenawamo vatano wo urairije raokaisyo Rinai arono wo anakotare rameseno Rinai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 6 Naume mo Amisye Apa anuga mamaisye raroron, 
\q2 weye Amisye taune Pirati Po ayao mamaisye rapatimu irati vatan tenambe mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Amisye pare: ‘‘Inya, Sya kawasae Israel weap, wapo Sya ayao raraniv! 
\q2 Risyirati Amisy, wapa Amisye Pi Risy, 
\q2 syare Syo anakangkivane rantuna wasai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Wapo anakotare rameseno Rinai kai, 
\q2 muno wapo ramesen ti ntuna tutir no inamune rai kai, 
\q2 omamo Syo wasanayao dai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye Risyamo inanuga nto irati sapi anya wapo makum ti wapare wapo aunande irati Rinai inta mai ramu, 
\q2 muno kambino anya wapo makume inta mai tavone ramu. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weye maere kotar tenambe ntuna no anate mamo Risyi syave rai, 
\q2 muno sapi ama manui nseo ribuge rakivan ntuna unate rai janyi mamo Risya ma. 
\q1  
\v 11 Insani kotar tenambe ntuna no unate mamo syave rai tavon, 
\q2 muno maere kotar nsyisyaube ntuna no anoko ayamuga rai mainy tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ranivara kayare po rinaveamo, Syo anaisye ranajo wasai ramu, 
\q2 weye mine so muno ama anakotaro ntuna no ama uga rai omamo ta Risyave rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weapare vemo Syo wapa sapi anya apa ine raisyare? 
\q2 Muno weapare vemo Risyo wapa kambine apa mavuge ramanam tavonare? 
\q1  
\v 14 Risyirati Amisy Titi Rave, syare wapo kove raura seno Rinai, 
\q2 omamo maisyare wapa anakotaro wapo rameseno Rinai wemaisy. 
\q2 Muno syare wasayae wapa urairi wadaokaisy nande Rinai rai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Syare wapo rinawain arono wana nsosobe ama uga rai, 
\q2 weamo Risyo wasapaya rai, 
\q2 weti wapo rinararimbe.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 Weramu vatano mamune nanawamo Amisye Po raura nanto mai pare: 
\q1 ‘‘Veanimaibe weapo Sya ananyao raura muno wapayao Sya urairi rai? 
\q2 Wakoe! Mamaisye ramu, weye weapamo waponae Rinai! 
\q1  
\v 17 Weaponae wapo Risya ananyao raraniv 
\q2 muno weapo Sya ayao ravakambe. 
\q1  
\v 18 Ranivara weapo vatano wanaonoambe mansaen, weamo watavondi matavon. 
\q2 Muno wata wasaijaro vatano wo anaerero vauname rangkate matavon. 
\q1  
\v 19 Weapamo wasawa mamo mamun dave, 
\q2 muno wasaunane mamo mansak. 
\q1  
\v 20 Weatuna wapayao tatugadi vayave wapa arakove kaijinta mai, 
\q2 muno wapo wapa arakovo isapintai ingkuja intabo rai aura tantunawi tavon. 
\q1  
\v 21 Arono weapo anakotare so raveamo rituna Syo wasanyanyut bayavea, 
\q2 weti waparemo Risya ana dave mo weapa ramai dako! 
\q1 Weramu soa umba Syo weasanayao rai ije, 
\q2 muno Syo anakangkivane rantuna wasamune rai tutudi ije. 
\q1  
\v 22 Inya, weapirati wasakirive Rinai weap, wadanide, 
\q2 indamu vemo Risyo mangke mo wasarisyi raugaje wasai nora, 
\q2 muno indati vatane inta po wasapaya irati rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 23 Are pirati po kove raura seno Rinai maisyare apa anakotaro po rameseno Rinai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno tavondi Sya unanui mamaisye obo rai, 
\q2 weaveti opamo beaje Rinai toije. 
\q1 Indati Risyirati Amisy, Risyo Sya vambunino Syo vatane mapaya irati kakaije rai rarorono ai.’’ 
\c 51  
\s1 Ayao kakaije raura kakavimbe no Amisye Amun 
\p  
\v 1-2 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Arono anawae Natan de po anayao weye Daud pe Batsyeba me inyaki.\f + \fr 51:1-2 \ft 2Sam. 11:1-12:15\f* Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Sya Amisy, syare naemeno rinai mamaisyo Nya muinyo no tawane rai, 
\q2 syare Nyo sya ana daveti ngkakai raupae irati rinai mamaisyo Nya kovo manakoe rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare Nyo inanuga rarondom indamu sya ana daveti ngkakai mpaya rinai, 
\q2 muno Nyo sya ayao kakai raupae bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye taune syo sya ana idaveti ngkakai raen to, 
\q2 muno sya ayao kakai mamo rinaemendi rai jivae. 
\q1  
\v 6 Nde irati Wibuiny Nai, risyo ayao kakaije rave irati Winai to, 
\q2 muno anakotaro windaena mamun, omamo syo rave to. 
\q1 Weti Winyo mangke raugaje omamo mamaisy, 
\q2 muno Winya ana ndapatimuge mamo moyar. 
\q1  
\v 7 Tugae ivae, ayao kakai no rinai, arono rinano aje kobe we, 
\q2 muno ayao kakai no rinai kobe no arono sya ingkoa ranakeave rinautane we. 
\q1  
\v 8 Tugae, Winya nanuga no irati vatano napirati anuga nsarokire ai, 
\q2 weti syare Nyo ana ratantona ntiti raugasyo ntami rinanuga so rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Syare Nyo sya ayao kakaije raupaeta, wea indati inanuga ngkakavin akato, 
\q2 Syare Nyo inanuga rarondom, wea indati mpoper akato irati kamayo kaipov mpope dave rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 10 Ranivara winyare Nyo sya ayao kakai rapaya, weamo rinanayanambe rave, 
\q2 rinanasine somamo Winyo rakupi rave to, weramu rinananibe akato kai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Vemo Nyo sya ayao kakai raen tutir inya, 
\q2 yara syare sya anakotaro idaveti ngkakai mamo Nyo raupaisy. 
\q1  
\v 12 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo inanuga so ranari ramu mpoper, 
\q2 muno Nyo inanuga ravera nggwanyin indamu ribekere ntindimu Amisye Winai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Syare vemo Nyo inavakano marambe mo rigwaravainyo irati Winai jinya, 
\q2 vemo Nyo Nya Anawayo Vambunine raugav akaore rinaora inya. 
\q1  
\v 14 Syare Nyo rinaveramu rinanayanambe akato, weye Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai to, 
\q2 syare Nyo rinaveramu inanuga rananibe ibeto irati Winai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Wea indati syo Nya ananyao raveano vatano ubeta Nai jewene mansanyao, 
\q2 indamu vatano wo ayao kakai rave umaso usakinav wakare irati Winai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo rinapaya irati mavugo mbe anatuvabe rinaije rai; 
\q2 sya AMISY, Wibuiny irati Amisy Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q2 Weti rikiny rinanayanambe, syo Nya moyare rariri. 
\q1  
\v 17 Sya Akoe, syare Nyo rinasopan da syayao, 
\q2 indamu syo kangkamane raura seo Nai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Yara anakotaro rameseo Naije omamo wimbekedaije ramu; 
\q2 ranivara syo maere\f + \fr 51:18 \ft Maere kotar maisyare sapi, domba, kambine muno kaije mainy.\f* rameseo Nai, wemamo winananibe rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 19 Yara ride irati inanuga rawaumbe rave rautan no Amisye Winui, wemi wimbekedai. 
\q2 Sya Amisy, ride irati inanuga rawaumbe rautan muno risakinavo sya ana daveti ngkakai rai, wemi winanayanambe rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Sya Amisy, syare Nya kove rarorono Sion\f + \fr 51:20 \ft Unato Sion ntami no munijo Yerusalem, weti Yerusalem rawain tavonamo ‘‘Sion.’’\f* rai omamo mamaisyo Winya mbekere rai, 
\q2 syare Nyo ama yano mandamisye rayan kijani akato indamu vemo reama marova usisa ama uga rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 21 Arono naije maere rameseo Nai mamaisyo Nya anaparatote rai indati mo anayanambe raugavo Nai, 
\q2 maere kotare ramer tantename rai, yara inta ransop inya. 
\q2 Muno vatane wo sapi anya amer tavon no Nya tewa orame rai. 
\c 52  
\s1 Amisye Po mangke raugaje irati vatano aarurijate mai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano ananyao, nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai.  
\v 2 Arono Doeg, vatano Edom, de po raura nanto Saul ai pare Daud to nanto no Abimelek apa yavar to.\f + \fr 52:1-2 \ft Ayao mo Doeg aura raen no 1Sam. 21:7, 22:9-19.\f* Daud po apa marova maura seo Amisye Ai no taiso: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Inya, vatano mbambunine winy, 
\q2 veanimaibe masyote tename opamo winararino nya ana ndaveti mamune rai, 
\q2 namirati nyo rave nanto irati vatano Amisye muinyo\f + \fr 52:3 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it hesed\+it* ama ine mare: ‘‘Amisye Apa muinyo Po raurairive no tawano Apa kawasae mai indati Po raveti mamaisy.’’\f* maije mai? 
\q1  
\v 4 Winyamo naunane maisyare vansyerere we, 
\q2 weti nyo aarurijate rator tutir, 
\q2 muno nyo mamune ratantona vatano kaije mai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Winyamo mbekero ana ngkakai rai mo nya mbekero ana ngkove rai rakivan, 
\q2 muno winyamo mbekero aarurijate rai mo nya mbekero ayao tugae rai rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 6 Inya, vatano naunane mansake winy, 
\q2 wimbekero ayao rator ti mo vatane manuga raveti njorame obo rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Weramu indati Amisye Po nya vambunine muno nya tamo ntiti raupaeta ti rakanive ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q2 Po nantaun muno Po nakarimu uje no nya yavare ama uga rai, 
\q2 umba Po naubaisy ti Po nakuvu asyo wene rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Weti vatano ubeta Amisy Ai wo ranyanyut unantoive rai rave, 
\q2 muno wanaikebe vatano mamune so ai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wo raura ware: ‘‘Inya, wapo vatane so aen! 
\q2 Ponae saroro Amisye Aiji. 
\q1 Yara anaveano apa ananugo manui obo ramen, 
\q2 muno saroro apa vambunino po rave vatane mandamisye rai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 10 Weramu risyamo maisyare inyo saitun njayaibe ntubai no Yavaro Amisye rai, 
\q2 weti risyamo rino kovo ngko dave obo rai. 
\q1 Syanave Amisy Apa muinyo no tawane raija ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 11 Risyo kove raura seo Amisye Winai tutir ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 weye anakotaro ngkove mamo Nyo raveti mamaisyo rinai to. 
\q1 Winyamo ngkov dave, weti syo Nya tame raura tutir 
\q2 no Nya kawasae nanawirati matawandi utavondi Nai mansamun. 
\c 53  
\s1 Vatane awa ana udave ngkakainoanive 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano ananyao. Mamaisyo ransyeran ‘‘Mahalat’’ rai. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Vatano wantatukambe wo raura no manuga ware: ‘‘Amisye Pa inta no ramu.’’ 
\q2 Awa ana udave mamo mamun muno ngkakainoanive 
\q2 vatan inta po ana ngkove rave ramu. 
\q1  
\v 3 No munijo Manunggara Amisy tuna Po vatan tenambe mansanyanyut, 
\q2 indamu Po mansaen vatane inta apa ana datantona ntiti no aija rako, 
\q2 muno beaje Aija nene rako. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weramu vatan tenambe makirive Ai, 
\q2 wenao tenambe awa ana udave ngkakainoanive. 
\q1 Vatan inta po ana ngkove rave ramu, 
\q2 vatan inta mamaisye jewen bayave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Amisy pare: ‘‘Vatano awa ana udave mamune so nanawamo 
\q2 awa ana udatantona no maija rako, jewena e? 
\q1 Wenanawamo wo Sya kawasae Syo matayao mave tatugadi, 
\q2 muno wonae usambayambe Rinaiji.’’ 
\q1  
\v 6 Indati vatano mamune umaso ujaniv dave, 
\q2 ujanive somamo mo awa wusyino ujanibe rakivan. 
\q1 Weye Amisye pare Po Israel wapa marova maubaisy muno Po manasine rakupi, 
\q2 wenawamo indati wapo mapinde muno wapo mave samaneve, 
\q2 weye Amisye ponae mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Syare koveamo Amisy Wepi no no Sion de Po Israel mapaya vatano mamune mai! 
\q2 Arono rui Amisy Po kovo ngko dave raugav akare Apa kawasae mai, 
\q2 Weamo indati Yakop apa susyo Israel mananibe. 
\c 54  
\s1 Amisye anajo arono sya marova umarovave rinai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano ananyao. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukinyo rai, wo itari\f + \fr 54:1 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai. \f* raeyan dai.  
\v 2 Arono vatano Sipi inta ude wo raura nanto Saul ai, ware: ‘‘Daud opamo to kokaibe no reama munijo Sipi.’’\f + \fr 54:2 \ft 1Sam. 23:19, 26:1\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo inapaya irati kakai raijo Nya vambunine rai, 
\q2 Nyo patimu moyare raugaje rinai Nya vambunine rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo sya ana danajo raraniv, 
\q2 namarikoame rasakinavo sya ana idatore so rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye vatano mararine ubesea ware umarovave rinai, 
\q2 vatano sivuiny dave ware wo rinaubaisy, 
\q2 onawamo wo Amisye winatantona ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Weramu tugae, Amisy Winyi Nyo inayaranande; 
\q2 Sya Akoe, Winyirati Nyo sopambe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Koveamo sya marova awa ana udave ti mamune mamo nsakinav akare ra mo taune makep, 
\q2 syare Nyo maupaeta ra makanive weye winteto Nya urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Sya AMISY, inanuga rananibe syo maere rameseo Winai, 
\q2 muno syo kove raura seo Winai weye Winyamo ngkov dave. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye Winyi Nyo inapaya irati anakotaro nsosobe ama uga rai, 
\q2 muno inami ntami sya marova maijo Nyo mapinde. 
\c 55  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu no wansaora irati marova mai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano ananyao. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukinyo rai, wo itari\f + \fr 55:1 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai\ft .\f* raeyan dai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, syare namarikoame rasakinavo sya sambaya rai, 
\q2 vemo winakirive sya ana danajo ore so rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare Nyo rinaraniv muno Nyo sya ana danajo ore so ravera mamaisy! 
\q2 Rinanuga nseo majeve muno syoyov weye rino ana nsosobe rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye sya marova ugwain akoeve ware wo inatondobe 
\q2 muno vatano mamune wo inatawanto. 
\q1 Muno wo rinansewabe, 
\q2 muno upari ti umarovave rinai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Inanuga so ntutar, 
\q2 weye yanivo wene mo inakukupi ti inanakea uga ntararai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Yanive mo inaveti tutar, 
\q2 ijanivo wene mo inatatuv asyo. 
\q1  
\v 7 Weti syo ratantona syare: ‘‘Ranivara sya pepake no rinai, 
\q2 maisyare insani puname\f + \fr 55:7 \fq puname \ft anigwano ‘‘merpati’’ ai.\f* amaisy datire, 
\q2 ibadirir ti to syo munijo ntanamanine rakani. 
\q1  
\v 8 Tugae, weamo ibadirir ti to nggwaravainy dave ije, 
\q2 indamu ito no no anoko kanen anamainitu rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Syavave syo varoro inamamavube rai rakani, 
\q2 risarar rito kokaibe irati marova awa panyoano 
\q2 maisyare ovar akoe tipu ti po inarone wemaisye rai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Sya Akoe, syare Nyo sya marova maveramu wananepabe, Nyo awa ana udatore rangkaunanive, 
\q2 weye syo raen no muni so maugaje nsivuiny muno wo arare rave. 
\q1  
\v 11 Namane rinit wo munije umaso rakijani, ntuna ntoabe yano orame ama vone rai, 
\q2 muno munije ama uga rai, inta wanakakaive muno wo ivuinye rave tutir. 
\q1  
\v 12 No muni so ama uga raita, wo siurije muno ana nsosobe raugavere rai, 
\q2 wo vatane matawanto muno wo maponae anyi no pasari. 
\q1  
\v 13 Ranivara sya marova mawakea vivibe rinai, 
\q2 weamo inatawandi rai. 
\q1 Ranivara vatano manuga mamuno rinai nanawirati mararin ware wo rinakivan, 
\q2 weamo rito no marambe mai yaje. 
\q1  
\v 14 Weramu sya arakovo imanivuvive winy, 
\q2 imanya kava muno syanave nai rave, 
\q2 winyirati nyo inave tatugadi. 
\q1  
\v 15 Wusyinoeamo ingkavave, 
\q2 muno inta kava no Yavar Amisy no vatano wanui awa yasyin. 
\q1  
\v 16 Koveamo wene mo sya marova maunto papabe\f + \fr 55:16 \ft Bil. 16:31-33\f* tenambe, 
\q2 mo mansaunto jayaibe asyo no amani. 
\q1 Weye mansanuga mamune obo mirati no mansai, 
\q2 no awa yavaruga. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Weramu risyamo syo Amisye awain, 
\q2 muno indati AMISY Po rinapaya irati sya marova mai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Namane rinit, syanonae akoeve muno syoyov, 
\q2 muno Opamo Po sya oyove raraniv. 
\q1  
\v 19 Sya marova udaran ti ude umarovave rinai, 
\q2 muno maroyaro rinai, 
\q2 weramu Amisye Po inapaya mai ti rino kovo saumane rai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Amisye Opirati be akarive no nugo pitawarowe, 
\q2 indati Po sya ana danajo raraniv muno Po mapinde. 
\q1 Weye wonae usakinavo awa ana udaveti ngkakai raiji, 
\q2 muno wo Amisye asyanive ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 Sya arakovo rimanivuvive umawe sarirae ti be marovave 
\q2 apa arakovo wusyinoeamo ube arakobe mansai jakato, 
\q2 po apa urairijo mo maokaisye rakanyoandi. 
\q1  
\v 22 Awa mamo manavan dave, 
\q2 weramu anuga mamo kakai mi po ratantona rai. 
\q1 Apa ana datore mamo mani nsaawa rai rave, 
\q2 weramu omamo maisyare weyamo po rave inaugake wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Nya anakotaro nanuga mamauno rai mamo ndaugave to no AMISY Nui, 
\q2 weamo indati Po sopambe nai.\f + \fr 55:23 \ft 1Ptr. 5:7\f* 
\q1 Weye vatano ubeto Ai nanawamo, 
\q2 Po mapaya ra awa marova wo mapinde jewen. 
\q1  
\v 24 Yara vatano maneme nijam 
\q2 muno wayarurijabe nanawamo 
\q2 indati awa tume raotar aje tumaimbe. 
\q1 Weye sya Amisy, indati Nyo mapinto atem mamai raito. 
\q1 Yara risyamo syanave Winai. 
\c 56  
\s1 Inanaveano Amisye amen arono sya marova wo inawatan 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Masmur po ratoe, arono vatano Pilistin wo aijar no munijo Gat.\f + \fr 56:1 \ft 1Sam. 21:10-15\f* Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Insani punam no no inyo akoe tarbantin\f + \fr 56:1 \fq tarbantin \ft omamo inyo akoe mo wayane ramaisy, vatano Israel wanave rai, weye ware vambunine inta no rai.\f* no waravaimbe rai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 weye vatane wo rinataka doyadi, 
\q2 masyote anteter umarovave rinai muno wo inatawanto. 
\q1  
\v 3 Masyote anteter sya marova wo inataka doyadi tutir, 
\q2 vatano umarovave rinai umaso wanui rave. 
\q1  
\v 4 Arono rui rijaniv, 
\q2 risyamo inanaveano Wibuiny namen. 
\q1  
\v 5 Rikangkamambe Amisy Ai Apa urairi rai, 
\q2 Amisye obo pirati inanaveano amen, weti ijanive ramu. 
\q2 Weti vatano are pirati indati po ana ngkakai inta raveti nande rinai jakato? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Masyote anteter sya marova wo sya ana datore rangkaunanive, 
\q2 wo kakai ratantona rinai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 7 Onawamo ukaokaibe ti wo inaman, 
\q2 inawanto no rui ruijamo wo inanyanyuti, 
\q2 muno wo varoro mamaisye rakani indamu wo inaubaisy. 
\q1  
\v 8 Awa ana udave ti ngkakai mamo indati upaya ama mangke rai rako? 
\q2 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo Nya pari mangke veano vatano wanave Nai jewene mapinde. 
\q1  
\v 9 Masyoto sya marova wo rinawatambewe mainyamo Winyo raen muno Nyo rator, 
\q2 inami ngkaru ma manui mamo Winyi Nyo raen.\f + \fr 56:9 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘syare Nyo inami ngkaru raugasya tenambe no karoa ugami rai.’’ Pemasmur po raura tai maisy weye beker pare Amisye Po apa siurijo manakoe raen.\f* 
\q2 Ana nande rinaive umaso mainyamo Nyo ratoevea rako? 
\q1  
\v 10 Arono syo winawain weamo sya marova wansuk, 
\q2 weye syo raen tugae, Amisy Nyo marimbe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Amisye obo pirati rikangkamambe Apa urairi rai, 
\q2 tugae, AMISY, obo pirati rikangkamambe Apa urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Amisye obo pirati inanaveano amen, weti rijanive ramu. 
\q2 Weti vatano are pirati indati po ana ngkakai inta raveti nande rinai jakato? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Sya Amisy, sya urairi syo raokae nande Winai mamo indati syo raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 muno syo anakotare rameseo Winai, mbe rarorombe syo kove raura seo Nai.\f + \fr 56:13 \ft Israel awa koane somamo raura kakavimbe no Imamat 7:12. \f* 
\q1  
\v 14 Weye Winyo rinapaya irati wene rai to, 
\q2 Winyi Nyo rinayaranande weti marova wo inapinde jewen. 
\q1 Wirati syanya no mine so, no Amisye Winui, 
\q2 no irati Nya varo kov mo rinaveti rijayaisye rai. 
\c 57  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu aemeno wansai arono marova wo wansawatan 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Masmur po ratoe, arono Saul po awatan ti sarar to no no tinda ama uga.\f + \fr 57:1 \ft 1Sam. 24\f* Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Vemo wapo vatane maupaisy inya.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, naemeno rinai, syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 weye Winyirati inamamavube Nai. 
\q1 Rigaugambe Nai jao ntoa ana nde ti mare mo inakupi so nde nto ra rakanive rati, 
\q2 maisyare mangkuere tuvane gaugambe irati akoe ama pepak ate rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syo Amisy Titi Rave awain, 
\q2 syo Amisy anajo indamu Apa bekere mirati mamaisyo rinai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Nai Manunggara, Po rinasopan muno Po rinapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 Po vatano wo rinatawanto mapinde. 
\q1 Amisye pamo teto Apa urairi rai tutir, 
\q2 muno Apa muinye mamo no tawano rinai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Rino no no sya marova awa yasyine rai, 
\q2 onawamo maisyare make sivuiny\f + \fr 57:5 \fq make sivuiny \ft ranigwano ‘‘singa’’ rai.\f* wo vatane maubaisy wemaisy. 
\q1 Matomokane nsiu dave maisyare weyam muno ato nsasiu dave wemaisy, 
\q2 muno mansaunane mamo mo inaveti inanuga njoram. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya Amisy, syare Nya ntiti rave raroron no naume warae, 
\q2 muno Nya kovo ntiti raroron no mine tename so rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Sya marova manatantonave rinai, maisyare wo isyeane ratugar ti mo inamane wemaisy, 
\q2 weti inanuga mamaun. 
\q1 Wo ateme rawae ti mo inaman no sya unanui idaito rai, 
\q2 weramu taune nawirati wakata utatae asyo rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Inanuga so ntindimu sya Amisye Winai, inanuga so ntindimu Nai. 
\q2 Syare rikinyo ransyerane rai, rikangkamambe Nai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Inya, syare ibeseo, syo itari anakoe muno itari mamaune\f + \fr 57:9 \fq itari anakoe muno itari mamaune \ft ranigwano ‘‘gambus’’ muno ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* raeyan, 
\q2 rikiny no arono akane mare ntipu kobe. 
\q1  
\v 10 Sya Akoe, Winyirati syare syo kove raura seo Nai no vatan tenambe so awa yasyin, 
\q2 syare rikinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo Winai no susye kotaro mine so awa yasyin. 
\q1  
\v 11 Weye Nya muinyo no tawane mamo ntitito no naume warae, 
\q2 muno winteto Nya urairi rai mamo nto rave ti mo kamure rakivan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Sya Amisy, syare Nya ntiti rave raroron no naume warae, 
\q2 muno Nya kovo ntiti raroron no mine tename so rai. 
\c 58  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po mangke raugaje akari mamune mai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Masmur po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Vemo wapo vatane maupaisy inya.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Inya, akari weap, wapa ana wadapatimu mamo mamaisyo Amisye Apa ananyao rai jivae e? 
\q2 Mangke wapo rapatimu irati vatane mai mamo moyar ivae e? 
\q1  
\v 3 Jewena! Weapa ana wadatantona no wasanuga wato mamo ana ngkakainoanive obo mi no wasai, 
\q2 muno wapo vatane manepati tatugadi vayave no munije so. 
\q1  
\v 4 Akari umaso nanawamo arono mano aje we ndea naisoamo makirive Amisye Ai, 
\q2 muno aarurijate obo mirati no mai arono mansano aje we ndea naiso. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wenanawamo mamun dave maisyare tawae mamune ramaisy, 
\q2 muno wonae wo ananyao raranivi, 
\q2 maisyare tawae mamuno ngkokobe kakai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weti wenawamo maisyare tawae mo vatano pare danyao da ngkokobe apa anamote raranive jewen, 
\q2 muno mo vatano po marandine raugaje rai aranive jewene wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo mapinde maisyare singa apa atomokano nsiu radaute wemaisy! 
\q2 AMISY, syare Nyo mapinde maisyare singa kamuramo usivuiny dave awa matomokane rapapatine wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare koveamo akari mamun umaso maumandita maisyare mana ama wayo nsaonto ti raumandi wemaisy, 
\q2 muno syare koveamo wenawamo mayondi maisyare insumaijo mayone wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 Syare koveamo wenawamo maumandita maisyare kangkinu baibindi, sanun ti pewene wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare arikainyo kakai no akoeya ranobon arono avaki rainy weti po vare raene jewen. 
\q1  
\v 10 Avave mangke raugaje mai maisyare anomano ntuna tanamo mbadurure rai weti kavuratawe mamoan dave. 
\q2 Syare avave da maupaeta maisyare ininai ugo ngkanen weti ovare damawisyamo rakaniveta. 
\q1  
\v 11 Indati vatano ubeta Amisye Ai nanawamo manayanambe arono wo raen Amisye Po mangke rasakinavo vatano mamune mai. 
\q2 Umba vatano kove wo vatano mamune awa mavu ratakadi muno usuijo rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Indati vatane wo raura ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Tugae ivae, vatano ubeta Amisye Ai nanawamo Amisye Po kove ratayao mai. 
\q2 Muno Amisye no tugae ivae, Wepi Po ayao mamaisye rapatimu vatano mine so mai.’’ 
\c 59  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu darino wansaora 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Masmur po ratoe, arono Saul po apa naite matutir ude wo Daud anyanyuti no apa yavar indamu wo aubaisy.\f + \fr 59:1 \ft 1Sam. 19:11-17\f* Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Vemo wapo vatane maupaisy inya.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo inapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo inayan kijani irati vatano ubesea ti umarovave rinaije mai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare Nyo inapaya irati vatano awa ana udave mamune mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo inapaya irati vatano maneme nijame mai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya AMISY, risyamo sya ana dave inta ngkakai ramu muno sya ayao kakai meweno rinai. 
\q2 Weramu Nyo raen! Sya marova ukaokaibe ti wo inaman, ware wo inaubaisy, 
\q2 vatano usansinao wanugan ti maroyaro rinai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Risyamo syo ana inta ravera ngkakai ramu, 
\q2 weramu onawirati wavave wanatatayaube ra wo rinaubaisy. 
\q2 Mbeseo ra Nyo rinaen! Syare Nyo inapaya irati mai. 
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY, Winyirati Amisy Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti, 
\q2 Winyirati Amisy vatano Israel ubeaje Nai. 
\q1 Mbeseo ra Nyo mangke raugaje susyo wanave Nai jewene mai, 
\q2 vatano mamun nanawirati wo awa arakove mansamavune nawamo vemo wimbekobe mai nora. 
\q1  
\v 7 Arono namandi, onawamo wakare akato, 
\q2 muno wanya wo muni rakijani, 
\q2 maisyare make karirimbe wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 8 Nyo mansaen, onawamo wo vatane maura tantunawi obo mirati mawa mpaato rai tutir, 
\q2 awa ana udatore mamo nsansinao dave maisyare omake wemaisy, 
\q2 weye wo ratantona ware awa ana udatore mamo Amisye Po mansanaun dai ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Weramu AMISY, Winyamo nyugoeno mansai, 
\q2 muno Nyo susyo wanave Nai jewene mansakekebe tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 10 Winyirati sya vambunine nsawa Nai, inanaveano namen, 
\q2 weye Winyirati sya yano oram ntiti no rinaora. 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya Amisye Apa muinye no tawano rinai, weti indati Opamo de teto rinatavon, 
\q2 sya Amisy indati Po inaveti inami ntami sya marova mai anawadive arono Po mataopon. 
\q1  
\v 12 Vemo Nyo mansaubaisyo usyeta kobe inya, indamu sya kawasae wo mansaeno Nyo mangke raugaje maiji, 
\q2 yara Nyo mampusyeko Nya vambunine rai. 
\q2 Sya Akoe, Winyirati ndarino reansaora, syare Nyo mapinde. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weye onawamo ayao kakai obo mirati no mawa rai, 
\q2 weti koveamo umararine mamo maisyare isyeano taune wakare ti usaawa rai wemaisy. 
\q2 Weye onawamo wanaamatambe vatane mai vayave muno wayarurijabe. 
\q1  
\v 14 Weti Amisy, syare Nya pari mangke mo maupaeta, 
\q2 Nyo maupaeta ra makanive. 
\q1 Indamu vatan tenambe wo raen, Winyirati mbe akarive Israel mai, 
\q2 muno muni tename so rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 15 Arono namandi, onawamo wakare akato, 
\q2 wo kakai ratantona, ti wanya wo muni rakijani, 
\q2 maisyare make karirimbe wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 16 Wanya umandayan wo anaisye rakani, 
\q2 ranivara uman dainy weamo ukaririmbe. 
\q1  
\v 17 Yara risyamo Nya vambunine mirati rikinyo rai, 
\q2 muno awatan ngkove anteteramo Nya muinyo no tawane mirati rikinyo ransyeran marinsawane raijo rai. 
\q1 Weye Winyirati yano oram ntiti no rinaora, 
\q2 ti inamamavube Nai arono rino irati ana nsosobe rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Sya Amisy, Winyirati sya vambunine nsawa Nai, 
\q2 rikiny syo nararimbe. 
\q1 Weye Winyirati yano oram ntiti no rinaora, 
\q2 Sya Amisy, Winyirati Nya muinye no tawan. 
\c 60  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po anasineko raunande wansai no marova rai 
\p  
\v 1-2 Daud apa ransyerano Masmur po ratoe, indamu mbe ananyaobe. Arono be marovave vatano Aram una no Mesopotamia muno Soba mai, muno arono Yoap po vatano Edome ribuge abusyin eane jirum (12.000) maubaisy, no Kaivo Mana Nsakam.\f + \fr 60:1-2 \ft Kaive som ama garame ntapekano rai, weti vatane wo rawae ti wo raugav.\f*\f + \fr 60:1-2 \ft 2Sam. 8:3-5, 10:6-18; 1Taw. 18:3-5\f* Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Aepare ama ug, mbe urairive rai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Sya Amisy, winseambe reansai muno nakirive reansai ti reama marova wo reansapinde, 
\q2 wimpari mangkebe reansai. 
\q1 Weramu reamare Nyo anakotare raveramu ngkovo reansai, 
\q2 maisyare arono wusyine wemaisy akato. 
\q1  
\v 4 Winyo marova ratande reansai ti mo reansakupi weti reanjaniv, 
\q2 maisyare mungki ravari ti kopa mpaporare wemaisy. 
\q1 Weti reamare Nyo anakotaro no reama munije rai raveramu ngkov akato. 
\q1  
\v 5 Winyo Nya kawasae reansaveti reana irati siuri mangke rai, 
\q2 Winyo siuri ratande ti mo reansavea reansamune nsadirae rai, maisyare vatane umaeno awije rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weramu vatano wo nasyanive nawamo Winyo tubino mo varoro mansamamavube rai rarorono mai, 
\q2 indamu upaya irati ato nsasiu rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Reamare Nyo reama ana ndanajo raraniv, 
\q2 muno Nyo reansapaya irati reama marova mai nanemo vambunine rai, 
\q2 indamu vatano winanuga no mai upaya irati kakai rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Arono Amisye Po kopa Kanaan raosoro vatano Israel mai, payao no Apa tuna ri ndandinit, 
\q2 pare: ‘‘Rinanayanambe ti syare Syo kopa Sikem raosor. 
\q2 Muno Syo kaivo Sukot rataun, indamu Syo raosor.\f + \fr 60:8 \ft Sikem no no mana Yordan ama ranijo varet, muno Sukot no no ama ranijo wanamuram, kopa umaso ibe rarorombe munijo Israel ama mantamito rai tenambe.\f* 
\q1  
\v 9 Kopa Gilead muno Manasye\f + \fr 60:9 \ft Gilead muno Manasye \ft no no mana Yordan ama ranijo wanamuram.\f* omamo Risya ma. 
\q2 Epraim\f + \fr 60:9 \ft Munijo Epraim omirati naito anaanive una ri we, yara munijo Yehuda omirati akari titi Israel no ri we.\f* omirati maisyare sapeo besi no inakari raora wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Yehuda wemirati Sya isyo akari titi raugaje nteto rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weramu munijo Moab\f + \fr 60:10 \ft Aneme so ama ine mare Amisye Apa ura kopa Moab muno Edom muno Pilistea rai tenambe, weramu ponae rai weye awa kawasae wanave Ai jewen.\f* omamo maisyare unggano inajo rarondomo rai mije. 
\q2 Muno Edom omamo inajo kokome ramauto ntami rai weti Sya ura rai. 
\q2 Muno rigwain inananibe weye syanasineko muni Pilistea rai.’’\f + \fr 60:10 \ft Ayao so ama ine mare vatano susye mandeije so nao–Moab, Edom, muno Pilistea–onawamo indati Amisye Po mapinde tenambe indamu munijo Israel mbe akarive mai.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Arepi indati po inaugave to no munijo Edom? 
\q2 Arepi tavono rinai ti rito no munijo ama yano orame ntindimu ratuije rai? 
\q1  
\v 12 Sya Amisy, Winyamo ntavondi reansai ramu ge? 
\q2 Muno naijaro reama naite matavon da wata marova rai ramu ge? 
\q1  
\v 13 Nde Nyo sopambe reansai inda reamo marova mapinde, 
\q2 weye vatan bayave wo sopambe reansai mamo mamaisye ramu. 
\q1  
\v 14 Ranivara Amisy wintavono reansai, weamo reambambunin dave, 
\q2 weye Winyi Nyo reama marova matakarasyo. 
\c 61  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po akari titi ayaranande 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukinyo rai, wo itari\f + \fr 61:1 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* raeyan dai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, syo winawain ti syare Nyo rinaraniv, 
\q2 syare Nyo sya ana danajo ore ranaun! 
\q1  
\v 3 Nai munijo nggwaravainy syo Amisye winawain, 
\q2 weye inanuga so mayondi rave. 
\q2 Syare Nyo rinaugav to no unato oram ntiti rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye tugae, Winyirati syakaore gaugambe Nai, 
\q2 maisyare soero mbambunin no rinaora irati sya marova mai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syare koveamo ride tutir no Nya randumo sambaya\f + \fr 61:5 \fq randumo sambaya \ft somamo mo wama randumo no no naiso ramaisye ramu. Yara Israel awa randumo no no ratuije mamo wo maero domba muno kambine awa kea wemi wo rave randumbe, omamo Akari Titi Daud wepi po ransano vayave ra usambayambe rai ma. 2Sam. 6:12-17\ft \f* raija ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 indamu rino mariraave no kovo saumane rai, 
\q2 maisyare mangkuere tuvane gaugambe akoe ama pepak ate rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Tugae, sya urairi syo raokae Amisy Winai mamo Nyo raraniv to, 
\q2 muno Nya kovo Nyo ratayao mamo Nyo raunande rinai to, 
\q2 namirati Nyo raunande vatan tenambe wo nasyanive mai indamu awa ura rai tawan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Syare Nyo reama akari titi ayaranande indamu apa matame nggwaravainy, 
\q2 muno apa be akarive raugakaje apa susyo miridi nto mai indamu utantuna rai tutir kobe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Amisy, syare reama akari titi apa be akarive ntoa nuge nuganui no winanem ate rai. 
\q2 Winyamo Nya muinye no tawan muno winteto Nya urairi rai, 
\q2 weti syare Nyo reama akari titi ayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weamo indati sya urairi syo raokaisyo Amisy Winai to mamo masyote anteter syo raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 muno indati rikinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo Nya tame rai tutir. 
\c 62  
\s1 Syanave Amisye Ai, weamo rino mariraave 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati Yedutun ai,\f + \fr 62:1 \fq Yedutun: \ft 1Taw. 16:41\f* wepirati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Amisye obo pirati syararaijo Ai, weamo sya jugara no saumane rai, 
\q2 Wepirati Po inapaya irati sya marova mai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Amisye obo Pirati maisyare unato oram inamamavube rai ti ripaya marova aneme rai, 
\q2 Opamo maisyare yano oram ntiti mo inayan kijani ti sya marova wo inapinde jewen. 
\q1  
\v 4 Inya, wea tenambe wamarovave rinaija ntoa nandui rati umba wasaneme mpayawa? 
\q2 Wapo inanepatija ngko to, syare ikakai vayave kobe. 
\q2 Sya vambunine mewen to, maisyare usuko marir muno yano mare mbari kobe. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wenawamo ubekedaije mamo ta ware wo sya tamo ntiti rapinde, 
\q2 wenawamo ta ubekero waarurijabea. 
\q1 Wenawamo mawa mamo mo kove ranajo, 
\q2 weramu mansanuga ma kakai mi wo ranajo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Amisye obo Pirati syararaijo Ai, weamo sya jugara no saumane rai, 
\q2 weye obo Pirati syanave tindimuve Ai, weamo rino mariraave. 
\q1  
\v 7 Amisye obo Pirati maisyare unato oram inamamavube rai ti ripaya marova aneme rai, 
\q2 Opamo maisyare yano oramo ntiti mo inayan kijani ti, sya marova wo inapinde jewen. 
\q1  
\v 8 Amisye Wepi Po rinapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 muno Wepi bewaramo sya tame ntiti. 
\q2 Amisye Opirati darino rinaora, muno Opamo maisyare unato oram inamamavube rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Inya, sya kawasae weap, syare wapanave tugaive Amisye Ai masyote anteter, 
\q2 muno anakotaro rui vayave wadantotobe no wasanuga raneka no Amun, 
\q2 weye Amisye Opirati darino wansaora. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Vatano awa tame maje nanawamo maisyare ovar bayave weti wansaroro mai kakai, 
\q2 vatano wakokoe titi nanawamo awa vambunine mamo aarurijate bo ma ti wansaroro mai kakai. 
\q1 Ranivara vatano maisyare so nanawamo awa vambunine rataunamo\f + \fr 62:10 \fq rataunamo: \ft ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘katijo mo mangke raroron.’’\f* maisyare ovar bayave, 
\q2 weye awa vambunine inta no mai ra wo kove raunande ramu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Vemo wasaroro romano wapo vatane mantitidi rai indamu wo raunande rai jinya, 
\q2 vemo wasanaveano ananugo wapo rantauno vatane maora rai nora. 
\q1 Ranivara wapa ananuge nseo ti manui rave kobe, 
\q2 weamo vemo wasanuga no obo rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 12 Syo Amisye anauno payaode intabo, 
\q2 omamo manuije inta mi syo ranauno Ai to: 
\q1 Tugae, Amisy Wibuiny irati mbambunin dave, 
\q1  
\v 13 muno tugae, Akoe, Winya muinyo no tawane manya tutir. 
\q1 Nyo kakai, kove, rasakinav akananto vatane nanentabo mai mamaisyo awa ana udave rai. 
\c 63  
\s1 Sya jugara bekero Amisye Winai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe arono no no anoko ngkanembe maninimbe munijo Yehuda.\f + \fr 63:1 \ft Daud kokaibe no anoko ngkanembe arono akarijo titi Saul pare po aubaisy. 1Sam. 23:14\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Amisy, Winyirati sya Amisy, 
\q2 rinanuga no Nai rave ti syo nakani. 
\q1 Sya jugara bekero Amisye Winai maisyare vatano awa ngkamandi ti bekero mana rai. 
\q2 Inanasine tename so mayondi ti mbekero Nai maisyare mino mana ngkanen dai weti mbekero mana nde rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weti ribekero syore mararai no Amisye Winui, no Nya ntuna ri ndandinit rai, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya vambunin muno Nya kovo ntiti raen. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syo Amisye winararimbe weye Nya muinyo no tawane\f + \fr 63:4 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it hesed\+it* ama ine ratoe tumaimbe naiso mare: ‘‘muinye no tawan.’’ Ama ino manakoe mare: ‘‘Amisye Apa muinye muno Apa anakotaro Po raurairive ti no tawan tutiro Apa kawasae Israel mansai mamo Po raveti mamaisy.’’\f* mamo manakoe, 
\q2 yara taune sya kovo mine somamo mamaun bayavea. 
\q1  
\v 5 Maisyare omaiti, risyo winararimbe no arono ta rikove so, 
\q2 rinaneme raijaseo syo Nya tame rawain. 
\q1  
\v 6 Rinanuga so ranayanambe, igwain syo Amisy naijaseo titive muno syo nararimbe. 
\q1 Sya jugara anayanambe Amisye Winai 
\q2 maisyare vatano anayanambe weye po maero manavan dave raisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Arono syaje niki no sya vasyoto niki ri inaemeno Amisye Winai, 
\q2 namano waravainyowe syo natantonave rave. 
\q1  
\v 8 Rikinyo ransyerane rai inananibe, weye Amisye Nyo inayaranande mamo ngko dave, 
\q2 maisyare mangkuero mo ama tuvane rarau wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 Risyo Amisye winaijaro matuve rave, 
\q2 weye Winya nanem ngkove\f + \fr 63:9 \fq nanem ngkove: \ft ama ine mare Amisye Apa vambunin.\f* wemi mo rinasopan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Weramu vatano ware wo rinaubaisye wenawamo 
\q2 indati ugwenen ti wo vatano ugwenen to awa una rije raronto. 
\q1  
\v 11 Onawamo ugweneno marova ama uga rai, 
\q2 muno awa koke ntuna ti mbe anaibeo make anate mansai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Yara risy akari titi vatano Israel, rinanayanambe weye Amisye Po inayaranande; 
\q2 muno vatano wo Amisye Apa tame veano awa urairije raokaisye nawamo umananibe ukangkamambe Ai. 
\q2 Yara vatano wo aarurijate ratore nawamo indati Amisye Po mawa rakuvu. 
\c 64  
\s1 Mangke Amisye Po raugaje vatano mamune maijem 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo inaranivo sya ana danajo no arono rino ana nsosobe raije so rai, 
\q2 syare Nyo inapaya irati sya marova syo masyaniv dave so mai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare Nyo inangkokaibe irati vatano mamun wanyinyaube rinai so mai, 
\q2 no rinaora irati vatano mamun manatantonave kakai rai mai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Mansaunane mamo nsansinao dave maisyare omake wemaisy, 
\q2 muno ayao wo ratore mamo mamun dave maisyare ato nsiu wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 5 No varoro ukaokaibe ri we, wo vatano ayao kakai meweno mai makekebe, 
\q2 awa ayao mamo wo rantotobe ramu maisyare ato wo veano mansaivuiny papabe wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Awa ubekero mamune obo mirati wo raijaro matuve, 
\q2 wanugan ti wayao indamu wo aviri ratugaro maninimbe, 
\q2 wo raura ware: ‘‘Vatane inta po wansaen dai ramu.’’ 
\q1  
\v 7 Onawamo manatantonave ana mamaisye jewene rai, 
\q2 wo raura ware: ‘‘Ana reamanyinyaube rai mamo reamanatatayaube raija mamai dave to.’’ 
\q2 Vatane awa ana wo ratantona no manuga mamo vatano kaijinta unanta rai kakai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Weramu Amisye Po parijo mangke veano matapo, 
\q2 muno Po maivuiny ti kavuratawe utaopon. 
\q1  
\v 9 Ayao kakai taune wo ratore ama mangke rasakinav akare mai, 
\q2 vatan tenambe wo mansaen makarije rangkiki mai, weye mangke raude mai mpanyoan dave. 
\q1  
\v 10 Naije kobe vatan tenambe ujani dave, 
\q2 ti wo Amisye Apa ana dave so ratantonave inda unanta rai, 
\q2 muno wo Apa ana dave ravovo vatano kaijinta mai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Vatano ubeta AMISY Ai umananibe Apa ana dave rai, 
\q2 muno wakata mansamamavube Ai. 
\q1 Vatano manuga nsarokiro Amisye Ai nawamo wo ararimbe. 
\c 65  
\s1 Kove raura seo Amisye Ai weye muinyo wansai ti wama nawaisye ama ine manui 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Ransyeran. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Reama Amisy, reangkakamambe Nai no munijo Sion omamo mamaisy, 
\q2 muno reama urairijo reandaokae nande Winaije mamo reandaveti mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 3 Indati vatan tenambe ude Nai, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Nyo anakotaro reandanajo raveti mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Arono rui reama ayao kakai manakoe ti mangkeo reansai rave, 
\q2 weamo Winyirati Nyo rapaya irati reansai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kove ngkov irati vatano taune Nyo matayao terave mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo mawain ti ude umararai indamu una no Nya Yavar! 
\q1 Reaman irati Nya kove rai no Nya Yavare ama uga, 
\q2 no Nya Yavaro ndandinit. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Winyo reama ana ndanajo raunande reansai mbe anaanibe rave mamaisyo Nya moyare rai, 
\q2 Winyirati Amisy Nyo reansapaya anakotaro ngkakai rai. 
\q1 Winyirati susye kotaro mine so mansanaveano namen, 
\q2 ti muija nto nupatimu nggwaravainye rai janyi muno munije ama mamarane rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 7 Winyo unate raveseo nsayae tindimuve irati Nya vambunine rai, 
\q2 mbe rarorombe Winyi Nya vambunine manakoe rave. 
\q1  
\v 8 Winyi Nyo mayane ama rarene muno ranauni mpanyoane rapamo akasyo ti ntanamanin, 
\q2 muno Nyo susye kotaro usea maugananave mapamo tavon. 
\q1  
\v 9 Maisyare omaiti vatan tenambe mine tename so 
\q2 wo Nya ana ndaveti mbe anaanibe umaso raen ti ujaniv. 
\q1 Nai ranijo muram ti nto no ranijo varet, 
\q2 Winyo anayanambe raude mai ti ukiny mananibe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Wimbekobe kopa so rai, muno Nyo maruge raugaje rai ti anare kotare ama ine raivuve. 
\q1 Amisy Winya mana njam tutir,\f + \fr 65:10 \ft Vatano Israel wo rakarae ware mana inta njam no Manunggara, omi Amisye Po raveti mbe maruve maje no mine vone so rai.\f* 
\q2 Winyo anare raveti ntubai ti ntuna mawebe vatane mai, 
\q2 tugae, Winyo ratayao ti mawe dave. 
\q1  
\v 11 Winyo maruge raugaje ti nsaakopo awa kopa wo rakarore rai janyi, 
\q2 muno Nyo mana raugaje ti nsaakopo kopa ngkanembe rai. 
\q1 Winyo maruge veano kopa ngkarendene randami ti ngkov dave, 
\q2 Nyo kove raugaje anare rai ti ama tuba ngkarimu sen muno ntubai ngkov dave. 
\q1  
\v 12 Nya kove omirati tume yanteteramo wo awa anamuke ama mane ranugane manui rave, 
\q2 munije rui mirati Nyo ratakaramo, anakotaro ngkove ntairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Ama anoke mainyamo ntairijo insumai njayaibe rai, 
\q2 papukame ama anakotaro ntubai rai mo vatane maveti manayanambe rai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Anoko insumai njayaibe umaso mamo maero kambin muno domba ntairi rai, 
\q2 muno ama pate mainyamo kasyambere mo ratatuv, 
\q2 weti papukame, anoke muno papate mananibe muno ukinyo ama kove rai. 
\c 66  
\s1 Kinyo ransyerane raijo Amisye Ai Apa ana dave rai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran Masmur. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1 Inya, vatano mine tename weap, wasananibe wagwain wapo Amisye abumbundi! 
\q1  
\v 2 Wakiny wapo Apa tame raijaseo titive, 
\q2 wapo abumbundi ransyeran kangkamane rai! 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare wapo raura to Amisye Ai, wapare: ‘‘Tugae, Nya ana ndave mamo mbe anaanibe rave! 
\q2 Nya vambunine manakoe rave, ti Nya marova ujaniv utarurandi no Namun. 
\q1  
\v 4 Vatano mine tename so ude ubeaje Nai, 
\q2 ukiny ukangkamambe Nai, 
\q2 ukiny ukangkamambe Nya tame rai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Wade ra wapo Amisye Apa ana dave raen, 
\q2 Apa ana dave vatane mansai umaso mamo mbe anaanibe. 
\q1  
\v 6 Purarijato mayane rai ti yasyine ngkanen,\f + \fr 66:6 \ft Kel. 14:21-22\f* 
\q2 muno Po mana raotar\f + \fr 66:6 \ft Yosua 3:14-17\f* ti reama aneno sinane wanya rainanta. 
\q1 Maisyare omaiti wansananibe Apa ana dave rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wepirati bambunin dave, weti be akarive ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 ami ntetero susyo wanave Ai jewene mai tenambe, 
\q2 indamu vatano ware umarovave Ai nawamo vemo umararin inya. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Inya, susyo mine tename weap, wapo reama Amisy ararimbe! 
\q2 Muno wakiny wapo ararimbe wasanamoto manakoe rai! 
\q1  
\v 9 Wepi Po reansayaranande ti reanjayaisy tutir, 
\q2 muno Po reansapaya vayave ra reantaopone jewen. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weye sya Amisy, Winyo reansatopan indamu Nyo reansanuga raveti ngkakavin, 
\q2 maisyare vatane wo perakije raugasya rauno taname rai indamu wo raveti mpoper ti mbe peraki kakuive.\f + \fr 66:10 \ft Vatane wo peraki raune mamo indamu ama anaingkainyo no rai mangkur ti mewen, weti ama kakui rave obo raen.\f* 
\q1  
\v 11 Winyo reansaugavo ana mo reansatopane raronto, maisyare reanta mparono aviri rai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Nyo ana mangke raugaje reansai ti reamo ranawan. 
\q1  
\v 12 Winyo reama marova mansanyanyut bayave ti wo reansataka doyadi, 
\q2 reansiuri rave maisyare vatano utatayasyo taname muno manayame rai wemaisy. 
\q1 Weramu Winyo reansaugavuje raora 
\q2 weti soamo reana kovo ana mawese rai jakato. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Indati syo anakotaro ridameseo Winai raugave siso no Nya Yavare ama uga, 
\q2 syo sya urairijo ridaokae nande Winai raveti mamaisy, 
\q1  
\v 14 namirati idaura inawa rai to wem, 
\q2 syurairive no arono rino irati ana nsosobe raije we. 
\q1  
\v 15 Indati anakotaro idameseo Winai mamo maero mani ti ngko dave mainy, 
\q2 omamo domba anya, sapi anya muno kambino anya mainy, 
\q2 indamu rameseo ti ama kijao ranavan nsainye nseo Winai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 Inya, vatano wapo Amisye asyanive weap, wade ra wadanaun, 
\q2 syare syo Apa ana dave rinai rariri. 
\q1  
\v 17 Syo awain to, indamu Po sopambe rinai, 
\q2 muno soamo syo abumbundi inawa so rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Ranivara syanatantonave kakai rai no inanuga ratire, 
\q2 indati Akoe Po rinaranive ramu. 
\q1  
\v 19 Weramu tugae rave, Amisye Po rinaraniv to, 
\q2 sya sambaya syo anajo mamo Po raraniv muno Po raveti mamaisyo rinai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Syo Amisye ararimbe, weye sya sambaya mamo Po rawatambe ramu, 
\q2 muno Apa muinyo no tawane mamo mpaya rinai ramu. 
\c 67  
\s1 Ransyeran kove raura seo Amisye Aijo Apa kove rai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran Masmur. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukinyo rai, wo itari\f + \fr 67:1 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai\ft .\f* raeyan dai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Reamare Amisye winaemeno reansai muno Nyo kove raugaje reansai, 
\q2 reamare Nya kove mbaro reansai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wirati vatano mine tename so wo Nya mbekere raen, 
\q2 muno susye kotar tenambe wo raen, Winyirati Nyo mapaya kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Amisy, reamare susye kotare wo kove raura seo Winai, 
\q2 reamare susye tenambe wo kove raura seo Winai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Reamare vatan tenambe mine so manayanambe muno ukiny mananibe. 
\q2 Weye Winyi mbe akarive susye kotare mai tenambe mamaisyo Nya moyare rai, 
\q2 muno Nyo vatan tenambe mine so maugavo mavabe. 
\q1  
\v 6 Amisy, reamare susye kotare wo kove raura seo Winai, 
\q2 reamare susye tenambe wo kove raura seo Winai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Kopa so mo ama anare ntuna raije ama ine rauguje to, 
\q2 Amisy, Opirati wama Amisy, Po kove raugaje wansai to. 
\q1  
\v 8 Amisye Po kove raugaje wansai to; 
\q2 koveamo susyo ntuna no mine tename so ubeaje Ai. 
\c 68  
\s1 Vovambe Amisye Apa anasineko rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Syare Amisye seo augananave inda Po Apa marova mangkat, 
\q2 muno vatano manuga mamuno Ai nanawamo unanajibe tatugadi aora. 
\q1  
\v 3 Amisye Po mawatan ti uta, maisyare kijao ovare po ramawita ti rakanive, 
\q2 maisyare inunijo\f + \fr 68:3 \fq inuni: \ft No ayao Ibrani raijamo mo ‘‘lilin’’ ratoe.\f* taname mo ranen ti ninimi. 
\q1 Maisyare omaisy tavon vatano wonae Amisye Ai nanawamo 
\q2 indati muenen ti makanive ta no Amisye Amun. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weramu syare vatano ubeta Amisye Ai nawamo indati mananibe, 
\q2 muno manayanambe, ugwain mananibe no Amisye Amun. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wakinyo ransyerane raijo Amisy Ai, wapo Apa tame rararimbe! 
\q2 Wapo unanui ratayao Ai, Wepirati Po kamure rave nyomambe no naume warae ti seo rai. 
\q2 Apa tame mirati AMISY; wasananibe no Amun! 
\q1  
\v 6 Opamo be ajaeve irati arikainyo wawate mai, 
\q2 muno be marimbe wanya kavini mansai, 
\q2 wepirati Amisy no no Apa Yavaro ndandinit rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Po vatano apa arakove meweno ai augav ti no irati yavaruga inta matavon. 
\q2 Muno Po vatano maijaro arove mapaya aroo rai, weti ukiny mananibe. 
\q1 Yara vatano wonae ubeta Amisye Ai wenawamo 
\q2 una kopa ngkanembe mana mewen dai rai.\f + \fr 68:7 \fq kopa ngkanembe mana mewen dai rai \ft ama ntunato rai mare vatano anakotare maweso mai jewen muno una irati ana sosobe ama uga rai.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Sya Amisy, arono Nyo Nya kawasae maugav ti wuje Mesir raora, 
\q2 Nyo maugav ti wanya no anoko ngkanembe raita. 
\q1  
\v 9 Arono naije mungki nande munije ntutar, 
\q2 muno maru pape no no naume warae ti ntemaje, 
\q1 weye Amisye Winde nanasine raroron no unato Sinai,\f + \fr 68:9 \ft Kel. 19:16-25\f* 
\q2 Winyirati Amisy, vatano Israel ubeaje Nai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Sya Amisy, Winyo maru pape raugaje ntapekambe, 
\q2 mo kove raugavo Nya kopa ngkanembe rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Nya kawasae una tawano rai no ratuije; 
\q2 sya Amisy, Winyirati Nyo vatano awa ana jajewembe mai mansayaranande, 
\q2 weye Nya kove manakoeyo mai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Amisye Po Apa ayao raura, 
\q2 weti vatano wanuije wo ravov, ware: 
\q1  
\v 13 Akari titi nanawe awa naite nao unanajibe. 
\q2 Muno wanya nanawirati una yavare rai wo ananugo raugav no marova rai ratodi mai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 14 Muno vatano utavondi marova rai jewen weye una ti wo domba mayaranande nao tavon, 
\q2 awa ura irati ana ratotov ti ranari insani punambe muno perakije veano apa pepake ranari, 
\q2 muno ananemane mamo emasije veano ranari ti ngkenav dave rai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 15 Arono Amisy, Wepi Bambunin dave, Po akari titi umawe mangkat, 
\q2 omamo maisyare salju\f + \fr 68:15 \fq salju: \ft omamo ama nanayao mo esije ramaisy weramu nsaon maisyare kapum ti mo nuge ratatuv.\f* maje unato Salmona rai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Tugae unato muni Basan, nya papukame ngkov dave, 
\q2 muno nya papukame manui rave. 
\q1  
\v 17 Weti unato Basan nya papukame manui rave nai winy, 
\q2 mbetai ruimaisy irati mparijo unato Sion Amisy Po ratayao terave amarom indamu tuna rai we rai? 
\q2 Omirati unato indati Amisye pare tuna rai ntoa nuge nuganui! 
\q1  
\v 18 Amisye Apa kereta marova mamo mo ribuge tename rakivan, 
\q2 muno ama manuije mamo ratore kakai; 
\q2 Amisy no no Sinai ti de to, de siso no Apa Yavaro ndandinit rai. 
\q1  
\v 19 Sya AMISY, arono winseo no Nya ntuna ri ntiti\f + \fr 68:19 \fq ntuna ri ntiti: \ft ayao so ama ine mare unato Sion. Aneme so ratoe akato no Epesus 4:8.\f* rai, 
\q2 Nyo vatano maijaro arove wanui rave maugav; 
\q2 Onawamo Nyo mataopon no marova rai ti wo romane raugaje Nai. 
\q1 Muno vatano wonae ubeta Nai nao wo romane raugaje Nai tavon kobe. 
\q2 AMISY Winyi sya Amisy, Winyi ntuna tawan no we. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Akoe ararimbe! 
\q2 Opirati Amisy Wepi Po wama ana nsosobe wansai ranawano masyote yanteter; 
\q2 muno Wepi Po wansapaya kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Wama Amisy Wepirati Amisyo Po wansapaya irati wama marova mai pije. 
\q2 Opirati AMISY, Wepi Akoe Po wama marova mapinde weti wo wansaove jewen. 
\q1  
\v 22 Tugae rave, indati Amisye Po Apa marova makari rakupi, 
\q2 Po makari pae rakupi, weye ayao kakai ntapekano mai. 
\q1  
\v 23 Akoe Po raura pare: ‘‘Inya Sya kawasae, 
\q2 indati Syo wapa marova awa pae ntuna no mayan ate raugav akasen, 
\q2 muno nai unato Basan Syo wapa marova awa koke raugav akare tavon, 
\q1  
\v 24 indamu wasea wapananave awa mavu rai, 
\q2 muno wapa make wo awa mavu ranenev anyija manobone mbinanebe rai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 25 Sya Amisy, vatane mami ntami Nya vovambe anasine ugav rai, 
\q2 omamo sya Amisy muno sya Akari Titi Nya vovano nyakaseo no Nya tuna ri ndandinit rai mije. 
\q1  
\v 26 Nai vovambe umaso vatano ukinyo ransyerane rai wanya no uisy, 
\q2 muno wanya kokovainyo wo airape\f + \fr 68:26 \fq airape \ft ranigwano ‘‘rebana’’ rai.\f* ranepate una no yasyin 
\q2 umba vatano wo itari\f + \fr 68:26 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* raeyane udijat no makiri. 
\q1  
\v 27 Ukiny ware: ‘‘Amisye Apa kawasae weap, wapo ararimbe no wapa anugane rai! 
\q2 Inya, weapirati Yakop apa ajavi weap, wapo AMISY ararimbe!’’ 
\q1  
\v 28 Susyo Benyamin nanawirati susyo mamaun dave wanya no wuisy, 
\q2 muno vatano ube akarive no susyo Yehuda wanugan wanya no yasyin, 
\q2 umba susyo Sebulon muno susyo Naptali aya vatano ube akarive udijat dave no makiri. 
\q1  
\v 29 Sya Amisy, reamare Nya vambunine rauguje, 
\q2 sya Amisy, Nya vambunine raroron, 
\q2 Nyo rave akato maisyare arono wusyin Nyo rarorombe reansai to wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 30 Akari titi wo awa romane raugavere Nai, 
\q2 indamu ude ubeaje Nai no Nya Yavar, no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 31 Sya AMISY, syare winsoowato Mesir mai weye awa vambunine rangkakeraive. 
\q2 Wenawamo maisyare sapi sivuinyo ukaokaibe no kuwae uga, 
\q2 muno maisyare sapi anya usivuiny dave ti awa tuvane ujaniv. 
\q1 Weti syare Winyo awa vambunine rapinde muno Nyo mataopon, 
\q2 indamu wo awa romano peraki raugavere ubeaje Nai. 
\q2 Tugae Amisy, indati Nyo susyo ubekero usisa marova raije mampusyek. 
\q1  
\v 32 Weti vatano akokoe Mesir wo ananugo ama mangke nseo raugavere Amisye Ai, 
\q1 maisyare omai tavon vatano akokoe Sudan\f + \fr 68:32 \fq Sudan \ft raura tavonamo ‘‘Etiopia,’’ omamo ntami no Mesir ama ranijo wanampui.\f* wavave ude maneme reanande 
\q2 indamu mbe rarorombe wenawamo manuga mpayaje Ai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 33 Inya, susyo mine tename weap, wakiny wapo Amisye ararimbe, 
\q2 wakinyo ransyerano kangkamane rai wapo Akoe ararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 34 Weye Wepi seo Apa nyomane rai ti toe de no naumo no pitawabe warae. 
\q2 Wadaniv Amisye payao, anamote ransyean maisyare katitire we, weti wadasyaniv. 
\q1  
\v 35 Susyo mine weap, syare wasakari ranseyai, wapo Amisye Apa vambunine ravovo, 
\q2 weye Wepirati be Akari anakoeve Israel mansai, 
\q2 muno wapo Apa vambunine we raen no naume rai. 
\q1  
\v 36 Amisy, Winyamo anaaniv arono nyuje no Nya ntuna ri ndandinit rai; 
\q2 Amisy Israel Wepi Apa vambunino manakoe raunande Apa kawasae mansai. 
\q2 Amisye ararimbe! 
\c 69  
\s1 Ransyerano weotor Amisye anonae arono no nsosobe ama uga rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Aepare ama ug.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo inapaya kakaije rai, 
\q2 weye soamo maisyare mana ndea nsopo sya isyisye rai to. 
\q1  
\v 3 Anakotaro nsosobe mangke rinai rave, 
\q2 maisyare itemasyo karunseno nsararane rai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno ibambunino ipaya rai kakai. 
\q1 Anakotare umaso nde ti mo inakupi, 
\q2 maisyare isayadi waro ntento rai, 
\q2 muno manayame mo inaugave wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syo Amisye winawain indamu Nyo sopambe rinai, 
\q2 weramu syanonae tutira imaririmbe, muno inakuiny mbasyine ngkanen. 
\q1 Syo Amisye winatunaowa nugoenta, 
\q2 ti syoyova inami tuga so nsansenai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Vatane manuga mamuno rinai vayave ayao mamaisye jewene rai, 
\q2 awa wanui mamo inakarivuinye so mamaun akato. 
\q1 Sya marova ware wo inaupaeta nawamo wanui rave, 
\q2 wangkarive ti wanaikebe rinai ware syanaonoambe. 
\q1 Syanaonombe ananuge inta rai jewen, 
\q2 weramu wo tuvake veano inave, ware syo ananu anaonoane inta raugakananto. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya Amisy, Winyirati Nyo sya ayao kakai raen tenambe, 
\q2 sya ana daveti ngkakainoanive mamo inta ngkokaibe no winamune ramu. 
\q1  
\v 7 Sya Akoe AMISY, Winyirati Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti, 
\q2 syare vemo ribe samaneve arakovo manaveano winamene mai jinya. 
\q1 Vatano Israel reama Amisy Winy, 
\q2 syare vemo ribe ayaobe irati vatano ubeaje Winai mai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 8 Weye syanave Winai ti vatane wo inaura tantunawi, 
\q2 weti sya tame ngkakai. 
\q1  
\v 9 No sya arakove mansamun, risyamo maisyare vatano marane wemaisy, 
\q2 muno taune sya ananuinye wo rinaen risyamo maisyare vatano wanisen. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weye inanuga no Winya Yavare rai ntipu tutir,\f + \fr 69:10 \ft Yoh. 2:17\f* 
\q2 weti vatane awa ayao wo winaura tantunawi mo rinaron tavon.\f + \fr 69:10 \ft Rom. 15:3\f* 
\q1  
\v 11 Syoyov muno inanasine so mpayaje inatawandi marore rai, 
\q2 weramu wo inaura tantunawi rai tutir kobe. 
\q1  
\v 12 Syo mana raijame jewen muno syo ansuno wusyine obo rave\f + \fr 69:12 \fq ansuno wusyine obo rave: \ft no koano Israel raijamo wo iije vasye karisya veano maakuvi.\f* weye inanimaumbe, 
\q2 weramu wugoeno rinai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Vatano ude wanugambe no unsanda akoe sisa no munije rai wo inampami, 
\q2 vatano umaene wo sya tame rambaono awa ransyerane rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Weramu AMISY, risyamo syo nanajo tutir, 
\q2 sya Amisy, syare Nyo sya ana danajo raveti mamai no Nya masyoto ngkove rai. 
\q1 Winyamo nteto Nya urairi rai tutir, weti syare Nyo inapaya sya marova mai, 
\q2 mamaisyo Nya muinyo manakoe no tawane rai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Syare Nyo rinapaya irati vatano manuga mamuno rinai mai, 
\q2 maisyare Nyo rinakarimu sen no karunseno nsararane rai wemaisy, 
\q2 vemo Nyo rinapayamo risayadi waro ntento rai nora. 
\q1  
\v 16 Syare vemo naneme mpaya rinai nora. 
\q2 Weye ana nsosobe mangke rinai somamo 
\q1 maisyare manayame mo inaugave wemaisy, 
\q2 maisyare risayadi no mayan ate ntento rai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare syasyo no atemo amanija ama ate rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 17 AMISY, syare Nyo sya ana danajo ravera mamaisy, 
\q2 weye Nya muinyo no tawane mamo ngkov dave. 
\q1 Syare namumbe de rinai weye winaemeno rinai manakoe rave. 
\q1  
\v 18 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, syare vemo winakirive rinai jinya, 
\q2 weye rino ana nsosobe ama uga rai, 
\q2 weti nyavave nde Nyo inapaya rai. 
\q1  
\v 19 Syare nde Nyo marimbe rinai, 
\q2 Nyo rinapaya irati sya marova mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Sya marova nawamo Amisye Winyo mansaen tenambe to. 
\q2 Arono wo rinaura tantunawi, wo rinave samaneve, 
\q2 muno wo sya tame raveti ngkakai mamo Nyo raen to. 
\q1  
\v 21 Awa ayao wo rinaura tantunawi mo inanuga so raveti mpatimu rave. 
\q2 Ribeker syare vatane inta mansaemeno rinai, weramu ta mamaisye jewen, 
\q2 syo vatano wo inayove makani weramu inanto inta mai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 22 Umba sya marova wo anaisyo nyowae rave rai raunande ridaisy, 
\q2 arono rinawa ngkangkamandi, wo anggurijo nsaisyine raunande ridamanam.\f + \fr 69:22 \ft Mat. 27:34,48; Mrk. 15:36; Luk. 23:36; Yoh. 19:29\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Amisy, syare Nyo mangke raugaje sya marova mansai! 
\q2 Koveamo awa ono wo maere rameseo Amisye Ai mamo,\f + \fr 69:23 \ft Paulus po ayao so raura kakavimbe no Roma 11:9-10.\f* maisyare isyeano nsawa mai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno omamo maisyare aviri awa arakove uparono rai tavone wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 24 Koveamo mansamije ntuba indamu wo ana raene jewen, 
\q2 muno makiri mona mayondi indamu umarovave rinai kakai. 
\q1  
\v 25 Syare Nya parijo mangke rasuire mansai, 
\q2 muno Nya parijo mbe tanam mamoambe mo mawatan damu mo mansanen. 
\q1  
\v 26 Koveamo awa munijo utantuna raije mbabivi, 
\q2 muno awa yavare ama uga nsugan.\f + \fr 69:26 \ft Arakov. 1:20\f* 
\q1  
\v 27 Amisy, Winyo vatano nanuga no maije manepat arono wo ayao kakai rave, 
\q2 weramu sya marova wo vatano Nyo manepate mave pabe tutir, 
\q2 muno useambe vatano Nyo mangke raugaje mai awa jajorame rai. 
\q1  
\v 28 Kovato awa ube tatugadije ratutumbe manuijo mai kai, 
\q2 vemo Nyo awa ayao kakai rapaya mai nora. 
\q1  
\v 29 Koveamo awa tame raupae no buku muni tawane rai, 
\q2 muno vemo awa tame ratoe tavon no vatano kove\f + \fr 69:29 \fq vatano kove \ft onawamo vatano ubeta Amisye Apa ananyao rai.\f* matavon inya. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 30 Yara risyamo vatano inatawanto, weti inanuga njoram. 
\q2 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo rinaijaseo, Nyo rinapaya marova mansaneme rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 31 Rikinyo ransyerane rai, syo Amisye Apa tame rangkakivambe, 
\q2 muno syo kove raura seo Ai, syo aijaseo titive. 
\q1  
\v 32 Omamo ngkov akato irati syo maere rameseo Ai rai; 
\q2 tugae, syo Amisye ararimbe mo syo sapi anya\f + \fr 69:32 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘sapi anya apa korodowai no ai ti panakoe to.’’\f* ameseo Ai rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 33 Weti vatano matawanto wo raen muno mansananibe, 
\q2 vatano ubeaje Amisye Ai, mansanuga mbambunin akato! 
\q1  
\v 34 Weye vatano una irati awa ana jajewembe rai nawamo AMISY Po maraniv arono wo awain, 
\q2 muno vatano makova nawamo ponae mai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 35 Inya, anakotaro ntuna no naume warae me mine so me, 
\q2 muno mayane me ama anakotaro ntuna rai rautan, wapo Amisye ararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 36 Weye indati Amisye Po vatano una no Sion mapaya irati marova rai, 
\q2 muno Po munijo Yehuda raijar akaseo ntet anyi. 
\q1 Indati Amisye Apa kawasae utantuna rai, muno weyave rai. 
\q1  
\v 37 Muno indati awa arikainye, ajavije awa ura rai tawan tutir, 
\q2 muno vatano manuga no Amisy Ai nawamo indati utantuna rai. 
\c 70  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu aemeno rinai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe, arono po anakotare rameseo Amisye Ai indamu Amisye aemeno ai. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, syare nde Nyo inapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 AMISY, nyavave Nyo inasopan! 
\q1  
\v 3 Vatano ware wo rinaubaisye nawamo 
\q2 koveamo Nyo mapinde ti usamane muno mpusyek tatugadi. 
\q1 Vatano ubekero siurije nande rinai nawamo, 
\q2 koveamo Nyo matamo ra wansuk akiri muno awa tame ngkakai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Vatano wugoeno rinai nawamo, 
\q2 koveamo usamane ti wansuk muno unanajibe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Vatan tenambe ude ubeaje Amisye Winai nawamo, 
\q2 koveamo mananibe muno manayanambe weye ube intabove Nai. 
\q1 Vatano mansanuga no Amisye Winai weye Nyo mapaya kakai rai nawamo, 
\q2 koveamo wo raura tutir ware: ‘‘Tugae, Amisy Opirati titi rave!’’ 
\q1  
\v 6 Weramu risyamo vatano no irati siuri rai muno sya ana jajewembe rinai; 
\q2 weti sya Amisy, syare nyavave ra nde! 
\q1 Indamu Nyo sopambe rinai muno Nyo inapaya irati rai, 
\q2 weti sya AMISY, syare vemo maneai nora! 
\c 71  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu tuna nautan no arono mbe vatan anuive 
\q1  
\v 1 Sya AMISY, Wibuinyirati syakaore gaugambe Nai, 
\q2 vemo Nyo rinapayamo sya marova wo inave samaneve inya. 
\q1  
\v 2 Amisy, Winyamo Nya ana ndave moyar, weti syare Nyo rinapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q2 Syare namarikoame rasakinavo sya ana danajo ore rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare Winyirati maisyare unato oram ntindimu inamamavube Nai, 
\q2 muno yano oram no rinaora indamu ripaya irati kakai rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Winyirati maisyare sya unato oram muno sya yano oram ntindimu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo rinapaya irati vatano mamune mansaneme rai, 
\q2 Nyo inapaya irati vatano mansamuno ivuinye muno usoowate no mai awa vambunine rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye Akoe Winy, Wibuinyirati inanaveano namen. 
\q2 AMISY, syanave Nai no arono ta ikamuramoe ndea naiso. 
\q1  
\v 6 Winy irati isaroro Nai, arono rino no ingkoa ranobon ti rinavaki aje kobe we ndea naiso, 
\q2 Winyo rinayaranande no arono rinano kobe we, 
\q2 weti Wibuinyirati syo nararimbe tutir. 
\q1  
\v 7 Winyirati ntindimu ti rigaugambe Nai, 
\q2 weti ibe rarorombe indamu vatano wanui wo rinaen ware Amisye Winyi Nyo vatane reansayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 8 Rikangkamambe Winai tutir, 
\q2 syo Nya kovo ntiti ravovo masyote anteter. 
\q1  
\v 9 Vemo Nyo rinavakambe no ibe vatan anuive so inya, 
\q2 muno arono ibambunin akato jewen to, weamo vemo winaneme mpaya rinai nora. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weye sya marova wanugan wayao inai, 
\q2 wanyinyaube, ubeker ware wo rinaubaisy. 
\q1  
\v 11 Wo raura ware: ‘‘Amisye aneme mpaya ai to, 
\q2 weti wade, wamo awatan indamu wamo aijar, 
\q2 weye indati inta po ayaranande akato ramu.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Amisy, syare vemo winggwaravainyo rinai nora! 
\q2 Sya Amisy, syare nyavave Nyo rinaijaseo! 
\q1  
\v 13 Koveamo Nyo sya marova mave samaneve muno Nyo maupaeta ramu makanive, 
\q2 koveamo vatano wanakakaive rinai nawamo, Nyo awa tame ravera ngkakai ti usamane. 
\q1  
\v 14 Yara risyamo Wibuinyirati inanaveano namen, 
\q2 muno syo nararimbe tutir. 
\q1  
\v 15 Nya ana ndaveti mamaisy muno moyar, 
\q2 muno Nyo inapaya kakaije rai mamo syo ravovo masyote yanteter, 
\q2 weramu risyamo mamaisyo syo rator bintabo kakai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Sya Akoe AMISY Winy, rikangkamambe Nya ana ndaveti makokoive rai, 
\q2 Wibuinyirati Nya ana ndaveti moyare mamo idararimbe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Sya Amisy, Winyo rinanyao no arono ta rikamuramoe ndea naiso, 
\q2 Nya ana ndave mbe anaanibe omamo ridavovo tutir. 
\q1  
\v 18 Sya Amisy, inakarivuinye nsavu muno imaun kobe so, 
\q2 syare vemo Nyo inapaya nora. 
\q1 Wirati indamu syo Nya vambunine ravovo tutir irati arikainyo varoro ubeseo akato so mai, 
\q2 muno susyo merere nto wo Nya vambunine ranaun tavon. 
\q1  
\v 19 Sya Amisy, Nya moyare mamo ntitito rave no naume warae. 
\q2 Winyirati Nyo anakotaro makokoe rave. 
\q2 Sya Amisy, inta po winamaisye ramu. 
\q1  
\v 20 Winyo anakotaro nsosobe manui ramayaro nande rinai, 
\q2 weramu indati Nyo vambunine raugakaje rinai jakato, 
\q2 muno Nyo inaijaseo ti ripaya wene rai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Indati Winyo sya tame raveti manakoe, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinayove akato. 
\q1  
\v 22 Sya Amisy, Winyamo nteto Nya urairi rai tutir, 
\q2 weti syo nararimbe, rikinyo ransyerane rai, syo itari anakoe\f + \fr 71:22 \fq itari anakoe \ft ranigwano ‘‘gambus’’ rai, gambus somamo ama wai raeyane abusyin.\f* raeyan dai. 
\q1 Sya Amisy, Winyirati ndandinit ti vatano Israel ubeaje Nai, 
\q2 rikinyo ransyerano kangkamane raijo Winai, syo itari mamaune\f + \fr 71:22 \fq itari mamaune \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai. \f* raeyan dai. 
\q1  
\v 23 Rinanayanambe gwain kinyo ransyerane rai, 
\q2 rikiny kangkamambe Nai weye Winyo rinapaya irati kakai rai to. 
\q1  
\v 24 Rinawa so mo Nya moyare ravovo masyote anteter, 
\q2 weye vatano ware wo rinave pabe nanawamo, 
\q2 awa ana ura mamaundi muno usamane. 
\c 72  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po kove raugaje akari titi ai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Salomo po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo Nya patimu mamaisye raveano akari titi anyao, 
\q2 muno Nya moyare raveano arikainyo be akari titive umaso anyao. 
\q1  
\v 2 Indamu po Nya kawasae maugav mamaisyo moyare rai, 
\q2 muno po patimu mamaisye raugaje irati Nya vatano matawan asyo mansai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare kovo ana mawese ntami unate muno papukamo munije so rai tenambe, 
\q2 muno kovo saumane ntami weye kawasae wo ana ngkove rarijat. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare akari titi be marimbe irati vatano matawanto mai, 
\q2 muno po vatano ananuge jajewembe mai mapaya awa siurije rai, 
\q2 yara vatano wo matawan asyo nawamo po maubaisy bintabo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Syare akarijo titi apa tume nggwaravainy indamu apa be akarive ntoa nugoenta, 
\q2 maisyare uma pe embae me ibar tutire wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Syare po kove raugavo apa kawasae mai maisyare maruge maje anare rai ti mo mane rauguje wemaisy, 
\q2 maisyare maru pape maje ti nsaakop irati nawaisye rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Syare moyare obo ntami no arono be akari titive so, 
\q2 muno saumano kove muno anakotare maweso kawasae mai no tawan tutir, 
\q2 maisyare embae mbar tutire wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare apa munijo po raijare mamo maneka ti nto no mayane ama nake rai muiya nto no ama nake rai, 
\q2 muno nai mana Eprat muija nto no munije ama maran. 
\q1  
\v 9 Indati vatano ntuna no anoko kanene ude ubeaje ai no amun, 
\q2 muno apa marova ude wo vukane ranteter wo ajo ranu, weye po anasineko mai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Indati akarijo titi munijo Tarsis\f + \fr 72:10 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisye wo ratantona ware munijo Tarsis omamo munijo Spanyol.\f* muno akarijo titi nupatimu wo romane raugavere ai. 
\q2 Akarijo titi munijo Arap muno Etiopia\f + \fr 72:10 \fq Arap muno Etiopia: \ft ayao Ibrani mare ‘‘Syeba’’ muno ‘‘Seba.’’\f* ude wo romane ravae nande ai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Akarijo titi nao tenambe indati ude ubeaje ai, 
\q2 muno susye kotare wanapatambe irati ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Weye vatano awa ana jajewembe mai ti wanonae nawamo po mapaya irati rai, 
\q2 muno vatano matawanto nanawirati inta wo sopambe mai jewene nawamo po mapaya awa siurije rai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Opamo aemeno vatano umayondi mai, muno vatano awa ana jajewembe maije mansai, 
\q2 vatano awa ana jajewembe mai nawamo po mapaya irati wene rai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Indati po mapaya irati vatano wo mave tatugadi muno wo matawanto mai, 
\q2 weye awa siuri mamo mo aveti aemeno mansai rave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 Koveamo indati akari titi apa tume nggwaravainy dave! 
\q2 Syare indati emasijo Arap raugavere ai. 
\q1 Syare indati apa kawasae usambayambe ai tutir, 
\q2 wo kove ranajo indamu raugaje ai tutir! 
\q1  
\v 16 Syare koveamo awa anare kasyambere ntairi awa muni rai, 
\q2 ti nseo mo unate ratatuv tenambe. 
\q1 Koveamo awa anare ntubai mawes maisyare anare ntubai mawebe no munijo Libanon ramaisy, 
\q2 muno apa kawasae nawamo awa wanui merere nseo maisyare insumai nsani ti mo kopa ratatuv wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 17 Syare koveamo akari titi apa tame mamo vatane maemendi rai ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno apa be akari titive mamo indati vatane wo ranaune merere nto kobe maisyare uma bar tutire wemaisy. 
\q1 Syare indati susye kotar tenambe ubeker ware kovo raugaje ai omamo raugaje irati mai tavon, 
\q2 muno indati vatan tenambe wo aura ware opirati no irati anayanambe rai pijep. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 Kangkamambe AMISY Ai, Opirati Amisy vatano Israel ubeaje Ai! 
\q2 Obo pirati mamaisyo Po anakotaro mbe anaanibe raroron! 
\q1  
\v 19 Kangkamambe Apa tamo ntiti rai jao ntoa nuge nuganui! 
\q2 Syare Apa kovo ntiti ntairi mine so rai tenambe! 
\q1 Tugae, syare tugae! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Daud, opirati Isai apa kavop, apa sambaya mainyamo ndea nsopi no naije. 
\c 73  
\ms1 ETET 3 
\ms1 MASMUR 73-89 
\s1 Vatano kove pe vatano mamune pe aya matam akari 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Tugae rave, Amisye pamo kov dave irati Apa kawasae Israel mansai, 
\q2 nanawirati vatano manuga ndandinite mai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Weramu risyamo, sya kawi rantukam ti kavintare ritemaje, 
\q2 kavintare umba sya anave raumandi. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye arono syo vatano mararine mansaen, 
\q2 onawamo vatano mamun, weramu una kovo ana mawese rai, 
\q2 weamo ribeker syo mansamaisy tavon. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye syo manyanyutamo siurije inta nande maije ramu, 
\q2 manasine mamo nsauman nsev dave muno ubambunin. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ana nsosobe nande vatane mansai mamo inta nande mai ramu, 
\q2 muno ana mangke mo vatane makep asyo inta nande mai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 6 Maisyare omaiti, wenawamo awa mararin dave raroron kakavimbe, 
\q2 muno mansamuno ivuinye obo mirati raeno mai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wenawamo manugave ananuge manui obo rai ti awa ayao kakaije miridi nseo, 
\q2 umba manuga ntairi awa ana udatantona ngkakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Wenawamo wanaikebe muno wo vatane maura tantunawi, 
\q2 mansanuga rararin, wo vatano kaije matawan asyo. 
\q1  
\v 9 Mansawa raijaseo wo Amisye aura tantunawi, 
\q2 muno wo vatano mine so awa tame rampami vayave! 
\q1  
\v 10 Weti Amisye Apa kawasae usakinav wakare utavondi vatano mamune umaso mai, 
\q2 muno utataopono awa ayao wo rakere rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Vatano mamun umaso wo raura ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Amisye pamo pantatukambe wama ana wandave raija, 
\q2 Amisy Titi Rave Opamo nanto rai ramu.’’ 
\q1  
\v 12 Vatano mamune umaso nanawamo 
\q2 awa ananuge ama manuije merere nseo kobe, 
\q2 ana nsosobe nande mai jewen, yara una mariraave obo rai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 13 Syo rakarae rikovo rinanuga ndandinite rai 
\q2 muno risyo ayao kakaije rapaya ra ntami wemamo ribea marudija. 
\q1  
\v 14 Weye risyamo ana nsosobe obo nande rinai masyote anteter, 
\q2 muno risyamo rinansewabe awatane yanteter. 
\q1  
\v 15 Ranivara syo raura taije maisy, 
\q2 weamo ribe tatugadi nanto irati Amisy Nya kawasae mai to ije. 
\q1  
\v 16 Arono ribeker syare syo ratantona mavabe indamu rinanto rai, 
\q2 weramu ana umaso nsosobe rave irati rinai. 
\q1  
\v 17 No ava risiso no Yavar Amisye rai, 
\q2 umba rinanto irati vatano mamune awa matam akari rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Tugae rave, Amisy, Winyo maveta una no unanuijo nsaremo rai, 
\q2 umba Nyo mapaya vayave ti utaopon, muenen ti mewen. 
\q1  
\v 19 Wakoe! Kavuratawe wenawamo maupaeta ti makanive wene rai, 
\q2 weno mangke mbambunin dave umaso mi mo maupaeta. 
\q1  
\v 20 Sya Akoe, vatano mamune umaso makanive vintabo arono winseo, Nyo maubaisy, 
\q2 maisyare vatane apa nikimarije rakaniveta apa ana datantona rai arono nikija seo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 Arono naijeamo rinanuga so rawaive rave, 
\q2 muno inanuga somamo maisyare rauwaki wemai dave. 
\q1  
\v 22 Muno risyamo syantukambe rave muno rinanto rai ramu, 
\q2 syananepabe vayave no Amisye Winamun, maisyare maero pananepabe vayave wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 23 Weramu risyamo syararai tutir irati Amisye Winai, 
\q2 Winyo rinanem ngkove raijar. 
\q1  
\v 24 Nya ananyao wemi mo rinaugav mavabe, 
\q2 indati ama marane mamo Nyo kovo ntiti raunande irati rinai. 
\q1  
\v 25 Amisye Winya jewen, umba arepi rati indati rinanaveano amen no munijo Manunggara? 
\q2 Muno mine somamo ribekero inta raije ramu, yara Amisye Wibuinya. 
\q1  
\v 26 Arono rui vayave rinanasine muno rinanuga so mayondi, 
\q2 weramu Amisy Winyo rinanuga so raijaseo ti mbambunin. 
\q2 Winyirati ribekero Nai tutir ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 27 Tugae, are nawirati ugwaravainyo Nai, indati muenen ti makanive. 
\q2 Muno are nawirati makirive Nai, Nyo maupaeta ti makanive. 
\q1  
\v 28 Yara taune risy, ribekero no mararaive Amisye winatavon, 
\q2 Akoe AMISY, syo napatimu indamu Winyirati ndarino rinaora, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya anakotaro ndave ravovo tenambe. 
\c 74  
\s1 Ransyerano weotor indamu Amisye aemeno Yerusalem rai 
\p  
\v 1 Asap apa ransyerano ananyao. 
\b  
\q1 Sya Amisy, winakirive reansai tutir bayave kobea e? 
\q2 Mbe animaibe wimpari mangkebe Nya domba reansai? 
\q1  
\v 2 Syare naemeno reansai: reami Nya kawasae Nyo reansatayao no wusyinoe, 
\q2 reami susyo Nyo reansapaya aroo rai, indamu nyeave reansai. 
\q2 Syare naemeno unato Sion rai, namirati Nyo ratayao indamu taune ntuna rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare nde nyanya munijo mandamisyi to umaso rai indamu ndaen, 
\q2 Nya Yavare mamo marova wo randamisyi vintabo to. 
\q1  
\v 4 Nya marova ugwagwaimbe no Nya Yavare ama uga, 
\q2 muno wo awa iije vasye rauseo ratugar, mbe rarorombe wo reansapinde to. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wenawamo maisyare vatano wo tama randarito inyo rai, 
\q2 indamu wo inyo anate raturi aje wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Ude usisa no Nya yavare ama uga, 
\q2 wo tama muno mambuv veano ama anainya ratotove raturi. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wo taname rapino Nya Yavare rai ti mangkudija masyo ruke rai rave, 
\q2 muno Nya ntuna ri ndandinit raveti nggwambe no Namun.\f + \fr 74:7 \ft Raen tavon no 2Raj. 25:9.\f* 
\q1  
\v 8 Wo raura no manuga ware: ‘‘Wade ramu wamo vatano Israel makupi vintabo!’’ 
\q2 Umba wo taname rapino varodoro reambeaje Amisy Ai no munije so\f + \fr 74:8,12,20 \fq munije so \ft ama ine mare Israel.\f* rai vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 9 Anapaporainye inta raroron akato ramu, 
\q2 muno anawae Amisy inta no munije so rai akato ramu, 
\q2 muno reamantukambe ntoa nanduija umba inta nande akato! 
\q1  
\v 10 Sya Amisy, ntoa nanduija umba reama marova wo winaura tantunawi, 
\q2 muno wo Nya tame rambaone so ntoa nsopija? 
\q1  
\v 11 Mbe animaibe winaneme mpaya irati reansai, 
\q2 muno naneme rakapan ti ntuna Nyo reansaen bayave? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Weramu Amisy, Winyirati reama Akari Titive kobe no arono wusyinoe, 
\q2 Winyirati Nyo reansapaya reama marova mai no muni so rai vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 13 Winyirati Nya vambunine mo mayane\f + \fr 74:13 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo rakarae ware mayane so omamo Mayano Kolsum, namirati Amisye Po raotar arono vatano Israel wuje munijo aroo Mesir raora wem. Ranivara ama ine no tai maisy, weamo tawae so raurata irati naito Mesir mansai, nanawirati usayadi no Mayano Kolsum rai. Weramu kuruno Ayao Amisy kaijinta wo ratantona ware mayane so omamo mayano Amisye Po ranari arono munije ama manasyinoe.\f* raota ti yasyine ngkanen, 
\q2 muno Nyo tawae mansakari ratuturi tenambe no mayane von.\f + \fr 74:13 \fq tawae mansakari ratuturi no mayane von \ft ama ino kaijinta mare: Mesir awa naito nsayadi no Mayano Kolsum.\f* 
\q1  
\v 14 Winyirati Nyo tawae akoe Lewiatan\f + \fr 74:14 \fq tawae akoe Lewiatan: \ft Arono wusyinoe vatano Israel wanave ware ana mamun maisyare tawae rako, jiane rako, mansakari mansak ti manui, inta ntuna no mayane rai. Wo tamo ‘‘Lewiatan’’ veano rawain. \f* mansakari rakupi,\f + \fr 74:14 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware Lewiatan mbe rarorombe munijo Mesir ama akari titi Piraon ai, napirati Amisye Po apinde no Mayano Kolsum.\f* 
\q2 muno Nyo awa ine raunanto ana mamun nsivuiny ntuna anoko kanene rai wo raisy. 
\q1  
\v 15 Winyirati Nyo mana muno mana ami rapapaya ti njam,\f + \fr 74:15 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware Keluaran 17:1-6 mo ayao so raura kakavimbe, arono Amisye Po vambunine raugaje Musa ai, weti po oramo akoe raporar no anoko kanen, umba mana nsui uje rai. \f* 
\q2 yara mana njaisye mamo nyurarijato rai ti ngkanen.\f + \fr 74:15 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware ayao so raura kakavimbe no Yosua moto 3 muno 4, arono Amisye Po mana akoe Yordan njam tutire ransopi, weti yasyine ngkanen.\f* 
\q1  
\v 16 Winyirati Nyo sansimane me namane me yanari, 
\q2 muno Nyo uma pe embae me yaosoro rai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Winyirati Nyo mine so ama anone raosor anyi, 
\q2 Nyo none aveti tami muno maru raveti ntami. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo raen, weye Nya marova wo naura tantunawi rave, 
\q2 muno susyo wantukambe Winaije wo Nya tame rambaon. 
\q1  
\v 19 Vemo Nyo Nya anugano Israel umaindi so maugavo marova manemo nsoowate mansaron inya!\f + \fr 74:19 \ft Ayao Ibrani mo ayao ananeneae ratoe rai, mare: ‘‘Vemo Nyo Nya insani puname aunanto ana mamun usivuinye mai nora.’’ Ayao ‘‘insani puname’’ aurata irati kawasae Israel mansai, muno ‘‘ana mamun usivuiny’’ maurata irati Israel awa marova mansai.\f* 
\q2 Vemo winanimari tutir irati Nya kawasae matawanto so mai nora! 
\q1  
\v 20 Syare winteto Nya urairi ndaokae nande reansai rai indamu mamaisy, 
\q2 weye munije so ntairi vatano mamun nanawirati ukaokaibe ama varodoro ngkaumudi raito tenambe mai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Nya kawasae matawanto sonawamo vemo naneme mpaya mai mo usamane inya, 
\q2 yara koveamo vatano matawanto muno una siuri rai so wo Nya tame rararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 22 Sya Amisy, mbeseo ra Nyo taune Nya mamaisye rarorono vatane mansai, 
\q2 syare Nyo raen, weye vatano wantatukambe Winaije wo naura tantunawi tutir. 
\q1  
\v 23 Nya marova wo winanenen, omamo vemo ndaraniv bayave inya, 
\q2 namirati wo naura usoowato rai rave kobe wem. 
\c 75  
\s1 Amisy Wepi Akari Titi Apa ana dapatimu moyar 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Vemo wapo vatane maupaisy inya.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Amisy, reamo kove raura seo irati Winai, 
\q2 reamo kove raura seo Nai muno reamo Nya tame rawain, 
\q2 muno reamo Nya ana ndave mbe anainambe ravovo. 
\q1  
\v 3 Amisye Po raura pare: ‘‘Arono Sya masyoto dapatimu mamaisy, 
\q2 weamo taune Risyirati Syo patimu moyare raugaje vatane mai mamaisyo awa ana udave rarijati. 
\q1  
\v 4 Arono mine so mantauno vatano ntuna rai mautan, 
\q2 weramu Risyirati Syo ama aji raveti ntindimu. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syo vatano mansararine maura syare: ‘Vemo wasararin nora,’ 
\q2 muno Syo vatano mamune\f + \fr 75:5 \fq vatano mamun \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.\f* maura syare: ‘Vemo wasangkakeraive wapa vambunine rai nora. 
\q1  
\v 6 Vemo wasangkakeraive, wapo wapa vambunine raijaseo titive inya, 
\q2 muno vemo wapo wapa popane ranepat inya.’ ’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Weye arono patimu maran omamo no no wanamuram muno ranijo varet umba nde ramu, 
\q2 muno no no ranijo wanampui\f + \fr 75:7 \fq wanampui: \ft Ayao Ibrani raijamo ama ine mare ‘‘anoko kanen,’’ weye anoko kanen ntami no Israel ama ranijo wanampui.\f* muno wanansai umba nde mo vatane maijaseo titive ramu. 
\q1  
\v 8 Yara Amisye Wepi Po patimugo marane raugaje, 
\q2 Po vatane inta mataopon yara Po vatano kaijinta maijaseo. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye AMISY Po Apa kapi raijar no aneme rai, ntairijo pari mangke rai, 
\q2 maisyare anggurijo mpariman dave ntairi rai no no aneme rai. 
\q1 No Apa kapi umaso rai, Po anggurije umaso rauvar, 
\q2 indamu vatano mamun mine so 
\q2 wo ramanam bintabo irati ama kapapere rautan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Yara risyamo rinananibe inanamote raijaseo tutir ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 rikangkamambe Amisy wama aneno Yakop beaje Aije Ai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Wepirati Po vatano mamune awa vambunine radaut, 
\q2 yara vatano kove\f + \fr 75:11 \fq vatano kove \ft onawamo vatano ubeta Amisye Apa ananyao rai mavabe.\f* nanawamo Po awa vambunine raveti miridi nseo. 
\c 76  
\s1 Amisy Po marova mataopon 
\p  
\v 1 Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukinyo rai, wo itari\f + \fr 76:1 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* raeyan. Masmur Asap po ratoe. Ransyeran. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Vatano una no munijo Yehuda wo Amisy aen tenambe 
\q2 muno Apa tame manakoe no Israel! 
\q1  
\v 3 Nai Salem\f + \fr 76:3 \ft Tamo ‘‘Salem’’ omamo tamo wusyin rave munijo Yerusalem rawain, ama tame rawain tavonamo ‘‘Sion.’’\f* Apa yavare ntami rije, 
\q2 Apa tuna ri rave mi Sion! 
\q1  
\v 4 Nai ratuije Wepi Po marova awa ato mbadurure radaut, 
\q2 muno awa vakane muno omako waravainy 
\q2 muno anaiyu randamisy tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wakoe! Amisy, Nya varo ngkove nggwaayan dave muno Winyi ntitito rave! 
\q2 Unato akokoe so nsayae no wusyinoe, 
\q2 weramu Winyi ntitijo rakivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 6 Vatano anaaniv awa anaiyu, awa ananuge rantauno mansai to, 
\q2 utaopon to, inta ubesea akato jewen. 
\q2 Naito anaaniv kakui awa vambunine rakanive mai to. 
\q1  
\v 7 Amisy, Winyirati reama aneno Yakop beaje Nai, Winyo mansanenen papabe, 
\q2 weti vatano usea kuda mai nawe, 
\q2 kuda nao ntaruran tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Wakoe, Wibuiny to, vatane wo nasyaniv! 
\q2 Vatane nawamo inta bambunin da te no namune rai kakai 
\q2 arono Nya pari mangke raugaje. 
\q1  
\v 9 Amisy, wino no munijo ntiti, arono Nyo patimuge raugaje, 
\q2 kawasae mine so ujani dave vintabo muno anamainitu mai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Arono wimbeseo indamu Nyo mangke raugaje, 
\q2 umba Nyo vatano matekarasyo no mine so maijaseo no awa siurije rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Tugae rave, vatano manuga mamun kai, 
\q2 AMISY Nyo masakinav weti ukangkamambe Nai. 
\q1 Muno vatano manuga pari no tawano maive onawamo indati ubevea marudija,\f + \fr 76:11 \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ine naiso mbare ramu. Ama ino kaijinta no taiso: Arono Amisye Po mangke raugaje Apa marova mai, vatano kaijinta wo raen ti indati ude utantuna Amisye akijani ubeaje Ai.\f* 
\q2 arono AMISY Nyo maugav akare ubeaje Nai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Ranivara wapo urairije raokokaisyo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 koveamo wasayae rai kobe. 
\q1 Vatan tenambe wana no AMISY akijani ri weap, 
\q2 koveamo wapo anakotare raugavere raunanto Ai, 
\q2 weye Opi mamaisyo asyaniv. 
\q1  
\v 13 Wepirati Po akari awa mangkakeraive radaut, 
\q2 Wepirati anaaniv kakuiveo akari titi mine so mai. 
\c 77  
\s1 Ransyeran weotoro Amisye anajo indamu aemeno wansai maisyare wusyinoe ramaisy 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. Nto irati Yedutun\f + \fr 77:1 \fq Yedutun: \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ayao so ama ine mare: ‘‘Kinyo ransyerane so rai mamaisyo Yedutun apa ananyao rai.’’ Yedutun apa anakere raura kakavimbe no 1Taw. 16:41-42.\f* ai, wepirati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Syo Amisye winawaino inanamoto manakoe rai, 
\q2 syo nawaino inanamoto manakoe rai, indamu Nyo rinaraniv. 
\q1  
\v 3 Arono rino irati ana nsosobe ama uga rai, syo Akoe winakani. 
\q1 No namano waravainyoe inaneme mamo mananai jewen, yara syo raijaseo tutir, indamu syo Amisye winanajo,\f + \fr 77:3 \ft Mamaisyo koano Yahudi rai, vatane maneme raijaseo arono ube sambayambe Amisye Ai, indamu wo anajo.\f* 
\q2 weramu mo inanuga so rayove ramu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ranivara syo Amisye winatantona, weamo syo winanonae, 
\q2 ranivara syo ratantonave, weamo sya vambunine meweno rinai rave kobe. 
\q1  
\v 5 Winyo inami raneka ti rigwaran tutir no arono naman, 
\q2 inanuga so ntanamanine jewen, weti syayao kakai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Syo masyoto arono wusyinoe ratantonave, 
\q2 syo tumo wusyino nde nto to ratantonave akare. 
\q1  
\v 7 Arono naman, syo rakaraebe, 
\q2 muno syo ratantonave no inanuga, ti syo raura syare: 
\q1  
\v 8 ‘‘Ntoa nuge nuganuija, Akoe ponae reansaija rao? 
\q2 Muno anuga ngkovo reansai jakato ramu rao? 
\q1  
\v 9 Apa muinyo no tawane mamo raumandi reansaija ntoa nuge nuganuija rako? 
\q2 Beto Apa urairi rai mamo ndea nsopi to rako? 
\q1  
\v 10 Amisye animari reansai ti bekobe reansai akato ramu to rako? 
\q2 Indako, pari ti aemeno reansai akato ramu rao?’’ 
\q1  
\v 11 Weti syo raura, syare: ‘‘Ana mo inaveti inanuga njorame mamo, 
\q2 Amisy Titi Rave, Apa vambunine meweno Ai to rako?’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Weramu AMISY, soamo rinaemen akato Nya ana ndave rai, 
\q2 syo Nya ana ndave mbe anainambe no arono wusyinoe ratantonave akare. 
\q1  
\v 13 Syare syo Nya ana ndave rakaraebeve, 
\q2 muno syo Nya ana ndave makokoive ratantonave. 
\q1  
\v 14 Sya Amisy, Nya ana ndave mamo ndandinit! 
\q2 Tugae, anawayo kotaro vatane wo masyanive nawamo inta awa vambunine mo Winya ramaisye ramu! 
\q1  
\v 15 Amisy, Wibuiny irati Nyo ana mbe anainambe raroron, 
\q2 Nyo Nya vambunine raroron ti susye kotare wo raen. 
\q1  
\v 16 Winyi nanemo vambunine veano Nya kawasae mapaya aroo rai no Mesir, 
\q2 onawirati susyo aneno Yakop muno Yusup.\f + \fr 77:16 \fq susyo aneno Yakop muno Yusup: \ft ama ine mare susyo Israel nao tenambe.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Sya Amisy, mayane mo naen ti njani dave, 
\q2 tugae, Mayano Kolsum mo naen ti ntutar, 
\q2 muno nawanano ntento ntutar dave. 
\q1  
\v 18 Andorame mo maru pape raveti maje, 
\q2 nai naume warae katitire ngkatitibe anyi, 
\q2 muno Nya ivake ratatukande maisyare atoe ratapo anyi wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 19 Nya katitire ravabari no ovaro maese uga rai, 
\q2 ivake mo nuge ravabasya, 
\q2 mine so mangkiki muno ntutar. 
\q1  
\v 20 Nyo Nya unanui rave no mayan,\f + \fr 77:20 \ft Mayane somamo Mayano Kolsum. \f* 
\q2 muno nyanya mayano mpanyoane umaso ama yasyine raito, 
\q2 weramu Nya une inta raene ramu. 
\q1  
\v 21 Nyo Nya kawasae maugav maisyare vatano po maero domba makume wemaisy, 
\q2 Musa muno Harun wenairati yo maugav. 
\c 78  
\s1 Amisye Apa anakotaro Po rave aneno Israel mai mbe ananyaobe wansai 
\p  
\v 1 Asap apa ransyerano ananyao. 
\b  
\q1 Inya, sya kawasae weap, wasamarikoame rasakinav de sya ananyao so rai, 
\q2 wapo rinaranivo sya ana idaura so rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Syare syo ananeneae mbe ananyaobe raura, 
\q2 muno syo anakotaro ngkokaibe no arono wusyine inta raura.\f + \fr 78:2 \ft Aneme so ratoe akato no Mat. 13:35. \f* 
\q1  
\v 3 Namirati reama aneno sinane wo rarire reansai ti, 
\q2 reamo ranaun muno no reansai, 
\q1  
\v 4 omamo reamo inta rangkokaibe irati reama arikainye mansai ramu. 
\q2 Yara reamo rarire indamu arikainyo mbeakaseo akato nawamo, 
\q1 wo AMISY Apa vambunine muno Apa ana dave makokoive, 
\q2 muno Apa ana dave mbe anaanibe ranaun. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Wepi Po Apa ananyao raugaje ntami vatano Israel mai, 
\q2 muno Po Apa anaparatote raunande Yakop apa susye umaso mai.\f + \fr 78:5 \ft Israel onawamo Yakop apa susyo po mampame naowa.\f* 
\q1 Po reama aneno sinane matutir 
\q2 indamu wo veano awa arikainye manyao. 
\q1  
\v 6 Indamu awa arikainyo mbeakaseo akato wo raen, 
\q2 onawamo arikainyo nanawirati mavaki rainye nao, 
\q2 ubeseo wo rarire irati awa arikainye mai akato. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wirati awa anave ransaroro Amisye obo Ai, 
\q2 muno vemo manimari Amisye Apa anakotaro Po rave rai jinya, 
\q2 yara ubeta Apa ananyao obo rai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 8 Indamu vemo wo awa aneno wusyine mansamaisy inya, 
\q2 nanawirati wonae ubeta Amisye Ai, muno usarirae ti umarovave Ai. 
\q1 Aneno susye umaso nawamo manuga ntindimu Amisye Ai jewen, 
\q2 muno matawandi utavondi Aije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 9 Naito susyo Efraim wo apae atoe raijar, 
\q2 weramu usarirae ti unanajibe arono usisa marova rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Onawamo usayae matuve urairi Amisye Po raokae nande mai raije ramu, 
\q2 muno wonae ubeta Apa anaparatote raiji. 
\q1  
\v 11 Onawamo manimarijo Apa anakotaro Po rave mai to rai, 
\q2 muno anakotaro mbe anainambe namirati Po rarorono mai to rai tavon. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 No awa anene mansamun, Amisye Po anainame rarorono mai, 
\q2 no munijo Mesir, nai anoko Soan.\f + \fr 78:12 \ft Anoko Soan no no mana akoe Nil ama ranijo wanamuram.\f* 
\q1  
\v 13 Po Mayano Kolsum raporar ti mansop, Po maugavo ama yasyine raito, 
\q2 mana umaso mamo Po ranoka ti ntet maisyare peno nteto rani rani ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 14 Apa kamuro kaipoe mirati mo mansaugavo unanui raito arono sansimane rai, 
\q2 muno taname mi mbaro mai no arono naman. 
\q1  
\v 15 Wepi Po oramo akoe raporar no anoko kanen, 
\q2 muno Po mana raunanto wo ramanam omamo Po raveti manakoe, maisyare waro nggwaro rave wemaisy.\f + \fr 78:15 \ft Kel. 17:1-7; Bil. 20:2-13\f* 
\q1  
\v 16 Po mana raveti muje no unato orame rai, 
\q2 muno Po raveti njam maisyare mana akoe wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Weramu nai anoko kanen onawamo wonae ubeta Amisy Titi Rave Aiji, 
\q2 wo ayao kakai rave tutiro Ai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Wo Amisye atopano awa ana udatantona no manuga rai, 
\q2 wo atan no anaisyo ubekedai rai.\f + \fr 78:18 \ft Kel. 16:2-15; Bil. 11:4-23,31-35\f* 
\q1  
\v 19 Wo Amisye aura tantunawi, ware: 
\q2 “Amisye pamo indati mamaisyo Po anaisye raunande wandaisy no anoko kanene so aje rako? 
\q1  
\v 20 Wamo raen to, Po oramo akoe ranepat, 
\q2 ti mana nsui uje rai, muno njam anyi. 
\q1 Weramu indati mamaisyo Po anaisyo roti me, maere me ratayao da 
\q2 Po raunande Apa kawasae reansai jaje rako?’’ 
\q1  
\v 21 Arono AMISY Po awa ayao wo rakere so ranaun, Opamo parijo mai rave, 
\q2 Po taname raugaje ti mo vatano susyo Yakop mansanen,\f + \fr 78:21 \ft Bil. 11:1-3\f* 
\q2 muno anuga ntatupamijo kawasae Israel umaso mai. 
\q1  
\v 22 Weye wanave Amisye Ai jakato ramu, 
\q2 muno mansanaveano amene ramu, ware Opamo bambunin da Po mapaya kakai rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 23 Weramu Po naume warae ratutir, 
\q2 indamu ama unsanda nsaneka anyi, 
\q1  
\v 24 umba Po anaisyo manna raugaje ti wo raisy, 
\q2 anaisyo manna so ntuna no munijo ntiti umba Po raugaje mai.\f + \fr 78:24 \ft Kel. 16:14-21; Bil. 11:7-9\f* 
\q1  
\v 25 Vatane umaso wo anaisyo naito Amisy wo raisye so raisy tavon, 
\q2 muno anaisyo Amisye Po ratayao mansamarome umaso mamo Po ratayao ti manui rave. 
\q1  
\v 26 Po ovaro wanamurame atutir ti puje no naume warae, 
\q2 muno Apa vambunine veano ovaro wanampui atutir ti tipu.\f + \fr 78:26 \ft Bil. 11:31-33\f* 
\q1  
\v 27 Po ovare umaso aveano insani maugav ti nde mansai manui rave, ti ratore kakai, 
\q2 muno ama manuije maisyare nayavo ntuna no mayane vone wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 28 Po insani umawe raveti ntatayaje no varodoro utantuna ri we rai janyi, 
\q2 ti mo awa randumo una rai rayapu kijani tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 29 Amisye Po awa bekere raunande mai ti mamaisyo mai, 
\q2 ti wo raisya uman to. 
\q1  
\v 30 Weramu arono uman dave rainy, 
\q2 yara ta wo raisya nene, 
\q1  
\v 31 arono naije Amisye anuga mamun ti pari mai rave. 
\q2 Weti Po vatano ubambunin ti upapirabe no Israel maubaisy, 
\q2 muno Po arikainyo baribuai Israel mansanave mamene maubaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 32 Maisyare omai damu wo ayao kakai rave tutir, 
\q2 muno wanave Amisye Apa anainamo Po rarorono mai rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 33 Maisyare omai ti Amisye Po awa matame raotar aje tumaimbe vayave ti makanive maisyare ovar bayave, 
\q2 muno tumo wo raijakaseo mamo una irati yanive ama uga rai. 
\q1  
\v 34 Arono Amisye Po inta maubaisy umba kaije usarirae ti wo akani wakare Ai jakato, 
\q2 usarirae wakare Ai manuga ntenami rautan. 
\q1  
\v 35 Naije umba mansaemen akare ware Amisye Wepirati unato oram mansamamavube Ai pije, 
\q2 muno Obo pi rati Amisy Titi Rave, Po mansapaya kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 36 Weramu onawamo wo apamponae, 
\q2 ayao aarurijate mi wo rator nanto Ai. 
\q1  
\v 37 Manuga nsarokir da no tawano Ai jewen, 
\q2 muno Apa urairi Po raokae nande mai mamo wo raijaro matuve ramu. 
\q1  
\v 38 Weramu Opamo aemeno mai tutir, 
\q2 Po mapaya irati awa ayao kakai rai, 
\q2 muno Po maubai da makanive jewen. 
\q1 Atawandi Apa parije rai tutir bayave, 
\q2 muno Apa pari mangke mamo Po rangkumi ti Po raude mai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 39 Opamo aemeno mansai weye onawamo vatan bayave nao ti, 
\q2 maisyare ovaro ta deto ti akanive ti pakare jewene wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 40 Abo! Arono nai anoko kanen onawamo wonae tutiro ubeta Aiji, 
\q2 muno wo aveti anuga ranimaumbe, arono una no anoko kanen umaso. 
\q1  
\v 41 Wo Amisye atopan tutir bayave, 
\q2 wo Amisy Dandinit, Israel taune ubeaje Ai, aveti anuga njoramo mai. 
\q1  
\v 42 Wo Apa vambunine ratantona ramu, 
\q2 namirati arono Po veano mapaya irati awa marova mai wem. 
\q1  
\v 43 Arono Po anainame raroron anyi no munijo Mesir, 
\q2 muno anapaporainyo Po rave no anoko Soan.\f + \fr 78:43 \ft Anoko Soan no no mana akoe Nil ama ranijo wanamuram no munijo Mesir.\f* 
\q1  
\v 44 Purarijato awa mana rai ti mbe mavuve,\f + \fr 78:44 \ft Kel. 7:17-21\f* 
\q2 weti wo ramaname mamo mamaisye jewen. 
\q1  
\v 45 Po abuu manui ratutiro mai ti mo mansayapu muno mo mansatatao, 
\q2 muno Po kunaije raveti mo anare munije we raisy ti mewen.\f + \fr 78:45 \ft Kel. 8:1-7\f* 
\q1  
\v 46 Po ao ratande ti mo awa anare raisy, 
\q2 muno nawaisye ama ine mamo kao mine wo raotar ti mewen.\f + \fr 78:46 \ft Kel. 10:1-20\f* 
\q1  
\v 47 Po maru orame raveti maje awa anare anggurije rai ti mo rakupi, 
\q2 muno inyo ara mamo Po maru es raude rai ti nsamondak.\f + \fr 78:47 \ft Kel. 9:22-25\f* 
\q1  
\v 48 Po maru orame raveti maje tavon irati awa maero makume mai, 
\q2 muno Po ivake ratukande tavon ti mo awa maero makume maubaisy. 
\q1  
\v 49 Po Apa parijo mamoane rapaya aje mai, 
\q2 pari me, siurije me yaude kava, 
\q2 maisyare naito wene inta maroyaro mai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 50 Opamo atawandi jakato Apa parije rai ramu, 
\q2 muno wene mamo Po mapaya rai akato jewen, 
\q2 yara Po waneno mangke raude ratutumbe mai kobe. 
\q1  
\v 51 Po arikainyo ananuiny Mesir mansao bintabo,\f + \fr 78:51 \ft Kel. 12:29\f* 
\q2 wenawamo arikainyo mavaki anuive no yavaruga Mesir rai janyi nao.\f + \fr 78:51 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘yavaruga Ham.’’ Munijo Mesir rawain tavonamo ‘‘munijo Ham,’’ weye Nuh apa arikainyo Ham muno apa susyo po mampame una no naije. \f* 
\q1  
\v 52 Po vatano Israel mansaugav wusya maisyare maero domba maugave wemaisy, 
\q2 Po maugav wanya no anoko kanen maisyare domba maugave wemaisy.\f + \fr 78:52 \ft Kel. 13:17-22\f* 
\q1  
\v 53 Po maugavo mavabe ti una kovo saumane rai muno ujanive jewen, 
\q2 yara awa marova nawamo Po makuvu asyo no mayane ate.\f + \fr 78:53 \ft Kel. 14:26-28\f* 
\q1  
\v 54 Po mansaugav usisa no kopa taune Apa ura raije rai, 
\q2 ude no unato taune Apa vambunine veano raugav amarome rai.\f + \fr 78:54 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware unate so omamo Unato Sion, yara kuruno kaijinta ware unate somamo unato ntuna anyi no munijo Israel.\f* 
\q1  
\v 55 Arono usisa no kopa so rai, Po susyo ntuna rai mawatano marambe mai. 
\q2 Umba Po muni umaso raosoro Israel mai indamu awa ura rai tutir. 
\q2 Muno Po susye umaso awa munije raunande susyo Israel mai tenambe indamu utantuna rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 56 Weramu wonae ubeta Amisy Titi Rave Ai, muno wo atopan, 
\q2 muno wo Apa ananyao raijaro matuve jewen. 
\q1  
\v 57 Onawamo matawandi utavondi Amisye Ai jakato jewen, yara makirive Ai, maisyare awa aneno sinane mansamaisy. 
\q2 Muno mansanuga nsarokiro Ai jakato jewen maisyare apae moto ngkavine wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 58 Wo Amisye aveti anuga njoramo mai rave, 
\q2 weye wo tewa orame ranarijo awa yare mansamarom no unate rai janyi, 
\q2 muno wo aveti anuga mamuno mai weye ubeaje yare obo mai. 
\q1  
\v 59 Amisye Po Israel awa ubetaije maisye raen, 
\q2 weti pari rave muno ponae mai rave kobe. 
\q1  
\v 60 Po Apa randumo tuna rai no Silo\f + \fr 78:60 \fq Apa randumo tuna rai no Silo: \ft omamo randumo manasyino Kasyamo Urairi ntuna rije, arono Yavar Amisy Yerusalem rauseo nte dainy. Kasyamo Urairi umaso mamo Harun apa isyo me, orame vasye jirum Anaparatot Amisy ratoe yai muno vabiu anaisyo manna raveasyo ntuna rai omirati ntuna uga rai.\f* rapaya ti ntami, 
\q2 omamo randumo de tuna\f + \fr 78:60 \fq randumo de tuna rai: \ft omamo Kasyamo Urairi mirati ntuna rai, mbe rarorombe Amisye de no mansatavon.\f* rai no vatano mine so awa yasyin. 
\q1  
\v 61 Kasyamo Urairi omirati Apa kovo ntiti raeno rai, 
\q2 omamo aneme mpaya rai ti marova wo raugav.\f + \fr 78:61 \ft 1Sam. 4:1-11\f* 
\q1  
\v 62 Pari Apa kawasae taune Po matayao terave amarome umaso mai ti, 
\q2 Po mapaya ti awa marova wo maotaro omake rai. 
\q1  
\v 63 Awa arikainyo anya baribuai nawamo marova mo maunto ti mewen,\f + \fr 78:63 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘taname mo mansanen ti makanive.’’\f* 
\q2 weti wanya kamurame inta ubauname ramu ti ransyerano vauname inta ranaun akatoe jewen. 
\q1  
\v 64 Awa syene nawamo marova wo maotaro omake rai, 
\q2 weti awa wanya ube kavinive, weramu woyovo mai kakai.\f + \fr 78:64 \fq woyovo mai kakai: \ft ama ine mare Israel wo marova rave tutir weti wo awa koke rantuna omamo mangkeo mai, muno naito mamune usoowato mai ti wanya kavini woyove kakai.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 65 Weti umba Akoe beseo kobe, maisyare vatano niki ti beseo kai wemaisy, 
\q2 maisyare anaanivo po angguri ramanam ti mo vambunine raugavo ai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 66 Weti Po Apa marova manepat ti wansuk akiri muno unanajibe, 
\q2 muno Po mapinde ti awa tame ngkakai\f + \fr 78:66 \fq awa tame ngkakai: \ft 1Sam. 5:6-12\f* ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 67 Ponae irati Yusup apa ajavi mai, 
\q2 onawirati Epraim apa susye nao, 
\q2 muno Po matayao akato ramu.\f + \fr 78:67 \ft Susyo Epraim una no munijo Israel ama ranijo wanansai, yara susyo Yehuda una no ranijo wanampui.\f* 
\q1  
\v 68 Yara Po susyo Yehuda obo matayao terave akato amarom, 
\q2 muno anuga no unato Sion rai indamu tuna rai.\f + \fr 78:68 \ft Unato Sion omamo no no munijo akoe Yehuda. \f* 
\q1  
\v 69 Po Apa Yavaro ndandinit rauseo nteto tindimuve, 
\q2 maisyare naumo ntiti me mine so me no tindimuve ntoa nuge nuganui wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 70 Po Daud wepi vatano panapatambeo Ai atayao, 
\q2 umba Po augav no apa anakero po maero domba mansayaranande rai. 
\q1  
\v 71 LuPo augav no apa anakero po domba akoe me tuvane me makume rai, 
\q2 indamu be akarive kawasae Israel\f + \fr 78:71 \fq Israel: \ft Ayao Ibrani mo ‘‘Yakop’’ ratoe. Susyo Yakop ama ine mare kawasae Israel, weye aneno Yakop awain tavonamo ‘‘Israel.’’\f* mai muno po mansayaranande, 
\q2 weye onawirati kawasae Amisye taune Po matayao terave amarom. 
\q1  
\v 72 Daud po mansayaranande anuga nsarokire rai, 
\q2 muno po mansaugavo mavabe unanui ngkove rai. 
\c 79  
\s1 Amisye anajo arono marova mo wansakupi 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Sya Amisy, susyo wanave Nai jewene unandesena utantuna Nya kopa no tawan Nyo ratayao reansai so rai to. 
\q1 Wo Nya Yavaro ndandinite raveti nggwambe,\f + \fr 79:1 \ft Mamaisyo vatano Israel awa ana udatantona rai, ranivara susyo marano wanave Amisye Ai jewen usisa no Yavaro Amisy, weamo wo raveti nggwambe.\f* 
\q2 muno wo Yerusalem randamisyi ti nsivuve ti ntuna.\f + \fr 79:1 \ft Anakotare so nande arono tumo 586 arono Yesus ano rainy. Ayao so raura kakavimbe no 2Raj. 25:8-10; 2Taw. 36:17-19; Yer. 52:12-14.\f* 
\q1  
\v 2 Wo Nya kawasae wo maubaisye awa koke randaraive ti ntuna, 
\q2 weti insani wo ana mbauge raisye ude wo raisy, 
\q2 muno make sansinao wo Nya vatano matawandi utavondi Nai umaso awa ine raisy. 
\q1  
\v 3 No Yerusalem ama uga raito, wo vatane maubaisy ti awa mavu njam maisyare mana, 
\q2 muno awa koke mamo inta umamaisyo wo rantuna ramu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Susyo una reansakijani so wo reansampami, 
\q2 wugoeno reansai muno wo reansaura tantunawi. 
\q1  
\v 5 Sya AMISY, indati wimpari reansaija ntoa nuge nuganuija e? 
\q2 Ntoa nanduija umba winanuga mpari ntatupami ti maisyare tanamo mbadurure ma nsopija? 
\q1  
\v 6 Syare Nya pari mangke rasuijo susyo wanave Nai jewene mai, 
\q2 muno munijo ubeaje Winai jewene mai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 7 Weye wo Nya kawasae Israel reansaupaeta ti reansakanive to, 
\q2 muno wo reama munije randamisyi ti ntuna. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Vemo Nyo reama anene awa ayao kakai raugakaje reandanawan inya. 
\q2 Syare nyavave ra naemeno reansai, 
\q2 weye reambambunin akato ramu to. 
\q1  
\v 9 Sya Amisy, Winyirati Nyo reansapaya irati kakai rai, syare naemeno reansai, 
\q2 wirati indamu Nya tame raijaseo titive! 
\q1 Syare Nyo reansapaya irati marova mai, muno Nyo reama ayao kakai rapaya tavon, 
\q2 wirati indamu Nya tame raijaseo titive! 
\q1  
\v 10 Abo! Mbeanimaibe susyo wanave Amisye Ai jewene wo reansaura ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Wapa Amisye Pi ro, yara Po wasayaranande ramu ge?’’ 
\q1 Koveamo mangke ndasakinavo susye umaso mai mamo reansami ntami rai anawadive, 
\q2 weye wo Nya kawasae maubaisy weti awa mavu nsopat. 
\q1  
\v 11 Syare Nyo vatano makova awa anonae ranaun, 
\q2 koveamo vatano mapatimu maubaisye so nawamo Nyo mapaya rai indamu ukov, 
\q2 mamaisyo Nya vambunino manakoe rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Akoe Winy, syare Nyo mangke rasakinavo susyo una reansakijani so mai, 
\q2 Nyo mangke ratutumbe mai,\f + \fr 79:12 \fq mangke ratutumbe mai: \ft Ayao Ibrani mare mangke raugaje mamo vari kaururum, ama ine mare mangke raugaje mamo ntairi rave. Mamaisyo vatano Israel awa ana wo ratantona rai, kaururum omamo vari mamai dave.\f* weye wo winaura tantunawi. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weti reami Nya kawasae maisyare maero domba Nyo reansakum, 
\q2 indati reamo kove raura seo Nai tutira ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno reama susyo mbakipambe iridito ukangkamambe Nai tutir. 
\c 80  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po anakotare raveramu ngkovo wansai jakato 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ransyerane so ama kine mo ransyerano kaijinta ramai tavon, namirati ama akari mare: ‘‘Aepare ama ug, mbe urairive rai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Inya Amisy, Winyirati Nyo vatano Israel makum maisyare vatano po maero domba makume wemaisy, 
\q2 syare namarikoame rasakinav de. 
\q1 Winyirati Nyo Yusup\f + \fr 80:2 \ft Tamo Yusup mare kawasae Israel nao.\f* apa susye maugavo mavabe maisyare vatano po maero domba maugave amaisy. 
\q1 Tugae, Winyirati nde ntuna no ana yatotov kerub\f + \fr 80:2 \fq kerub \ft omamo Israel awa ana akokoe wo ratotov indamu mo naito Amisy una no Manunggara mansanyi.\f* aya yasyine rai indamu mbe akarive, 
\q2 syare Nyo Nya kovo ntiti raroron, 
\q1  
\v 3 ndaroron irati susyo Epraim, Manasye\f + \fr 80:3 \fq Epraim, Manasye \ft onayamo Yusup apa kavo nanaije, susye jirume so yaurata irati kawasae Israel nanawirati utantuna no wanansai mai. Yara Benyamin opamo Yusup apa rijata pije, susyo Benyamin aurata irati kawasae Israel nanawirati utantuna no wanampui mai.\f* muno Benyamin mai. 
\q2 Wimbeseo ra Nyo Nya vambunine rarorono reansai, 
\q2 muno nde ramu Nyo reansapaya irati marova rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Amisy, reamare Nyo anakotare raveramu ngkovo reansai maisyare arono wusyine wemaisy akato, 
\q2 Reamare Nya kove mbaro reansai, wirati indamu reampaya irati kakai rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY, Winyirati Amisy Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti, 
\q2 Nya kawasae reansambayambe Winai to, 
\q2 weramu wimpari mangkebe reansai tutir bayave kobea e? 
\q1  
\v 6 Nyo siuri manakoe raugaje reansai ti reamoyov tutir, 
\q2 weti reansami ngkaru nsoyan maisyare omirati reama anaisye mije, 
\q2 muno maisyare omirati reama mana ramaname wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Winseambe reansai ti susyo una reansakijani so taune warare vambinibe mai reama kopa rai, 
\q2 reama marova wo reansaura tantunawi muno wugoeno reansai. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY, Winyirati Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti, 
\q2 reamare Nyo anakotare raveramu ngkovo reansai maisyare arono wusyine wemaisy akato. 
\q2 Reamare Nya kove mbaro reansai, wirati indamu reampaya irati kakai rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Nya kawasae Israel reamamo maisyare angguri moto Nyo rapatin ti ndaugav no Mesir. 
\q2 Nyo susye kotar una no Kanaan\f + \fr 80:9 \fq kawasae Kanaan: \ft Vatano utantuna wusyimbe munijo Kanaan rai onawamo vatano Het, Girgasi, Amori, Kanaan, Feris, Hewi, Yebus. Raen no Ul. 7:1-6.\f* mawatan ti uta muno Nyo reansaveti reantantuna awa muni rai akato, 
\q2 maisyare Nyo angguri mote umaso rantet no awa kopa rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 10 Maisyare kopa ndatayao ti angguri ranteto rai wemaisy, 
\q2 Winyo munije ratayao Israel reansamarom. 
\q1 Muno maisyare angguri ndantete umaso ama wantainye musyo rai wemaisy, 
\q2 Winyo reansaveti reambambunin, weti reamo munije umaso ratatuv tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 11 Reantantuna munijo Kanaan rai tenambe, maisyare angguri ntubai ti nsani manakoe rave wemaisy, 
\q2 ti ngkamajugambe irati unate rai janyi muno ama wate mo inyo aras makokoe ratatuv.\f + \fr 80:11 \ft Unate ntami no munijo Kanaan ama ranijo wanampui, muno inyo araso ntiti ntubai no Libanon no no ranijo wanansai, weti ananeneae so ama ine mare kawasae Israel utantuna no munijo Kanaan ama ranijo wanampui muiya nto no ranijo wanansai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 12 Maisyare angguri wate nsonao usyo no mayane vone wemaisy, 
\q2 Israel utantuna munije we raita ti nto musyo no mayane vone. 
\q1 Maisyare wai nsani ti nto nggwaravainye wemaisy, 
\q2 Israel utantuna munije we raita ti nto nanto no mana Eprat. 
\q1  
\v 13 Sya Amisy, mbe animaibe wino reansaora akato jewen? 
\q2 Israel reama marova usisa ti wo reansakupi, 
\q2 muno susyo mamun una reansakijani ude wo reama ananuge raugaveto reansaora.\f + \fr 80:13 \ft Ayao Ibrani mo ananeneae so ratoe, mare: ‘‘naneme mpaya reansai ti marova wo reama nawaisye ama yane randamisyi, ti vatano wo raide wo ama ine raowen ti mewen.’’ Ayao umaso ama ine maisyare ratoe no aneme so wemaisy.\f* 
\q1  
\v 14 Maisyare uge siso po nawaisye rakumbire wemaisy, 
\q2 muno gusye po nawaisye raisy ti mewene wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 15 Amisy Winyirati Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti, 
\q2 wintuna no munijo Manunggara, syare nsakina de muno Nyo reansaeno ana mo reansakupi so rai! 
\q2 Syare Nyo angguri moto ndantet, omirati Israel, reansayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 16 Taune Winyirati Nyo reama aneno Israel matayao maisyare Nyo angguri mote rantete wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Nyo ama kamino wanyine raveti mbambunin. 
\q1  
\v 17 Weramu soamo reama marova wo raotar bintabo muno wo taname veano ramer, 
\q2 weti syare Nya pari mangke veano reama marova umaso maupaeta ra makanive! 
\q1  
\v 18 Syare Nyo Nya kawasae nanuga no maije reansayaranande, 
\q2 weye reamamo vatano Nyo reansatayao terave namarom to. 
\q1  
\v 19 Weti indati reamusya marambe Winai jakato ramu. 
\q2 Syare Nyo kovo wanyine raude reansai, weamo indati reangkangkamambe Nya tame rai. 
\q1  
\v 20 AMISY, Winyirati Amisy Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti, 
\q2 reamare Nyo anakotare raveramu ngkovo reansai maisyare arono wusyine wemaisy akato. 
\q2 Reamare Nya kove mbaro reansai, wirati indamu reampaya irati kakai rai. 
\c 81  
\s1 Amisye Po Apa kawasae mansanayao indamu wo araniv 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Mamaisyo ransyeran ‘‘Gitit’’\f + \fr 81:1 \ft Ayao ‘‘Gitit’’ ama ine raene ramu. Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware ama ine mare ransyerano munijo Gat, weramu kuruno kaijinta ware omamo ransyerano vatano Israel ukiny dai arono wo anggur ama mane rakugan no mampiriare rai, weye ayao Gat ama ine mare ‘‘mampiriaro anggur.’’\f* rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Syare wangkinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo Amisye Ai, Wepirati wama vambunine nsawa Ai. 
\q2 Wansananibe wanggwain wamo Amisye aijaseo titive, Wepirati aneno Yakop beaje Ai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare wangkinyo ransyerane raijo wansanamoto manakoe rai, muno wamo airape\f + \fr 81:3 \fq airape \ft ranigwano ‘‘rebana’’ rai. Rebana ranepat maisyare airape ranepat wemaisy.\f* ranepato rai, 
\q2 muno wamo itari anakoe muno itari mamaun\f + \fr 81:3 \fq itari anakoe muno itari mamaun \ft ranigwano ‘‘gambus’’ muno ‘‘kecapi’’ yai.\f* raeyan dai indamu ama kine marinsawan dave. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare wamo tavuna\f + \fr 81:4 \fq tavuna \ft ranigwano sangkakala Israel wo rave rai, omamo kambino anya apa korodowai. \f* ramawisy arono wama masyoto akokoe rai, 
\q2 arono embae wanyine mpirak kai, 
\q2 muno arono embae nsiso ntunai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye wemamo Amisye Po rapatimu to indamu vatano Israel utavondi rai, 
\q2 omamo ananyao Amisy aneno Yakop beaje Ai Po rapatimu. 
\q1  
\v 6 Amisye Po Apa ananyao umaso raugaje ntami irati vatano Israel\f + \fr 81:6 \fq Israel: \ft ayao Ibrani mo ‘‘Yusup’’ ratoe, ama ine mare vatano Israel.\f* mai, 
\q2 no arono Opamo be marovave vatano Mesir mai, 
\q2 no arono we reamo ayao kaijinta reamantatukambe raije inta ranaun. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Amisye Po raura aje reansai pare: ‘‘Syo mangke nsawa wasaivame rai rapaya to, 
\q2 muno Syo wasaneme rapaya irati anakero mangke rai to. 
\q1  
\v 8 Arono wana irati nsosobe ama uga rai weapo rinawain, weamo Risyo weasapaya rai to. 
\q2 No katitire kine ama uga rai Rino no we, syayao nande irati wasai, 
\q2 Risyo wapa anave ratopan no mana ami Meriba.\f + \fr 81:8 \ft Kel. 17:1-7 muno Bil. 20:1-13 \f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Inya, Sya kawasae weap, Syare Syo wasanayao ti wadaraniv! 
\q2 Inya Israel, ribeker syare wapo rinaraniv! 
\q1  
\v 10 Vemo wasambayambe irati anawayo akoe rui vayave inta ai nora, yara Ribui inai,\f + \fr 81:10 \ft Kel. 20:3\f* 
\q2 muno vemo weabeaje irati vatano marane awa anawayo kotare mai nora. 
\q1  
\v 11 Risyirati AMISY, weapa Amisy wabeaje Ai Wepi Risy, 
\q2 Risyirati Syo wasaugav uje irati munijo Mesir raora. 
\q2 Arono rui weamaror, weamo Syo anaisye raunande ti weapo raisya wea man dave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Weramu Sya kawasae wonae wo Sya ayao ranauni, 
\q2 muno kawasae Israel wonae ubeta irati Rinaiji. 
\q1  
\v 13 Maisyare omaiti, inaneme mpaya indamu una manuga matu rautan, 
\q2 muno utavondi taune awa bekere rai kai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Syare ranivara Sya kawasae wo rinaraniv, 
\q2 ranivara Israel utavondi Sya unanuije rai, wea umbaya! 
\q1  
\v 15 Arono naije kobeamo, indati Syo awa marova mataruran kobe, 
\q2 muno rinanemo vambunine mo awa marova mapinde. 
\q1  
\v 16 Vatano manuga mamuno Rinai nanawamo indati ujaniv ti ututar no Rinamun, 
\q2 muno awa mangke mamo indati ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 17 Weramu Sya kawasae weap, Syo anaisyo ngkov dave raunande wasai, 
\q2 muno Syo weasaveti waman irati anyaune ama mana manavan dave rai.’’ 
\c 82  
\s1 Amisy Po mamaisye rapatimugo ana akokoe\f + \fr 82:0 \fq ana akokoe: \ft ama ine mare ana ntuna no naume warae, maisyare anawayo akoe dako naito Amisye dako, nanawirati Amisye Po vambunine raugaje mai indamu ube akarive susye kotaro mine so mai. Umba ama ino kaijinta ntavonamo mare vatano akokoe nanawirati ube akarive no mine vone so rai.\f* Po manari mai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. 
\q1 Amisye Pi be akarive anugano akoe rai no Manunggara, 
\q2 umba Po patimu mamaisye raugaje ana akokoe nanawirati Po vambunino manakoe raunanto maije mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Pare: ‘‘Ntoa nandui rati umba patimu wadaugaje ti mamaisyo Sya bekere rai jewene ma wadapayawa? 
\q2 Muno wasamunggarerave vatano mamune\f + \fr 82:2,4 \fq vatano mamune: \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Ai muno Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.\f* mai nsopija? 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare wapo mamaisye rapatimugo arikainyo wawate muno vatano mayondi mai, 
\q2 muno wapo marimbe vatano siuri mai muno awa ana jajewembe mai, mamaisyo Sya ananyao rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare wapo vatano mayondi muno awa ana jajewembe mai mapaya, 
\q2 syare wapo mapaya irati vatano mamune mansaneme rai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 5 Ana akokoe umaso nanawamo wananepabe muno awa ana udakarae ngkove ramu. 
\q2 Wenawamo wanya tutir no kaumure rai.\f + \fr 82:5 \fq wanya tutir no kaumure rai: \ft ama ine mare wo mamune bo raijar tutir.\f* 
\q2 Ananyao mo kawasae wansaokaisye mamo wo ratakar doyadi. 
\q1  
\v 6 Syo raura mai to, syare: ‘‘Weapamo maisyare Amisye rinamaisy,\f + \fr 82:6 \ft Yoh. 10:34\f* 
\q2 Amisy Titi Rave Apa arikainye nanawirati wea tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 7 Weramu weapamo Syo mangke raugaje wasai: 
\q2 indati wananta wene rai maisyare vatane mansamaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare akarijo mine waraya mansamaisy tenambe, indati wakakai tavon.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Sya Amisy, syare wimbeseo Nyo mamaisye rapatimu mine so rai, 
\q2 weye susyo mine tename so mainyamo taune Winya ma. 
\c 83  
\s1 Amisye anajo inda be marovave Israel awa marova mai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Asap po ratoe. Ransyeran. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Amisy, vemo wimanin bayave nora, 
\q2 sya Amisy, vemo Nyo rinaranivi vayave nora, 
\q2 vemo winaneme kapan ti ntuna vayave inya. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye ndaen, Nya marova usea utararae, 
\q2 vatano manuga mamuno Naije umaso mangkakeraive ware umarovave Nai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Onawamo makari nsansinao ti wanyinyaube inda umarovave Nya kawasae mai, 
\q2 manatantonave kakai raijo Nya vatano winanuga no maije mai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wo raura ware: ‘‘Wade ra wamo susye so raupaeta ra rakanive, 
\q2 indamu tamo Israel ranaumbe akato inya.’’ 
\q1  
\v 6 Tugae, onawamo manuga mbe intabove to, 
\q2 wo urairije raokaisy ware umarovave Winai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Onawamo susyo Edom\f + \fr 83:7 \ft Susyo Edom onawamo Esau apa susyo bakipambe nanawije, utantuna no Israel ama ranijo wanampui. Umarovave vatano Israel mai tutir. Kej. 36; Maz. 137:7; Amos 1:11-12\f* muno susyo Ismael,\f + \fr 83:7 \ft Susyo Ismael onawamo Ismael apa susye nao, utantuna no mana Yordan ama ranijo wanamuram. Kej. 25:12-16\f* susyo Moab\f + \fr 83:7 \ft Susyo Moab onawamo Lot apa susye nao, utantuna no mana Yordan ama ranijo wanamuram no varoro wanampui. Umarovave vatano Israel mai tutir. Kej. 19:36-38; Bil. 22-24; Amos 2:1-3\f* muno susyo Hagar.\f + \fr 83:7 \ft Susyo Hagar onawamo Hagar ama susye nao, utantuna no mana Yordan ama ranijo wanamuram arono Saul be akarive Israel rai. 1Taw. 5:10, 19, 20\f* 
\q1  
\v 8 Susyo Gebal,\f + \fr 83:8 \ft Susyo Gebal \ft utantuna mararai no Mayano Nsakam rai, no Israel ama ranijo wanampui. Yosua 13:5\f* Amon\f + \fr 83:8 \ft Amon \ft onawamo Lot apa susye inta nanawije, utantuna no mana Yordan ama ranijo wanamuram, no Moab ama ranijo wanansai. Umarovave vatano Israel mai tutir. 2Taw. 20:10; Amos 1:13-15\f* muno Amalek,\f + \fr 83:8 \ft Vatano Amalek inta utantuna no mana Yordan ama ranijo wanamuram muno inta utantuna no Yehuda ama ranijo wanampui. 1Sam. 15:2\f* 
\q2 Pilistea\f + \fr 83:8 \ft Pilistea utantuna no Israel ama ranijo varet, mararai no Mayano Nsakam. 1Sam. 4:1, 29:1\f* muno vatano ntuna munijo Tirus\f + \fr 83:8 \ft Munijo Tirus omamo kota no no Israel ama ranijo wanansai inta mije. Amos 1:9-10\f* raije rautan. 
\q1  
\v 9 Umba Asyur\f + \fr 83:9 \ft Asyur omamo munijo manakoe muno mbambunin dave no Israel ama ranijo wanansai. 2Raj. 15:19\f* wanugande maijaro matavon, 
\q2 indamu wo sopambe Lot apa susye mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Amisy, syare Winyo mangke rasakinavo mai maisyare Nyo vatano Midian mansao to wemaisy.\f + \fr 83:10 \ft Hakim 6-7\f* 
\q2 Umba maisyare Nyo Sisera muno Yabin\f + \fr 83:10 \ft Yabin opamo akari titi munijo Kanaan, muno Sisera opirati be akarive naite mai. Hakim 4.\f* yaubai no mana Kison wemaisy, 
\q1  
\v 11 muno aya naite maubaisy no En-Dor, 
\q2 weti awa koke ntuna vayave ti mandamisy no kopa we rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Muno awa akari usayae usye rai nao maubai tavon maisyare Oreb muno Seeb\f + \fr 83:12 \fq Oreb muno Seeb: \ft Hakim 7:23-8:3\f* yamaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare Sebah muno Salmuna\f + \fr 83:12 \fq Sebah muno Salmuna: \ft Hakim 8:4-21\f* yamai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 13 Awa ana udaura mare: ‘‘Wade ra wansisa ntantuna nande Amisye Apa kawasae Israel awa kopa raora, 
\q2 indamu wamave rai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 14 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo mansavera maisyare anaingkainyo kupe nsaone wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare kapumo ovare damawisyamo nsaon tavone wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 15 Syare Nyo maupaeta ra makanive maisyare taname mo anate ranen ti mewene wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare ama vadurure mansanano unate rai janyi ti mangkudi wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 16 Maisyare omaisy, Nyo repe atutir indamu dijat po mangkat, 
\q2 muno Nyo mapapabe irati ovaro maese ai indamu ujaniv. 
\q1  
\v 17 Sya AMISY, koveamo Nyo awa tame ravera ngkakai, 
\q2 indamu wo Nya vambunine raen, muno ude ubeaje Nai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Koveamo usamane muno ujaniv ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno awa tame ngkakai ti wene mo maugav kobe. 
\q1  
\v 19 Wirati wo raen ti wo naura ware Wibuinyirati AMISY, 
\q2 Wibuinyirati Amisy Ntiti Rave wimbe akarive mine tename so rai. 
\c 84  
\s1 Bekero to no Yavaro Amisy 
\p  
\v 1 Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukinye maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Mamaisyo ransyeran ‘‘Gitit’’\f + \fr 84:1 \ft Ayao ‘‘Gitit’’ ama ine raene ramu. Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware ama ine mare ransyerano munijo Gat, weramu kuruno kaijinta ware omamo ransyerano vatano Israel ukiny dai arono wo anggur ama mane rakugan no mampiriare rai, weye ayao Gat ama ine mare ‘‘mampiriaro anggur.’’\f* rai. Masmur vatano susyo Kora wo ratoe. 
\q1  
\v 2 Wakoe, reama AMISY, vatane manayanambe Nya ntuna ri rai weye ngkov dave. 
\q2 Tugae AMISY, Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti pi Winy! 
\q1  
\v 3 Tugae, inanuga ntove rave AMISY Nya Yavare ama wanijate rai. 
\q1 Inanasine tename so ranayanambe, 
\q2 nggwain Amisy aijaseo titive, Wepirati Amisy noa pitawabe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Umba insani pisye po apa ene ranari 
\q2 muno insani pisawane apave ene rai 
\q2 indamu apa tuvane utantuna rai, 
\q1 mararai no tewa oram anakotare rameseo AMISY Ai rai. 
\q2 Tugae, AMISY, Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti pi Winy! 
\q2 Winyirati sya Akari Titi muno sya Amisye pi Winy. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kove ngkov irati vatano utantuna no Nya yavare rai mai, 
\q2 masyote yanteter wo nararimbe tutir. 
\q1  
\v 6 Kove ngkov irati vatano nanawirati awa vambunine nsawa Nai mai, 
\q2 nanawirati ubeker wuruta ubeaje Nai no Unato Sion. 
\q1  
\v 7 Arono wanya kaivo ngkanembe raita, 
\q2 AMISY Po mana ami raveti ntatipu rai. 
\q2 Muno maruge makare mo kove raugavo kaivo ngkanene we rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Wenanao wanya wiridi uta, ubambunin dave kobe, 
\q2 weti uta nanta no Amisye Amun no Sion. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Sya AMISY, Winyirati Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti, 
\q2 syare namarikoame rasakinavo sya ana danajo rai. 
\q1 Winyirati Amisy reama aneno Yakop beaje Nai, 
\q2 syare Nyo inaraniv mavabe sya ana danajo ore rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Amisye Winy, syare Nya kove rarorono reama akari titi mine so ai, wepi teto reansaora, 
\q2 muno wepirati vatano Nyo atayao be akari titive reansai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Masyote intabo rino natavon no Nya yavar, 
\q2 omamo ngkov akato irati masyote pakoe ta na no varoro kaijinta. 
\q1 Sya bekere mamo syare tuna tawan no sya Amisye Apa Yavare ama unsanda akoe indamu syo rayaranande, 
\q2 omamo ngkov akato irati rino no vatano wonae Amisye Ai awa yavar. 
\q1  
\v 12 Weye AMISY Opamo wama Amisy Po wansayaranande, 
\q2 Wepirati muinyo wansai muno Po wansaijaseo kovo ntiti rai, 
\q1 AMISY Opamo bekobe irati vatano beto Aije ai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Tugae AMISY, Winyirati Akari Titi naito munijo ntiti, 
\q2 kove ngkov irati vatano napirati panave Naije ai. 
\c 85  
\s1 Vatano Israel wo Amisye anajo indamu Po kovo wanyine raugav akare mai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur susyo Kora wo ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, wusyinoeamo wimbekobe Nya muni Israel rai to, 
\q2 ti Nyo vatano Israel\f + \fr 85:2 \fq Israel: \ft Ayao Ibrani mo ‘‘Yakop’’ ratoe, ama ine mare kawasae Israel, weye aneno Yakop awain tavonamo ‘‘Israel.’’\f* maugav akare una kovo wanyine rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Nya kawasae awa ayao kakai mamo ndapaya mai to, 
\q2 awa ana udaveti ngkakai mamo Nyo raupae mai to. 
\q1  
\v 4 Nya pari mamo Nyo rakarimuta maora to, 
\q2 Nya parijo mamoane mamo makarea nanayao to. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Winyirati Amisy Nyo reansapaya irati kakai rai, reamare Nyo kovo wanyine raugav akare reansai, 
\q2 muno vemo mparijo reansai akato inya. 
\q1  
\v 6 Indati wimpari reansaija ntoa nuge nuganuija e? 
\q2 Muno Nya parije umaso no tawano susyo miridi nto mai kobea e? 
\q1  
\v 7 Reamare Nyo kovo maisyare wusyine ramaisye raugav akare reansai jakato, 
\q2 wirati indamu Nya kawasae reansananibe weye wimbekobe reansai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Sya AMISY, Nya muinyo no tawane rarorono reansai kai, 
\q2 muno Nyo reansapaya irati ana ngkakai rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Risyamo ibeke dave syare syo AMISY\f + \fr 85:9 \ft Ayao Ibrani mo tame jirum veano Amisye aura: \ft \+it Elohim YHWH.\+it* Ayao Yawa mo tame intabo obo ratoe: \+it AMISY.\+it*\f* Apa ayaowe raraniv. 
\q2 Weye Amisy Po raura pare Po kovo saumane raude Apa kawasae mai, 
\q1 nanawirati vatano matawandi utavondi Aije nao, 
\q2 indamu vemo usarirae wo ayao kakaije rave akato inya. 
\q1  
\v 10 Tugae rave, Opamo panatatayaube ra Po vatano wo asyanive mapaya kakai rai, 
\q2 wirati indamu no tawano Apa kovo ntiti rautan no wama munijo Israel so rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Amisy Apa muinyo no tawane me vatane awa matawandi utavondi Aije me ide yanunugambe, 
\q2 Apa moyare me vatane awa kovo saumane me yaneme raijar. 
\q1  
\v 12 Vatane awa matawandi utavondi Amisye Ai ntubai no mine so, 
\q2 muno Amisy Opamo moyar, tuna no munijo Manunggara Po mansanyanyut. 
\q1  
\v 13 Tugae, indati AMISY Po anakotaro ngkove raugaje wansai, 
\q2 muno wama kopa somamo anare rayanyum dai ama ine nande rai kobe. 
\q1  
\v 14 Amisy Po anakotar tenambe rave mamaisyo Apa moyare rai, 
\q2 weye Apa moyare muisyeve Ai mo unanui ratayao Ai. 
\c 86  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu aemeno rinai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ana danajo Amisye Ai. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, syare namarikoame rasakinavo rinai muno Nyo sya ana danajo ravera mamaisy, 
\q2 weye risyamo vatano mayondi muno sya ana jajewembe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Syare Nyo sya jayaisye so rayaranande weye risyamo inatawandi tavondi Winai tutir, 
\q2 risyamo syanapatambe Nai, muno syanave Nai, weti syare Nyo inapaya kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sya Akoe, Winyirati sya Amisy, syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 weye Wibuiny irati syo nawaino masyote anteter. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya Akoe Winy, risyamo syanapatambe Nai, weti syare Nyo anayanambe raugaje inanuga so rai, 
\q2 weye inanuga somamo daijaseo Winai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye tugae, Akoe Winyamo ngkov dave muno mayaro Nyo vatane awa ayao kakai rapaya, 
\q2 vatan tenambe wo nawaine nawamo, Nya muinyo no tawane mamo Nyo raveti njam tutiro mai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo sya ana danajo raraniv, 
\q2 muno Nyo sya ana dawain ore so ranaun, syare naemeno rinai! 
\q1  
\v 7 Arono rui rino ana nsosobe ama uga rai, risyo winawain, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Nyo sya ana danajo raveti mamaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Sya Akoe Winy, anawayo kotaro vatane wo masyanive nawamo inta wo winamaisye ramu, 
\q2 muno inta umamaisyo wo ana inta ravera mo Winya ramaisye kakai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Sya Akoe Winy, susye kotar tenambe Nyo manari nanawamo indati ukarimu ude, 
\q2 ude ubeaje no Winamun, 
\q2 muno wo naijaseo titive. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weye Winyirati mbambunin muno Nya ana ndave mamo mbe anaanibe, 
\q2 Wibuiny irati Amisye Pi Winy. 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo rinanyao Nya unanui rai, 
\q2 indamu syanya mamaisyo Nya ayao tugae rai. 
\q2 Syare Nyo inaveramu syo winasyaniv irati inanuga ntenami rautan. 
\q1  
\v 12 Sya Akoe, Winyirati sya Amisy, syo kove raura seo irati Winai rinanuga ntenami rautan, 
\q2 muno syo Nya tame rararimbea ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 13 Weye Nya muinyo no tawan omamo manakoeyo rinai, 
\q2 muno Nyo sya jugara apaya irati wene rai ti syasyo no amani jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Sya Amisy, vatano mararine ubesea ware umarovave rinai, 
\q2 vatano usoowate inta wanugan ti ware wo rinaubaisy, 
\q2 muno wo Amisy winatantona akato ramu. 
\q1  
\v 15 Weramu sya Akoe, Winyirati sya Amisy, Winyamo muiny dave muno naemeno rinai; 
\q2 Winyamo natawandi ngkov dave; 
\q2 Nya muinyo no tawane muno winteto Nya urairije rai mamo manakoe tutir. 
\q1  
\v 16 Syare namumbe de rinai muno naemeno rinai. 
\q2 Risyamo syanapatambe irati Nai, weti syare Nyo vambunine raugaje rinai. 
\q2 Muno risyamo, sya ingkoa mamo vatano manapatambe Winai, weti syare Nyo rinapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Sya AMISY, syare Nya kove inta raugaje rinai indamu mbe rarorombe Winyamo mbekobe irati rinai. 
\q2 Wirati vatano manuga mamuno rinai wo raen muno usamane, 
\q2 weye Nyo rinayaranande muno Nyo rinayove. 
\c 87  
\s1 Kangkamambe Amisye Apa munijo Yerusalem rai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran. Masmur vatano susyo Kora wo ratoe inta mi som. 
\b  
\q1 Nai unato ndandinit, AMISY Po Apa munije rauseo nteto rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Munije kotaro no no Israel, 
\q2 Yerusalem wemirati AMISY anuga no rai rave. 
\q1  
\v 3 Inya, Amisye Apa munije winy ndanide, 
\q2 Amisye Po ayao ngko dave raura aje Yerusalem wibuiny nai, pare: 
\q1  
\v 4 ‘‘Wakoe! Vatano Mesir\f + \fr 87:4 \fq Mesir: \ft no Ayao Amisy kaijinta mo ama tamo wusyine ratoe tavon, omamo Rahab. \f* muno Babel kavinta nakato Syo maugave siso Sya vatano ubeto Rinai matavon. 
\q1 Mo namije rakivan akato mamo vatano Pilistea, Tirus muno Sudan\f + \fr 87:4 \ft Sudan raura tavonamo Etiopia, omamo ntami no Mesir ama ranijo wanampui.\f* wenawamo 
\q2 Syo mausiso ube munive vatano utantuna munijo Yerusalem rai matavon tenambe, 
\q2 umba Syo mato siso irati kawasae Yerusalem mai tavon.’’ 
\q1  
\v 5 Munijo Sion\f + \fr 87:5 \fq Sion \ft rawain tavonamo ‘‘Yerusalem.’’\f* indati vatane wo raura ware: 
\q2 vatano susye kotar usisa utantuna rai tenambe, maisyare vatano ta utantuna rai to wemaisy. 
\q2 Muno Amisye Titi Rave taune Po rayaranande ti ntindimu tutir. 
\q1  
\v 6 Arono AMISY Po vatano susye kotar awa tame ratoeve, 
\q2 umba Po mato siso kawasae Yerusalem matavon. 
\q1  
\v 7 Vatano susye kotare so ukiny, usarer wo Sion rangkakivambe ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Sion, rikov di winui.’’\f + \fr 87:7 \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ine naiso mbare ramu.\f* 
\c 88  
\s1 Ransyeran weotor Amisye anonae arono waneno mangke nande nai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran. Masmur susyo Kora wo ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. Ukinyo rai mamaisyo ransyeran ‘‘Mahalat Leanot’’ ama kine rarijati. Heman vatano Esrahi apa ransyerano ananyao mijem. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, Winyirati Amisy Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 nai arono masyot syo winawain, muno arono naman ride no Winui. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare sya sambaya so more no Winui, 
\q2 syare namarikoame rasakinav de sya anonae so rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye anakotaro nsosobe manui rave rinai to, 
\q2 muno inajo rani mamo mararaijo unsanda amanija rai to. 
\q1  
\v 5 Vatane wo rinatantona maisyare vatano pasyo no atemo wen akoe rai to wemaisy, 
\q2 risyamo maisyare vatano apa vambunine meweno ai to wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Risyamo maisyare vatano apaya ti tami vatano ugwenen to mansatavone wemaisy, 
\q2 maisyare vatano kakai rarove ti pasyo tami no aipapo rai wemaisy. 
\q1 Muno maisyare vatano Amisye winanimari ai to wemaisy, 
\q2 weye winaneme mpaya ai ti Nyo ayaranande akatoe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 7 Winyo rinapin asyo tami no amani ama ate waraya, 
\q2 no ama ate masyo rave ti ngkaumudi rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Nya pari mo rinatawan asyo mangkebe, 
\q2 Nya pari mangke maisyare aneae akokoe mbumu ti mo inatatuv asyo wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 Nyo sya manivuvi manso ta ti ugwaravainyo rinai, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinaveti ribe noanive mai. 
\q1 Risyamo maisyare rimakova ti syusyo kakai, 
\q2  
\v 10 risyoyov tutir ti inami ndadiri weye rino siuri rai. 
\q2 Sya AMISY, masyote yanteter inaneme raijaseo syo winawain. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Umba indati Winyo anainame rarorono vatano ugwenen to maije? Jewena! 
\q2 Indako indati raroo ubesea akato ti ukangkamambe Naije? Jewena! 
\q1  
\v 12 Vatano wasya utantavainy no aipapo rai to nawamo indati wo Nya muinyo no tawane ravove ramu. 
\q2 Muno vatano ugwenen ti wasya no amani rai to nawamo indati inta wo winteto Nya urairije rai rariri ramu. 
\q1  
\v 13 Indati vatano utantavainy no amani ngkaumure ama uga rai wo Nya anainamo ndave raene ramu. 
\q2 Munijo wene\f + \fr 88:13 \fq Munijo wene: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘munijo animari,’’ ama ine mare arono vatane ugwenen ti wasya no amani rai, weamo Amisye dako, vatane inta dako aemeno mai jakatoe ramu, yara animari mai.\f* somamo indati vatane wo Nya moyare raen ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Yara sya AMISY, risyamo Winyirati syo nawain indamu Nyo sopambe rinai, 
\q2 muno awatan ngkov yanteter risambayambe Winai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Sya AMISY, veanimaibe Nyo rinatugaro marambe? 
\q2 Mbeanimaibe nakirive rinai? 
\q1  
\v 16 Arono rimamaune wea ndea naiso yorame mo inaron tutira kavintare ikakai; 
\q2 siurijo Nyo raude rinai mo rinaveti rinanuga mamaun muno ribambunin da rinatawandi rai jakatoe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 17 Nya pari mamoan dave mo inatamo, 
\q2 Nya pari mangke raude ti mo inaupaeto! 
\q1  
\v 18 Nya pari obo mirati ndaude ti mo inatatuv tutir bayave maisyare manayame ramaisy, 
\q2 mo rinatatuv kijani vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 19 Sya arakov reangkavave muno vatano inanuga no mai nawamo Nyo mansop ti ugwaravainyo rinai to, 
\q2 weti kaumure obo mirati soamo mbe arakobe rinai jakato. 
\c 89  
\s1 AMISY teto Apa urairi raijo vatano Po atayao ai 
\p  
\v 1 Etan vatano Esrahi\f + \fr 89:1 \fq Etan vatano Esrahi\ft : 1Raj. 4:31\f* apa ransyerano ananyao. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY, Nya muinyo no tawane mamo syare kinyo rai jao ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 winteto Nya urairi rai mamo syo rariri tutir irati susyo merere nto mai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye syo raen tugae, Nya muinyo no tawane mamo no pitawabe, 
\q2 winteto Nya urairi rai mamo maisyare naumo ntindimu no tawan tutire warae ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Amisye Winyo raura to, nyare: ‘‘Syo urairi raokae nanto vatano Syo atayao ai to. 
\q2 Syo urairi raokae nanto Daud ai to, opirati Sya vatano panapatambe Rinai: 
\q1  
\v 5 ‘Indati Daud nya mbe akari titive mamo Syo raveti ntindimu, 
\q2 no tawan tutiro nya susyo miridije nto mai. 
\q1 Nya kursijo akari titi mamo Syo nya susyo nyo mampame inta maijaseo utantuna rai tutir ntoa nuge nuganui.’ ’’\f + \fr 89:5 \ft 2Sam. 7:12-16; 1Taw. 17:11-14; Maz. 132:11; Arakov. 2:30\f* 
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY, anakotaro ntuna no Manunggara wo Nya anainamo ndave rararimbe, 
\q2 muno winteto Nya urairi rai mamo rabumbundi no anugano ndandinit\f + \fr 89:6 \fq anugano ndandinit: \ft Omamo anugano no no Manunggara, weti kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware omamo anugano naito Amisy. \f* awa yasyin. 
\q1  
\v 7 Weye sya AMISY, nai naume watoamo inta po namaisye ramu, 
\q2 naito ntuna no Manunggara wato nawamo inta wo namaisye ramu. 
\q1  
\v 8 Ana akokoe una no anugano ndandinit no Manunggara ubeaje Amisye Winai, 
\q2 Winyirati anaaniv weti nasyaniv dave irati ana akokoe utantuna nakijani makivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 9 Sya AMISY, Winyirati Amisy mbe akarive naito munijo ntiti mai, 
\q2 AMISY, arepi indati bambunin da Po namaisy? Jewena! 
\q2 Muno winteto Nya urairi raijo anakotare rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 10 Nya vambunine mo rareno mayan mpanyoane rakivan, 
\q2 arono aneae ntatipu weamo Winyirati Nyo rapamo ti ntanamanin. 
\q1  
\v 11 Winyirati Nyo Rahap\f + \fr 89:11 \ft Rahap omamo tawae akoe ntami no mayane warave ama tame mijem. Raen no Ayub 9:13, 26:12; Yes. 51:9. Weramu kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona Rahap mbe rarorombe munijo Mesir rai, yara kuruno kaijinta wo ratantona ware mbe rarorombe irati nugo mbe rarembe namirati ntami mine so rai arono Amisye Po ranari rainyoe.\f* rakupi ti maisyare vatane inta aubaisye wemaisy, 
\q2 Nya vambunine obo mirati mo Nya marova mapinde ti mpusyek tatugadi. 
\q1  
\v 12 Naume warae muno mine somamo Winya ma, 
\q2 mine so muno anakotaro ntuna ama uga rai mamo Winyi Nyo ama ruke rantet. 
\q1  
\v 13 Amisy Winyo ranijo wanampui muno wanansai ranari, 
\q2 unato Tabor muno Hermon\f + \fr 89:13 \ft Tabor omamo unato no no Onae Galilea ama ranijo varet. Yara Hermon omamo unato no no munijo Israel ama ranijo wanansai. \f* yananibe ikangkamambe Nai, maisyare vatane ukangkamambe Nai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 14 Wakoe! Amisye Winya naneme\f + \fr 89:14 \fq naneme: \ft Ayao Ibrani raijamo terave Amisye anem ngkove rai, omamo mbe rarorombe Apa vambunine rai.\f* mbambunin dave, 
\q2 muno Nya vambunine mbe anaanibe rave! 
\q1  
\v 15 Winya mbe akarive mamo winteto moyare muno patimu mamaisye rai, 
\q2 Nya muinyo no tawane omirati winteto rai ti ntavono Nai no Nya anakotaro ndave rai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Kove ngkov irati vatano ubeaje AMISY Winai, ugwain umananibe rautane mai, 
\q2 onawamo ujaisy weye Nya kove mbaro mai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Masyote tename wepamo umananibe weye Winya ura mai, 
\q2 onawamo manuga manakoeve rave weye Winyamo mbekobe mai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Weye Winyirati reama vambunino ntitije ama ruke pi Winy, 
\q2 muno Winya kove omirati mbewaramo reambambunin no marova rai.\f + \fr 89:18 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Nyo reama korodowai raijaseo titive.’’ Korodowai mbe rarorombe vambunin arono marova rai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 19 Weye reama akari titi AMISY taune Nyo atayao, opirati maisyare vakano no reansaora; 
\q2 reama Amisy ndandinit vatano Israel reambeaje Nai, Winyirati Nyo reama akari titi umaso aijaseo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 No wusyinoe Amisye winarorono Nya vatano panapatambe Nai inta ai 
\q2 no apa nikimarije rai, Nyo raura nyare: 
\q1 ‘‘Syo vambunine raugasyo anaanive inta ai to, 
\q2 opamo vatano Syo atayao no kawasae umaso awa yasyin indamu Syo aijaseo be akari titive mai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Rinanto Daud ai to, opamo Sya vatano panapatambe Rinai, 
\q2 Syo manino ndandinit terave Rinai rauvaro akari rai indamu Syo aijaseo akari titi rai.\f + \fr 89:21 \ft 1Sam. 16:11-13; Arakov. 13:22. Manine mamo veano Daud atayao terave anakero akari titi rai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 22 Risya vambunine mi indati mo asopan tutir kobe, 
\q2 Sya vambunine mo ausuru ti bambunin. 
\q1  
\v 23 Apa marova nawamo indati wo apinde jewen, 
\q2 muno vatano mamune nawamo wo atawanto jewen. 
\q1  
\v 24 Apa marova nawamo indati Syo maotar ti makanive, 
\q2 muno vatano are nawirati mansanuga mamuno ai nawamo Syo maubaisy. 
\q1  
\v 25 Sya muinye mamo no tawano ai muno riteto Sya urairi Syo raokae nanto aije rai tutir, 
\q2 muno Syo Sya vambunine veano apa be akarive rasopan ti ntindimu.\f + \fr 89:25 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Sya tame mi mbewaramo Syo apa korodowai raijaseo titive.’’ Ama ine maisyare ratoe no naiso.\f* 
\q1  
\v 26 Syo asopan ti indati munijo be akarive rai mamo po raijanande ti muiya nto musyo no mayane von, 
\q2 muno muiya nto no mana Eprat. 
\q1  
\v 27 Indati akari titi Daud umaso po rinawain, pare: ‘Winyirati sya Injaya Pi Winy, 
\q2 Winyirati sya Amisy, Winyirati sya unato oram inamamavube Nai ti ripaya marova maneme rai.’ 
\q1  
\v 28 Indati Daud umaso pamo Sya arikainyo anui waino ai,\f + \fr 89:28 \ft Arono wusyinoe no munijo Israel, weamo arikainyo anya anuije opirati ave kobe rave apa rijate makivan. Weti indati apa ura anakotaro manakoe rai mo apa rijate awa ura rai rakivan arono ajaya kakai.\f* 
\q2 muno opirati akari titi Syo aijaseo ti apa tame manakoeve akari titi kaijo mine so makivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 29 Indati Sya muinyo no tawane mamo mpaya ai jewen ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno Sya urairijo Syo raokaisyo ai mamo ntindimu tutir. 
\q1  
\v 30 Indati apa kursijo akari titi mamo Syo raveti ntindimu tutir 
\q2 maisyare naume warae nteto ntindimuve tutire wemaisy, 
\q1 ti Syo apa susyo po mampame maveti utantuna rai tutir kobe. 
\q1  
\v 31 Weramu ranivara apa susyo merere nto wo Sya anaparatote rapaya ti ntami, 
\q2 muno wanya mamaisyo Sya ananyao rai jewen; 
\q1  
\v 32 ranivara wo Sya anaparatote so rakanyoandi, 
\q2 muno wo Sya ananyao raijar akatoe jewen, 
\q1  
\v 33 weamo Risyo Sya vuga omane veano manepati weye wo Sya anaparatote rakanyoandi. 
\q2 Muno Syo kaijo waije veano manepati weye wo ayao kakai rave. 
\q1  
\v 34 Weramu Sya muinyo no tawane mamo indati Syo raugavo Daud aora jewen, 
\q2 muno Sya urairi idaokae nande ai mamo Syo rapaya ramu, yara riteto rai tawan. 
\q1  
\v 35 Sya urairi Syo raokae nanto ai mamo indati Syo inta rakanyoandi jewen, 
\q2 muno Sya ana idaurairive inawa rai to mamo Syo inta ranigwane ramu. 
\q1  
\v 36 Syo Sya tamo ndandinite veano Sya urairije raokae nanto Daud ai to, 
\q2 omamo Syo raokae intabom dave kobe ti indati ntoa nuge nuganui; 
\q2 Syo Daud aponae jewen. 
\q1  
\v 37 Apa susyo po mampame nawirati indati ube akari titive tutir, 
\q2 muno apa kursijo akari titi mamo no tawan tutiro mai, maisyare uma ta no tawane wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 38 Maisyare embae no tawan no naume warae wemaisy, 
\q2 mo raroron kakavimbe apa be akari titive mamo no tawan.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 39 Weramu, sya Amisy, soamo akari titi Winyo atayao pamo nyonae ai to, 
\q2 muno Nyo avakambe marambe weye mparijo ai mangkebe. 
\q1  
\v 40 Nya urairijo ndaokae nande akari titi panapatambe Nai aije mamo Nyo ransopi vintabo to, 
\q2 muno Nyo augaje\f + \fr 89:40 \fq augaje: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Nyo apa kakiono emasije ratakar asyo no kopa rai ti nggwambe.’’\f* apa kursijo akari titi rai to. 
\q1  
\v 41 Yano oram no apa munije rakijani mamo Nyo randujai vintabo, 
\q2 yavaro ntindimu ndarino maora mainyamo Nyo rangkati ti ntuna. 
\q1  
\v 42 Vatan tenambe nanawirati wo awa munije raideto wo awa ananuge raowenta maora, 
\q2 susyo kaijo una mararaive maije useambe mai. 
\q1  
\v 43 Winyo anasineko raunanto apa marova mai jakato, 
\q2 muno Nyo apa marova maveti manayanambe. 
\q1  
\v 44 Yara akari titi Israel umaso apa anaiyu marova mamo Nyo raveti ngkavur, 
\q2 muno Nyo sopambe ai jakato no marova ama uga rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 45 Apa vambunino be akari titive mamo Nyo ransopi, 
\q2 muno apa kursijo titi mamo Nyo rangkuku asyo ntami no min. 
\q1  
\v 46 Nyo apa tumo ta kamurame raotar aje tumaimbe ti maisyare be vatan anuive vayave kobe wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Nyo ave samaneve ti mo atatuv asyo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 47 Sya AMISY, winamune rangkokaibe reansaija ntoa nanduija? 
\q2 Ntoa nanduija umba Nya pari maisyare tanamo mbadurure ma nsopija? 
\q1  
\v 48 Syare winaemeno rinai, weye sya tumo rijaisyo rai somamo ntumainy bayavea, 
\q2 vatano Nyo reansanari reamamo reamatu ra no tawane jewen. 
\q1  
\v 49 Vatano arepi indati kov tutir, yara wene nde ai jewen? 
\q2 Arepi indati paya irati amanija ama vambunine rai? 
\q1  
\v 50 Sya Akoe Winy, Nya muinyo no tawan no manasyinoe mamo? 
\q2 Namirati ndaurairive irati Daud ai nyare indati winteto rai kobe omamo? 
\q1  
\v 51 Sya Akoe Winy, risyamo Nya vatano syanapatambe Nai, ti syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 weye vatano kaije wo rinaura tantunawi rave. 
\q2 Susyo kaijo wanui awa ayao useambe rinai mamo mo inaveti inanuga njoram. 
\q1  
\v 52 Sya AMISY, Nya marova wo akari titi Nyo atayao apa tame rambaon dave, 
\q2 pare to no rui ruijamo wo aura tatugadi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 53 AMISY ararimbe ntoa nuge nuganui! 
\q2 Tugae, syare tugae! 
\c 90  
\ms1 ETET 4 
\ms1 MASMUR 90-106 
\s1 Amisye Opirati no pitawabe ti mamaisyo vatane wamakata nggaugambe Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Musa, opamo vatano panapatambe Amisye Ai, apa sambaya. 
\b  
\q1 Reama Akoe, Winyirati reamakaore nggaugambe Nai no arono wusyinoea ndea naiso. 
\q1  
\v 2 Arono Nyo unate ranari rainy, 
\q2 arono Nyo munije muno mine tename so ama anakotaro ntuna rai ranari rainy, 
\q2 nai nugo pitawaroe ntoa nuge nuganui, Winyirati Amisy no pitawabe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Winyo vatane maugav akasyo no kopa rai, 
\q2 Nyo raura, nyare: ‘‘Vatane weap, wapakasya ra wabe kopave akato!’’ 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye tume ribuge intabo nde nto to omainyamo, 
\q2 windaena ta maisyare masyote intabo bayave amaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare namanoe deto to amaisy. 
\q1  
\v 5 Nyo vatane reama tume raotar ti mavave mewen. 
\q2 Reamaisyare nikimari ta nde nto vayave wemaisy, 
\q2 muno reamaisyare insumaijo ntubai wemaisy: 
\q1  
\v 6 Arono awatan ngkov insumaije ntubai merere nseo, 
\q2 weramu arono namandi mayon muno ngkanen akato. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Tugae, Nya parijo mamoane mo reansaveti reanjani dave, 
\q2 muno Nya pari mo reansaupaeta ti reansakanive. 
\q1  
\v 8 Reama ana ndaveti ngkakai mamo Nyo raen tenambe to, 
\q2 muno reama ayao kakai reamo rangkokaibe mamo Winyo raen to. 
\q1  
\v 9 Nya pari mo reama kove so raotar aje tumaimbe, 
\q2 reama tumo reamanya rai no mine so nto nsopi vayave maisyare nanawayo ta ramawita wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 10 Reama tumo reanjayaisyo rai mamo nseo tename mandeij eane abusyine\f + \fr 90:10 \fq tename mandeij eane abusyin\ft : 70\f* rai, 
\q2 muno ranivara reambambunina nene wea umba nseo tename mambisye\f + \fr 90:10 \fq tename mambisy\ft : 80\f* rai. 
\q1 Weramu ana nsosobe muno siuri omirati reansansowave rai; 
\q2 reanjaisye somamo ntumainy bayave, umba wene mo reansaugav\f + \fr 90:10 \fq wene mo reansaugav: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘reansaonto ti reansakanive.’’\f* ti reansakanive. 
\q1  
\v 11 \f + \fr 90:11 \ft Aneme somamo ayao Ibrani ama ine mbare ramu.\f*Nya pari panyoane mamo vatane inta po ama vambunine raene jewen, 
\q2 tugae, Nya pari mamoane mamo mangke dave ti mamaisyo vatane reandasyaniv. 
\q1  
\v 12 Reamare Nyo reansanyao indamu reamo masyoto reangkove so ratantona kobe weye manui jewen, 
\q2 wirati indamu reamanya rai mamaisyo ana ratantona ntiti rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Reama AMISY, wimparijo reansai mamo ntoa nanduija? 
\q2 Reamamo Nya kawasae reamanapatambe Nai, 
\q2 weti reamare nyakare reansai muno naemeno reansai! 
\q1  
\v 14 Reamare Nyo Nya muinyo no tawane raude mawebe reansai awatan ngkove yanteter, 
\q2 indamu reansananibe muno reangkiny reansanayanambe no arono ta reangkove so. 
\q1  
\v 15 Reamare Nyo anayanambe raude reansai ama masyote manui mamaisyo masyoto Nyo siuri raude reansai ama manuije ramaisy akato, 
\q2 muno mamaisyo tumo reana siurije rai ama manuije ramai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 16 Reamare Nya ana ndave ti mbe anaanibe raroron kakavimbe Nya kawasae reamanapatambe Nai reansai jakato, 
\q2 muno Nya kovo ntiti rarorono reama susyo merere nto mai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 17 Akoe, Winyirati reama Amisy, reamare Nyo kove raugaje reansai, 
\q2 muno Nyo reama anakero reandaijare ravera mamaisy, 
\q2 tugae, reama ana ndaijare mamo ndavera mamai tugae. 
\c 91  
\s1 Amisy Opirati darino wansaora 
\q1  
\v 1 Vatano mansamamavube Amisy Titi Rave Ai, 
\q2 muno ugaugambe Amisy Opirati Bambunin dave Ai, 
\q1  
\v 2 wo raurato AMISY Ai ware: ‘‘Winyirati sya Amisy, Winyirati syanave Nai. 
\q2 Winyirati ndarino rinaora muno mbe yambe rinaora.’’ 
\q1  
\v 3 Tugae, indati Amisye Po napaya irati ana ngkakai ngkokaibe ti mo namane rai,\f + \fr 91:3 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘indati Amisye Po napaya irati pamuno mo namane rai.’’\f* 
\q2 muno waneno mangke mo wene raugavo nai rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Indati darino naora, maisyare mangkuero mo ama tuvane rarauv no pepak ate rai wemaisy. 
\q1 Indati winyamo nggaugambe Ai, maisyare mangkuere tuvane ugaugambe akoe ama pepak ate rai wemaisy. 
\q1 Amisy teto Apa urairi rai mamo maisyare vakano ntindimu no naora wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 5 Vemo nyo anakotaro ngkakai manya namane rai rasyaniv inya, 
\q2 muno ana ngkakai nande\f + \fr 91:5 \fq ana ngkakai nande\ft : Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘ato ratapo ti mo naron de.’’\f* nai papabe no mbare rai rasyaniv tavon nora. 
\q1  
\v 6 Waneno mangke nande no arono namane rai mamo vemo ndasyaniv inya, 
\q2 muno ana ngkakai rui vayave mo nakupi no masyote yasyine rai mamo ndasyaniv tavon nora. 
\q1  
\v 7 Ranivara vatane ribuge intabo ugwenen no nya nori we, 
\q2 muno ribuge abusyine mueneno nakijani kai, 
\q2 weramu winyamo ngkakai tavone ramu. 
\q1  
\v 8 Winyamo indati nami ntamijo 
\q2 mangke rasakinavo vatano mamune maije rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye AMISY Opirati darino naora, 
\q2 Amisy Titi Rave Opirati nyo aijaro naora. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weti ana ngkakai mangke mamo inta mo narone jewen, 
\q2 muno waneno mangke inta nde mararaijo nya yavare rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 11 \f + \fr 91:11 \ft Anemo 11a muno 12 aya ayao ratoe akato no Mat. 4:6 muno Luk. 4:10.\f*Weye indati Amisye Po Apa naite matutir ti ude wo nayaranande, 
\q2 indamu udarino naora no nya unanui anya nto no rui rui vayave rai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Indati wo naijaseo maneme rai, 
\q2 inda vemo najoe rantukamo orame rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 13 \f + \fr 91:13 \ft Luk. 10:19\f*Indati make sivuinye pe\f + \fr 91:13 \fq Make sivuiny \ft ranigwano ‘‘singa’’ rai. Make sivuiny muno tawae mamun mbe rarorombe marova mai muno anakotaro ngkakai kaije rai tavon.\f* tawae me nayamo ndatakadi vayave, 
\q2 muno make sivuinyo kamurame pe tawae mamune me nayamo ngkamugaje yai vayave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Amisye Po raura pare: ‘‘Tugae, vatano are pirati anuga no Rinai pamo indati Syo apaya kakaije rai, 
\q2 vatano napirati po rinaen tugaeve no anuga rai pamo ridarino aora. 
\q1  
\v 15 Ranivara po rinawain, weamo Syo apa bekere raveti mamaisyo ai. 
\q2 Arono no irati ana nsosobe rai, weamo rituna autan. 
\q2 Indati Syo apaya irati kakai rai muno Syo apa tame raijaseo vombe. 
\q1  
\v 16 Indati Syo apa tume raveti nggwaravainy ti anayanambe, 
\q2 muno indati Syo apaya irati kakaije rai.’’ 
\c 92  
\s1 AMISY ararimbe weye Po patimu moyare raugaje 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran. Masmur Israel ukiny dai no masyoto Sabat.\f + \fr 92:1 \ft Masyoto Sabat omamo vatano Yahudi awa masyoto sambaya. Wo rator no arono masyoto Jumat ama namandi mansanan ava masyoto Sapitu ama namandi.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Tugae, reangkiny reamo kove raura seo AMISY Winai, 
\q2 muno reamo ransyerane veano AMISY Ntiti Rave nararimbe omamo ngkov. 
\q1  
\v 3 Tugae, reamo Nya muinyo no tawane ravov no awatan ngkov, 
\q2 muno winteto Nya urairije rai ravov no arono naman, omamo ngkov tavon. 
\q1  
\v 4 Reangkiny reamo itari ama waije abusyine raeyan dai, 
\q2 muno itari anakoe me, itari mamaune me yaeyan dai tavon.\f + \fr 92:4 \fq Itarijo anakoe \ft muno \fq itari mamaune \ft ranigwano ‘‘gambus’’ muno ‘‘kecapi’’ rai. \f* 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye sya AMISY, Nya ana ndave mo inanuga so raveti ranayanambe, 
\q2 Nya ana ndave omirati rikiny, inananibe rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Wakoe, sya AMISY! Nya ana ndave makokoive rave, 
\q2 muno Nya ana ndatantona mamo ntiti rave, weti vatane reansea rai kakai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Vatano awa ana udatantona ngkove jewene unanta rai kakai, 
\q2 muno vatano wantatukambe unanta rai jewen tavon. 
\q1  
\v 8 Ana unanta rai jewene mamo: Nai mine vone so vatano mamune ubakipambe usea wanui, 
\q2 maisyare insumai ntubai ti nseo mo muni ratatuv wemaisy, 
\q2 weramu onawamo indati Amisye Po maupaeta ti makanive. 
\q1 Muno unanta rai jewen tavone miso: vatano awa ana udave ngkakaije wo ana mawese ratayao mai no mine so, 
\q2 weramu indati Amisye Po maupaeta vintabo ti makanive ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 9 Yara AMISY Winyirati mbe akari titive ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weye sya AMISY, Nyo Nya marova mansaen, 
\q2 Nya marova umaso nawamo indati Nyo maupaeta ti makanive, 
\q2 vatano awa ana udave ngkakai nawamo indati Nyo mampusyeto. 
\q1  
\v 11 Winyo rinaveti ibambunin, maisyare maero banteno bambunin dave wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Nyo Nya kove raugaje rinai, maisyare manino mbovov\f + \fr 92:11 \ft Manino mbovov vatano Israel wo rave mamo manino saitun.\f* nggwanyine rauvaro inakarije rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 12 Syo raen Winyi Nyo anasineko sya marova mai, 
\q2 arono Nyo mapinde weamo wanonae ti syo manaun. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Vatano ubeta Amisye Ai nawamo ujayaisy ti utubai maisyare inyo korma\f + \fr 92:13 \ft Inyo korma nteto matuve muno man tutir ntoa nugoenta. Wamo raenamo omamo maisyare angkaji ramaisy muno ama mote ngko dave maisyare karowa ramaisy.\f* ramaisy, 
\q2 muno utubai ti ubambunin maisyare inyo aras no no Libanon ramaisy.\f + \fr 92:13 \ft Inyo aras ntubai ti ntiti rave muno ama mote matu muno ngko dave. Wamo raenamo omamo maisyare inyo ajare ramaisy.\f* 
\q1  
\v 14 Onawamo ujaisy muno ubambunin no AMISY Amun, 
\q2 maisyare inyo matu rantet no Yavaro Amisye rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 15 Onawamo ube vatan anuive to weramu ubambunin muno awa ana udave ngkov tutir, 
\q2 maisyare inyo njayaibe tutir muno mo mane rauguje tutire wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 16 Weti vatano kove umaso wo raura ware: 
\q2 ‘‘AMISY Opamo moyar, 
\q1 Opirati maisyare unato oram inamamavube rai, 
\q2 Opamo Apa ana dave mamo nsarokir dave.’’ 
\c 93  
\s1 AMISY Opi Akarijo Titi no tawan 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY Wepirati Akarijo Titi! 
\q2 Apa kovo ntiti maisyare ansun akoe Po rave, 
\q2 Apa vambunine maisyare tarandino Po rave ansune rauvat. 
\q1 Tugae, mine so ntet tindimuve tawan, 
\q2 mangkiki jewen weye Amisye taune Po rantet. 
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY, wimbambunin ntuna tawano 
\q2 Nya mbe akarive rai kobe arono wusyinoe, 
\q2 nai nugo pitawar Winyamo no tawan. 
\q1  
\v 3 Abo AMISY, mana njam merere nseo, 
\q2 mana njam ama kine merere nseo, 
\q2 mana njam ama kino mpusyek merere nseo. 
\q1  
\v 4 Tugae, mana njam manakoe ama kine merere nseo, 
\q2 nde no rareno aneae mpanyoan, 
\q2 weramu AMISY no no munijo ntiti bambunin dakivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY, Nya ananyao ntindimu no tawan. 
\q2 Nya yavare ndandinita nuge nuganui. 
\c 94  
\s1 Amisye Po patimu moyare raugaje vatane mai mamaisyo awa ana udave rai 
\q1  
\v 1 Sya AMISY, Winyirati Amisy Nyo mangke rasakinavo vatano mamune\f + \fr 94:1 \fq vatano mamun \ft wenawamo vatano wonae ubeta Amisye Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.\f* mai, 
\q2 Amisy, mangke ndasakinavo mai mamo syare Nyo raroron kakavimbe. 
\q1  
\v 2 Amisy Winyirati Nyo mamaisye rapatimu mine so rai, syare wimbeseo! 
\q2 Syare Nyo kakai rasakinavo vatano mararine mai mamaisyo awa ana udave rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sya AMISY, ntoa nandui rati umba nsopija? 
\q2 Ntoa nandui rati umba vatano mamune so umananibe mamo nsopija? 
\q1  
\v 4 Wenawamo awa ayao mbe manayambe muno manuga rararino rai, 
\q2 vatan tenambe nanawirati wo ana ngkakai rave onawamo umararin dai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Sya AMISY, vatano mamune so wo Nya kawasae matawanto, 
\q2 muno wo Nya vatano Nyo matayao terave namarome matakarasyo. 
\q1  
\v 6 Wo wanya kavini muno arikainyo wawate maubaisy, 
\q2 muno vatano maran udesen una tavon no munijo Israel maubaisy tavon. 
\q1  
\v 7 Muno wo raura tavon ware: ‘‘AMISY Opamo Po raene ramu, 
\q2 Amisy aneno Yakopa beaje Ai, Opamo pantatukambe reama ana reamo rave rai.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Inya, akari weapi wapantatukambe no vatane awa yasyine weap, syare wapo raraniv! 
\q2 Inya, vatano wapo ana raene ramu weap, ntoa nandui rati umba wapa ana wadatantona ngkova?! 
\q1  
\v 9 Amisye Wepi Po vatane mansamarikoame ranari, weti ayao kakaijo wapo ratore mamo Po ranaun ivae. 
\q2 Muno Po vatane mamije ranari, weti ana wapo raveti ngkove jewene mamo Po raen dirive to. 
\q1  
\v 10 Wepi Po vatano susyo Yahudi jewene manayao, weti indati Po mangke raude wasai tavon aje! 
\q2 Wepirati Po ana raene rave vatane manyao. 
\q1  
\v 11 AMISY Po vatane awa ana wo ratantona mamo Po raen bintabo; 
\q2 Pare awa ana udatantona umaso mamo maisyare ovar bayave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Kove ngkov irati vatano AMISY Winyo manayao indamu ubeta Naije mai, 
\q2 nanawirati Nyo manyao irati Nya anaparatote rai mai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Indati Nyo mansapaya irati ana nsosobe rai weti una mariraave, 
\q2 nto ava Nyo akari mamune mapinto atemo Nyo ratayao mansamarome rai to. 
\q1  
\v 14 Weye AMISY Opamo akirive Apa kawasae mansai ramu, 
\q2 Opamo Po Apa vatano Po matayao terave amarome mapaya vayave ramu. 
\q1  
\v 15 Arono naije indati patimu akari wo raugaje mamo mamaisyo Amisye Apa moyare rai jakato, 
\q2 muno vatan tenambe nanawirati manuga nsarokire nanawamo indati utavondi rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 Are pirati indati be marimbe rinai irati vatano mamune mai? 
\q2 Are pirati indati po rinasopan irati vatano wo ana ngkakai rave mai? 
\q1  
\v 17 Ranivara AMISY Po rinayaranande jewen datire, 
\q2 kavintare risyasyo no amanija ama uga rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Arono syo ratantona syare kavintare ritandupuisy ti temaje,\f + \fr 94:18 \fq kavintare ritandupuisy ti temaje: \ft Ayao so ama ine mare Pemasmur apa anave mamaun, janivo wene nande aiji. \f* 
\q2 weramu sya AMISY, Nya muinyo no tawan\f + \fr 94:18 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it hesed\+it* ama ine ratoe tumaimbe naiso mare: ‘‘muinyo no tawan.’’ Ama ino manakoe mare: ‘‘Amisye Apa muinye muno Apa anakotaro Po raurairive ti no tawan tutiro Apa kawasae Israel mansai mamo Po raveti mamaisy.’’\f* wemirati mo rinasopan tindimuve. 
\q1  
\v 19 Ranivara rinanuga mamaun, 
\q2 weamo Winyo rinayove ti inanuga ranayanambe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Akari mamuno wo patimu mamaisye jewene raugaje nanawamo Amisy winaijaro matavone ramu, 
\q2 wenawamo manatantonave ana ngkakai obo rai mamaisyo Nya ananyao ngkove rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 21 Wenawamo wanyinyaube ware umarovave vatano ubeta Amisye Ai mai, 
\q2 muno wo mangke kakai raugaje vatano awa ayao kakaije meweno maije mai. 
\q1  
\v 22 Weramu AMISY Opamo sya yano oram no rinaora pije, 
\q2 sya Amisy Opamo sya unato oram inamamavube Ai pije. 
\q1  
\v 23 Wepi indati Po mangke rasakinav akananto akari mamune mai mamaisyo awa ayao kakaije rai, 
\q2 muno indati Po maupaeta ti makanive weye awa ana udave mamun. 
\q2 AMISY, Wepirati wama Amisy, indati Po maupaeta ti makanive. 
\c 95  
\s1 Wade wamo Amisye ararimbe muno wamo araniv 
\q1  
\v 1 Wade, wangkiny wansanamoto manakoe rai AMISY Ai, 
\q2 wansananibe wanggwain akoeve to irati Ai, 
\q2 Opamo maisyare unato oram, Po wansapaya irati anakotaro ngkakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Wade, wanta no Amisy Amun, wamo kove raura seo Ai. 
\q2 Wansananibe, wangkinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo wansanamoto manakoe rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye AMISY Wepirati Amisy panakoeve rave, 
\q2 muno be Akari Titive irati anawayo kotaro vatane wo masyanive mansakivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 4 Mine ama ate waraya mamo Po raijanande vintabo, 
\q2 muno papukamo ntiti wemamo Apa ura rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wepi Apa ura mayane rai, weye taune Pi Po ranari, 
\q2 muno yawa ntavon taune Pi Po ranari aneme rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Wade ra wamo vukane ranteter wambeaje Ai, 
\q2 wade ra wamo vukane ranteter no AMISY Wepi Po wansanari Amun. 
\q1  
\v 7 Weye Wepirati wama Amisye Pije, 
\q2 muno Apa kawasae ura wansai, taune Po wansayaranande, 
\q2 maisyare vatano po maero domba makume wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1 Inya, Amisye beker pare wapo araniv no unumeso!\f + \fr 95:7 \ft Anemo 7d-11 ama ayao ratoe akato no Ibr. 3:7-11,15. \f* 
\q1  
\v 8 Pare: ‘‘Vemo wasanuga matu nora, 
\q2 maisyare wapa aneno wusyine mansamai no munijo Meriba\f + \fr 95:8 \ft Kel. 17:1-7; Bil. 20:2-13; Ul. 6:16. Ayao \fq Meriba \ft ama ine mare ‘‘ayaowi,’’ muno ayao \fq Masa \ft ama ine mare ‘‘ratopan.’’\f* wemaisy inya, 
\q2 muno maisyare arono una no munijo Masa no anoko kanen. 
\q1  
\v 9 Nai ratuije weapa anene wo rinatopan, 
\q2 Risya ana dave mamo wo raen dave to weramu wo rinatopan. 
\q1  
\v 10 Tume tename jirum nggwaravainy dave Risyamo syonae susye so mai\f + \fr 95:10 \fq susye so: \ft ama tunato raije mare vatano Israel nanawirati ube vatan anuive arono wuje munijo Mesir raora.\f* rave to. 
\q2 Weti Syo raura syare: ‘Tugae, vatane so nanawamo makirive Rinai to, 
\q2 muno wenawamo wonae Risya ananyao raiji.’ 
\q1  
\v 11 Maisyare wemaisy Ripari syanaamatambe, 
\q2 syare: ‘Wenawamo indati usisa una mariraave no munijo Syo raurairive mai rai jewen.’ ’’ 
\c 96  
\s1 AMISY Opamo Akarijo Titi mine so rai 
\q1  
\v 1 Wakinyo ransyeran wanyine raijo AMISY Ai! 
\q2 Inya, vatano mine tename weap, wakinyo ransyerane rai AMISY Ai! 
\q1  
\v 2 Wakinyo ransyerane rai AMISY Ai, Apa tame rararimbe, 
\q2 wapo Apa kovo Po wansapaya marova mai ravovo masyote anteter. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wapo Apa kovo ntiti raririjo susye kotaro mine so mai 
\q2 muno Apa anainamo Po rave raura vatano mine so mai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY Wepi panakoeve rave, weti obo Pi mamaisyo aura titive, 
\q2 Obo pirati asyaniv daveo anawayo kotaro vatane wo masyanive makivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye vatano mine so awa anawayo kotare nawamo mamaisye ramu tenambe, 
\q2 yara wama AMISY obo pirati Po naume ranari. 
\q1  
\v 6 Apa kovo ntiti mo amuman, 
\q2 Opamo bambunin, muno Apa Yavare mamo ndandinit muno ngkov dave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Inya, susye kotaro mine weap, wapo AMISY ararimbe, 
\q2 wapo Apa kovo ntiti muno Apa vambunine rararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 8 Wapo AMISY Apa tamo ntiti rararimbe, 
\q2 wapo anakotaro rameseo Aije raugave ta no wanijate Yavaro Amisy! 
\q1  
\v 9 AMISY Opa dandinit weti wabeaje Ai. 
\q2 Inya, vatano munije tenam, watutar no Amisye Amun!\f + \fr 96:9 \fq watutar no Amisye Amun: \ft ama ine mare Amisy asyaniv.\f* 
\q1  
\v 10 Wapo ravovo susye kotaro mine so mai, wapare: ‘‘AMISY Opamo Akarijo Titi! 
\q2 Tugae, Wepi Po mine so ranteto tindimuve, ti mansope jewen. 
\q1 Po mangke rapatimu susyo mine so mansai 
\q2 mamaisyo taune Apa moyare rai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 11 Inya, kotaro ntuna no naum muno mine so wasanayanambe, 
\q2 inya, mayane me ama anakotar no no ama uga, 
\q2 wasanamote mbeseo panyoambe tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 12 Inya, anok muno anakotaro ntubai rai, wasanayanambe, 
\q2 inyo kotaro ayamuga wakiny wasananibe no AMISY Amun, 
\q1  
\v 13 weye AMISY pakare be akarive no mine so. 
\q2 Pakare indamu Po mangke rapatimu mine tename so rai. 
\q2 Indati Po mangke rapatimu vatano mine so mai mamaisyo Apa moyare rai, 
\q2 muno Po mangke rapatimu susye kotaro mine so mai mamaisyo Apa ayao tugae rai. 
\c 97  
\s1 AMISY Opamo Akarijo Titi 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY Opamo Akarijo Titi! 
\q1 Koveamo vatano mine vone so manayanambe, 
\q2 koveamo vatano utantuna no nupatimu manui rave so mananibe! 
\q1  
\v 2 Andorame muno ananamane mo Amisy Apa tuna rije rakijani, 
\q2 Wepi rati be akarive vatane mai, tavondi Apa mamaisye muno Apa moyare rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Taname muje no Amisy Amun 
\q2 muno mo Apa marova mansanen ti mangkur bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 4 Apa ivake ratatukande, ama vare mo nuge so ravabasya, 
\q2 mine so wo raen muno ututar. 
\q1  
\v 5 Papukame nsoyandi maisyare inunijoe no AMISY Amun, 
\q2 wepirati Akoe be akarive mine tename so rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Naume mo Amisye Apa mamaisye raroron, 
\q2 muno susye kotaro mine so wo Apa kovo ntiti raen tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 7 Vatano ubeaje yare rai muno wo awa pinugane mararin 
\q2 indati usamane weye mo kove raunande mai jewen. 
\q2 Anawayo kotaro rui vayave indati ubeaje Amisye Ai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Sya AMISY, vatano Sion\f + \fr 97:8 \fq Sion \ft omamo munijo Yerusalem ama tamo wusyine mijem.\f* wo ranaun muno mananibe, 
\q2 vatano utantuna no munijo Yehuda mansanayanambe, 
\q2 weye Winyo mangke rapatimu. 
\q1  
\v 9 Winyirati AMISY Titi Rave no mine tename so. 
\q2 Wibuinyi ntiti rave anawayo kotaro vatane wo masyanive makivan bintabo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Inya, vatano wamuiny irati AMISY Aije weap, 
\q2 ana ngkakaije mamo wapo rawatambe! 
\q1 Weye AMISY Wepi Po vatano matawandi utavondi Aije awa ujayaisye rayaranande, 
\q2 Wepi Po mansapaya irati vatano mamune\f + \fr 97:10 \fq vatano mamune \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.\f* mansaneme rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Kovo Amisy mbaro vatano ubeta Amisye Ai mai, 
\q2 muno anayanambe nde irati vatano manuga ngkakavin dave mai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Inya, vatano wabeta Amisye Ai weap, 
\q2 wasanayanambe rave weye AMISY Apa ana dave obom mbewar. 
\q1 Muno weapo kove raura seo Ai, weye Apa tame mi ndandinit. 
\c 98  
\s1 AMISY Opi Po mine so rakom 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur. 
\q1 Wakinyo ransyeran wanyine raijo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weye Po anainame rave! 
\q1 Wepi Po anasineko marova mai 
\q2 taune Apa vambunine rai muno anem ngkovo ndandinite rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY Po anasineko raroron kakavimbe 
\q2 weye Po marova mapinde. 
\q1 Apa dapatimuge moyar Po raroron kakavimbe 
\q2 susye kotar mine so mai tutudi. 
\q1  
\v 3 Opamo aemendi Apa muinyo no tawan tutiro Israel mansai rai, 
\q2 muno teto Apa anakotaro daurairive mansai rai. 
\q1 Kawasae mine so wo raen to, 
\q2 wama Amisye Po anasineko raunande wansai no wama ana nsosobe rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Inya, vatano mine weap, wasananibe wagwain AMISY aijaseo titive! 
\q2 Wasananibe muno wakiny ransyeran marinsawan! 
\q1  
\v 5 Wakiny, wapo itari\f + \fr 98:5 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* veano AMISY ararin, 
\q2 wakiny muno wapo itari raeyan indamu ararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 6 Terompeti muno tavuna\f + \fr 98:6 \ft Tavuna Israel wo rave mamo korodowai kambino anya.\f* ramawisy, 
\q2 wasananibe wagwain AMISY aijaseo titive, 
\q2 Opamo wama Akarijo Titi pije. 
\q1  
\v 7 Mayane me ama anakotar no no ama uga, 
\q2 muno muni me ama anakotar ntuna no ama uga 
\q2 ranamote mbeseo panyoambe tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare koveamo mana akokoe maneme rapoam, 
\q2 maisyare vatano anayanambe aneme rapoam. 
\q1 Muno papukame rananibe 
\q2 maisyare vatane mananibe ukinyo ransyerane rai 
\q2 nai AMISY Amun. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye pakare indamu Po mangke rapatimu 
\q2 susye kotar mine so mansai 
\q2 mamaisyo taune Apa daeno moyare rai muno tugae bo rai. 
\c 99  
\s1 AMISY, Akarijo Titi dandinit 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY Opamo Akarijo Titi, 
\q2 weti susye kotare wapo asyaniv watutar! 
\q1 AMISY de tuna no ana yatotov kerub\f + \fr 99:1 \ft Kerub omamo Israel awa ana wo ratotov indamu mo ana una no Manunggara mansamaisy maisyare naito Amisy. Wo kerub jirum yatotov yaugaje jantuna Kasyamo Urairi ama vone rai nai yavaro Amisy tanoano ndandinit dave rai. Mamaisyo Israel awa anave wusyine rai, weye ware Amisye de tuna no kerub aya pepake no yai aya yasyine rai, maisyare var.\f* aya yasyine rai indamu be akarive wansai, 
\q2 weti mine vone so mangkiki. 
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY Apa vambunine manakoe no Sion,\f + \fr 99:2 \fq Sion \ft omamo munijo Yerusalem ama tamo wusyine mijem.\ft \f* 
\q2 Opamo titi, no vombe rave kobe, 
\q2 Opamo titi susyo mine so makivan. 
\q1  
\v 3 Koveamo wenawamo ukiny, 
\q2 wo Nya tamo namirati manakoe muno mbambunin dave rararimbe; 
\q2 Winyamo ndandinit dave! 
\q1  
\v 4 Winyamo Akari Titi mbambunin, nanuga no moyare rai. 
\q2 Winyirati Nyo vatane manyao indamu wo ana mamaisye obo raijar. 
\q1 Ananyao muno moyar no no vatano Israel\f + \fr 99:4 \ft Ayao Ibrani naiso maisyare so: ‘‘Yakop apa susyo po mampam,’’ ama ine mare vatano Israel.\f* awa yasyin, 
\q2 Winyirati Nyo ana mamaisye raugaje. 
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY aijaseo titive, Wepirati wama Amisy! 
\q2 Muno wamo vukane ranteter wambeaje Ai no Apa tuna ri. 
\q2 Opamo dandinit dave! 
\q1  
\v 6 Musa muno Harun wenayamo yator siso syeno Amisy matavon no awa yasyin, 
\q2 muno Samuel no tavon no vatano usambayambe Apa tame raije awa yasyin tavon. 
\q1 Onawamo usambayambe AMISY Ai, 
\q2 muno Wepirati Po awa sambaya raveti mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Kamayo mo unanuije rarorone\f + \fr 99:7 \ft Kamayo somamo Kamayo ngkamajugambe Israel maora arono wuje no Mesiri ti wanya no anoko kanen. Kel. 13:21-22\f* ama uga 
\q2 AMISY payao nanto Israel mansai; 
\q1 onao ubeta Apa ananyao rai 
\q2 muno anaparatot raugaje mansaije rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY reama Amisy, arono awa ana udave ngkakai, 
\q2 Nyo mangke raugaje mai. 
\q1 Weramu arono usambayambe Nai, 
\q2 Nyo maraniv, Nyo awa ayao kakaije rapaya mai. 
\q1  
\v 9 AMISY aijaseo titive, Opirati wama Amisy! 
\q2 Wamo vukane ranteter wambeaje Ai no Unato Sion, Apa tuna ri ndandinit! 
\q2 Weye AMISY wama Amisy opamo dandinit! 
\c 100  
\s1 Ransyerano kove raura seo AMISY Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran kangkaman kove raura seo AMISY Ai.\f + \fr 100:1 \ft Arono wusyinoe Israel wo anakotare ramer indamu wo kove raura seo AMISY Ai. Imamat 7:12\f* 
\b  
\q1 Inya, vatano mine weap, wasananibe wagwain AMISY aijaseo titive! 
\q1  
\v 2 Wasambayambe AMISY Aijo wasanuga ranayanambe rautan. 
\q2 Wade no Amune raijo ransyeran marinsawan rautan. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare wapo raura wapare AMISY Opirati wama Amisy. 
\q2 Wepirati Po wansanari to, weti Wepirati Apa ura wansai. 
\q1 Wamamo Apa kawasae, weti Po wansayaranande 
\q2 maisyare vatano po maero domba mansakume wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare wapanya sisa unsanda akoe wanijate Yavaro Amisye rai, 
\q2 wakiny wapo kove raura seo. 
\q1 Syare wasisa no ama wanijate rai, wakinyo ransyeran kangkaman rai, 
\q2 kove raura AMISY Ai, muno Apa tame rararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye AMISY Opamo ko dave, 
\q2 muno Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 Opamo teto Apa urairi rai tawano susyo miridi nto mai. 
\c 101  
\s1 Akari titi apa urairi po raokaisy nanto Amisye Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, rikinyo Nya muinyo no tawan muno Nya patimu moyare rai, 
\q2 weti rikinyo ransyerano kangkamane raijo Winai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Syo sya unanui syanya rai rakarae mavabe ramu ngkakainoanive nora yara nsarokir. 
\q2 Nanduija Winde no rinui indamu Nyo rinasopan? 
\q2 Syare rino irati inanuga nsarokire rai no sya yavaruga. 
\q1  
\v 3 Ayao kakainoanive mamo syonaeyo raugavere no rinamune raiji. 
\q1 Risyamo syonaeyo vatano usarirae ti makirive akato irati Amisye Aije mai, 
\q2 muno indati ritavondi awa ana udave raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Risyamo syare vatano awa ana udave ngkakai musyo marambe nanawamo ugwaravainyo rinai, 
\q2 muno syonae tavobombe ana rave ti ngkakai raiji. 
\q1  
\v 5 Vatano nanawirati wo awa arakove awa tamo ngkov raura tantunawi maninimbe nawamo 
\q2 indati syo maupaeta ti makanive. 
\q1 Vatano mararin muno wo taune maijaseo vombe onawamo 
\q2 indati syo mavakano marambe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Vatano matawandi utavondi Amisye Ai no munije so\f + \fr 101:6 \fq munije so \ft ama ine mare Israel.\f* nanawamo 
\q2 indati syo mawainde utantuna rinatavon no sya yavar. 
\q1 Vatano nanawirati ugwambe ayao kakaije rai jewene nanawamo 
\q2 indati syo mawain ude wanapatambe wo anakero akari raijaro rinatavon. 
\q1  
\v 7 Vatano wo anapamponae rave nanawamo 
\q2 syo mansamayaro ude sisa una no sya yavare rai ramu, 
\q1 vatano wo aarurijate ratore nanawamo 
\q2 vemo ude usayae no inamune rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 8 Arono awatane anteter, vatano mamun\f + \fr 101:8 \fq vatano mamun \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.\f* una no munije so rai nanawamo 
\q2 syo maupaeta ti makanive tenambe. 
\q1 Vatano awa ana udave mamun tenambe, 
\q2 indati syo maotar ti makanive AMISY Apa munijo Yerusalem so rai. 
\c 102  
\s1 Vatano kamuram no siuri rai apa ana danajo Amisye Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Vatano no siuri rai apa ana danajo Amisye Ai, arono anasine mayondi muno po apa siuri no no anuga raura to AMISY Ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo sya ana danajo so raraniv, 
\q2 syare sya anonae so more irati Winai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Vemo winakirive rinai nora, 
\q2 arono anakotare mo inakikipi. 
\q1 Syare namarikoame rasakinavo rinai arono syo winawain, 
\q2 Nyavave Nyo sya ana danajo ravera mamaisyo rinai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Rikov ti no somamo nde nto ti rakanive, maisyare kijao wemaisy, 
\q2 sya pae so raranitowa maisyare taname raon dai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 5 Inanasine so ntarurandi, maisyare insumai mayone wemaisy, 
\q2 muno inanuga syisyisye inta no ramu. 
\q1  
\v 6 Syanonae akoeve, 
\q2 weti umba inanasine somamo kea bo mo pae rakom. 
\q1  
\v 7 Risyamo ribui tuna mumuimbe, maisyare insani tatekari una no umbuga rai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare insanijo koo no no munijo vatane inta una rai jakato jewene wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 8 Risyamo niki kakai, 
\q2 maisyare insani tuna mumuimbe no yavare tati wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 Namane rinit sya marova wo inaura tantunawi, 
\q2 wo sya tame rave wanaamatambe vatane mai, ware indati awa siurije mo sya ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 10 Syo kapume obo ratukami asyo maisyare omirati sya anaisye mijem, 
\q2 inami ngkaru nsororop ti masyo sya mana damaname rai, 
\q1  
\v 11 weye wimpari mangkebe irati rinai. 
\q2 Winyavakaje inai ti Nyo inandarito maisyare anaingkainye inta raepato wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 12 Rikove somamo indati raumandi maisyare uma pasyo ti sya ugara aumandi wemaisy, 
\q2 risyamo mayondi maisyare insumai mayone wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Weramu sya AMISY, Winyirati mbe akari titive ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno susyo miridi nto wo Nya tame raijaseo titive tawan tutir. 
\q1  
\v 14 Indati taune mbeseo ra naemeno Sion\f + \fr 102:14 \fq Sion \ft omamo Yerusalem ama tamo wusyine mijem.\f* rai, 
\q2 weye ama masyote mi som indamu raijaseo mbambunin akato, 
\q2 soamo ama masyoto Nyo rapatimu rai nande. 
\q1  
\v 15 Weye Nya vatano Israel wanapatambe Naije onawamo mansanuga no awa yavaseno Sion rai, 
\q2 mandamisyija mbe kampumbe to, weramu wenawamo mansaemeno rai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Indati susye kotaro mine so wo AMISY asyaniv, 
\q2 muno akari titi mine so wo Apa kovo ntiti rasyaniv. 
\q1  
\v 17 Anakotare so nande arono indati AMISY Po Sion raijar akaeyo ntet akato, 
\q2 umba Apa kovo ntiti raeno rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Opamo indati Po Apa kawasae awa ananuge meweno mai awa ana udanajo Ai raraniv, 
\q2 muno Po awa ana udanajo Ai rawatambe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 19 Koveamo Amisy Apa anakotaro Po rave umaso ratoe, 
\q2 indamu ntami arikainyo mbeakaseo akato mansamarom, 
\q2 muno susyo indati mansavaki akato nao wo AMISY ararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 20 Weye AMISY tuna no munijo ntiti ndandinit muno peravaje, 
\q2 nai Manunggara, Po munije so raen tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 21 Indamu Po Israel wanonae siuri rai no munijo aroo ranaun. 
\q2 Muno vatano mangke raugaje mai indamu maubaisye nawamo Po mapaya rai. 
\q1  
\v 22-23 Weti arono indati susye kotaro mine so muno munijo vatane ube akarive rai 
\q2 wangkuire tenambe indamu ubeaje irati AMISY Ai, 
\q1 weamo wo Apa tame ravovo no Sion, 
\q2 muno wo ararimbe no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 24 Amisye Po sya vambunine radaut arono ta rikamurame so, 
\q2 muno Po sya tume ransopaje ti ntumainy. 
\q1  
\v 25 Syo raura syare: ‘‘Sya Amisy, Winyi no pitawabe ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 syare vemo Nyo wene raugaje rinai kobe no ta ikamurame so inya.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 26 Arono manasyin dave\f + \fr 102:26 \ft Ayao anemo 26-28 ratoe tavon no Ibr. 1:10-12.\f* Winyirati Nyo mine so ranari, 
\q2 muno Nyo naumo warae ranari tavon. 
\q1  
\v 27 Weramu anakotare umaso indati rakanive vintabo, yara Winyamo no tawan tutir. 
\q1 Mine so muno naume warae noa mbe wusyimbe to, 
\q2 maisyare ansuno mbe wusyimbe to ramaisy. 
\q1 Indati Winyo mine so me naume warae me yaepata, 
\q2 maisyare ansuno mbe wusyimbe raepata ti rakanive wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 28 Weramu Winyamo mbe ninuwanive jewen, 
\q2 Winya marane ntami intai jewen, 
\q2 yara wino tawan tutira nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 29 Nya kawasae reama arikainye, ajavi miridi nto nawamo una mariraave, 
\q2 muno una kovo saumane rautan no winanem uga rai. 
\c 103  
\s1 Syare syo AMISY ararimbe! 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Inya sya jugara, nyo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Nyo Apa tamo ndandinite rararimbe nanuga ntenami rautan! 
\q1  
\v 2 Inya sya jugara, nyo AMISY ararimbe, 
\q2 mbemo nanimarijo Apa kovo Po rarorono nai rai jinya! 
\q1  
\v 3 Opirati Po nya ayao kakai rapaya tenambe, 
\q2 Opirati Po saumane raunande nai no waneno nande nai rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Opirati Po napaya irati atemo amanija rai, 
\q2 muno Opirati aemeno nai ti Po naainyave irati Apa muinyo no tawane rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wepirati Po nya mbekere raunande nai mamaisyo Apa kovo ngkov dave rai, 
\q2 weti winyamo mbambunin muno nya kamurame no tawan, maisyare insanijo mangkakane amaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY Po ana mamaisy muno moyare raugaje, 
\q2 Po raugaje irati vatano matawanto mai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Po Apa bekere rarorono Musa ai to, 
\q2 muno Apa ana dave rarorono kawasae Israel mansai to. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY Opamo muiny dave muno aemeno wansai, 
\q2 Opamo atawandi ngko dave muno Apa muinyo no tawane manakoe rave. 
\q1  
\v 9 Opamo Po wansanayao tutire ramu, 
\q2 muno pari wansai tutira ntoa nuge nuganui ramu. 
\q1  
\v 10 Mangke daude mamo Po rataun mamaisyo wama ayao kakai rarijati ma jewena, 
\q2 muno Po rasakinavo wansaija mamaisyo wama ana wandaveti ngkakai rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Weye maisyare muno naumo ntanenae ti manakoeve\f + \fr 103:11 \fq ntanenae ti manakoeve \ft ranigwano ayao ‘‘ntiti’’ rai indamu ama ine mbar.\f* warae wemaisy, 
\q2 maisyare wemai tavon Apa muinyo no tawane mamo manakoeve rave vatano wo asyanive mai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Maisyare wanamurame nggwaravain dave irati varete rai, 
\q2 wama ayao kakai mamo Po raepata ti musyo marambe wansai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Mamaisyo injae aemeno apa arikainye mansai, 
\q2 maisyare wemaisy, AMISY aemeno Apa vatano wo asyanive mai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Weye Po wansanari animaisye rai, Opamo Po raen to; 
\q2 Po raen to, wamamo kopa ama waum bayave.\f + \fr 103:14 \ft Kej. 2:7\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 Vatane wanjaisye no ra nugoenta ramu yara wamaisyare insumai kavinta mayon akato, 
\q2 maisyare kavasasi ama uge ngkenav vavai wemaisy, 
\q1  
\v 16 ranivara ovare damawisyamo ama ugem umawe numu ti raumandi, 
\q2 muno ama ava numu raije raene jewen. 
\q1  
\v 17 Weramu AMISY Apa muinye no tawan irati vatano wo asyanive maija ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q2 Apa bekobe mamo ntami tawano awa ubakipambe iridi to mai tutir, 
\q1  
\v 18 nanawirati wo Apa urairi Po raokaisyo mai raijaro matuve mai, 
\q2 muno Apa anaparatote mamo ubeto rai tawane mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 AMISY tuna no Apa kursijo ntiti rai no Manunggara, 
\q2 Opamo be akari titive anakotare rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 20 Inya, naito Amisye weap, wapo AMISY ararimbe, 
\q2 weapirati Apa naito anaaniv wapo Apa ayao ranaun muno wabeta rai weap. 
\q1  
\v 21 Inya, naito kotar ntuna no Manunggara wea tenambe, wapo AMISY ararimbe, 
\q2 weapirati Apa naito wapanapatambe Ai ti wapo Apa bekere raveti mamaisye weap. 
\q1  
\v 22 Inya, anakotaro Po ranari mainy tenambe, namirati no no anem ate rai no no rui rui vayave, wapo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Inya, sya jugara, nyo AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 104  
\s1 AMISY ararimbe weye Wepirati Po nuge so ranari tenambe 
\q1  
\v 1 Inya sya jugara, nyo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 AMISY, sya Amisy, Winyirati nyanakoeve! 
\q1 Nya kovo ntiti muno Nya kovo manakoe mo namuman 
\q2 maisyare ansuno akoe naasadi rai, 
\q1  
\v 2 muno Nya varo ntiti mo nakom maisyare ansun akoe. 
\q2 Nyo naume raneka maisyare tanije\f + \fr 104:2 \fq tani: \ft Ayao Ibrani raijamo ama ine mare ‘‘tenda.’’\f* inta raneka, 
\q1  
\v 3 Winyi Nyo Nya yavare rauseo nte no mana ntuna no naume warae\f + \fr 104:3 \fq mana ntuna no naume warae: \ft raen tavon no Kej. 1:6-7.\f* ama vone rai. 
\q1 Winyo kamure rave nyomambe ti nseo rai, 
\q2 nseo ovare ai ti mansanano nautan maisyare insani apa pepako mbadiriro nautane wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Winyo ovare atutir ti poroto Nya mbekere rai, 
\q2 muno Nyo tanamo mbadurur\f + \fr 104:4 \fq tanamo mbadurur: \ft naiso ama ine mare ‘‘ivak.’’ Ibr. 1:7\f* raveti manapatambe Nai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Winyo munije so raugaje ntamijo aji ntindimu rai, 
\q2 weti mangkiki kakai ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 6 Arono mine so ranari rainyoe, Nyo nawanane rayanundi mo nuge ratatuv, 
\q2 muno nseo ti mo unate ratataanaje. 
\q1  
\v 7 Weramu AMISY winsoowato mana rai ti nsararo rakiri, 
\q2 Winy nanamote ravari ti mana mansanano panyoambe ti nin kobe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Mana njam no unat ti masyo no kaibiv, 
\q2 nto no varoro Nyo rapatimu ti nto ntanandi. 
\q1  
\v 9 Winyo anone raugaje ntami mana rai to, indamu vemo mo rakivandi akato inya, 
\q2 wirati vemo mo muni ratatuv akato nora. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Winyo mana ami rapapaya ti njamo kaibive rai, 
\q2 weti njam no unate ama varodore rai, 
\q1  
\v 11 indamu maere kotaro mandayan bayave wo ramanam, 
\q2 muno mo maero keledai mawa ngkamandi rapaya tavon. 
\q1  
\v 12 Mararai no mana we rai insani kotare wo ene ranari rarijat, 
\q2 muno ukiny no inyo uga we rai. 
\q1  
\v 13 No naume vono warae Winyo maru raveti maje papukame rai, 
\q2 mine so ntairi Nya ana ndaijare ama ine rai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Winyo insumai raveti ntubai indamu maere\f + \fr 104:14 \fq maere: \ft no ayao Ibrani raijamo ama ine mare maero anakokoe vatane wo makum, maisyare sapi, kambin muno domba. \f* wisyisyo rai, 
\q2 muno Nyo anare ratayao vatane mansai indamu wo rayanyum, 
\q2 wirati nai kopa rai wo awa anaisye raugavo rai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Muno Winyo anggurije raveti ama poke muje rai, weti vatane mananibe rai, 
\q2 muno manino saitun raveti randi mansamune rai ti ngkenav, 
\q2 muno anaisye ratavon ti vatane ubambunin dai. 
\q1  
\v 16 AMISY Po inyo arase rayanyum no munijo Libanon, 
\q2 Apa inyo Po rayanyume wem njayaisy, weye maruge maje ntapekan dai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Nai inyo arase umaso ama awi insani kotare wo ene ranari rai, 
\q2 muno insani mansyuri wo ene ranari tavon no we. 
\q1  
\v 18 No papukamo ntiti rai kambino mandayane ntuna rai, 
\q2 no ama orame varodore rai maero pelanduk\f + \fr 104:18 \fq pelanduk: \ft maisyare karawae amaisy. \f* no rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Winyi Nyo embae ranari indamu mo matame raroron, 
\q2 muno uma apa ami pasyo rai mamo Winyi ndapatimu. 
\q1  
\v 20 Ranivara Nyo namane raude, weamo kaumure nande, 
\q2 arono naije maere kotaro anate muje mandayan. 
\q1  
\v 21 Singa kamurame ukaririmbe wo maero wo raisye rakani, 
\q2 maero Amisye Po ratayao mansamarome rakani. 
\q1  
\v 22 Ranivara uma pare tipu seo, weamo singa unanajibe wakata no awa una ri rai, 
\q2 wakata unakijo atentemo ukaokaibe raije rai. 
\q1  
\v 23 Umba vatane wusya awa anakere rai, 
\q2 wo awa anakere raijara ntoa namandi. 
\q1  
\v 24 Wakoe! AMISY, Nya ana ndave manui rave, 
\q2 Nyo anakotaro ranawayo no rai ranari Nya ana ndatantona ntiti rai, 
\q2 weti mine so ntairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 25 Waperata mayano manakoe muno ntanenae ratuije, 
\q2 jiane muno anakotaro njaisyo rai, ama manui ratora marudi, 
\q2 momoyainy muno akokoe ntuna njai rai. 
\q1  
\v 26 Jiano saroe\f + \fr 104:26 \fq Jiano Saroe: \ft no ayao Ibrani rai mo ratoe mare \ft \+it Lewiatan,\+it* ama ine mare ‘‘tawae akoe.’’ Raen tavon no Ayub 41:1; Maz. 74:14; Yes. 27:1.\f* Nyo anari seo baono rai, 
\q2 muno nyomano mayane ntovabe rai. 
\q1  
\v 27 Anakotar tenambe so nao manaveano Akoe winamen, 
\q2 indamu Nyo anaisye raunande mai arono wo ranajo. 
\q1  
\v 28 Ranivara Winyo anaisye raude, weamo wo raugav, 
\q2 muno ranivara winaneme rarorono mai, weamo umano Nya kove rai. 
\q1  
\v 29 Weramu ranivara winakirive mai, weamo ujaniv dave, 
\q2 muno ranivara Nyo manawayo akarimu, weamo wene mo maugav, 
\q2 weti wenawamo wakasya ti ube kopave. 
\q1  
\v 30 Weramu Winyo kovo wanyine raugakaje mine so rai, 
\q2 weye arono rui Nyo nanawayoe raugaje, weamo mo anakotare inta ranari wanyimbe akato. 
\q1  
\v 31 Syare indati AMISY Apa kovo ntiti no tawana ntoa nuge nuganui! 
\q2 Muno syare indati AMISY anayanambe Apa anakotaro danari rai! 
\q1  
\v 32 Po munije so raerade, weamo mungki nande rai, 
\q2 muno pantukamo papukame raijamo kijao mpatututo rai. 
\q1  
\v 33 Syare kinyo ransyerane raijo AMISY Ai arono ta rikov, 
\q2 muno rikangkamambe sya Amisye aijo ransyerane rai arono ta rituna. 
\q1  
\v 34 Amisye Po inanuga raveti ranayanambe, 
\q2 weti ribeker syare risya syo AMISY atantona mo anayanambe raugavo Ai. 
\q1  
\v 35 Syare koveamo vatano wo ayao kakai rave maumandita no mine vone so rai, 
\q2 koveamo vatano wonae Amisy Ai muenen da maumandita. 
\b  
\q1 Inya sya jugara, nyo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe!\f + \fr 104:35 \ft No ayao Ibrani raijamo mo \ft \+it haleluyah\+it* ratoe, ama ine mare ‘‘AMISY ararimbe.’’\f* 
\c 105  
\s1 Amisye ararimbe weye beto Apa urairi rai 
\q1  
\v 1 Kove raura seo AMISY Ai, Apa tame rawain no wapa sambaya ama uga rai, 
\q2 wapo Apa anakotaro Po rave ravovo susye kotaro mine so rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 2 Wakiny wapo AMISY ararimbe, muno wapo ransyeran kangkaman raura seo Ai, 
\q2 wapo Apa anainame kotaro Po rarorone ravovo tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wasanuga manakoeve AMISY Ai weye Opamo dandinit dave, 
\q2 syare vatan tenambe wasanayanambe, wasambayambe AMISY Ai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Wamararai ta AMISY Ai, muno wapo anajo vambunine rai, 
\q2 wabeaje Ai tutir, indamu tuna wasautan tutir. 
\q1  
\v 5-6 Inya, Abraham wepi panapatambe AMISY Ai apa ajavi weap; 
\q2 inya, weapi wasaura Yakop apa susye tavon, 
\q2 wea tenambe AMISY Po wasatayao terave amarom. 
\q1 Syare wasaemeno Apa anainame muno anapaporainyo Po rarorone rai, 
\q2 muno mangke Po raugaje wama marova mai rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 AMISY opirati wama Amisy, 
\q2 Wepi Po ayao mamaisye rapatimu vatano mine tename so mansai mamaisyo awa ana udave rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Opamo aemen tutiro Apa urairi rai ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 teto rai tawano susyo mbakipambe iridito rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Po urairi so raokaisyo Abraham ai, 
\q2 umba purairive panyoambe Isak ai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Apa urairi wem, Po rapatimu akato irati Yakop ai, 
\q2 indamu urairi we no tawano kawasae Israel mansai ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 11 Apa urairije no taiso: ‘‘Yakop, winyirati indati Risyo muni Kanaan raunande nai, 
\q2 indamu susyo nyo rampam iridito awa ura rai tawan tutir.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 AMISY purairive somamo arono apa kawasae Israel wenawamo 
\q2 maisyare vatano maran una no munijo Kanaan ratuije, 
\q2 awa wanui mamaun bayave. 
\q1  
\v 13 Wuija uta no susye inta mai wakaujea uta no susye inta mai jakato, 
\q2 wuija unanta no munije inta rai wakaujea uta no munijo kaijinta rai jakato. 
\q1  
\v 14 AMISY Po mapaya vayave ramu, inda vatano kaije wo mansewabe inya, 
\q2 Pare Po Apa kawasae mansayaranande, weti Po akari titi manayao. 
\q1  
\v 15 Pare: ‘‘Vemo wapo Sya vatano Syo matayaowe mave tatugadi nora, 
\q2 muno vemo wapo kakai rave Sya anawae\f + \fr 105:15 \fq anawae: \ft Abraham, Isak muno Yakop mawaino anawae, weye wenawirati AMISY Apa ayao nde mai no arono naije.\f* mai jinya.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 AMISY Po marore raugaje ntamijo muni Kanaan rai, 
\q2 awa anaisye rakaniveta vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 17 Weramu AMISY Po vatane inta apatimu po usyeve mai: 
\q2 wepirati Yusup, amavunta be arove no Mesir. 
\q1  
\v 18 No no makova wo ajo raugasya aitamu rai, 
\q2 apa isyisye mamo poor besi raugasya nsawa rai. 
\q1  
\v 19 Ndeve ava ana raurairive wusyimbe we mamaisy,\f + \fr 105:19 \ft Kej. 41:1-36\f* 
\q2 AMISY Po ayao Yusup po raura umaso raveti mamai dave kobe. 
\q1  
\v 20 Akari titi Mesir po apa vatane matutir wo Yusup apaya no makova rai, 
\q2 akarijo vatano Mesir we po apaya kobe. 
\q1  
\v 21 Akari titi we po Yusup aijaseo be akarive no apa yavaruga rai, 
\q2 muno panaveo ai indamu po apa anakotare raija nande tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 22 Yusup po Mesir awa akari akokoe matutiro apa bekere rai, 
\q2 muno po awa vatano matu manyao irati ana ratantona ntiti rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Umba Yakop, awain tavonamo Israel, poroto no Mesir, 
\q2 muno apa yavaruga matavon, una no we maisyare vatano maran no munijo Ham\f + \fr 105:23 \ft Munijo Mesir rawain tavonamo ‘‘munijo Ham,’’ weye Nuh apa arikainyo Ham muno apa susyo po mampame una no naije. \f* umaso. 
\q1  
\v 24 AMISY Po Apa kawasae Israel awa wanui raveti miridi nseo, 
\q2 muno Po maveti ubambunin dave vatano Mesir makivan. 
\q1  
\v 25 Wepi Po vatano Mesir maveti manuga mamuno Apa kawasae mansai, 
\q2 weti wo Apa kawasae wanapatambe Ai maponae. 
\q1  
\v 26 Umba AMISY Po Musa, wepi panapatambe Ai, atutir to no Mesir, 
\q2 muno Po Harun atayao ti Po atutiro atavon. 
\q1  
\v 27 Wenanai yo AMISY Apa anainame raroron no vatano Mesir awa yasyin, 
\q2 muno Apa anapaporainye raroron no munijo Ham umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 28 AMISY Po ananamane raveti nande weti nuge ngkaumudi vintabo, 
\q2 weramu vatano Mesir wanave Apa ayao rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 29 AMISY Po mana ntuna no Mesir ranigwan ti mavu vintabo, 
\q2 weti jiane muenen bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 30 Karavinane mo muni Mesir rayapu, 
\q2 muno nsiso ti Akari Titi apa tanoane ntairi janyi. 
\q1  
\v 31 Amisye Po raura, naije kobe abuu nde, 
\q2 muno anyira nde tavon mo awa munije rayapu vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 32 Amisye Po maru ranigwan ti nanayao dave weti mbe maru orambe maje, 
\q2 muno Po ivake raveti ratatukande nuge rai vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 33 Maisyare omaisy, Amisye Po awa angguri muno inyo ara rababari, 
\q2 muno inyo ntuna no awa muni rabibiti vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 34 Amisye Po raura, naije kobe kao mine nsen, 
\q2 kao mino nsen wemainy awa wanuije mamo ratore kakai. 
\q1  
\v 35 Wo anare kotaro ntubai no munijo Mesir raisy bintabo, 
\q2 muno wo awa nawaisye ama ine raisy tavon ti mewen. 
\q1  
\v 36 Amisye Po arikainyo anui Mesir mao tenambe vintabo, 
\q2 weti awa vambunino arikainyo anui indamu mo yavaruga rampam iridito, mayondi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 37 Umba AMISY Po vatano Israel maugav uje munijo Mesir raora, 
\q2 wo perak muno emasije inta raugav tavon, 
\q2 wenao bintaboamo manakea nsauman muno ubambunin. 
\q1  
\v 38 Vatano Mesir wo vatano Israel masyaniv dave, 
\q2 weti arono vatano Israel wuje, vatano Mesir mananibe rave. 
\q1  
\v 39 Amisy Po kamure raugaje ti ngkamajugambe irati vatano Israel mai, 
\q2 muno Po taname raugaje ti mbaro mai no naman. 
\q1  
\v 40 Wo AMISY anajo anaisye rai, 
\q2 weti Po insani muno roti\f + \fr 105:40 \fq roti: \ft anaisye somamo raura tavonamo \ft \+it manna.\+it* Kel. 16:31\f* raugaje no naume warae, ti wo raisya uman dave. 
\q1  
\v 41 AMISY Po oramo akoe\f + \fr 105:41 \ft Kel. 17:1-6\f* raporar ti mana nsui uje rai, 
\q2 umba njam maisyare mana akoe no anoko kanen. 
\q1  
\v 42 Weye AMISY aemen tutiro Apa urairi rai, 
\q2 namirati Po raokaisyo Abraham ai, Apa vatano panapatambeo Ai. 
\q1  
\v 43 Arono Po Apa kawasae maugav uje, manayanambe rave, 
\q2 weti Apa vatano Po matayao wenao, ukiny mananibe. 
\q1  
\v 44 AMISY Po susye kotare awa kopa raunanto Apa vatano Israel mai indamu weyave rai, 
\q2 muno wo vatano kaije awa nawaisye ama ine raugavo mamarom. 
\q1  
\v 45 Wirati indamu Apa kawasae ubeta Apa anaparatote rai, 
\q2 muno utavon irati Apa ananyao rai tutir. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 106  
\s1 AMISY Apa muinyo Po raroron irati Apa kawasae mai 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 Kove raura seo irati AMISY Ai, weye Wepi kov dave! 
\q2 Apa muinyo no tawane mamo ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 2 Vatane inta mamaisyo po AMISY Apa ana dave makokoive ratore kakai, 
\q2 muno bambunin da kangkamambe Ai ti mamai dave jewen. 
\q1  
\v 3 Kove ngkov irati vatano are nawirati utavondi moyare raije mai, 
\q2 muno awa ana udave mamaisyo Amisye Apa ananyao rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya AMISY, naemeno rinai tavon arono wimbekobe irati Nya kawasae mai, 
\q2 muno arono Nyo mapaya awa marova mai, syare Nyo rinapaya tavon. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ribeker syare syo Nya kovo no irati vatano Nyo matayao maije raen; 
\q2 syare ritavondi Nya kawasae mananibe matavon; 
\q2 syare syo nararimbe tavon irati Nya vatano Winya ura terave mai matavon. 
\q1  
\v 6 Reamo ayao kakai rave tavon to, maisyare reama anene mansamaisy, 
\q2 reama ana ndave musyo marambe, reama ana ndave ngkakainoanive. 
\q1  
\v 7 Arono reama anene una no Mesir, 
\q2 anainamo Amisy Nyo rarorone mamo wo ratantona kobe jewen. 
\q1 Wenawamo uparandeno Nya muinyo manakoe no tawane rai, 
\q2 muno no Mayano Kolsum ama tuga, wonae ubeta Amisy Ntiti rave Winai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Weramu Po mapaya irati ana nsosobe ama uga rai, wirati Apa tame raijaseo titive, 
\q2 indamu Po Apa vambunino manakoe raroron kakavimbe. 
\q1  
\v 9 Amisye soowato Mayano Kolsum\f + \fr 106:9,22 \ft Mayano Kolsum ama tamo kaijinta mamo: ‘‘Mayano Nijam,’’ ‘‘Gelaga’’ muno ‘‘Teberau.’’ Kel. 14:21; Arakov. 7:36; 1Kor. 10:1; Maz. 136:11\f* rai, weti mparikisy, 
\q2 umba Po Apa kawasae maugav ti wanya mayane ama yasyine raito maisyare wanya no anoko kanene rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 10 Maisyare omaisy, Po mapaya irati vatano manuga mamuno mai maneme rai, 
\q2 muno Po mapaya irati vambunino marova rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Awa marova nanawamo mayane mo matatuv asyo, 
\q2 weti vatane inta kov akatoe ramu. 
\q1  
\v 12 Arono naije umba vatano Israel wanave Amisy Apa ayao rai, 
\q2 umba ukinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo Amisye Ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Weramu nugoenta jewen manimari akato irati Amisye Apa anakotaro dave rai, 
\q2 muno matawandi wo Apa ananyao raranive jewen. 
\q1  
\v 14 Umba nai anoko kanen, manuga wisyisy ntipu mai, 
\q2 muno wo Amisye atopan no we. 
\q1  
\v 15 Po awa ana wo ranajo raunande mai, 
\q2 weramu Po wanene raunande irati mai tavon. 
\q1  
\v 16 Arono una no anoko kanen, manuga mamuno Musa ai, 
\q2 muno Harun ai tavon, vatano AMISY Po atayao terave indamu be syembe.\f + \fr 106:16 \ft Bil. 16:1-35\f* 
\q1  
\v 17 Wetiva kopa mporar mo Datan aunto, 
\q2 muno mo Abirama pe apa arakove nanawe matatuv tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 18 Amisye Po tanamo mbadurure raugaje vatano kaijo utavondi maije mai, 
\q2 mo vatano mamune manen ti mangkur. 
\q1  
\v 19 Nai unato Sinai, wo emasi ranari sapi tuvane rainyi, 
\q2 umba ubeaje yaro emasi umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Wo awa Amisy Wepi titi rave apaya vayave, 
\q2 yara wo anigwano yaro sapi po insumai raisye obo ai.\f + \fr 106:20 \ft Kel. 32:1-14\f* 
\q1  
\v 21 Manimari irati Amisy Ai, Wepi rati Po mapaya awa ana nsosobe maije rai, 
\q2 napirati Apa ana dave makokoive rarorono mai no Mesir wep. 
\q1  
\v 22 Tugae, Po anapaporainye rave no munijo Ham,\f + \fr 106:22 \ft Munijo Ham raura tavonamo ‘‘Mesir.’’\f* 
\q2 Apa anainamo mbe anaanibe no Mayano Kolsum ama tuga rai. 
\q1  
\v 23 Weti Amisye Po raura pare Po Apa kawasae umaso mao, 
\q2 weramu Musa, vatano Amisye Po atayao terave amarome so, teto yasyimbe mai, 
\q2 weti umba po Amisye Apa parije umaso rapamo. 
\q1  
\v 24 Umba ware wonae munijo ngkov dave raurairive mai we rai, 
\q2 weye wanave Amisye Apa urairije we rai akato jewen. 
\q1  
\v 25 Wenawamo wo nuge rapanan no awa randumo utantuna ri, 
\q2 muno wonae wo AMISY Apa ayao raranivi. 
\q1  
\v 26 Weti Po urairive panaamatambe, 
\q2 pare Po mansao bintabo no anoko kanen, 
\q1  
\v 27 umba Po awa arikainye, ajavije mampusyek ti uta na susye kotare marijat, 
\q2 muno uta una muni kaije raito. 
\q1  
\v 28 Umba nai Peor ubeaje irati yaro Baal rai,\f + \fr 106:28,30 \ft Bil. 25:1-13\f* 
\q2 muno wo anaisyo rameseo vatano ugwenene maije raisy tavon. 
\q1  
\v 29 Awa ana udave taije maisye mo AMISY aveti pari mai rave, 
\q2 weti Po waneno mangke raugaje mai. 
\q1  
\v 30 Weramu Peneas beseo kobe po mangke raugaje vatano yo ayao kakai rave yai, 
\q2 weti umba Amisye Po waneno mangke umaso ransopi. 
\q1  
\v 31 Muno Peneas apa ana dave umasom Amisye Po raen pare omamo mamai no Amune rai, 
\q2 weti vatano Israel maemendi rai tutira ntoa nugoenta. 
\q1  
\v 32 Nai mana ami Meriba rai vatano Israel wo AMISY aveti pari mai, 
\q2 awa ana wo rave mbewar ana nsosobe nande Musa ai.\f + \fr 106:32 \ft Amisye parijo Musa ai tavon, weti Po aorai indamu vemo siso no munijo ngkov dave raurairive rai nora. Bil. 20:2-13\f* 
\q1  
\v 33 Weye wo Musa aveti anuga mamuno mai, 
\q2 weti po ayao kove jewene rator. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 34 AMISY Po Apa ananyao raugaje Israel mai, pare wo susye kotaro una no Kanaan maubaisy. 
\q2 Weramu wo maubaisye ramu,\f + \fr 106:34 \ft Ul. 7:2-5,16\f* 
\q1  
\v 35 yara uta maijaro matavon, 
\q2 muno utavondi awa ana udave rai tavon kobe. 
\q1  
\v 36 Vatano Israel ubeaje irati susye kotare umaso awa yare rai, 
\q2 wemirati mo matopan weti makirive Amisye Ai.\f + \fr 106:35-36 \ft Hakim 2:1-3, 3:5-6\f* 
\q1  
\v 37 Muno wo awa arikainyo anya muno wanya mansaotar, 
\q2 wo mansamer nanto irati anawayo kakai mai.\f + \fr 106:37 \ft 2Raj. 17:17\f* 
\q1  
\v 38 Wo vatano ayao kakaije meweno maije awa mavu raveti nsopat, 
\q2 omamo taune awa arikainyo anya muno wanya nanawirati wo maotare awa mavu mije, 
\q1 indamu wo ramer nanto irati vatano Kanaan\f + \fr 106:38 \ft Vatano Kanaan sonanawamo vatano Het, Girgasi, Amori, Kanaan, Feris, Hewi, Yebus. Ul. 7:1-6\f* awa yare mai. 
\q2 Weti wo munijo we raveti nggwambe irati mavuge rai. 
\q1  
\v 39 Awa ana wo rave taije maisye mo maveti ugwambe no Amisye Amune rai, 
\q2 muno makirive Ai jirati awa ana udaveti ngkakainoanive rai. 
\q1  
\v 40 Weti AMISY pari mangkebe irati Apa kawasae Israel mai, 
\q2 muno anuga mamuno Apa vatano Po matayao terave amarome mai. 
\q1  
\v 41 Weti Po maunanto irati susye kotaro wanave jewene maneme rai, 
\q2 indamu vatano manuga mamuno Israel mai ube akarive irati mai. 
\q1  
\v 42 Umba awa marova wo matawanto, 
\q2 muno wo mapinaje no manem ate rai. 
\q1  
\v 43 Amisye Po Israel mapaya ana nsosobe maije rai mamo manui to, 
\q2 weramu wenawamo wo patimu rave ware wonae wo aranivi, 
\q2 weti awa ayao kakai mbewar Amisye Po mapaya ti utataopon. 
\q1  
\v 44 Weramu AMISY Po mansaen arono una ana nsosobe ama uga rai, 
\q2 Po mansanaun arono wo awain. 
\q1  
\v 45 Opamo aemendi Apa urairijo Po raokaisy nanto irati maije rai, 
\q2 muno aemeno mai mamaisyo Apa muinyo manakoe no tawane rai. 
\q1  
\v 46 Po maveti awa marova ubekobe mai, 
\q2 nanawirati wo maijaro arove nanao. 
\q1  
\v 47 AMISY, reama Amisy, reamare Nyo reansapaya irati reama marova aneme rai jakato, 
\q2 reamare Nyo reansanugan akare susye kotaro wanave jewene maora. 
\q1 Indamu reamo Nya tamo ndandinite rawain, 
\q2 reamo kove raura seo Nai muno reamo nararimbe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 48 AMISY ararimbe, Wepirati Amisy vatano Israel ubeaje Ai, 
\q2 nai nugo pitawar ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1 Muno syare vatan tenambe wo raura ware: ‘‘Tugae!’’ 
\q2 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 107  
\ms1 ETET 5 
\ms1 MASMUR 107-150 
\s1 Vatano AMISY Po mapaya irati kakai rai awa ransyeran wo kove raura seo Ai 
\q1  
\v 1 Kove raura AMISY Ai, weye Opamo ko dave! 
\q2 Apa muinye no tawan\f + \fr 107:1 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it hesed\+it* ama ine ratoe tumaimbe naiso mare: ‘‘muinye no tawan.’’ Ama ino manakoe mare: ‘‘Amisye Apa muinye muno Apa anakotaro Po raurairive ti no tawan tutiro Apa kawasae Israel mansai mamo Po raveti mamaisy.’’\f* ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 2 Inya, vatano AMISY Po wasapaya to weap, koveamo wapo ayao umaso raura tutir, 
\q2 weapirati vatano Po wasapaya irati anakotaro nsosobe rai weap. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weapamo Amisye Po wasanugan akare to, 
\q2 no munijo maran wata wanari we, 
\q1 nai wanamuram muno nai varet, 
\q2 nai wanansai muno nai wanampui.\f + \fr 107:3 \fq wanampui: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘mayan.’’ Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ama ine mare Mayano Akaba no no Israel ama ranijo wanampui, yara kuruno kaijinta wo ratantona ama ine mare Mayano Yasyin no no Israel ama ranijo varet.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Vatane umaso inta nawamo wanya ti umandayan bayave no anoko kanen, 
\q2 muno wantatukambe unanuijo nto no munijo vatane una raije inta rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 5 Marore po mave muno mansawa ngkangkamandi, 
\q2 muno mansanuga mamaun dave. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weti arono una irati anakotaro nsosobe umaso rai, wo AMISY anonae, 
\q2 umba Po mapaya irati awa ana nsosobe umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Po maugav wanya irati unanuijo nsarokire obo raito, 
\q2 wanawadi unanta no munijo vatane utantuna rije rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare wo kove raura seo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weye Apa muinye no tawan tutir, 
\q2 muno Apa ana Po rave mbe anainambe vatane mai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weye Po mana raunande vatano mansawa ngkangkamandije mai indamu wo ramanam, 
\q2 muno Po anaisyo ngkov dave raunanto vatano umarore mai indamu uman.\f + \fr 107:9 \ft Ayao so ratoe akato no Luk. 1:53.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Yara vatane inta nawamo utantuna no kaumuro ntapekane rai,\f + \fr 107:10,14,16 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware kaumuro ntapekan muno poor besi mbe rarorombe arono vatano Israel mave arove no munijo Babel.\f* 
\q2 onawamo vatano makova nanawirati poor besi raasaro mai ti una siuri rai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Usiuri weye wonae ubeta irati Amisye Apa ayao raiji, 
\q2 muno Amisy Titi Rave Apa ananyao mamo wo ramumuibe. 
\q1  
\v 12 Wemi mbewar Po anakero mangke veano matawan asyo kobe, ti awa mayare rakanive mai, 
\q2 awa vambunine meweno mai ti utaopon, muno vatane inta po sopambe mai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 13 Arono una irati anakotaro nsosobe umaso rai, wo AMISY anonae, 
\q2 umba Po mapaya irati awa ana nsosobe mai umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Po maugav uje irati ngkaumudi ntapekane raora, 
\q2 muno Po poor besije rapaya irati mai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Syare wo kove raura seo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weye Apa muinye no tawan tutir, 
\q2 muno Apa ana Po rave mbe anainambe vatane mai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 16 Weye Po unsanda tembaga randujai ti ntuna, 
\q2 muno Po ama kekepo besi raotadi ti ndanduiny. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Vatane inta nawamo vatano wananepabe weye wonae ubeta Amisye Aiji, 
\q2 onawamo usiuri mangkebe weye wo ana ngkakai rave. 
\q1  
\v 18 Wenawamo wonae anaisye rai tenambe, 
\q2 muno onawamo uta usayae unsanda amanija rai to. 
\q1  
\v 19 Weti arono una irati anakotaro nsosobe umaso rai, wo AMISY anonae, 
\q2 umba Po mapaya irati awa ana nsosobe umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Payaode mai vayave weamo usauman kobe, 
\q2 muno Po mapaya irati atemo wene rai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Syare wo kove raura seo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weye Apa muinye no tawan tutir, 
\q2 muno Apa ana Po rave mbe anainambe vatane mai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 22 Syare wo maere raugav wo rameseo indamu wo kove raura seo Amisye Ai, 
\q2 muno mansanayanambe wo Apa ana dave rariri! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Vatane inta nawamo wo nyomane vone raiyaive no mayane vone warave, 
\q2 nai mayano maneka wem wanamavumbe. 
\q1  
\v 24 Wo AMISY Apa anakotaro Po rave raen, 
\q2 muno wo anapaporainyo Po rave no mayano ntento warave raen tavon. 
\q1  
\v 25 Purarijato mayane rai ti ovaro repe tipu, 
\q2 aneae akokoe ntitije mpapoambe. 
\q1  
\v 26 Mo nyomane raijaseo ti nto no kakavine warae, 
\q2 mo rantuvudi akasyo aneae ama uga raito, 
\q2 onawamo ujaniv dave weye mansansowave ana ngkakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 27 Aneae mo maijaseo maugaje ti mansamune nsadirae, 
\q2 muno ubabarive maisyare vatane inta maeno awije rai wemaisy, 
\q2 muno awa ana udatantona meweno mai. 
\q1  
\v 28 Weti arono una irati anakotaro nsosobe umaso rai, wo AMISY anonae, 
\q2 umba Po mapaya irati awa ana nsosobe umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 29 Po ovaro rep umaso ansopi ti tanamanin, 
\q2 umba aneae mpapoambe ntanamanin tavon. 
\q1  
\v 30 Vatano una no nyomane rai umaso manayanambe weye ovare tanamanin to, 
\q2 umba Amisy Po maugavo munijo ubekedai raronto. 
\q1  
\v 31 Syare wo kove raura seo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weye Apa muinye no tawan tutir, 
\q2 muno Apa ana Po rave mbe anainambe vatane mai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 32 Koveamo wo Amisye aijaseo titive no anugane awa yasyin, 
\q2 muno wo ararimbe no vatano ube akarive anugane rai mansamun.\f + \fr 107:32 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘vatano awa akoe matu,’’ ama ine mare ube akarive.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 33-34 Vatano munije inta nawamo awa ana udave ngkakainoanive, 
\q2 weti Amisye Po mana raveti mparikisy anyi ti mbe anoko sapave, 
\q1 muno mana ama vune ngkanen anyi tavon ti mbe kopa ngkanembe, 
\q2 muno Po kopa minsine raveti nsakam ti anare ntubai kakai. 
\q1  
\v 35 Weramu umba Amisye Po anoko kanene umaso raveti mana ntananamo rai, 
\q2 Po kopa ngkanen dave raveti mana ami ntatipu rai jakato. 
\q1  
\v 36 Po vatano marore maugaveto una no we, 
\q2 weti wo munije inta rauseo ntet indamu utantuna rai no we. 
\q1  
\v 37 Wo nawaisye raperam ti wo anare kamije rangkiki rai janyi, 
\q2 muno wo anggurije rayanyumo rai, 
\q2 ti mo mane rauguje nsamumbe rave ti wo ranugan anyi. 
\q1  
\v 38 Amisye Po kove raugaje mai ti awa arikainye wanui rave, 
\q2 muno maero wo makume awa wanui miridi nseo rave kobe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 39 Weramu soamo utaopon to muno awa wanui miridi makaje, 
\q2 weye awa marova wo mapinde, wo matawanto mangkebe ti mansanimaumbe rave. 
\q1  
\v 40 Amisye seambe vatano akokoe mai ti Po maveti awa tame maje, 
\q2 muno Po maveti wanya umandayan bayave no munijo ngkanembe unanui wo raito mewen dai rai. 
\q1  
\v 41 Weramu vatano awa ananu jajewembe mai nawamo, Amisye Po maijaseo no awa siuri rai, 
\q2 muno Po kove raugaje mai ti awa susyo wo mampame wanui rave kobe. 
\q1  
\v 42 Vatano manuga nsarokiro Amisye Ai wo Apa ana dave umaso raen ti umananibe, 
\q2 yara vatano mamune nawamo mawa ntapumi ti wayao kakai. 
\q1  
\v 43 Are pirati apa ana datantona ngkov? 
\q2 Weamo syare po ana so ratantona mavabe, 
\q2 muno po AMISY Apa muinyo no tawane ratantonave. 
\c 108  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po wansapaya irati marova mai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran. Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Inanuga so ntindimu sya Amisy Nai, 
\q2 syare rikinyo ransyerane rai, rikangkamambe Nai inanuga ntenami rautan. 
\q1  
\v 3 Inya, syare ibeseo, syo itari anakoe muno itari mamaune\f + \fr 108:3 \fq itari anakoe \ft muno \fq itari mamaune \ft ranigwano ‘‘gambus’’ muno ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* raeyan, 
\q2 rikiny no arono akane mare ntipu kobe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya AMISY, Winyirati syare syo kove raura seo Nai no vatan tenambe so awa yasyin, 
\q2 syare rikinyo ransyeran kangkamane raijo Winai no susye kotaro mine so awa yasyin. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye Nya muinyo no tawane mamo ntitito no naume warae, 
\q2 muno winteto Nya urairi rai mamo nto rave ti mo kamure rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya Amisy, syare Nya ntiti rave raroron no naume warae, 
\q2 muno Nya kovo ntiti raroron no mine tename so rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Reamare Nyo reama ana ndanajo raraniv, 
\q2 muno Nyo reansapaya irati reama marova mai nanemo vambunine rai, 
\q2 indamu vatano winanuga no mai upaya irati kakai rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Arono Amisye Po kopa Kanaan raosoro vatano Israel mai, payao no Apa tuna ri ndandinit, 
\q2 pare: ‘‘Rinanayanambe ti syare Syo kopa Sikem raosor. 
\q2 Muno Syo kaivo Sukot rataun, indamu Syo raosor.\f + \fr 108:8 \ft Sikem no no mana Yordan ama ranijo varet, muno Sukot no no ama ranijo wanamuram, kopa umaso ibe rarorombe munijo Israel ama mantamito rai tenambe.\f* 
\q1  
\v 9 Kopa Gilead muno Manasye\f + \fr 108:9 \ft Gilead muno Manasye no no mana Yordan ama ranijo wanamuram.\f* omamo Risya ma, 
\q2 Epraim\f + \fr 108:9 \ft Munijo Epraim omirati naito anaanive una ri we, yara munijo Yehuda omirati akari titi Israel no ri we.\f* omirati maisyare sapeo besi no inakari raora wemaisy, 
\q2 muno Yehuda wemirati Sya isyo akari titi raugaje nteto rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Weramu munijo Moab\f + \fr 108:10 \ft Aneme so ama ine mare Amisye Apa ura kopa Moab muno Edom muno Pilistea rai tenambe, weramu ponae rai weye awa kawasae wanave Ai jewen.\f* omamo maisyare unggano inajo rarondomo rai mije, 
\q2 yara Edom omamo inajo kokome ramauto ntami rai weti Sya ura rai, 
\q2 muno rigwain inananibe weye syanasineko muni Pilistea rai.’’\f + \fr 108:10 \ft Aneme so ama ine mare vatano susye mandeije so–Moab, Edom, muno Pilistea–onawamo Amisye indati Po mapinde tenambe indamu munijo Israel mbe akarive mai.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Arepi indati po inaugave to no munijo Edom? 
\q2 Arepi tavono rinai ti rito no munijo ama yano orame ntindimu ratuije rai? 
\q1  
\v 12 Sya Amisy, Winyamo ntavondi reansai ramu ge? 
\q2 Muno naijaro reama naite matavon da wata marova rai ramu ge? 
\q1  
\v 13 Nde Nyo sopambe reansai inda reamo marova mapinde, 
\q2 weye vatan bayave wo sopambe reansai mamo mamaisye ramu. 
\q1  
\v 14 Ranivara Amisy wintavono reansai, weamo reambambunin dave, 
\q2 weye Winyi Nyo reama marova matakarasyo. 
\c 109  
\s1 Vatano aura tantunawi apa sambaya 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1 Sya Amisy, Winyi syo nararimbeve tutir, 
\q2 syare vemo manin bayave inya. 
\q1  
\v 2 Weye vatano mamun muno vatano mawa ntairi aarurijate rai 
\q2 wo rinaura tantunawi muno wayao angkarive irati rinai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Awa ayao wo inaura ti mamune mamo wo veano inanepat, 
\q2 muno wo inakekebe vayave ayao mamaisye jewene rai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Risyamo bekobe mai muno syo Amisye anajo indamu Po kove raugaje mai, 
\q2 weramu wo rasakinav akare mamo, ayao kakai mi wo rantutibe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Risyamo ibekobe mai yara onawamo wo rasakinavo ana ngkakai rai, 
\q2 risyamo muinyo mai weramu wo rasakinavo manuga mamune rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Syare Nyo vatano mamune inta atayao da tet no akarije amun, 
\q2 indamu po ayao kakai rantutibe sya marova ai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Arono indati ayao rapatimu sya marova umaso ai, weamo syare mangke wemi ntende ai, 
\q2 muno apa ana danajo Amisye Ai mamo mbe ayao kakaive taune ai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Koveamo apa matame raotar aje tumaimbe, 
\q2 muno apa anakero po raijare mamo vatano kaijinta po anigwano rai kai.\f + \fr 109:8 \ft Ayao so ratoe akato no Arakov. 1:20.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Koveamo apa arikainye ube arikainyo wawat be, 
\q2 muno apa anamu mbe kavinive. 
\q1  
\v 10 Koveamo apa arikainye mapaya ti ntuna mandup bayave muno wanatambe, 
\q2 muno mawatan inda wusya irati awa yavaro randujai ti ntuna we raora. 
\q1  
\v 11 Syare koveamo vatano de po atan irati ananugo davae dainye raijep, po apa ananuge raugaveto vintabo aora, 
\q2 muno vatano pantatukambe maije inta wo apa mamoane raugaveto aora tavon. 
\q1  
\v 12 Vemo vatane inta ubekobe ai jakato inya, 
\q2 muno apa arikainyo po mapaya ti una wenao, vemo inta maemeno mai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 13 Koveamo arikainyo po mampame maotar da makanive, 
\q2 muno nto irati susyo jirume rai, vemo apa tame ranaun akato inya. 
\q1  
\v 14 Koveamo apa anene awa ayao kakai mamo AMISY animari irati rai jinya, 
\q2 muno apa akoeam ama ayao kakaije raupaisy inya. 
\q1  
\v 15 Koveamo awa ayao kakai namijem, AMISY ami ntami rai tutir, 
\q2 muno vatano mine so maemen akato maive inya. 
\q1  
\v 16 Weye vatane sop, ponae po muinye inta rarorombei, 
\q2 yara po vatano usiuri muno awa ananuge meweno maije mawatan muno po mansewabe, 
\q2 muno po vatano manuga mpatimu maubaisy. 
\q1  
\v 17 Opamo anayanambe panaamatambe vatane mai, 
\q2 weti koveamo apa anaamatane nsakinav makare taune ai. 
\q1 Opamo ponae po Amisye anajo indamu Po kove raugaje vatano kaijinta maiji, 
\q2 weti koveamo kovo Amisye raugaje ai jewen tavon. 
\q1  
\v 18 Apa ana no ai tenambe tutire mamo anaamatane bom, 
\q2 ramaisyare apa ansuno po rave masyote antetere wemaisy. 
\q1 Anaamatane umaso maisyare mana ramanam, weti mo anasine rarijate wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare manino veano anasine rayarer, ti mo rauva nto pae rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 19 Koveamo apa anaamatane ama mangke mo atatuv maisyare ansuno mo akakipimbe wemaisy, 
\q2 maisyare tarandino rarajuto ateririje rai ti mo aokae tutire wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 20 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo mangke rapinde irati sya marova wo ayao kakai rantutibe rinaije so mai, 
\q2 onawamo vatano nanawirati wo mamune ratoraje rinai nao. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 Yara sya AMISY, Winyirati sya Akoe pi Winy, 
\q2 syare Nyo sopambe rinai indamu Nya tame raijaseo titive, 
\q1 muno Nyo inapaya irati inansuimbe so rai, 
\q2 weye Nya muinyo no tawane ngkov dave. 
\q1  
\v 22 Weye risyamo vatano siuri muno sya ana jajewembe rinai, 
\q2 muno inanuga so njoram dave. 
\q1  
\v 23 Risyamo kavintare inaumandi kobe maisyare arono uma pasyo ti sya ugara aumandi kobe wemaisy. 
\q2 Muno risyamo maisyare kao insumai no no nyovara wao rai, ovare po amawisy ti saonto wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 24 Inatawandi marore rai indamu risambayambe, weti umba sya vukane ntutar, 
\q2 muno inanasine ndupan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 25 Vatano wo rinaene wo inaura tantunawi, 
\q2 umba makari rangkikive rinai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 26 AMISY, Winyirati sya Amisy, syare naemeno rinai, 
\q2 Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai mamaisyo Nya muinyo no tawane rai. 
\q1  
\v 27 Indamu sya marova wo raen ware tugae, AMISY Winyirati Nyo inapaya kakai rai to. 
\q2 Winya nanemo vambunine omirati mo inapaya kakai umaso rai. 
\q1  
\v 28 Maisyeamo wanaamatambe rinai kai, weramu kove mi ndaugaje rinai, 
\q2 ware umarovave rinai kai, weramu Nyo mapinde ti usamane, 
\q2 yara Nya vatano syanapatambe Nai risyamo inanayanambe. 
\q1  
\v 29 Syare koveamo vatano wo ayao kakai rantuna rinai nawamo usamane, 
\q2 muno usamane dave maisyare ansuno manawadi inta mo matatuve wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 30 Syare syo kove raura seo manakoe irati AMISY Ai, 
\q2 muno syo ararimbe no anugane ama yasyin no Yavar Amisy. 
\q1  
\v 31 Weye Opirati Po marimbe vatano mayondi mai,\f + \fr 109:31 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Opamo tet no vatano mayondi manem ngkove rai,’’ ama ine mare Amisye no mautan muno Po marimbe mai.\f* 
\q2 indamu Po mapaya irati vatano ware wo mangke maubaisye raugaje maije mai. 
\c 110  
\s1 Amisye Po kove raugaje akarijo titi Israel ai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY Po raura nanto sya Akarijo Titi ai pare: 
\q2 ‘‘Nyaje ntuna no inanem ngkove rai java 
\q1 Syo nya marova maveaje utantuna no najo ate rai 
\q2 indamu wimbe akarive mai.’’\f + \fr 110:1 \ft Mat. 22:44; Mrk. 12:36; Luk. 20:42-43; Arakov. 2:34-35; Ibr. 1:13\f* 
\q1  
\v 2 Nai munijo Sion, AMISY Po nya vambunino mbe akarive raneka ti nyo munijo kai raijanande tenambe, 
\q2 syare wimbe akarive irati nya marova mai tenambe! 
\q1  
\v 3 Masyoto arono winde irati nya vambunino mbe akarive rautan, 
\q2 no unato ndandinit, 
\q2 weamo nya kawasae nawamo umayar ti ubesea ude. 
\q1 Maisyare aakop arono awatan ngkove wemaisy, 
\q2 winde irati nya vambunino kamurame rautan.\f + \fr 110:3 \ft Aneme somamo ayao Ibrani ama ayao muno ama ine mbare ramu.\f* 
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY purairive to, muno Apa urairi mamo Po ranigwane ramu, yara teto rai tawan, 
\q2 pare: ‘‘Winyirati nawaino syene raija ntoa nuge nuganui, maisyare Melkisedek\f + \fr 110:4 \ft Kej. 14:17-20\f* amaisy.’’\f + \fr 110:4 \ft Ibr. 5:6, 6:20, 7:17,21\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY Opirati te no nanem ngkove rai, 
\q2 arono masyoto Apa parijo mangke nde, weamo Po akarijo titi makupi vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 6 Po mangke raude susye kotaro wanave Ai jewene mai, 
\q2 weti ugwenen muno awa koke mamo randaraive ti ntuna, 
\q2 muno vatano akokoe mine so nawamo Po makupi vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 7 Yara akarijo titi pamo po mana ramanam no mana njam no unanuije tuga rai, 
\q2 weti bambunin akato muno po anasineko. 
\c 111  
\s1 AMISY Apa bekobe 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 \f + \fr 111:1 \ft Masmur so omamo ransyerano Ibrani \ft \+it akrostik\+it* inta mije, weye ntavondi urupijo Ibrani ama ntetebeaje rai. Weramu ayao Yawa ntavondi urupije so rai jewen. \f*Syare syo kove raura seo AMISY aijo inanuga ntenami rai no anugane rai, 
\q2 no vatano utavondi Apa bekere rai awa yasyin. 
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY Apa ana dave makokoive, 
\q2 omamo vatano manuga no rai nawamo wo ratantona mavabe tutir. 
\q1  
\v 3 Apa ana dave ama kovo ntiti no rai muno mamaisyo raura titive, 
\q2 muno Apa moyare mamo no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 4 Apa ana dave mbe anainambe ma pare indamu 
\q2 mansanimari rai nora yara mansaemendi rai. 
\q2 AMISY Opamo muiny dave muno aemeno mai rave. 
\q1  
\v 5 Anaisye omamo Po raunande vatano wo asyanive mansai, 
\q2 muno Amisy Opamo aemendi tutir irati Apa urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Apa vambunine mamo raen no Apa ana dave rai, 
\q2 namirati Po rarorono Apa kawasae Israel mai, 
\q2 omamo Po susye kotar awa kopa raunande Apa kawasae umaso mai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Apa ana daijaro aneme rai mamo mamai dave muno moyar. 
\q2 Muno Apa ananyao mamo ntindimu ti anave rai, 
\q1  
\v 8 ntindimu tutir muno no pitawabe, 
\q2 Amisy Po raugaje mamaisyo Apa moyare muno Apa mamaisye rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wepi Po apa kawasae Israel mapaya aroo rai to, 
\q2 muno purairive maijo Apa ura mai tawan. 
\q2 Wepirati Amisyo dandinit muno bambunin! 
\q1  
\v 10 Arepi beker peyave ana ratantona ntiti rai 
\q2 weamo po AMISY asyani dati, 
\q1 Vatano ubeta Apa ananyao rai wenawamo awa ana wo ratantona ngkov. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe mamo ntoa nuge nuganui! 
\c 112  
\s1 Kove ngkov irati vatano ubeta AMISY Aije mai 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 \f + \fr 112:1 \ft Masmur so omamo ransyerano Ibrani \ft \+it akrostik\+it* inta mije, weye ntavondi urupijo Ibrani ama ntetebeaje rai. Weramu ayao Yawa ntavondi urupije so rai jewen. \f*Kove ngkov irati vatano are pirati po AMISY asyanive ai, 
\q2 napirati anayanambe beto ananyao AMISY rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Apa arikainye nanawamo indati ube akarive no munije so;\f + \fr 112:2 \fq munije so \ft ama ine mare munijo Israel.\f* 
\q2 muno susyo vatano utavondi Amisy Ai nanawamo indati Po kove raugaje mai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Apa yavaruga mamo indati romane muno ananuge ntairi rai, 
\q2 muno opamo beto ananyao Amisye obo rai tawan tutir. 
\q1  
\v 4 Opamo be unanuive vatano kaijo utavondi Amisye Ai mai, 
\q2 maisyare yawainyo mbaro unanui ngkaumudi rai wemaisy. 
\q2 Opamo muiny dave, aemeno vatano kaije mai, muno moyar. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kove ngkov irati vatano are pirati bekobe ti po apa ananuge rapapaya vayave irati vatano wo ranajo mai, 
\q2 opamo anakere kotaro po raijare mamo po raijaro anuga moyare obo rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weye vatano beto Amisye Ai opamo teto tindimuve tawan tutira ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 weti vatano kaijinta mansaemendi ai tutira nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 7 Ayao ngkove jewen nde ai mamo po rasyanive ramu, 
\q2 anuga mamo mbambunin weye panave tugaive AMISY Ai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Opamo anuga ntindimu, muno janive ramu, 
\q2 weye po raen indati AMISY Wepi Po apa marova mapinde. 
\q1  
\v 9 Po apa romane raunanto manakoeve irati vatano awa ana jajewembe mai, 
\q2 muno opamo beto ananyao Amisye obo rai tawan tutir. 
\q2 Weti opamo vambunine raugasyo ai\f + \fr 112:9 \fq vambunine: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘korodowai raijaseo,’’ mbe rarorombe vambunine rai.\f* muno vatane wo apa tame raijaseo titive. 
\q1  
\v 10 Vatano mamune wo anakotaro ngkov nde ai raen, umba manuga ntatupami ai; 
\q2 upari ai ti matomokane ntitiki ai. 
\q1 Weramu umaso nao ugwenen ti mewen, 
\q2 muno awa ubekero wo ratantona mamo raumandita vintabo. 
\c 113  
\s1 AMISY ararimbe weye Po wasaijasea 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 Inya, vatano wapanapatambe AMISY Ai weap, 
\q2 Weapo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Syare AMISY Apa tame rararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 2 Unumeso muno ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 syare AMISY Apa tame rararimbe tutir! 
\q1  
\v 3 Nai munijo rani muram uma seo ri 
\q2 nto nanto no munijo varet uma pasyo rije rai, 
\q2 no rui rui vayave tamo AMISY wemi rararin. 
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY opamo akari titi no vombe irati susye kotaro mine so mai, 
\q2 Apa kovo ntiti mo naume rapapayaje vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 5 Are pirati indati po wama AMISY amaisy? 
\q2 Opamo tuna no kursijo titi rai no munijo ntiti. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weramu beakaje rave ti 
\q2 Po nugo naume muno mine so raen kava. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wepi Po vatano ananuge meweno ai aijaseo no anaingkainyo kindua\f + \fr 113:7 \ft Kindua omamo anaingkainyo wanijate vatane wo raisyaniv.\f* ama uga rai, 
\q2 muno vatano mamanaive ai jewene, aijaseo no apa mayondi rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Indamu aijaseo tuna akarijo wo nuge raijanande matavon tenambe, 
\q2 weti apa tame ngkovo akari matavon no kawasae Amisye Apa ura maije mansamun. 
\q1  
\v 9 Amisye wepi Po akoeyo nte bayave raijaseo no ama yavaruga, 
\q2 weti ama arikainye inta mansaen no rai, 
\q2 wemirati akoeyo ranuga ntairi anayanambe rautan\f + \fr 113:9 \ft 1Sam. 2:1-10\f*. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 114  
\s1 Amisy Po anainame raroron 
\q1  
\v 1 Arono kawasae Israel wuje no munijo Mesir, 
\q2 arono Yakop apa ajavi wo munijo maran rapaya ntami, 
\q1  
\v 2 kopa Yehuda Amisy Po varoro we ratayao terave indamu ndandinit Wepi tuna rai, 
\q2 munijo Israel ratayao terave indamu Wepi be akari titive rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Mayano Kolsum\f + \fr 114:3 \ft Mayano Kolsum ama tamo kaijinta mamo: ‘‘Mayano Nijam,’’ ‘‘Gelaga’’ muno ‘‘Teberau.’’ Raen tavon no Kel. 14:21; Arakov. 7:36; 1Kor. 10:1; Maz. 136:13.\f* mo Amisy aen weti mansop, 
\q2 mana akoe Yordan njame nto kakai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Unate mainy nsasopati maisyare kambine we, 
\q2 papukame mpapiraki maisyare domba tuvan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Inya, mayano Kolsum, animaisye mi mbeti winyansop, 
\q2 muno mana akoe Yordan njame nto kakai? 
\q1  
\v 6 Inya, unate mainy, veanimaibe weasasopati maisyare kambine we, 
\q2 muno inya, papukame weap, wapapiraki maisyare domba tuvano we? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Inya, munije tenam, ntutar no Akoe Amun, 
\q2 nai Amisy Yakop beaje Ai Amun. 
\q1  
\v 8 Wepi Po unato oram ranigwan weti mbe mana warove, 
\q2 muno oramo mantantuman ranigwan mbe mana wun.\f + \fr 114:8 \ft Kel. 17:1-7; Bil. 20:1-13\f* 
\c 115  
\s1 AMISY Wepi bambunin dave ti kangkamambe Ai 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY, reama tame mamo mamaisyo raijaseo titive jewen, 
\q2 yara Winya tame omirati mamaisyo raijaseo titive, 
\q2 weye Winya muinye no tawan\f + \fr 115:1 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it hesed\+it* ama ine mare: ‘‘Amisye Apa muinyo Po raurairive no tawano Apa kawasae mai indati Po raveti mamaisy.’’\f* muno winteto Nya urairije rai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 2 Veanimaibe susye kotare wo reansaura ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Weapamo wapa Amisye noa e?’’ 
\q1  
\v 3 Wama Amisye opamo no ivae, no no Manunggara, 
\q2 muno anakotar tenambe beker pare Po rave, omamo Po rave kobe ti mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Yara awa yare omainyamo wo emasije muno peraki veano ranari, 
\q2 muno taune wo ranarijo mansaneme rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Awa yare mamo mawa no mai, weramu wayaove kakai, 
\q2 mamije no mai, weramu wo nuge raene jewen. 
\q1  
\v 6 Mamarikoame no mai, weramu wo ana ranaune ramu, 
\q2 muno mansatume no mai, weramu wo ana ranu jewen. 
\q1  
\v 7 Maneme no mai, weramu ana raijare omamo wo ranaune jewen, 
\q2 muno majoe no mai, weramu taune wanya kakai, 
\q2 muno mansanamote inta ngkin no awa isyisye jewen tavon. 
\q1  
\v 8 Vatano wo yare ranari muno vatano wanave rai, 
\q2 wenawamo indati awa vambunine meweno mai maisyare awa yare ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 Inya, Israel, wapanaveo AMISY Ai! 
\q2 Wepi Po wasayaranande Apa vambunine rai muno darino wasaora 
\q2 maisyare naite apa vakano po raijaro aora ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 10 Inya, syeno Harun apa susye weap, wapanaveo AMISY Ai! 
\q2 Wepi Po wasayaranande Apa vambunine rai muno darino wasaora 
\q2 maisyare naite apa vakano po raijaro aora ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 11 Inya, vatan tenambe wapo AMISY asyanive weap, wapanaveo Ai! 
\q2 Wepi Po wasayaranande Apa vambunine rai muno darino wasaora 
\q2 maisyare naite apa vakano po raijaro aora ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 12 AMISY Opirati aemeno wansai, muno indati Po kove raugaje wansai: 
\q2 Opirati indati Po kove raugaje kawasae Israel wansai, 
\q2 Opirati indati Po kove raugaje syeno Harun apa susye mansai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 13 AMISY indati Po kove raugaje vatano wo asyanive mansai, 
\q2 umba vatano awa tame ntiti mansai muno awa tame ntiti jewene mansai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 14 Syare AMISY Po kovo manakoe raugaje wasai, 
\q2 muno nde irati wapa susyo wadampame mai. 
\q1  
\v 15 Syare AMISY Po kove raugaje wasai, 
\q2 Opirati Po naume muno mine so ranarijo ama anakotare rautan tenambe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 Naume omamo AMISY apave rai, 
\q2 yara munije so, wemi Po raugaje vatane wansai. 
\q1  
\v 17 Vatano ugwenene wenawirati wo AMISY ararimbea jewen, 
\q2 vatano nanawirati wasya no aipapo rai nawamo anamainitu mai vayave. 
\q1  
\v 18 Yara wamirati ta wangkov, wamirati wangkangkamambe Ai tutir, 
\q2 unumeso muno ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 116  
\s1 AMISY Po inapaya irati vambunino wene rai 
\q1  
\v 1 Rinanuga no AMISY Ai, weye Po inanamote ranaun, 
\q2 muno Po sya ana idawainto Ai raraniv. 
\q1  
\v 2 Weye amarikoame rasakinav de sya ana danajo Ai rai, 
\q2 weti arono ta rikove soamo Opirati syo awain. 
\q1  
\v 3 Waijo wene mo inapapakai to, 
\q2 wen akoe maisyare aviri mo inaman ti rijanivo rikakaiji, 
\q2 mo rinaveti rinanuga so nseo majeve muno rinanimaumbe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Umba syo AMISY Apa tame rawain, syare: 
\q2 ‘‘Sya Amisy, syare Nyo inapaya irati kakai so rai!’’ 
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY Opamo muiny dave muno moyar, 
\q2 wama Amisye Opamo aemeno wansai rave. 
\q1  
\v 6 Vatano wananepabe nawamo AMISY Po mansayaranande; 
\q2 risyamo mayondi rave to, weramu Po inapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Koveamo rinanuga so ntanamanin akato, 
\q2 weye AMISY bekobe rinai to. 
\q1  
\v 8 Tugae, Po rinapaya wene rai to, 
\q2 muno risyoyove mamo Po ransopi, 
\q2 muno Po rinapaya ra vatane wo rinapinde jewen. 
\q1  
\v 9 Weti indati syanya syararai tutir irati AMISY Ai, 
\q2 no arono ta rikov no mine vone so. 
\q1  
\v 10 Syo raura kai, syare: ‘‘Risyamo siuri mo rinatawanto rave, 
\q2 weramu syanave no tawano Amisye Ai.’’\f + \fr 116:10 \ft Ayao so ratoe akato no 2Kor. 4:13.\f* 
\q1  
\v 11 Arono rijaniv, syo raura syare: 
\q2 ‘‘Vatan tenambe nawamo aarurijate nawa.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 AMISY Opamo bekobe rinai rave to, 
\q2 weti syo Apa kove rasakinav tai rui? 
\q1  
\v 13 Indati syo kapi ntairi angguri rai raugavere AMISY Ai, syo kove raura seo Ai, 
\q2 syo Apa tame rararimbe weye Po inapaya irati kakai rai to. 
\q1  
\v 14 Syo sya urairijo ridaokae nande AMISY Ai raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 no Apa kawasae mansamun tenambe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 AMISY animaumbe rave 
\q2 arono vatano anuga no aije inta kakai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Sya AMISY, risyamo Nya vatano syanapatambe Nai, 
\q2 maisyare sya ingkoa manapatambe Nai wemaisy, ritavon syanapatambe Nai, 
\q2 Winyi Nyo rinapaya vambunino wene rai to. 
\q1  
\v 17 Syare syo maere raugav syo rameseo Nai, indamu syo kove raura, 
\q2 muno syo AMISY Nya tame rararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 18 Syo sya urairijo ridaokae nande AMISY Nai raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 no Nya kawasae mansamun tenambe, 
\q1  
\v 19 no AMISY Nya Yavare ama wanijate, no munijo Yerusalem ama yasyin. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 117  
\s1 Kangkamambe AMISY Ai 
\q1  
\v 1 Inya, vatane kotar mine weap, AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Inya, susye kotar, wapo aijasea titive! 
\q1  
\v 2 Weye muiny AMISY manakoe nde wansai, 
\q2 muno teto Apa urairi rai ma no tawan ao nuge nuganui. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 118  
\s1 Kangkamambe Amisye Ai, weye Po anasineko raunande wansai no marova rai\f + \fr 118:1 \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy wo ratantona ware Masmur somamo akari titi Israel inta apa ayao po kove raura seo Amisye Ai ma, weye Amisye Po anasineko raunande kawasae Israel mai no marova rai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 1 Kove raura AMISY Ai, weye Opamo ko dave! 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan\f + \fr 118:1 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it hesed\+it* ama ine ratoe tumaimbe naiso mare: ‘‘muinye no tawan.’’ Ama ino manakoe mare: ‘‘Amisye Apa muinye muno Apa anakotaro Po raurairive ti no tawan tutiro Apa kawasae Israel mansai mamo Po raveti mamaisy.’’\f* ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 2 Koveamo vatano Israel wapo raura wapare: 
\q2 ‘‘Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui.’’ 
\q1  
\v 3 Koveamo syeno susyo Harun\f + \fr 118:3 \ft Susyo Harun onawirati susyo Amisye Po matayao terave indamu ube syembe muno wanapatambe Ai. \f* wapo raura wapare: 
\q2 ‘‘Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui.’’ 
\q1  
\v 4 Koveamo vatano wapo AMISY asyanive wapo raura wapare: 
\q2 ‘‘Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui.’’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 \f + \fr 118:5 \ft No anemo 5-21 omamo akari titi Israel po taune obo aura tutir, weramu tugae mamo apa ayao ama ine mo vatano Israel maura tenambe.\f*Arono rino irati ana nsosobe ama uga rai, syo AMISY anonae, 
\q2 umba Po sya ana danajo raveti mamaisy, ti Po inapaya irati ana nsosobe rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY Po marimbe rinai, weti rijanive ramu, 
\q2 vatano arepi indati po ana ngkakai inta raveti nande rinai jakato?\f + \fr 118:6 \ft Anemo so ratoe akato no Ibr. 13:6.\f* 
\q1  
\v 7 AMISY Po marimbe rinai, Po sopambe rinai, 
\q2 sya marova nawamo inami ntami maijo Po mataoponi. 
\q1  
\v 8 Koveamo nggaugambe AMISY Ai, 
\q2 wemi ngkov akato irati nanaveano vatane mansamene rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Koveamo nggaugambe AMISY Ai, 
\q2 wemi ngkov akato irati nanaveano vatano akokoe mine so mansamene rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Susyo wantatukambe Amisye Ai wo rinawariki wanui rave, 
\q2 weramu tugae, tamo AMISY obom risyo mapinde. 
\q1  
\v 11 Wo inakijaniri tenambe ti maroyaro rinai, 
\q2 weramu tugae, tamo AMISY obom risyo mapinde. 
\q1  
\v 12 Maroyaro rinai maisyare anyivane inta mangkato rinai, 
\q2 weramu kavuratawe Po mao bintabo maisyare taname inta mansanano insumai kanene rai ti mewen to wemaisy. 
\q2 Tugae, tamo AMISY obom risyo mapinde. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Maroyaro rinai mangkebe ti kavintare wo rinapinde kobe, 
\q2 weramu AMISY Po sopambe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 14 AMISY Opirati sya vambunine nsawa Ai Pije, muno rikiny syo ararimbe Pije, 
\q2 Wepi Po rinapaya irati marova mai to. 
\q1  
\v 15 Amisye Apa kawasae umananibe muno ukinyo ransyerano anasineko rai no awa randumo una ri raito anyi, ware: 
\q2 ‘‘AMISY Apa vambunine mi mo ana makokoive so rave wansai! 
\q1  
\v 16 Anemo vambunine mi mo anasineko raunande wansai, 
\q2 AMISY Apa vambunine mi mo ana makokoive so rave wansai!’’ 
\q1  
\v 17 Risyamo indati rikakai jewen, yara rikov tutir, 
\q2 indati syo AMISY Apa ana dave ravovo. 
\q1  
\v 18 AMISY Po inanepati mangkebe, 
\q2 weramu Po inaugavo wene raronto ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Syare unsanda akoe sisa no Yavar Amisy rausiso rinai, 
\q2 indamu risiso no ama uga, 
\q2 muno syo kove raura seo AMISY Ai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Unsanda akoe umaso mirati vatane wo raisisa indamu ubeaje AMISY Ai, 
\q2 vatano ubeta Ai obo nawirati mamaisyo wo raisisa. 
\q1  
\v 21 Syo kove raura seo Winai, weye Winyo sya ana danajo raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 muno Winyi Nyo rinapaya irati marova mai to. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 22 Oramo vatano wo yavare ranari wonayo rai, ti wo ramauta vayave, 
\q2 omirati oramo manasyin dave Amisye Po ratayao indamu yavare rauseo nteto rai, mo raijar matuve.\f + \fr 118:22 \ft Arono Masmur so ratoeyamo, vatano Israel wo ratantona ware orame so mbe rarorombe taune awa munijo Israel rai, weye omirati munijo kaijinta wonayo rai, weramu Amisye Po ratayao indamu Apa ura rai muno Po kove raugaje rai. Muno orame so mbe rarorombe Yesus Ai tavon. Opamo vatano wanui wonayo Ai, weramu Opirati Mesias Amisye Po atayao indamu Po wansapaya kakai rai. Aneme so ratoe akato no Luk. 20:17; Arakov. 4:11; 1Ptr. 2:7\f* 
\q1  
\v 23 Ana somamo AMISY Apa ana dave ma, 
\q2 tugae, wamo raenamo nsinam dave.\f + \fr 118:22-23 \ft Ayao so ratoe akato no Mat. 21:42 muno Mrk. 12:10-11.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 24 Masyote so mirati AMISY Po rapatimu wansai,\f + \fr 118:24 \ft Amisy Po masyote umaso rapatimu vatano Israel mai indamu umananibe rai, weye mansaemendi irati arono Amisy Po awa marova mapinde no marova rai. \f* 
\q2 ti waderamu wansananibe muno wansanayanambe masyoto unumeso rai! 
\q1  
\v 25 Reama AMISY, reambeke dave reamare Nyo reansapaya irati kakai rai! 
\q2 AMISY, reambeke dave reamare Nyo anasineko raude reansai! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 26 Kove ngkov irati Napi de tamo Amisye rautane Ai!\f + \fr 118:26 \ft Ayao so ratoe akato no Mat. 21:9, 23:39; Mrk. 11:9; Luk. 13:35, 19:38; Yoh. 12:13.\f* 
\q2 Nai Yavaro Amisye ama uga so, reamo AMISY anajo indamu Po kove raugaje wasai! 
\q1  
\v 27 AMISY Opirati wama Amisye Pije, 
\q2 Opamo Po kove raugaje wansai to, maisyare vare mbaro wansai wemaisy. 
\q1 Wade! Wapo kaipe wao raijaro wasaneme rai, indamu wambovambe, 
\q2 tewa oram anakotare rameseo Amisye Ai rakijani. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 28 Winyirati sya Amisy, syare syo kove raura seo Nai, 
\q2 sya Amisy, Winyirati syo nabumbundi. 
\q1  
\v 29 Kove raura AMISY Ai, weye Opamo ko dave! 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 119  
\s1 Kove ngkov irati vatano ubeta ananyao AMISY rai mai 
\q1  
\v 1 Kove ngkov irati vatano are nawirati ugwambe ayao kakai rai jewene mai, 
\q2 muno ubeto irati anaparatot AMISY rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Kove ngkov irati vatano are nawirati usayae matuve Apa ananyao rai mai, 
\q2 muno manuga ntenami wo AMISY akani. 
\q1  
\v 3 Kove ngkov irati vatano utavon irati AMISY Apa unanui rai mai, 
\q2 muno wo ana ngkakai rave jewen. 
\q1  
\v 4 AMISY, Winyirati Nyo Nya anaparatote raugaje reansai, 
\q2 indamu reambeto rai tugaeve. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ribeker syare ritindimu sya ana dave rai, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya anaparatote raijaro matuve. 
\q1  
\v 6 Ranivara ribeto mavabe Nya ananyao rai, 
\q2 weamo risya samane intai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 7 Ranivara syo Nya patimu moyare ranyao, 
\q2 wea umba syo kove raura seo Naijo inanuga nsarokire rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare indati riteto matuve Nya anaparatote rai, 
\q2 weti vemo winaneme mpaya rinaijo intai jinya. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Arikainy kamurame inta be tai ruimaisy, indamu vemo gwambe no AMISY Amune rai nora? 
\q2 Weamo po apa ana dave rayaranande mamaisyo Nya ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Inanuga ntenami syo winakani, 
\q2 weti vemo Nyo inapayamo syusyo marambe Nya ananyao rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 11 Nya ayao mamo syo raugasyo ntonamo inanuga so rai, 
\q2 indamu vemo syo ayao kakaije rave no winamune rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 12 Sya AMISY, syo winararimbe, 
\q2 Syare Nyo inanyao irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 13 Nya anaparatoto ndaunande mamo, 
\q2 syo raura tetebe inawa so rai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Inanayanambe ibeto irati Nya ananyao rai, 
\q2 maisyare vatano tuna ananuge vone rai ti anayanambe rave wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 15 Syare syo Nya anaparatote ratantona tutir, 
\q2 muno inami ntamijo Nya unanui ngkove rai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Nya anaparatote mo anayanambe raugavo rinai, 
\q2 weti Nya ayao mamo rinanimari raije ramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, syare wimbekobe rinai, 
\q2 indamu rijayaisy tutir muno ibeto Nya ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Syare Nyo inami raneka indamu syo ana raen, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya ananyao mbe anaanibe raen no Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 19 Risyamo rino no mine vone so maisyare vatano maran ta de inta amaisy, 
\q2 weti syare Nyo Nya ananyao rarorono rinai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Inanuga so ntove rave, 
\q2 ntove rave Nya ayao mamaisye rai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Nyo vatano mararine mansanenen, 
\q2 muno Nyo kakai ratande vatano wusya akirive Nya ananyao raije mai. 
\q1  
\v 22 Syare Nyo inapaya irati awa ana wo rinaura tantunawi muno wo inakaajiane rai, 
\q2 weye risyamo beto Nya ananyao rai. 
\q1  
\v 23 Akari mamune wanyinyaube kai ware umarovave rinai, 
\q2 weramu Nya anaparatote obo mirati syo ratantona no inanuga, weye risyamo syanapatambe irati Nai. 
\q1  
\v 24 Nya ananyao obo mirati mo anayanambe raugavo inanuga rai, 
\q2 muno mo rinanyao ana ratantona ngkove rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 25 Risyamo kavintare wene mo rinaugav, 
\q2 weti syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugav akare rinai mamaisyo Nya ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 26 Sya ana dave mamo syo raura kakavimbe Nai, umba Nyo ayaowe rasakinavo rinai. 
\q2 Syare Nyo rinanyao Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 27 Syare Nyo inaveramu inanto irati Nya anaparatote rai, 
\q2 weamo syo Nya ana ndave mbe anaanibe ratantona tutir. 
\q1  
\v 28 Inanuga mpatimu rave weye inanimaumbe ntapekano rinai, 
\q2 weti syare Nyo vambunine raugaje rinai mamaisyo Nya ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 29 Syare Nyo aarurijate raveto marambe irati inawa so rai, 
\q2 muno wimbekobe rinai, Nyo rinanyao Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 30 Syo rapatimu to indamu ibeto Winai, 
\q2 muno Nya anaparatote mamo inaemendi rai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 31 Sya AMISY, syo Nya ananyao raijaro matuve indamu ritavondi rai, 
\q2 weti vemo winaneme mpaya rinai mo risamane inya. 
\q1  
\v 32 Sya AMISY, rinamune mayar dave ritavondi irati Nya ananyao rai, 
\q2 weye Winyo inanuga so raneka ti rinanto irati rai tugaeve. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 33 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo rinanyao indamu ritavondi Nya anaparatote rai tugaeve, 
\q2 indamu syo raijaro matuvea ntoa rikakai. 
\q1  
\v 34 Syare Nyo inaveramu inanto irati Nya anaparatote rai, indamu syo raijaro matuve, 
\q2 muno ribeto rai inanuga ntenami rautan. 
\q1  
\v 35 Syare Nyo sya unanui anya no mine vone so raugav mamaisyo Nya ananyao rai, 
\q2 weye omirati rinanayanambe rai. 
\q1  
\v 36 Syare Nyo inanuga so raveramu mbekero Nya ananyao obo rai, 
\q2 mo taune sya bekero ananugo mine so rai rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 37 Syare Nyo inansopi indamu vemo syo anakotaro ama ine mewen dai rakani inya, 
\q2 yara syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugakare rinai mamaisyo Nya ayao obo rai. 
\q1  
\v 38 Risyamo syanapatambe Winai, weti syare Nyo Nya urairi raveramu mamaisyo rinai, 
\q2 namirati Nyo raunanto irati vatano wo nasyanive mai wem. 
\q1  
\v 39 Sya marova wo inaura tantunawi ti rijaniv, weti syare Nyo raveto marambe, 
\q2 weye Nya anaparatote mirati ngkov. 
\q1  
\v 40 Syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugakare rinai mamaisyo Nya moyare rai, 
\q2 weye ribeker ibeto irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 41 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo Nya muinyo no tawane rarorono rinai, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinapaya kakai rai mamaisyo Nya urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 42 Wirati indamu syo ayao rasakinavo vatano wo inaura tantunawi mai, 
\q2 weye syanave irati Nya ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 43 Nya ayao tugae mamo vemo Nyo rapaya inawa so rai nora, 
\q2 weye risyamo inanaveano Nya patimu moyare ramen. 
\q1  
\v 44 Nya anaparatote mamo syare syo raijar tutir 
\q2 ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 45 Weti sya marova wo rinansosobe akato ramu, 
\q2 weye ribekero itavondi irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 46 Risyamo indati risamane intai ramu 
\q2 arono syo Nya ananyao ravovo akari titi mai. 
\q1  
\v 47 Weye Nya ananyao wemirati inanuga no rai, 
\q2 weti rinananibe ibeto rai. 
\q1  
\v 48 Nya ananyao mamo syo raura titive muno inanuga no rai rave, 
\q2 muno Nya anaparatote mamo syo ratantonave tutir. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 49 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, syare naemeno Nya ayao Nyo raura rinai to rai, 
\q2 namirati Nyo raurairive ti inanaveano ramene wem. 
\q1  
\v 50 Nya urairi mo inayove no sya siuri ama uga rai, 
\q2 weye tugae, wemirati mo kovo wanyine raugavo rinai. 
\q1  
\v 51 Vatano umararine wo rinaura tantunawi, 
\q2 weramu risyamo rinakirive Nya anaparatote rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 52 Sya AMISY, rinaemendi tutir irati Nya anaparatoto ntami no wusyin to rai, 
\q2 weamo mo inanuga so rayove. 
\q1  
\v 53 Ripari mangkebe irati vatano mamune mai, 
\q2 weye wenawamo wo Nya anaparatote ravakambe. 
\q1  
\v 54 Rino no rui rui vayave no mine so, 
\q2 Nya anaparatote wemirati sya ransyerano kangkamane mije. 
\q1  
\v 55 Arono namane yasyin syo AMISY winatantonave, 
\q2 weti syo Nya anaparatote raijaro matuve. 
\q1  
\v 56 Ribeto Nya anaparatote rai tutir, 
\q2 weti Nyo kove raugaje rinai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 57 Sya AMISY, Wibuiny irati ribekero Nai, 
\q2 syurairive syare ibeto Nya ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 58 Nde irati inanuga ntenami rautan, syo Amisy Nya mbekobe ranajo, 
\q2 syare naemeno rinai, mamaisyo Nya urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 59 Arono syo sya ana dave ratantonave, 
\q2 syo patimu rave syakare irati Nya ananyao rai. 
\q1  
\v 60 Rimaneai akatoe ramu yara risyavave 
\q2 inda ibeto irati Nya ananyao rai. 
\q1  
\v 61 Vatano mamune wo avirije ratugar mo inaman, 
\q2 weramu risyamo inanimarijo Nya anaparatote rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 62 Namane yasyin riseo syo kove raura ore Amisye Winai, 
\q2 weye Winya anaparatote mamo moyar. 
\q1  
\v 63 Risyamo imanivuvive irati vatan tenambe wo Amisy winasyanive matavon, 
\q2 muno ribe arakobe irati vatano ubeta irati Nya anaparatote raije matavon. 
\q1  
\v 64 Sya AMISY, mine tename so ntairi irati Nya muinyo no tawane rai, 
\q2 weti syare Nyo rinanyao irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 65 Sya AMISY, risyamo syanapatambe Nai, 
\q2 Nya kove mamo Nyo rarorono rinai to, 
\q2 mamaisyo Nya urairije rai. 
\q1  
\v 66 Syare Nyo rinanyao irati ana ratantona ngkove rai muno ana ratantona ntiti rai, 
\q2 weye risyamo syanave Nya ananyao rai. 
\q1  
\v 67 Arono risyanya akirive, weamo Amisy Nyo ana nsosobe raude irati rinai. 
\q2 Weramu soamo risyo Nya ananyao raijaro matuve akato to. 
\q1  
\v 68 Winyi ngko dave muno Nya ana ndave ngkov, 
\q2 syare Nyo rinanyao irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 69 Vatano umararine wo rinampami, 
\q2 weramu risyamo inanuga so ntenami ibeto irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 70 Onawamo manuga matu, weti wo ana ngkove, ngkakai raene ramu, 
\q2 yara risyamo inananibe ibeto irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 71 Mangke Amisye Winyo raude rinai mamo ngkovo rinai, 
\q2 indamu rinanto Nya anaparatote rai tugaeve. 
\q1  
\v 72 Nya anaparatoto Nyo raugaje mamo ngkovo rinai, 
\q2 mo emasi muno peraki ama manui nseo rave rakivan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 73 Winyirati Nyo inanarijo naneme rai, 
\q2 syare Nyo ana ratantona raugaje rinai indamu syo Nya ananyao ranyao mavabe. 
\q1  
\v 74 Vatano wo Amisy nasyanive manayanambe, 
\q2 weye wo rinaen risyamo inanaveano Winya ayao obo ramen. 
\q1  
\v 75 Tugae sya AMISY, arono syo ayao kakaije rave, syo raen mangkeo Nyo rapatimu mamo moyar, 
\q2 Nyo mangke raude rinai weye winteto Nya urairi rai.\f + \fr 119:75 \fq winteto Nya urairi rai: \ft Amisye teto Apa urairijo Po mangke raugaje vatano awa ana udave ngkakainoanive maije rai. Raen tavon no Ibr. 12:5-8.\f* 
\q1  
\v 76 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, 
\q1 koveamo Winya muinyo no tawane wemi mo inanuga so rayove, 
\q2 mamaisyo Nya urairijo ndaura nande rinai rai. 
\q1  
\v 77 Syare naemen irati rinai, indamu rijayaisy tutir, 
\q2 weye Nya anaparatote mo anayanambe raugavo inanuga so rai. 
\q1  
\v 78 Koveamo vatano umararine mavera usamane, 
\q2 weye wo aarurijate raker ti nande rinai, 
\q2 yara risyamo Nya anaparatote omirati syo ratantonave. 
\q1  
\v 79 Kovato vatano wo AMISY nasyanive ude no rinai, 
\q2 nanawirati unanta Nya ananyao rai nao. 
\q1  
\v 80 Syare Nyo inanuga so raveramu nsarokir ribeto Nya anaparatote rai, 
\q2 indamu vemo risamane inya. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 81 Rinanuga so mbeke dave syare AMISY Winyo rinapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q2 Risyamo inanaveano Nya ayao obo ramen. 
\q1  
\v 82 Syo nanyuto Nyo Nya urairi raveti mamaisye raija marudi, ti inami njoram to, 
\q2 weti syo raura syare: ‘‘Nandui rati umba Nyo rinayove?’’ 
\q1  
\v 83 Weye risyamo sya ana intai akatoe ramu, 
\q2 maisyare karoa ugamijo rata kijao rai ti ngkanena mpoopove wemaisy, 
\q2 weramu Nya anaparatote mamo rinanimari raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 84 AMISY, risyamo syanapatambe Nai, risyo winanyuta ntoa nanduija? 
\q2 Ntoa nanduija umba Winyo mangke raugaje irati vatano wo rinawatane mai? 
\q1  
\v 85 Vatano mararine wo ateme rawae ti mo inaman, 
\q2 nanawirati wonae ubeta Nya anaparatote rai nao. 
\q1  
\v 86 Nya ananyao mainy tenambe, omamo ntindimu ti anave rai. 
\q2 Syare naemeno rinai! Weye vatano angkarije ntapekano mai wo rinawatan bayave. 
\q1  
\v 87 Kavintare umba wo rinaubaisy bayave kobe, 
\q2 weramu risyamo syo Nya anaparatote rapaya ra ntami ramu. 
\q1  
\v 88 Syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugakare rinai mamaisyo Nya muinyo no tawane rai, 
\q2 indamu ribeto Nya ananyao ndaugaje rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 89 Sya AMISY, Nya ayao mamo ntindimu 
\q2 no munijo ntiti ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 90 Winyamo nteto Nya urairi rai tawano susyo miridi nto mai, 
\q2 Winyo muni so ranteto matuve ti no tawan. 
\q1  
\v 91 Anakotaro no ti nde somamo mamaisyo Nya patimuge rai, 
\q2 weti wemainyamo manapatambe Winai. 
\q1  
\v 92 Ranivara ibekero Nya anaparatote rai jewen datire, 
\q2 somaisyamo rikakai no sya siuri ama uga rai to. 
\q1  
\v 93 Nya anaparatote mamo inanimari rai jewen ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 weye wemi mbewar Winyo kovo wanyine raugav akare rinai. 
\q1  
\v 94 Winyi Nya ura rinai, weti syare Nyo inapaya kakai rai, 
\q2 weye Nya anaparatote mirati ibeto rai mavabe. 
\q1  
\v 95 Vatano mamune wo inaman indamu ware wo rinaubaisy, 
\q2 weramu Nya ananyao obo mirati syo ratantonave. 
\q1  
\v 96 Anakotaro ngkov dave no mine somamo inta no tawane ramu, 
\q2 yara Nya ananyao obo mirati no tawan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 97 Wakoe, inanuga no Nya anaparatote rai rave! 
\q2 Syo ratantona tutiro masyote anteter. 
\q1  
\v 98 Nya ananyao omirati no rinai tawan tutir, 
\q2 weti mo ana ratantona ntiti raunande rinai, mo sya marova awa ana udatantona rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 99 Sya ana datantona ngkov mo kuruno wo rinanyao awa rakivan, 
\q2 weye risyo Nya ananyao ratantonave tutir. 
\q1  
\v 100 Sya ana datantona mo vatano awa akoe matu to awa ana udatantona rakivan, 
\q2 weye syo Nya anaparatote raijaro matuve. 
\q1  
\v 101 Unanui ngkakainoanive mamo syonaeyo tavono raiji, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya ayao obo raijaro matuve. 
\q1  
\v 102 Winya anaparatote mamo idapaya ra ntami jewen, 
\q2 weye Winyirati Nyo rinanyao rai. 
\q1  
\v 103 Wakoe! Nya ananyao mamo manavan dave no rinaunane rai, 
\q2 ama manavane mo anyaune ama poke rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 104 Nya anaparatote wemirati mo rinanyao ti syo kove, kakai raen, 
\q2 weti ana raveti musyo marambe mamo syonaeyo rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 105 Amisy, Nya ayao mi mbe yawaimbe inawanto rije rai, 
\q2 muno mbar irati sya unanui rai. 
\q1  
\v 106 Nya anaparatote mamo moyar, 
\q2 weti syurairive patimuve, syare syo raijaro matuve. 
\q1  
\v 107 Sya AMISY, risiuri rave, 
\q2 syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugav akare rinai mamaisyo Nya urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 108 AMISY, syare winanayanambe sya kangkaman idaura ore so rai, 
\q2 omamo maisyare anakotaro rameseo Nai ramaisy, 
\q2 muno syare Nyo rinanyao irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 109 Risya kove somamo ito no wene ama usye rai to, weti kavintare kakai, 
\q2 weramu Nya anaparatote mamo inanimari raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 110 Vatano mamune wo avirije ratugar mo inaman, 
\q2 weramu risyamo susyo marambe Nya anaparatote rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 111 Nya ananyao wemirati romano sya ura raija ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 omirati mo anayanambe raugavere inanuga so rai. 
\q1  
\v 112 Inanuga so ama mbeke dave mamo ritavono Nya anaparatote rai, 
\q2 ntoa sya matam akarije rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 113 Vatano anuga mbe jirumbe pamo syonaeyo ai, 
\q2 yara Nya anaparatote obo mirati inanuga no rai. 
\q1  
\v 114 Winyirati rikokaibe no nanem ate rai indamu wino rinaora, 
\q2 maisyare naite apa vakane wemaisy, 
\q2 muno risyamo inanaveano Nya ayao obo ramen. 
\q1  
\v 115 Inya, vatano mamune weap, wata ramu wagwaravainyo rinai, 
\q2 indamu syo sya Amisye Apa ananyao obo raijaro matuve. 
\q1  
\v 116 Rinanaveano winamen, weti vemo naneme mpaya rinai mo risamane nora, 
\q2 yara Nyo sopambe rinai mamaisyo Nya urairi rai indamu rijayaisy tutir. 
\q1  
\v 117 Nyo sopambe rinai indamu ripaya irati marova aneme rai, 
\q2 weti Nya anaparatote mamo ibeke dai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 118 Vatano wusya akirive Nya anaparatote rai nawamo Nyo mavakano marambe, 
\q2 weye onawamo anapamponae umamaisye jewene naowa. 
\q1  
\v 119 Vatano mamun mine so nawamo Amisye Nyo mansaena maisyare anaingkainyo rauvata, 
\q2 omi mbewar risyamo inanuga no Nya ananyao obo rai. 
\q1  
\v 120 Risyamo syo Amisye winasyaniv weti inanakea uga nsayae, 
\q2 rinanuga so ntutar dave irati Nya mangke ndaugaje rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 121 Risyamo syo ana mamaisye muno moyare obo rave to, 
\q2 weti vemo Nyo rinaunanto vatano maneme nsoowate mai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 122 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, 
\q2 weti syare Nyo urairive rinai paep, nyare Winyi Nyo rinakum ti rikov, 
\q2 vemo winaneme mpaya rinai mo vatano mararine wo rinataka doyadi nora. 
\q1  
\v 123 Risyo winanyuto Nyo inapaya kakai rai raija marudi ti inami njoram to, 
\q2 risyo Nya urairijo ngkov dave ratunao Nyo ravera mamaisyo rinaiji. 
\q1  
\v 124 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, 
\q2 syare wimbekobe irati rinai mamaisyo Nya muinyo no tawane rai, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinanyao irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 125 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, 
\q2 syare Nyo sya ana datantona raneka 
\q2 indamu rinanto Nya ananyao rai, wirati syo raen tugaive. 
\q1  
\v 126 AMISY, masyote ndea mamai to, weti syare winseo Nyo mangke rapatimu! 
\q2 Weye vatane wo Nya anaparatote rakanyoandi. 
\q1  
\v 127 Risyamo inanuga nto Nya ananyao rai, 
\q2 mo rinanuga nto emasi rai rakivan, 
\q2 tugae, mo inanuga nto emasi kakui rai rakivan dave. 
\q1  
\v 128 Wemirati mbewar ritavondi Nya anaparatote rai inanuga nsarokire rai, 
\q2 muno ana raveti musyo marambe mamo syonaeyo rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 129 Nya ananyao mbe anaanibe rave, 
\q2 wemi mbewar ribeto rai mavabe. 
\q1  
\v 130 Nya ayao mamo ranivara ama ine raura kakavimbe, weamo mo vare raunande reansai, 
\q2 muno mo ana ratantona ngkove raugavo vatano wananepabe mai. 
\q1  
\v 131 Inawa so ntavaeya no muno inanawayo ntove, 
\q2 weye inanuga ntove rave Nya ananyao rai. 
\q1  
\v 132 Syare namumbe de rinai, muno naemeno rinai, 
\q2 maisyare wimbekobe vatano mansanuga no Winai maive wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 133 Syare Nyo rinaugavo sya unanui syanya rai, mamaisyo Nya urairi rai, 
\q2 vemo winaneme mpaya rinai mo ayao kakai mbe akarive rinai nora. 
\q1  
\v 134 Syare Nyo rinapaya irati vatano wo rinatawanto mai, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya anaparatote raijaro matuve. 
\q1  
\v 135 Risyamo syanapatambe Nai, syare Nya kove mbaro rinai, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinanyao irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 136 Inami ngkaru so njam maisyare mana we, 
\q2 weye vatane ubeto Nya anaparatote rai jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 137 Sya AMISY, Winyirati moyar, 
\q2 muno Nya ana ndapatimu mamo mamai dave. 
\q1  
\v 138 Nya ananyao Nyo raugaje omirati moyar, 
\q2 muno mamai dave ti anave rai. 
\q1  
\v 139 Sya pari mo rinantutup dave, 
\q2 weye sya marova manimari irati Nya ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 140 Nya urairi wemi ntindimu muno anave rai, 
\q2 weti risy, Nya vatano syanapatambe Nai, rinanuga no rai. 
\q1  
\v 141 Risyamo vatano sya tame maje muno vatane wo inaura tantunawi, 
\q2 weramu Nya anaparatote mamo inanimari rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 142 Winyamo moyar muno Nya moyare ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno Nya anaparatote omamo ayao tugae. 
\q1  
\v 143 Anakotaro nsosobe muno mangke mo inakikipi, 
\q2 weramu Nya ananyao wemi mo anayanambe raugavo inanuga so rai. 
\q1  
\v 144 Nya ananyao mamo moyar ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 syare Nyo inaveramu inanto rai indamu rijayaisy tutir. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 145 Sya AMISY, rinanuga ntenami syo winawain, 
\q2 syare Nyo sya ana danajo ravera mamaisyo rinai, 
\q2 weamo ibeto irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 146 Syo winawain syare Nyo rinapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya ananyao raijaro matuve. 
\q1  
\v 147 Ribeseo awatan ngkobe, syo winanonae indamu naemeno rinai, 
\q2 risyamo inanaveano Nya ayao obo ramen. 
\q1  
\v 148 Namane mamo riniki jewen, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya urairi ratantonave tutir. 
\q1  
\v 149 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo sya ana danajo ore so raraniv mamaisyo Nya muinyo no tawane rai, 
\q2 syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugakare rinai mamaisyo Nya patimu moyare rai. 
\q1  
\v 150 Vatano wo kakai ratantona rinai wo inawatana wararai jirati rinai to, 
\q2 onawamo ugwaravainyo Winai, ubeta Nya anaparatote rai jewen bayave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 151 Weramu sya AMISY, Winyamo nyararai jirati rinai rave, 
\q2 muno Nya ananyao mainyamo ayao tugae. 
\q1  
\v 152 Nya ananyao mainyamo Nyo raveti no tawana nuge nuganui, 
\q2 omamo syo raeno rai no arono wusyinoe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 153 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo sya siurije so raen muno Nyo rapaya rinai, 
\q2 weye risyamo inanimarijo Nya anaparatote rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 154 Sya Amisy, syare Nyo marimbe rinai muno Nyo inapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugakare rinai mamaisyo Nya urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 155 Vatano mamune nanawamo Nyo mapaya kakaije rai ramu, 
\q2 weye onawamo ubekero Nya anaparatote rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 156 Sya AMISY, winaemeno rinai mamo manakoe rave, 
\q2 syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugakare rinai mamaisyo Nya patimu moyare rai. 
\q1  
\v 157 Vatano umarovave rinai muno wo rinawatane wanui rave, 
\q2 weramu risyamo syusyo marambe Nya ananyao rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 158 Syo vatano ubeta Amisye Winai jakato jewene mansaenamo inanuga mamuno mansai rave, 
\q2 weye onawamo utavono Nya ananyao rai jakato ramu. 
\q1  
\v 159 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo rinaen, risyamo inanuga no Nya anaparatote rai rave, 
\q2 syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugakare rinai mamaisyo Nya muinyo no tawane rai. 
\q1  
\v 160 Nya ayao mainy tenambe omamo tugae, 
\q2 muno Nya ana ndapatimu moyare mamo no tawana ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 161 Akari akokoe wo rinawatan bayave ayao mamaisye jewene rai, 
\q2 weramu Nya ayao bo mi syo rasyaniv. 
\q1  
\v 162 Inananibe irati Nya urairije rai, 
\q2 maisyare vatano ananibe romano po raugav no marova rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 163 Risyamo syonae daveo ayao aarurijate rai, 
\q2 yara Nya anaparatote obo mirati inanuga no rai. 
\q1  
\v 164 Masyote intabo rikangkamambe Naije kaururum, 
\q2 weye Nya patimu mamo moyar dave. 
\q1  
\v 165 Vatano manuga no Nya anaparatote rai nawamo una irati kovo saumane rai, 
\q2 unanta irati ana nsosobe inta rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 166 Sya AMISY, syo winanyuto Nyo inapaya irati kakai raiji, 
\q2 muno Nya ananyao mamo ibeto irati rai. 
\q1  
\v 167 Nya ananyao omirati syo raijaro matuve, 
\q2 muno inanuga no rai rave. 
\q1  
\v 168 Nya anaparatote muno Nya ananyao mamo syo raijaro matuve, 
\q2 weye sya ana dave mainy tenambe, omamo Nyo raen to. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 169 Sya AMISY, syare sya ana idawaine so more no Winui: 
\q2 syare Nyo ana ratantona ngkove raude rinai mamaisyo Nya ayao rai. 
\q1  
\v 170 Syare sya ana idanajo so more no Winui: 
\q2 Nyo inapaya kakai rai, mamaisyo Nya urairi rai. 
\q1  
\v 171 Koveamo inawa so mpaato kangkamane bo raijo Winai tutir, 
\q2 weye Nyo rinanyao irati Nya anaparatote rai. 
\q1  
\v 172 Koveamo inaunane so ngkiny irati Nya urairije rai, 
\q2 weye Nya ananyao mainy tenambe, omamo moyar dave. 
\q1  
\v 173 Syare Nyo rinasopan irati naneme rai, 
\q2 weye Nya anaparatote mirati syo patimu rave ritavondi rai. 
\q1  
\v 174 Sya AMISY, ribeke dave syare Nyo rinapaya irati kakai rai, 
\q2 muno Nya anaparatote mirati mo anayanambe raugavo rinanuga so rai. 
\q1  
\v 175 Koveamo Nyo inayaranande indamu rijayaisy tutir, wirati rikangkamambe Nai, 
\q2 muno Nya anaparatote omirati mo sopambe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 176 Risyamo vatano syanapatambe Nai, weramu syusyo marambe to, 
\q2 maisyare domba aumandi wemaisy. 
\q1 Weti sya Amisy, syare winde Nyo rinakani, 
\q2 weye Nya ananyao mamo rinanimarijo rai ramu. 
\c 120  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po inapaya irati vatano aarurijate mansai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavaro Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Syo AMISY awain arono rino irati ana nsosobe ama uga rai, 
\q2 muno Po sya ana danajo raveti mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo inapaya irati vatano wo aarurijate raker, 
\q2 muno wo anapamponae ratore mai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Inya, vatano wasaunane mansake weap, animaisye mi indati Amisye Po raugaje ratutumbe tavono wasai? 
\q2 Muno mangke mbetai ruimaisye mirati indati Po raugaje wasai? 
\q1  
\v 4 Wepi Po naite maveti wo ato nsasiu veano wasaivuiny, 
\q2 muno nuja ama nene nsundive rave\f + \fr 120:4 \fq nuja ama nene nsundive rave: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘nuja arar ama nene nsundive.’’ Nuja arar somamo inyo matu maisyare maraande ramaisy.\f* veano wasamer. 
\q1  
\v 5 Wakoe, kakaije nde rinai weye rino vatano wanave Amisye Ai jewene matavon, 
\q2 maisyare vatano mamun Mesek muno Kedar awa yasyine wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 6 Ntoa nugoenta rave to, 
\q2 rino irati vatano wonae kovo saumane rai umaso matavon. 
\q1  
\v 7 Risyamo ibekero kovo saumane rai, weramu ranivara syayao dai, 
\q2 weamo onawamo ubekero ivuinye obo rai. 
\c 121  
\s1 AMISY Opirati Po wansayaranande tutir 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano vatano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavar Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Syo unate so ranyanyube anyi, 
\q2 indati arepi de po rinasopan? 
\q1  
\v 2 De ti po rinasopane pamo AMISY, 
\q2 Opirati Po naume muno mine so ranari tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 3 Opamo aneme mpaya nai jewen, ti nto ntemaje ramu, 
\q2 Opamo ami maomombe ramu ti Po nayaranande tutir. 
\q1  
\v 4 Tugae, Amisy Po vatano Israel mansayaranande Opamo, 
\q2 ami maomono intai jewen muno niki intai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY Opirati Po nayaranande tutir, 
\q2 AMISY Opirati tuna nautan\f + \fr 121:5 \fq tuna nautan: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘tet no nanem ngkov,’’ omamo mbe rarorombe Opamo tuna nautan.\f* indamu darino naora. 
\q1  
\v 6 Weti indati uma apa mamoano masyote yasyine mo nanene jewen, 
\q2 muno embae ama vare mo anakotaro ngkakai raugavo nai jewen.\f + \fr 121:6 \ft Embae mamo arono wusyinoe vatane inta wanave ware mo wanene raugavo vatane mai.\f* 
\q1  
\v 7 Indati AMISY Po nayaranande ti anakotaro ngkakai inta nande nai jewen, 
\q2 muno Po nya njayaisye so rayaranande tutir. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY Po nayaranande tutir arono winto no rui rui vayave, 
\q2 nai unumeso ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 122  
\s1 Kovo saumane ranajo Yerusalem rai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavaro Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Rinanayanambe rave arono sya arakove wo rinawain ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Nde wanta no Yavaro AMISY.’’ 
\q1  
\v 2 Soamo reande wansayae to 
\q2 no unsanda akoe sisa no munijo Yerusalem. 
\q1  
\v 3 Yerusalem rauseo ntet to, 
\q2 omamo munijo vatane wo ranari ti ngkov dave muno ntindimu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Nai munije so, susyo Israel wangkuire, 
\q2 onawamo AMISY taune Apa kawasae nanawije, 
\q2 indamu wo AMISY Apa tame rawain, wo kove raura seo Ai, 
\q2 mamaisyo Apa ananyao Po raugaje\f + \fr 122:4 \ft Amisye Po ananyao raugaje Apa kawasae Israel mansai pare ude ubeaje Ai no Yerusalem tume intabo susye mandeij. Ul. 16:16-17. \f* Israel maije rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 No Yerusalem so, akari titi utantuna no awa kursijo titi rai indamu wo mangke rapatimu, 
\q2 akari umaso nanawamo una no tanoano susyo Daud. 
\q1  
\v 6 Syare wapo AMISY anajo indamu Po kovo saumane raugaje ntami Yerusalem rai: 
\q2 ‘‘Syare vatano manuga nto munijo Yerusalem raije nao awa ura irati kovo saumane rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Syare kovo saumane ntami no Yerusalem nya yano orame ama uga rai, 
\q2 muno nya soero ramane rai indamu nya vatano wo ramane utantuna mariraave vayave.’’ 
\q1  
\v 8 Rinaemen irati sya yavaruga muno sya arakovo Israel mai, weti syo raura syare: 
\q2 ‘‘Kovo saumane ntami no Yerusalem nya uga rai tutir!’’ 
\q1  
\v 9 Inanuga nto Yavaro AMISY, wama Amisye Apa yavare rai, 
\q2 weti risyo anajo indamu Po kove raugaje Yerusalem nai. 
\c 123  
\s1 AMISY anajo indamu aemeno wansai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavaro Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Sya Amisy, Winyirati Akari Titi ntuna no munijo Manunggara, 
\q2 Winyirati inamumbe ore Nai, syare syo nanajo. 
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY, reama Amisy, reamo winanyut ava naemeno reansai! 
\q2 Reansanaveano winamen, maisyare anya inta anaveano apa akari panapatambe ai amene wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare wanya ranaveano ama akoeyo manapatambe raije ramene wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 3 Naemeno reansai! AMISY, reamare naemeno reansai, 
\q2 weye vatane wo reansaura tantunawi tutira ndea naiso rave to. 
\q1  
\v 4 Vatano utantuna ananuge vone rai wo reansakaajiana nugoenta rave to, 
\q2 muno vatano umararine wo reansaura tantunawi tavon. 
\c 124  
\s1 AMISY ararimbe weye Po wansapaya wama marova mai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavar Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Ranivara AMISY be marimbe wansai jewen datire? 
\q2 Inya, vatano Israel, koveamo wapo raura taiso maisy: 
\q1  
\v 2 Ranivara AMISY be marimbe wansai jewen datire? 
\q2 Arono vatane usea ti umarovave wansai, 
\q1  
\v 3 weamo wo wansaubaisy ti wene mo wansaunto jayaibe, 
\q2 weye manuga mamune ntatupami wansai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weti wo wansao bintabo, maisyare manayame inta mo wansaugaveta wemaisy, 
\q2 muno maisyare manayame nsepadi wansai wemaisy, 
\q1  
\v 5 muno maisyare manayamo mpanyoane ama vambunine mo wansakupita wemaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY ararimbe, weye Opamo Po wansaunanto wama marova mai jewen, 
\q2 onawamo maisyare make sivuiny ware wo wansarisyi wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Yara wampapaya mai to, 
\q2 maisyare insanije upaya irati pamuno nsawa maije rai. 
\q2 Pamuno wem mpatimu ti wampapaya rai to. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY Wepirati Po naume muno mine so ranari, 
\q2 Opirati Po wansapaya irati kakai rai. 
\c 125  
\s1 Wana kovo saumane rai no Amisye anem uga 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavar Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\q1 Vatano wanave AMISY Ai onawamo maisyare unato Sion mangkiki kakai, 
\q2 nteto tindimuve tawan tutira nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 2 Maisyare papukame mo Yerusalem rayan kijani, 
\q2 omai tavon AMISY Po Apa kawasae mayan kijani Apa vambunine rai, 
\q2 arono naiso ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 3 Vatano mamun\f + \fr 125:3 \fq vatano mamun \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai. \f* indati ube akarivea nugoenta rave jewen, 
\q2 no kopa AMISY Po raosoro vatano kove mai rai, 
\q2 wirati vemo vatano kove\f + \fr 125:3 \fq vatano kove \ft onawamo vatano ubeta Amisye Apa ananyao rai.\f* utavondi wo anakotaro ngkakai rave tavon nora. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya AMISY, syare Winyo kove raugaje irati vatano kove mai, 
\q2 onawamo vatano utavondi Nya bekere rai nanawije. 
\q1  
\v 5 Yara vatano wo Nya unanuije rapaya ti ntami, wakata no unanuijo kakai nsosobe rai, 
\q2 koveamo AMISY Winyo mangke raugaje mansaijo vatano mamune mautan tenambe. 
\b  
\q1 Kovo saumane ntami Israel wansai! 
\c 126  
\s1 Wama siuri ma indati wamo ama ine raen 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavaro Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Arono AMISY Po Israel wansapaya munijo aroo rai indamu wamakare tantuna no Yerusalem rai, 
\q2 wakoe! omamo maisyare wanakimarive wemaisy, weye ana kove so nande wansai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Arono naije, anayanambe ntairijo wansanuga rai, 
\q2 muno wansananibe, wangkinyo ransyerane rai. 
\q1 Muno no susye kotare raito vatane wo raura ware: 
\q2 ‘‘Ana mbe anainambe somamo AMISY Wepi Po rave mai.’’ 
\q1  
\v 3 Tugae, AMISY Po ana mbe anainambe rave wansai to, 
\q2 omi mbewaramo wansanayanambe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Reama AMISY, reamare Nyo anakotare raveramu ngkovo reansai maisyare arono wusyine wemaisy akato, 
\q2 maisyare maru pape maje ti mana sapa anoko Negep\f + \fr 126:4 \ft Negep omamo anoko kanen no no Israel.\f* njam akato wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 5 Vatano po anare rayanyum ti siuri raija poyov, 
\q2 arono mare nsin to yamo gwain ananibe rautan. 
\q1  
\v 6 Vatano kumbaro anare rai ti siurija amingkaru ntende, 
\q2 indati gwain ananibe arono apa ingkuja ntairi ama ine rai ti nin ndautan. 
\c 127  
\s1 Amisy Apa bekobe rararimbe 
\p  
\v 1 Salomo apa ransyerano vatano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavar Amisy, no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Yavare ma ranivara AMISY Pi dauseo ntete jewen, 
\q2 weamo vatano wo ranarije onawamo ubea marudi. 
\q1 Ranivara AMISY Po munije ramane jewen, 
\q2 weamo vatano wo ramane onawamo ubea marudi tavon. 
\q1  
\v 2 Vemo nanuga mamauno anaisye rai jinya, 
\q2 weye Amisye Wepi Po vatano anuga no mai mansayaranande. 
\q1 Weramu ranivara nyo vambunine randari da nyo anaisye rakani ti 
\q2 winseo awatan ngkobea nyo anakere raijara nepata kaumure guisya nai, weamo mbea marudi, 
\q2 weye Amisye Pi Po nya mbekedaije raugaje nai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Tugae, arikainye nanawamo AMISY Wepi Po maugaje wansai, 
\q2 onawamo Apa kovo Po ratayao indamu wama ura rai inta mije. 
\q1  
\v 4 Arikainyo nanawirati mavaki arono aja pe akoeya me ta ikamuram, 
\q2 omamo raurata irati naite inta po ato raijar no aneme rai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kove ngkov irati vatano apa arikainye wanui ai, 
\q2 maisyare naite po ato manui rave raugasya no ama kokome rai ramaisy. 
\q1 Indati wepamo apa marova wo apinde kakai 
\q2 arono wo ayao kakai rantuna ai no akari mansamun. 
\c 128  
\s1 Kovo maje irati yavaruga rai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavaro Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Kove ngkov irati vatano are nawirati wo AMISY asyanive mai, 
\q2 muno ubeto irati Apa ananyao obo rai mai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Winyamo indati nyisyisyo nya anakero ndaijare ama ine rai, 
\q2 muno indati nanayanambe, wino kovo ngko dave obo rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Nya wanya mamo maisyare anggurije moto ama mane manui ramaisy, 
\q2 indati mo arikainye wanui mavaki no nya yavaruga rai. 
\q1 Nya arikainye nanawamo indati wanui, utantuna nya tewa\f + \fr 128:3 \fq tewa\ft : Ayao Ibrani raijamo ama ine mare ‘‘meja.’’\f* rakijani, 
\q2 maisyare inyo saitun ama kamine manui ntubai rakijani ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Maisyare omaisy tavon anya are pirati po AMISY asyaniv, 
\q2 indati Po kove raugaje ai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syare AMISY no no Sion Po kove raugaje irati nai, 
\q2 syare Po kovo ngko dave raugaje Yerusalem rai 
\q2 indamu nyo raen arono ta wingkove so. 
\q1  
\v 6 Syare indati nya tume nggwaravainy 
\q2 indamu ntuna nyo nya arikainye, ajavi mansaen. 
\q1 Syare kovo saumane ntami vatano Israel wansai. 
\c 129  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po kakai rasakinavo marova mai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavar Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 ‘‘Wama marova wo wansansuimbe no arono manasyine wea ndea naiso.’’ 
\q2 Omamo syare vatano Israel wapo raura nakato, wapare: 
\q1  
\v 2 ‘‘Wama marova wo wansansuimbe no arono manasyine wea ndea naiso, 
\q2 weramu wo wansapinde kakai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wo wansanepati ti pare ntuna wansakiri mona so rai janyi, 
\q2 maisyare vatane wo kopa rakarore ravabari ti ngkaipiti wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weramu AMISY Opamo moyar, 
\q2 Po wansapaya vatano mamune awa vambunine rai to.’’\f + \fr 129:4 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Po inapaya irati vatano mamun awa kaijo waije rai.’’ Arono vatano Israel una no munijo aroo Mesir, vatano mamune wo kaijo waije veano vatano Israel manepato mansakiri mona rai, wo mansantitidi mangkebe awa anakere rai.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Vatano mansanuga mamuno Sion\f + \fr 129:5 \ft Unato Sion no no Yerusalem, Yavaro Amisye ntuna rije.\f* rai nawamo, 
\q2 koveamo Nyo mapinde indamu wansuk akirive usamane. 
\q1  
\v 6 Koveamo onawamo maisyare insumai ntubai no manyume von,\f + \fr 129:6 \ft Arono wusyinoe vatano Israel awa yavare mamo yavaro oram ama vone mavae vayave muno kopa ntuna rai, weti intanamo insumai ntubai rai.\f* 
\q2 arono ntubai kaijoe, vatane wo rapatin akato ti mewen. 
\q1  
\v 7 Insumai umaso mo ininai ntubai no nawaisye ramaisy, 
\q2 vatane wo raugave ramu yara wo rapatin ti ntuna vayave. 
\q1  
\v 8 Weti vemo vatane inta ube arakobe mai jinya, 
\q2 vemo wo kove raura mai jinya, muno vemo usambayambe mai nora. 
\c 130  
\s1 Amisye anonae indamu aemeno wansai no nsosobe ama uga rai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran Israel ukiny dai arono wanya ti usea no Yavar Amisy rai no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, syo nawain arono rino ana nsosobe ama uga rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Sya Akoe Winy, syare Nyo sya anonae so ranaun, 
\q2 koveamo namarikoame rasakinav de sya ana danajo ore rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sya AMISY, ranivara Nyo reama ayao kakai ama manuije rator tenambe, 
\q2 weamo tugae, indati reanajivo Akoe Winya mangke raora kakai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weramu Winyirati mayaro Nyo vatane reama ayao kakaije rapaya reansai, 
\q2 indamu vatane reamo nasyaniv muno reambeaje Nai. 
\q1  
\v 5 AMISY, Winyirati syo nanyube, 
\q2 inanuga ntenami syo nanyube, 
\q2 muno Nya ayao mirati inanaveano ramen. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya jugara so bekero sya Akoe Winai, 
\q2 mo naito po munije inta rayaranande namane rai ti bekero nsansiman bavai, apa bekere rakivan. 
\q2 Tugae, mo naito po munije inta rayaranande namane rai ti bekero nsansiman bavai, apa bekere rakivan. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Inya, kawasae Israel wasanaveano AMISY obo amen! 
\q2 Weye AMISY Apa muinye no tawan, 
\q2 muno Opirati mayaro Po wansapaya kakai rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Opirati Po Israel wansapaya irati 
\q2 wama ana wandaveti ngkakai rai tenambe. 
\c 131  
\s1 Risaroro AMISY Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavar Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 AMISY, risyamo syo taune rinararine ramu, 
\q2 muno syo sya popane ranepate ramu. 
\q1 Risyamo inanuga nto irati anakotaro ntiti rave raije ramu, 
\q2 muno nto irati anakotaro mo sya ana idaene rakivane raije ramu. 
\q1  
\v 2 Weramu tugae, risyamo imainda no muno rino mariraave, 
\q2 maisyare arikainyo tuvane tuna akoeya rarijate wemaisy.\f + \fr 131:2 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘arikainyo po akoeya ama ukame rapaya to pa.’’\f* 
\q1 Arikainye niki mariraave arono akoeya mo akepan, 
\q2 maisyare wemaisy rinanuga som no mariraave. 
\q1  
\v 3 Inya, Israel syare wasanaveo AMISY amen, 
\q2 nai unumeso ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 132  
\s1 AMISY Po Daud aijaseo akari titi rai muno Po Sion ratayao terave Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavar Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, syare naemeno Daud ai, 
\q2 vemo mparandeno ai no apa siuri kotare rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 2 Vemo AMISY winanimari apa urairi po raokae nande Nai rai jinya, 
\q2 urairijo namirati po raokae nande Israel\f + \fr 132:2 \fq Israel\ft : ayao Ibrani mo ‘‘Yakop’’ ratoe weye aneno Yakop awain tavonamo ‘‘Israel.’’\f* reama Amisy Mbambunin Dave Winai rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 3 Po raura pare: ‘‘Tugae, risyamo indati risiso tuna no sya yavare ama uga rai rainy, 
\q2 riseo niki no vasyoto riniki ri rai jewen. 
\q1  
\v 4 Tugae, inamije mamo syo ratu ra niki jewen, 
\q2 indako, inamije maomon da niki mariraave jewen, 
\q1  
\v 5 weye syana syo yavare rauseo nteto mumuimbe AMISY amarom ndainy. 
\q2 Israel wama Amisy Bambunin Dave Apa tuna ri mamo syo ranari rainy.’’ 
\q1  
\v 6 Kasyamo urairije\f + \fr 132:6 \ft Kasyamo urairi omirati Amisye Apa urairi Po raokaisyo Israel mai raugasyo ntami rai.\f* mamo arono reana no Eprata\f + \fr 132:6 \fq Eprata \ft omamo Betlehem ama tamo wusyine mijem. \f* weamo reamo ranaun to, 
\q2 umba reamo rakanija reananta rai no anoko Yaar.\f + \fr 132:6 \fq Yaar \ft omamo munijo no no Yerusalem ama ranijo wanansai, ama nggwaravainyo Yerusalem rai mamo kilometeri abusyin eane mambisy (14), omirati kasyamo urairi raugaveto ntuna no we. Kasyamo urairi raugaveto ntuna no Yaar umasoamo nseo no tume tenam (20), no arono vatano Pilistin wo raugav akare kobe we, weye wo raugavo vatano Israel maora arono umarovave vatano Israel mai no wusyinoe. 1Sam. 4:1-6:16, 7:1-2; 2Sam. 6:2-15; 1Taw. 13:5-8, 15:5-12\f* 
\q1  
\v 7 Umba wo raura ware: ‘‘Wade ra wanta no AMISY Apa yavaro tuna ri, 
\q2 wade ra wambeaje Ai no Amun no Apa kursijo titi tuna ri.’’ 
\q1  
\v 8 Sya AMISY, syare mbeseo ra nde no tawan no Nya Yavar, 
\q2 nde no irati kasyamo urairi mbe rarorombe irati Nya vambunine raije rautan. 
\q1  
\v 9 Syare syeno wanapatambe Nai nawamo awa ana udave mamaisyo Nya mbekere rai, 
\q2 muno Nya kawasae nawamo ukiny mananibe. 
\q1  
\v 10 Daud opamo Nya vatano panapatambe nai, 
\q2 weti vemo nakirive Nya akarijo titi Nyo aijaseo umaso ai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 11 AMISY Po urairi raokae nande Daud ai to, 
\q2 muno Opamo indati Po Apa urairije rakanyoandi ramu, yara teto rai kobe. 
\q1 Po raura pare: ‘‘Daud nya arikainyo nyo avaki inta pirati indati Syo aijaseo akari titi rai, 
\q2 indamu be akari titive po nanigwan akato.\f + \fr 132:11 \ft 2Sam. 7:12-16; 1Taw. 17:11-14; Maz. 89:4-5; Arakov. 2:30\f* 
\q1  
\v 12 Weti ranivara nya arikainye, ajavije wo Sya urairi idaokae raijaro matuve, 
\q2 muno ubeta irati Sya ananyao Syo raugaje mai rai, 
\q1 weamo ntoa nuge nuganuijamo indati awa susyo wo mampame wo nanigwan utantuna akari titi rai tutir kobe.’’ 
\q1  
\v 13 Weye AMISY Po unato Sion rapatimu to, 
\q2 Opamo anuga no irati rai indamu tuna no we. 
\q1  
\v 14 Po raura pare: ‘‘Unato Sion so mirati indati ride no tawan no we, ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 unate so mirati indati rituna rai, weye rinanuga no rai mijem. 
\q1  
\v 15 Anaisye kotaro vatano una no Sion ubekedaije mamo indati Syo raunande ti mawes no awa munije we rai. 
\q2 Muno vatano ana jajewembe mai nawamo Syo anaisye raugaje mai ti wo raisya uman dave. 
\q1  
\v 16 Indati syeno una no Sion wo raura irati kawasae Israel mai, ware Risyirati Syo mapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q2 Muno vatano una no Sion nawamo ukiny mananibe. 
\q1  
\v 17 Indati nai Daud apa susyo po rampame rai, Risyo akari titi bambunine inta aijaseo no Sion rai. 
\q2 Indati apa be akari titive mamo Syo raveti ntindimu no tawan, 
\q2 maisyare yawainyo mbar ti no tawan tutire wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 18 Apa marova nawamo indati Syo mapinde ti usamane,\f + \fr 132:18 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘usamane dave maisyare ansuno manawadi inta mo matatuve wemaisy.’’\f* 
\q2 yara apa be akarive mamo Syo rainyave kovo no tawane rai.’’\f + \fr 132:18 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘apa kakiono emasije mamo indati mba dave,’’ ama ine mi ratoe no naiso. Kakiono emasi mbe rarorombe Daud apa be akarive rai.\f* 
\c 133  
\s1 Wambe arakobe mamo ngkov dave 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavar Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\b  
\q1 Tugae, ranivara wambe arakobe muno wantantuna kava wambe intabove, 
\q2 omamo ngkov dave muno wansananibe rave. 
\q1  
\v 2 Wambe arakobe ama kove mamo maisyare manino mbovov rauvaro syeno Harun akari rai, 
\q2 muno nsororop ti maje irati awarame rai, 
\q2 muno miridi makaje kobe apa ansune rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Muno wambe arakobe ama kove maisyare aakop maje unato Hermon rai, 
\q2 muno maje tavon no unato Sion rai janyi wemaisy. 
\q1 Nai ratuije AMISY Po Apa kove raugaje no we, 
\q2 omamo kovo nuge nuganui mije. 
\c 134  
\s1 AMISY ararimbe arono naman 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyerano Israel ukiny dai arono wanya usea no Yavaro Amisy no Yerusalem. 
\q1 Inya, syeno wapanapatambe AMISY Ai weap, 
\q2 wade wapo AMISY ararimbe, 
\q2 weapirati wade wapanapatambe Ai no Apa Yavar arono naman. 
\q1  
\v 2 Wasamumbe to no tanoano ndandinite\f + \fr 134:2 \ft Tanoano ndandinit ntami no Yavaro Amisye ama uga rai. Syeno titi obo pirati amayaro siso rai. Tanoane so kasyamo urairi raugaje ntuna rai. \f* rai, 
\q2 wasaneme raijaseo wasambayambe wapo AMISY ararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 3 Syare AMISY wepi no no Sion Po kove raugaje wasai, 
\q2 Wepi Po naume muno mine so ranari tenambe. 
\c 135  
\s1 AMISY Obo pirati mamaisyo ararimbe 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 AMISY Apa tame rararimbe! 
\q2 Inya, vatano wapanapatambe AMISY Ai weap, wapo ararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 2 Inya, syeno wapanapatambe AMISY Ai no Apa Yavare uga weap, 
\q2 weapirati wade wasambayambe no wama Amisye Apa Yavare ama wanijate. 
\q1  
\v 3 Wapo AMISY ararimbe weye Opamo kov dave, 
\q2 wakinyo ransyerane rai, wapo Apa Tame rararimbe weye Opamo aemeno wansai rave. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye AMISY Po Yakop apa susye matayao terave amarom, 
\q2 Israel wenawirati kawasae taune Apa ura terave mai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Weye syo raen tugae, AMISY Opamo panakoeve rave, 
\q2 Wepi rati Akoe, titi rave Po anawayo kotaro vatane wo masyanive makivan bintabo. 
\q1  
\v 6 Anakotar tenambe AMISY bekedaije mamo Po rave, 
\q2 nai naume warae muno mine so, 
\q2 mayane muno nawanano ntento. 
\q1  
\v 7 Nai mandepe ama ruduke rai, Wepi Po kamure raveti ntipu ti nde, 
\q2 Wepi Po ivake raveti ntavono maruge rai, 
\q2 muno Wepi Po ovare atutir indamu puje no apa tipugo raije rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Wepi Po arikainyo anui vatano Mesir mao bintabo, 
\q2 muno awa maere kotaro wo makume awa tuvano manasyin dave matavon. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wepi Po anainame muno anapaporainye rarorono vatano Mesir mai, 
\q2 omamo mangke Po raugaje irati Piraon muno apa aneneme mai vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 10 Wepi Po susye kotare wanui mataopon, 
\q2 muno Po awa akari titi awa vambunine rangkakeraive mansao: 
\q1  
\v 11 Wenawamo Amori awa akari titi Sihon, 
\q2 munijo Basan awa akari titi Og, 
\q2 muno akari titi susye kotaro ntuna no munijo Kanaan. 
\q1  
\v 12 Umba Po awa kopa raunanto irati Apa kawasae Israel mansai, 
\q2 indamu Apa kawasae Po matayao so awa ura rai tawan tutir. 
\q1  
\v 13 Sya AMISY, Nya tame mamo indati no pitawabe ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno sya AMISY, Nya tame mamo indati susyo miridi nto wo raen. 
\q1  
\v 14 Weye AMISY Po moyare rapatimu Apa kawasae mansai, 
\q2 muno aemen irati Apa vatano wanapatambe irati Aije mai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 Susye kotare nanawamo ubeaje irati yaro taune wo ranari maneme raije rai, 
\q2 omamo wo ranari irati peraki muno emasi rai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Mawa no mai, weramu wayaove kakai, 
\q2 mamije no mai, weramu wo nuge raene jewen, 
\q1  
\v 17 mamarikoame no mai, weramu wo ana ranaune ramu, 
\q2 weye manawayo meweno mai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Vatano wo yare ranari muno vatano wanave rai, 
\q2 wenawamo indati awa vambunine meweno mai maisyare awa yare ramaisy. 
\q1  
\v 19 Inya, kawasae Israel, wapo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Inya, syeno susyo Harun, wapo ararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 20 Inya, vatano susyo Lewi\f + \fr 135:20 \ft Susyo Lewi wanapatambe no Yavaro Amisy ama uga rai, wanapatambe irati syene awa anakere rai.\f*, wapo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Inya, vatan tenambe wabeaje AMISY Ai weap, wapo ararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 21 Wapo AMISY ararimbe no unato Sion, 
\q2 nai Yerusalem Apa tuna ri. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 136  
\s1 Amisye muiny dave 
\q1  
\v 1 Kove raura AMISY Ai, weye Opamo ko dave! 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye\f + \fr 136:1 \ft Ayao Ibrani \ft \+it hesed\+it* ama ine ratoe tumaimbe naiso mare: ‘‘muinye no tawan.’’ Ama ino manakoe mare: ‘‘Amisye Apa muinye muno Apa anakotaro Po raurairive ti no tawan tutiro Apa kawasae Israel mansai mamo Po raveti mamaisy.’’\f* no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 2 Kove raura Amisye Ai, Opi titi rave anawayo kotaro vatane wo masyanive makivan bintabo! 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 3 Kove raura Akoe Ai, Opi akarijo titi Po akari titi makivan tenambe! 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 4 Kove raura AMISY Ai, Obo pirati bambunin Po anainamo manakokoe raroron! 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 5 Po naume ranari jirati Apa ana datantona ntiti rai! 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 6 Opirati Po mine so raneka no mana ama vone rai!\f + \fr 136:6 \ft Kej. 1:9-10\f* 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wepi Po anakotaro ama vare manakokoe ranari no naume rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 8 Uma baro sansimane rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 9 Embae muno tume mbaro namane rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 10 Kove raura irati Amisye Ai, Opi po arikainyo anui Mesir mao tenambe.\f + \fr 136:10 \ft Muno Po maero makume awa tuvano manasyine mao tavon. Kel. 12:29\f* 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 11 Wepi Po vatano Israel maugav uje no munijo Mesir raora. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 12 Po maugav uje irati Apa vambunino manakoe rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 13 Kove raura irati Ai, Wepi Po Mayano Kolsum\f + \fr 136:13 \fq Mayano Kolsum: \ft ama tamo kaijinta mamo: ‘‘Mayano Nijam,’’ ‘‘Gelaga’’ muno ‘‘Teberau.’’\f* raotar ti mbe jirumbe. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 14 Wepi Po kawasae Israel maugav ti wo Mayano Kolsum ama yasyino kanene rainanta. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 15 Yara Piraona pe apa naite nanawamo Po matatuv asyo Mayano Kolsum rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 16 Kove raura Amisye Ai, Opi po Apa kawasae Israel maugav wanya no anoko kanene rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 17 Kove raura Amisye Ai, Wepi rati Po akarijo titi ubambunin mataopon. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 18 Wepi Po akarijo titi awa tame manakokoe mao. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 19 Po vatano Amori awa akari titi Sihon aubaisy. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 20 Muno Po munijo Basan awa akari titi Og aubaisy.\f + \fr 136:19,20 \ft Bil. 21:21-24,33-35; Ul. 2:30-33; 3:1-6\f* 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 21 Po awa kopa raunanto irati Apa kawasae mai indamu awa ura rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 22 Indamu Apa kawasae Israel wanapatambe Aije awa ura rai tawan tutir. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 23 Opamo aemeno Israel wansai tutir arono wama marova wo wansapinde. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 24 Muno Opi po wansapaya irati wama marova mai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 25 Wepi Po anakotaro njayaisye ravavirijo anaisye rai. 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 26 Kove raura Amisye Ai, Opi rati be akarive munijo ntiti rai! 
\q2 Tugae, Apa muinye no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 137  
\s1 Ransyerano weotor Israel maemembe akare Sion rai 
\q1  
\v 1 Nai mana akokoeyo njam anyi no munijo Babel ama tuga, 
\q2 wantantuna wamoyov wansaemembe akato Sion rai. 
\q1  
\v 2 Nai mana tuga umaso, 
\q2 wamo wama itari\f + \fr 137:2 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* ravesea nsaawa\f + \fr 137:2 \fq itari ravesea nsaawa: \ft ama ine mare vatano Israel wonae wo awa itari so raeyambe akato no munijo aroo ratuije, weye mansaemen akare awa munijo Sion rai.\f* inyo gandarusa rai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Weye vatano wo wansaijaro arove wo wansantitidi 
\q2 wangkinyo ransyerane raijo mansai. 
\q1 Vatano wo wansatawanto umaso wo wansantitidi 
\q2 indamu wangkinyo ransyerano marinsawane rai, muno wo wansakekebe ware: 
\q1 ‘‘Wakinyo ransyerano wakiny dai we no Sion inta raijo reansai!’’ 
\q1  
\v 4 Abo! Ransyerano wangkiny daive AMISY Ai mamo, 
\q2 no munijo marane so, mamaisyo wangkiny dai ramu! 
\q1  
\v 5 Inya, Yerusalem, ranivara inaemen akato winai jewen, 
\q2 weamo inanem ngkove so maindi kai, 
\q2 ti mo itari raeyan akato kakai! 
\q1  
\v 6 Ranivara inanimari Yerusalem winai, 
\q2 muno rinanayanambe manakoe winai akato rave jewen, 
\q2 weamo inaunane so ntumainy kai indamu rikiny akatoe jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Sya AMISY, syare naemeno vatano Edom awa ana udave rai, muno Nyo mangke rasakinavo mai. 
\q2 Onawamo arono naito Babel wo Yerusalem randujai we, 
\q2 wo raura ware: ‘‘Randamisyi! Randamisyi rave ramu masyo ruke rai rave!’’ 
\q1  
\v 8 Inya, munijo Babel, winyamo indati naupaeta ti nakanive! 
\q1 Weye nyo reansave tatugadi, 
\q2 weti syare kove ngkov irati vatano indati po mangke rasakinavo winai ai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Kove ngkov irati vatano po Babel nya arikainyo tuvane marigwainye ai, 
\q2 muno po maugaje mavari no orame rai ai.\f + \fr 137:9 \ft Wusyinoe, arono naite wo awa marova mapinde, weamo wo marova awa arikainye maugaje mavari no orame rai. 2Raj. 8:12; Yes. 13:16; Nahum 3:10\f* 
\c 138  
\s1 Ransyeran kangkamambe AMISY Ai, weye aemeno wansai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, syare syo kove raura seo Nai inanuga ntenami rautan, 
\q2 nai ana akokoe\f + \fr 138:1 \fq ana akokoe: \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware ayao so ama ine mare naito Amisy muno ana akokoe bambunin una no Manunggara, yara kuruno kaijinta ware ama ine mare ana akokoe wangkarive.\f* ubambunin no Manunggara mansamun, 
\q2 risyo ransyeran kangkamane veano nangkakivambe. 
\q1  
\v 2 Rinamumbeto no Nya Yavaro ndandinit, 
\q2 ribeaje Nai muno syo Nya tame rararimbe. 
\q1 Weye Winyamo Nya muinye no tawan muno winteto Nya urairi rai; 
\q2 weye Nya tame muno Nya urairi mamo Nyo raijaseo titive mo anakotaro kaijinta rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 3 Arono syo winanonae, Winyo sya ana idanonae ore raveti mamaisy, 
\q2 Winyo inanuga raveti mbambunin, weti rijanive jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Sya AMISY, vatan tenambe ube akarive no mine so nawamo indati wo nararimbe, 
\q2 weye wo Nya ayao ranaun to. 
\q1  
\v 5 Onawamo indati ukinyo ransyerane rai wo AMISY Nya ana ndave rangkakivambe, 
\q2 weye Nya kovo ntiti manakoe rave. 
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY Winyamo ntiti rave, weramu naemeno vatano awa tame maje rave mai, 
\q2 yara vatano umararine nawamo winggwaravainyo mansai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Ranivara rino irati ana nsosobe ama uga rai, 
\q2 Winyi Nyo rinayaranande ti rikov tutir. 
\q1 Winyavakare muno nanemo vambunine mo rinapaya, 
\q2 mo rinapaya irati marova awa parije rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY, Winya urairi mamo indati Nyo raveti mamaisyo rinai, 
\q2 sya AMISY, Nya muinyo no tawane mamo ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q2 Syare vemo naneme mpaya Nya kawasae reansai jinya! 
\c 139  
\s1 Amisye Po sya anakotare raen bintabo muno Opamo no no rui rui vayave 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, Winyo rinayasiro mavabe muno Nyo rinaen. 
\q1  
\v 2 Risya ana syo rave mamo Winyo raen bintabo; 
\q2 Wino no munijo ntiti weramu winanto risya ana syo ratantona rai tenambe to. 
\q1  
\v 3 Winami ntami rinai arono syo anakere raijar muno arono inaneme mpaya anakere rai; 
\q2 Winyo sya ana idave raen tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye tugae, AMISY, syana syo ayao inta raura rainyamo 
\q2 Winyo raeno wusyimbe to. 
\q1  
\v 5 Winyo rinayan kijani, 
\q2 muno Winya vambunine mo rinayaranande. 
\q1  
\v 6 Winya ana ndaene mamo ntiti rave rinakivan, 
\q2 weti vatane risyamo mamaisyo seo rai jewen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Nai rui rui rati syoroto ri umba Winya no no we jewen e? 
\q2 Nai rui rui vayave syoroto ri Winyamo no no sya wuisy! 
\q1  
\v 8 Ranivara risyare to seo no naumo warae, Winyamo no no we; 
\q2 ranivara risyare syakasyo niki no amanija ama uga waraya, Winyamo no no we.\f + \fr 139:8 \ft Amisye pamo wene nande Ai jewen, yara ayao so ama ine mare nai rui rui vayave vatane inta poroto ri, Amisye pamo no no we.\f* 
\q1  
\v 9 Ranivara ribadirir ti syo uma seo ri rakivan, 
\q2 muno syui ti to nanto no nawanane ama marano uma pasyo ri rai, 
\q2 Winyamo no no we, 
\q1  
\v 10 naije tavon Winyo rinaugav mavabe 
\q2 naije tavon winanem ngkov vambunine mo rinasopan kobe. 
\q1  
\v 11 Ranivara syare kaumure mo inatatuv mo rinangkokaibe, 
\q2 muno varo mo rinavare rakanive ta, yara kaumure bo ntami, 
\q2 ti syo rakarae syare Winyo rinaene ramu. 
\q1  
\v 12 Yara ana tugae mamo kaumuro namije mo rinangkokaibe Amisye Winya ana ndaene raije ramu, 
\q2 weye Winyo namane raen maisyare sansimane ntami, muno kaumure maisyare vare ntami. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Amisy, Winyirati Nyo inanuga muno rinanasine ranari tenambe vintabo; 
\q2 Nyo rinanari mavabe arono rino no ingkoa ranobon. 
\q1  
\v 14 Risyo nararimbe weye Winyo rinanarije mamo 
\q2 mbe anainambe muno mamai dave. 
\q1 Kotaro Winyo ranari tutudi mamo mbe anainambe, 
\q2 muno risyo raen omamo tugae rave. 
\q1  
\v 15 Risya pae mamo ngkokaibe Nai jewen 
\q2 arono rinanari no varoro ngkokaibe rai, 
\q2 arono Winyo rinanari no ingkoa ranobon.\f + \fr 139:15 \fq no ingkoa ranobon: \ft ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘no kopa ama ate,’’ ama ine mare ‘‘ingkoa ranobon.’’ \f* 
\q1  
\v 16 Amisy winami ntami rinai arono ta ribe manave no ingkoa ranobon. 
\q1 Risya masyoto rikovo rai tenambe 
\q2 omamo Winyo ratoe Nya bukuge raija ntuna to. 
\q1 Masyote umaso mainyamo Nyo rapatimu to 
\q2 arono umaso inta mana mamai dainy. 
\q1  
\v 17 Wakoe! Sya Amisy, Winya ana datantona mamo risosobe rinanto raiji, 
\q2 ama manui ma ratore kakai! 
\q1  
\v 18 Ranivara risyare idator, omamo mo nayavo mayano warave rakivan. 
\q1 Risyo Winya ana datantona ratora ntoa rui kai, rimamaisye jeweno rai vintabo, 
\q2 yara Winyamo ntuna rinautan tutir. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Syare Amisy Winyo vatano mamune\f + \fr 139:19 \fq vatano mamun \ft wenawamo vatano wonae Amisye Apa ananyao rai muno ananyao rui vayave rai.\f* maubaisy indamu mansaumandi, 
\q2 muno vatano wo mavuge rave maeparo marambe rinai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Onawamo wo mamune ratantona Nai, 
\q2 wayarurijabe muno ubesea umarovave Nai. 
\q1  
\v 21 Sya AMISY, vatano manuga mamuno Nai onawamo inanuga mamuno mai, 
\q2 muno syonae vatano ube marovave Winaije mai. 
\q1  
\v 22 Rinanuga mamuno mai rave tugae, 
\q2 muno rimarovave irati mansai tavon. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Sya Amisy, syare Winyo inanuga rakewar asyo indamu winanto inanuga rai; 
\q2 Syare Winyo inayasiro mavabe indamu winanto sya ana syo ratantona rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 24 Nyo inanuga raen ayao kakaije inta no rinaija rako? 
\q2 Syare Winyo rinaugav mavabe to no unanuijo kovo nuge nuganui rai. 
\c 140  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu darino wansaora irati vatano mamune mai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. Nto irati akari po vatano matayao ukiny maugavo ransyerane rai ai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo inapaya irati vatano mamune mai, 
\q2 no rinaora irati vatano wo ivuinye rave mai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Onawamo mansanuga mamo ana ngkakai obo mirati manantonave rai, 
\q2 muno masyote anteter wo arare raveti ntipu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Mansaunane mamo maisyare tawae mamune we, 
\q2 awa ana udatore mamo mamun dave maisyare tawae wakane ama mamune wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 5 Sya AMISY, syare ndarino rinaora irati vatano mamune awa vambunine rai, 
\q2 no rinaora irati vatano wo ivuinye rave mai, 
\q2 nanawirati ubeker ware wo inapinto nao. 
\q1  
\v 6 Vatano umararine wo isyeane ratugaro maninimbe ti mo inaman, 
\q2 muno wo pame rantet ti mo inaman indamu risawa rai, 
\q2 wo aviri ratugar ti mo inaman tavon no sya unanui idaito rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Syo raura AMISY Winai syare: ‘‘Winyirati sya Amisy, 
\q2 syare AMISY winamarikoame rasakinavo sya ana danajo so rai!’’ 
\q1  
\v 8 Sya Akoe AMISY, Winyirati mbambunin ti Nyo inapaya kakai rai, 
\q2 Winyirati ndarino rinaora no arono risiso marova rai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo vatano mamune awa ubekere ransopi, 
\q2 anakotaro kakai manatantonave rai mamo Nyo raorai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Syare vemo sya marova wo rinawariki so awa popane ranepataje rinai jinya, 
\q2 koveamo awa ana udator ti ngkakai makare ra mo taune manepat! 
\q1  
\v 11 Koveamo Nyo mangke tanamo nene nsundive rasui mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo mapinto atem mamai raito, indamu wakasen akatoe kakai. 
\q1  
\v 12 Vemo Nyo vatano wayarurijabe maen bayave mo una tawan no mine so inya, 
\q2 vatano wo ivuinye rave nawamo syare anakotaro ngkakai mo mansamayo rijat da mo makep. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Syo raen tugae, indati AMISY Nyo patimu moyare raugaje vatano matawanto mai, 
\q2 muno Nyo marimbe vatano awa ananuge jajewembe mai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Vatano ubeta Amisye Winai nawamo indati wo Nya tame rararimbe, 
\q2 muno vatano manuga nsarokire nawamo indati utantuna winatavon. 
\c 141  
\s1 Syare Amisye Winyo rinapaya irati vatano mamune awa vambunine rai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, syo winawain, weti syare nyavave Nyo rinaijaseo, 
\q2 syare Nyo rinaraniv arono syo winawain! 
\q1  
\v 2 Sya ana danajo seo Nai somamo syare Nyo rator siso 
\q2 maisyare kemenyano mbovov rameseo Winai wemaisy. 
\q1 Inaneme raijaseo ibe sambayambe somamo syare Nyo rator siso 
\q2 maisyare maero rameseo Nai no arono namandi wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo inawa so rayaranande, 
\q2 indamu vemo mpaato ayao kakaije rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 4 Syare Nyo inanuga so rayaranande, 
\q2 indamu vemo ntento ana ngkakainoanive rai jinya. 
\q1 Vemo syo ayao kakai rave inya, 
\q2 vemo rito naijaro vatano mamune matavon inya, 
\q2 vemo itavondijo awa one\f + \fr 141:4 \fq one: \ft Kuruno Ayao Amisy inta wo ratantona ware one somamo vatane wo rave indamu ubeaje awa yare rai.\f* rai tavon inya. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 \f + \fr 141:5-7 \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ayao no anemo 5-7 omamo mba kobe jewen.\f*Ranivara vatano mamai no Amisye Amune rai inta po inanayao, 
\q2 weamo muinyo rinai ije. 
\q1 Muno po inanyao indamu risakinavo sya ayao kakai rai, 
\q2 omamo maisyare manino mbovov randi inakari rai wemaisy; 
\q2 weti vemo syo rawatambe inya. 
\q1 Syo Amisye anajo tutir indamu Po vatano mamune awa ana udave ransopi. 
\q1  
\v 6-7 Arono indati vatane awa akari mamune maeparo pene rai, 
\q2 awa pae mamo mpusyiki no amani, 
\q2 maisyare orame raturi ti mpusyiki no min. 
\q1 Wea umba vatane wo raen ware sya ana daurave mamo tugae. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Weramu AMISY, Winyirati sya Akoe, syo naijaro sya usye rai, 
\q1 syare vemo winaneme mpaya rinai mo rikakai inya, 
\q2 weye Winyirati syakaore inamamavube Nai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Syare Nyo inayaranande irati isyeano sya marova wo ratugar ti mo rinamane rai, 
\q2 muno avirijo vatano mamune wo ratugar ti mo inaman tavone rai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Syare koveamo vatano mamune awa vavumo wo rave mamo taune wakata utatayasyo rai, 
\q2 yara risyamo inaugavo marambe rai. 
\c 142  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu no naora 
\p  
\v 1 Daud apa ransyerano ananyao arono no no tinda ama uga, umba po Amisye anajo.\f + \fr 142:1 \ft 1Sam. 22:1-2\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Inanamote raijaseo akoeve syo AMISY awain, 
\q2 syo AMISY anajo indamu aemeno rinai. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sya anakotaro syanonae rai mamo syo rave uje no Amisye Winamun, 
\q2 anakotaro nsosobe rinai mamo syo raura vintabo no Winamun. 
\q1  
\v 4 Arono sya vambunine kavintare mewen kobe, 
\q2 Winyamo Nyo sya unanuijo rito syakasiso rai raen to. 
\q2 Unanui syanya raito som, sya marova wo aviri ratugar maninimbe ti mo inaman. 
\q1  
\v 5 Syeravo inakiri, indati arepi de teto inakiri rai? 
\q2 Jewen bayave, inta po marimbe rinai ramu. 
\q1 Syansanan daowane meweno rinai to, 
\q2 vatane inta po inatantona akato ramu. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sya AMISY, risyo winawain, 
\q2 Wibuiny irati rigaugambe Nai, 
\q2 Wibuiny irati ribekero Nai arono ta rikov no mine so. 
\q1  
\v 7 Syare Nyo rinanyanyuto mavabe sya ana dawain ore rai, 
\q2 weye risyamo siuri rave, 
\q1 syare Nyo rinapaya irati sya marova mai 
\q2 weye onawamo awa vambunine mo inakivan. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare Nyo rinapaya irati ana nsosobe\f + \fr 142:8 \fq ana nsosobe: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘inapaya no makova rai.’’ Ama ine mare: ‘‘inapaya ana nsosobe mo inakikipi rai.’’ \f* mo inakikipi rai, 
\q2 indamu syo Nya tame raijaseo titive. 
\q1 Vatano ubeto irati Winai nawamo indati ude wanunugambe inakijani wenawe reamo nararimbe, 
\q2 weye wimbekobe irati rinai mamo manakoe. 
\c 143  
\s1 Amisye anajo indamu Po sopambe wansai muno Po wansaugavo unanui nsarokire raito 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Sya AMISY, syare namarikoame rasakinavo sya sambaya rai, 
\q2 syare Nyo sya ana danajo raraniv, 
\q1 muno Nyo ravera mamaisyo rinai, 
\q2 weye Winyamo moyar dave muno winteto Nya urairi rai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 2 Risyamo Nya vatano syanapatambe Nai, 
\q2 ti vemo Nyo mangke rapatimugo sya ayao kakai rai jinya, 
\q2 weye vatane inta mamai dave no winamune rai jewen bayave.\f + \fr 143:2 \ft Ayao so ama ine ratoe akato no Roma 3:20 muno Galatia 2:16 rai.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Weye sya marova po inangkarimu muno po inapinde, 
\q2 po rinaugaveto po rinansowave no varoro ngkaumudi rai, 
\q2 ti risyamo maisyare vatano rikakaija ntoa nugoenta to wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 4 Sya mayare nsaonto ti rakanive rinai to, 
\q2 muno inanuga mamaun dave. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Inaemen akato masyoto nde nto to rai janyi, 
\q2 syo Nya anakotaro ndave ratantonave, 
\q2 muno syo Nya ana ndave rakaraebeve. 
\q1  
\v 6 Inaneme raijaseo ore no Winui, syo winawain, 
\q2 sya jugara bekero Amisye Winai maisyare kopa ngkanembe mbekero mana nde rai wemaisy. 
\q1  
\v 7 Sya AMISY, syare nyavave Nyo sya ana danajo ravera mamaisy, 
\q2 weye ripapirabe akato ramu to! 
\q1 Vemo winakirive rinai nora, 
\q2 indamu vemo risyamo maisyare vatano kakai ti pasyo no atemo amanija rai to wemaisy inya. 
\q1  
\v 8 Syare Nya muinyo no tawane rarorono rinai no awatan ngkove yanteter, 
\q2 weye Wibuiny irati inanaveano namen! 
\q1 Syare Nyo unanui mamaisyo ritavondi rai rarorono rinai, 
\q2 weye Winyirati syo sya sambaya raura ore Nai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo inapaya irati sya marova mai, 
\q2 weye Wibuiny irati syakaore gaugambe Nai! 
\q1  
\v 10 Syare Nyo inanyao da ibeto Nya mbekere rai, 
\q2 weye Winyirati sya Amisye Pi Winy. 
\q1 Syare Amisye Winya Wayo Kove mo inaugav tutir 
\q2 no unanuijo nsarokire raito. 
\q1  
\v 11 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo kovo wanyine raugakare rinai, wirati syo Nya tame raijaseo titive, 
\q2 Nyo inapaya irati ana nsosobe rai weye Winyamo moyar muno ngkov dave tutir. 
\q1  
\v 12 Nya muinye no tawano rinai, weti syare Nyo sya marova maupaeta, 
\q2 muno vatano wo inansewabe nawamo Nyo mansaubaisy, 
\q2 weye risyamo Nya vatano syanapatambe Nai. 
\c 144  
\s1 Amisye ararimbe muno kove ranajo Ai 
\p  
\v 1 Masmur Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 Syo AMISY ararimbe! Wepirati sya unato oram inamamavube Ai. 
\q2 Wepirati Po inaneme ranyao marova rai, 
\q2 Wepirati Po inanyao indamu syo marova rave. 
\q1  
\v 2 Wepirati Apa muinye no tawano rinai muno be yambe inaora sya marova mai, 
\q2 Wepirati rinino aowan muno Po rinapaya kakai rai. 
\q1 Wepirati darino rinaora maisyare vakane ramaisy, ti rigaugambe Ai, 
\q2 Po susye kotare maveaje utantuna no inajo ate rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Sya AMISY, vatane nanawamo animai dave, weti Winyo mansatantona rave? 
\q2 Muno arikainyo vatane nanawamo animai dave ti Winyo matantona rave? 
\q1  
\v 4 Vatane nanawamo maisyare ovar bayave, 
\q2 awa ukov ti una no mine somamo maisyare ugara de to ti akanive. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Sya AMISY, syare Nyo naume raneka muno Nyaje no mine so, 
\q2 nyantukamo papukame rai indamu kijao mpatututo rai. 
\q1  
\v 6 Winyo ivake ratatukande, indamu sya marova mpusyek, 
\q2 Winyo Nya atoe ratapo, indamu sya marova unanajibe tatugadi. 
\q1  
\v 7 Winyi no no munijo Manunggara, syare naneme rareande indamu Nyo inapaya irati kakai rai. 
\q2 Syare Nyo rinapaya irati sya marova wanui rave\f + \fr 144:7 \fq marova wanui rave: \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Syare Nyo rinapaya irati mana njame rai.’’ Ayao ‘‘mana njam’’ omamo ananeneae ama ine mare marova wanui rave.\f* so mai, 
\q2 Nyo rinapaya irati sya marova susyo marane awa vambunine rai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Wenawamo ubekero wo aarurijate bo raker, 
\q2 muno wangkarive vayave arono wo urairije raokaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Sya Amisy, syare rikinyo ransyerano wanyine raijo Winai, 
\q2 syo itari anakoe\f + \fr 144:9 \fq itari anakoe \ft ranigwano ‘‘gambus’’ rai.\f* ama wai abusyin raeyan dai syo winararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 10 Winyirati Nyo anasineko raunande irati akari titi Israel mansai, 
\q2 muno Nyo Daud,\f + \fr 144:10 \fq Daud: \ft ayao so mo akari titi Daud obo aura jewen, yara mo apa susyo bakipambe nanawirati ube akari titive maura tenambe. \f* akari titi panapatambe irati Winai, apaya irati apa marova mai. 
\q1  
\v 11 Syare Nyo vatano mamune awa omake raveto marambe irati rinai, 
\q2 muno Nyo rinapaya irati susyo marane awa vambunine rai. 
\q1 Wenawamo ubekero wo aarurijate bo raker, 
\q2 muno wangkarive vayave arono wo urairije raokaisy. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Amisye, syare reama arikainyo anya nanawamo maisyare anare ntubai mavave muno ubambunin no arono ta ukamurame so. 
\q1 Muno syare reama arikainyo wanya nanawamo maisyare ajijo rave yavare rai, ratotov ti ngko dave. 
\q1  
\v 13 Syare reama yavare mamo ntairi anaisye kotare rai. 
\q1 Syare reama maero domba ntuna no anoke mainyamo mbaki janyi ti ama manui nseo ribuge abusyin rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 14 Syare reama maero sapi mainyamo indati ubakija\f + \fr 144:14 \fq ubakija: \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ino kaijinta mare: ‘‘Syare reama maero sapi mainyamo ubambunin dave indamu wo nawaisye ama ine raugav.’’ \f* awa tuvane wanui rave kobe, 
\q2 muno\f + \fr 144:14 \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ayao naiso mbare ramu. Ama ino kaijinta mare: ‘‘Vemo vatano Israel awa marova wo munijo Israel randamisy, wo mapinde umba wo maugaveto arove inya.’’\f* awa tuvane inta aumandi ramu muno tuvane inta kakai kamurambe no akoe ranobone ramu. 
\q1 Syare reama munije ama uga so raita, vemo reamo vatane inta mansanauno wanonae awa siuri rai jinya. 
\q1  
\v 15 Kove ngkov irati vatano nanawirati Amisye Po kovo maisyare umaso maisye raugaje mansai mai! 
\q2 Kove ngkov irati vatano are nawirati wo AMISY aura ware Opamo awa Amisye Pije! 
\c 145  
\s1 Ransyeran kangkaman weye AMISY Opamo muiny dave 
\p  
\v 1 Ransyeran kangkaman Daud po ratoe. 
\b  
\q1 \f + \fr 145:1 \ft Masmur so omamo ransyerano Ibrani \ft \+it akrostik\+it* inta mije, weye ntavondi urupijo Ibrani ama ntetebeaje rai. Weramu ayao Yawa ntavondi urupije so rai jewen.\f*Sya Amisy, Winyirati sya Akari Titi pi Winy, syare syo naijaseo titive, 
\q2 muno syare syo Nya tame rararimbe tutir ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 2 Masyote yanteter risyo nararimbe, 
\q2 muno syo Nya tame raijaseo titive tutira ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 3 AMISY Wepi panakoeve rave, weti obo Pi mamaisyo aura titive, 
\q2 Apa panakoeve mamo rarope kakai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Susyo mbakipambe iridito wo Nya anakero ndave rararimbe, 
\q2 muno wo Nya ana ndave makokoive ravovo mai tutir. 
\q1  
\v 5 Risyo winatantona tutir bayave, 
\q2 weye Nya kovo ntiti manakoe rave, 
\q2 muno Nya anainamo Nyo rarorone manakokoe. 
\q1  
\v 6 Nya anakotaro ndave manakokoive mamo indati susyo miridije nto wo ravovo tutir, 
\q2 muno Nya vambunino manakoe mamo indati syo rariri tutir. 
\q1  
\v 7 Indati susye umaso wayao akoeve Nai rave, weye Winyamo ngkov dave, 
\q2 muno ukinyo manamoto manakoeve rai irati Nya moyare rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 AMISY Opamo muiny dave muno aemeno wansai, 
\q2 Opamo atawandi ngkov dave, 
\q2 muno Apa muinyo no tawan omamo manakoe tutir. 
\q1  
\v 9 AMISY Opamo bekobe irati vatan tenambe mai, 
\q2 muno Opamo aemeno Apa anakotaro Po ranarije rai vintabo. 
\q1  
\v 10 Sya AMISY, anakotar tenambe Nyo ranari mo kove raura seo Nai, 
\q2 muno Nya kawasae nanawirati matawandi utavondi Nai nanawamo indati wo nararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 11 Wo ravov ware Wibuiny irati mbe akarive anakotare rai tenambe ngkov dave 
\q2 muno wo Nya vambunine raura kakavimbe. 
\q1  
\v 12 Indamu vatan tenambe wo Nya ana ndaveti makokoive raen, 
\q2 muno wo raen Nya mbe akarive anakotare rai tenambe omirati ngko dave. 
\q1  
\v 13 Winya mbe akari titive anakotare raije mamo ntoa nuge nuganui, 
\q2 muno Nya vambunine mamo manya tutir irati susyo miridije nto mai. 
\q1 AMISY teto Apa urairi rai tenambe tutir, 
\q2 muno anakotar tenambe Po rave mamo ntairijo Apa muinye rai. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 AMISY Po vatano utatayasyo maijaseo muno Po sopambe mai tutir, 
\q2 muno Po vatano matawanto maijaseo ti usayae tindimuve. 
\q1  
\v 15 Anakotar tenambe njayaisye manaveano AMISY winamen, 
\q2 muno Nyo anaisye raunanto mai arono ubeke dai. 
\q1  
\v 16 Ranivara Winy naneme rarorono mai, 
\q2 weamo awa anaisyo ubekedaije mamo Nyo raunanto mai. 
\q1  
\v 17 AMISY Po anakotar tenambe rave mamaisyo Apa anuga mamaisye rai, 
\q2 muno Apa muinye no tawan tutiro Apa anakotaro danari rai tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 18 AMISY Opamo pararai jirati vatano wo anonae tutire mai, 
\q2 muno vatano nanawirati wo anajo manuga ntenami rai. 
\q1  
\v 19 Wepamo Po vatano arenao bayave ubeaje Ai awa ana ubekedai raunande ti mamaisyo mai, 
\q2 muno Opamo po vatane awa ana wo ranonae seo Ai raraniv muno Po mapaya irati awa siurije rai. 
\q1  
\v 20 AMISY Po vatan tenambe manuga no Ai tugaive mayaranande, 
\q2 yara vatano wonae Ai nanawamo Po mao. 
\q1  
\v 21 Risyamo syare syo AMISY ararimbe tutir, 
\q2 syare vatan tenambe wo AMISY Apa tamo ndandinit rararimbe tutir ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\c 146  
\s1 Kove ngkovo vatano anaveano AMISY amen 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Inya sya jugara, nyo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 2 Syare syo AMISY ararimbe arono ta rikov, 
\q2 muno rikinyo ransyerane rai sya Amisy Ai arono ta rituna. 
\q1  
\v 3 Mbemo mamanaive nanto akari mine so mai jinya, 
\q2 muno nanto vatano rui vayave mai jinya, 
\q2 weye ubambunin wo kove raugave kakai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Arono ugwenen, wakasya no kopa, masyoto we tavon wenawamo 
\q2 awa ana wo ratantona ti ware wo raijare mamo raumandita. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kove ngkov irati vatano manaveano AMISY amen, 
\q2 weye awa Amisyo panapatambe mai Opirati Yakop apa Amisye tavon. 
\q1  
\v 6 Wepirati Po naume, munije muno mayane ranari 
\q2 muno anakotar ntuna no ama uga rautan; 
\q2 Wepi teto Apa urairi rai ma no tawan ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q1  
\v 7 AMISY Wepi be marimbe vatano matekarasyo mai ti Po maijaseo kove rai, 
\q2 muno Po anaisye raunanto vatano marore mai. 
\q1 Po vatano makova mapaya, 
\q1  
\v 8 muno vatano mansamije ntuba nanawamo Po mamije raneka weti wo nuge raen. 
\q1 AMISY Wepi Po vatano utatayasyo maijaseo usayae tindimuve, 
\q2 muno bekobe vatano ubeto Aije mai. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wepi Po vatano maran udesen mansayaranande; 
\q2 Wepi panapatambe irati wanya kavini muno arikainyo wawate mai, 
\q2 yara Po vatano wonae Ai awa bekere ransopi. 
\q1  
\v 10 AMISY Opamo akarijo titi ntoa nuge nuganui. 
\q2 Inya, munijo Sion\f + \fr 146:10 \fq Sion \ft omamo Yerusalem ama tamo wusyine mije.\f*, winya Amisye be akarive susyo miridije nto mansai tutir. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 147  
\s1 AMISY ararimbe weye Opamo bambunin dave 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 Tugae, wama Amisye ararimbe omamo ngkov, 
\q2 wangkiny Amisy ararimbe omi mamaisy muno ngkov dave. 
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY Po Yerusalem raijar akaeyo ntet, 
\q2 Po vatano Israel maepar no aroo rai maugav akare.\f + \fr 147:2 \fq vatano Israel maepar no aroo rai: \ft Vatano Israel nawamo awa marova Babel wo mapinde ti wo maugavo arove uta no muni Babel rai. Nugoenta umba Amisye Po Apa kawasae Israel mapaya aroo rai, Po maugav akare no taune awa munijo Israel rai jakato.\f* 
\q1  
\v 3 Wepi Po saumane raunanto vatano manuga mpatimu mai, 
\q2 muno Po awa pare ratavabandi. 
\q1  
\v 4 Wepi Po tumo naume warae ama manui rapatimu, 
\q2 muno Po tame raunanto mai tutudi. 
\q1  
\v 5 Akoe Opamo panakoeve rave muno vambunine ntairi Ai, 
\q2 Apa ana daene mamo manakoe rave ti rarope kakai. 
\q1  
\v 6 AMISY Po vatano matakarasyo mansasopambe, 
\q2 yara Po vatano wonae Ai matakarasyo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Wakinyo ransyerane rai kove raura seo AMISY Ai, 
\q2 itari\f + \fr 147:7 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai. \f* raeyan, kinyo ransyerane rai veano wama Amisye ararimbe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Wepi Po kamure raveti mo naume ratatuv, 
\q2 Wepi Po maru ratayao mine so rai, 
\q2 muno Po insumai raveti ntatubai unate rai janyi. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wepi Po anaisye raunanto maere kotare mai, 
\q2 muno Po anaisye raunanto wawake tuvano wo anaisye ranajo mai. 
\q1  
\v 10 Amisye opamo anayanambe kuda marova awa vambunine rai ramu, 
\q2 muno Opamo anayanambe naite awa vambunine rai ramu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Yara AMISY anayanambe irati vatano wo asyanive mai, 
\q2 wenawamo vatano manaveano Apa muinyo no tawan tutire ramen. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Inya, vatano Yerusalem, wapo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Inya, vatano Sion,\f + \fr 147:12 \fq Sion \ft \fq \ft omamo Yerusalem ama tamo wusyine mije.\f* wakangkamambe wapa Amisye Ai! 
\q1  
\v 13 Weye Wepirati Po wapa munije rayaranande ti bambunin 
\q2 muno Wepi Po kove raugaje wapa arikainye mai. 
\q1  
\v 14 Wepi Po wapa muni rayaranande ti no irati kovo nsaumane rai, 
\q2 muno Po anaisyo ngkov dave\f + \fr 147:14 \ft Ayao Ibrani ama ine maisyare so: ‘‘gandum.’’\f* raunande wasai inda waman. 
\q1  
\v 15 AMISY Po Apa ayao raugaje ntami mine so rai, 
\q2 naije kobe Apa ana daura so nande mamaisy. 
\q1  
\v 16 Wepi Po salju\f + \fr 147:16 \ft Salju omamo ama nanayao mo esije ramaisy weramu nsaon maisyare kapum ti mo nuge ratatuv.\f* raugaje mo mine so ratatuv maisyare tani wemaisy, 
\q2 Po raavaro mine so rai maisyare kapumo we. 
\q1  
\v 17 Po maru oram raeparo mine so rai maisyare oram kami we, 
\q2 indati vatane inta atawandi teto ama nanayao rai kakai. 
\q1  
\v 18 Arono AMISY payao aje maru orame rai, ninimi kobe ti mbe manave, 
\q2 Po ovare amawisy ti mo mana ninimi umaso raveti njam. 
\q1  
\v 19 AMISY Po Apa ayao raura aje Yakop apa susye obo mai, 
\q2 Po Apa ananyao muno Apa anaparatote raura aje Apa kawasae Israel\f + \fr 147:19 \ft Israel onawamo Yakop apa susyo po mampame nawa.\f* umaso obo mansai. 
\q1  
\v 20 Yara Po raugaje susyo kaijinta mai ramu, 
\q2 muno wenawamo wantatukambe Apa ana dapatimu rai. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 148  
\s1 Naume muno mine so kangkamambe AMISY Ai 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 Kangkamambe AMISY Ai no Manunggara, 
\q2 Kangkamambe Ai no munijo ntiti! 
\q1  
\v 2 Inya, naito Amisy wea tenambe, wakangkamambe Ai! 
\q2 Inya, Apa naito wapanapatambe Aije wea bintabo, wakangkamambe Ai! 
\q1  
\v 3 Inya, uma muno embae, kangkamambe AMISY Ai! 
\q2 Inya, kotaro tumo mba dave, kangkamambe Ai! 
\q1  
\v 4 Inya, naumo ntiti rave, kangkamambe Ai! 
\q2 Inya, mana ntuna no naume ama vono warae,\f + \fr 148:4 \fq mana ntuna no naume ama vono warae: \ft Kej. 1:6-7\f* kangkamambe Ai! 
\q1  
\v 5 Koveamo anakotar tenambe kangkamambe AMISY Ai, 
\q2 weye Wepi anamote webo mamo anakotare no tenambe. 
\q1  
\v 6 Wepi Po anakotar tenambe raosor muno Po ama ntuna rije rapatimu, 
\q2 ti inta mo inta rakivandije kakai yara no tawan tutira nuge nuganui. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Kangkamambe AMISY Ai no mine so, 
\q2 inya, nawanan maneka muno tawae akokoe kotar ntuna no ama uga rai! 
\q1  
\v 8 Inya, ivake muno maru oram, aivavu muno kamayo, 
\q2 ovaro rep mbeto Apa anamote rai! 
\q1  
\v 9 Inya, unate muno papukame, 
\q2 inya, inyoaman rayanyum muno inyo kotaro ntubai no anate rai! 
\q1  
\v 10 Inya, maere kotaro nsisyaube muno kotaro ngkokobe, 
\q2 anakotaro nsanon muno insani! 
\q1  
\v 11 Inya, akarijo titi mine weap muno susye kotar tenambe mine so, 
\q2 akarijo rui vayave muno pemerinta mine so tenambe! 
\q1  
\v 12 Inya, arikainyo anya mansae muno arikainyo wanya mansae weap, 
\q2 vatan anui muno vatano kamuram! 
\q1  
\v 13 Koveamo wea tenambe wakangkamambe AMISY Ai 
\q2 weye Apa tame webo mirati ntitijo kaije rakivan, 
\q2 Apa kovo ntiti mo mine so muno naume warae rakivan. 
\q1  
\v 14 Wepi Po Apa vambunine raugasyo Apa kawasae mansai to.\f + \fr 148:14 \ft Ayao Ibrani maisyare so: ‘‘Amisye Po korodowai raijaseo,’’ ama ine mare Amisye Po vambunine raugaje Apa kawasae Israel mansai ti ubambunin no marova rai.\f* 
\q2 Weti Apa vatano matawandi utavondi Ai nawamo wo ararimbe, 
\q2 onawirati vatano Israel, Amisy taune anuga no mansai rave. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 149  
\s1 Ransyeran kangkaman anasineko 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 Wakinyo ransyerano nggwanyine raijo AMISY Ai! 
\q2 Inya, vatano wasatawandi watavondi Amisye Ai weap, wapo ararimbe no wapa anugane rai! 
\q1  
\v 2 Inya, Israel, wasanayanambe weye Wepi Po wasanari; 
\q2 Inya, vatano wana no Sion,\f + \fr 149:2 \ft \fq Sion \ft omamo munijo Yerusalem ama tamo wusyine mijem, muno veano vatano Israel mawain tavon.\f* wasananibe weye wapa Akarijo Titi pije! 
\q1  
\v 3 Wasarer indamu Apa tame rararimbe, 
\q2 weapo itari raeyan muno airape\f + \fr 149:3 \fq itari \ft ranigwano ‘‘kecapi’’ rai muno \fq airape \ft ranigwano ‘‘rebana’’ rai.\f* ranepat indamu AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 4 Weye AMISY anuga no irati Apa kawasae mai; 
\q2 muno Wepi Po anasineko marova mai raunanto irati vatano manuga mpaaje mai. 
\q1  
\v 5 Indati Apa vatano matawandi utavondi Aije nawamo umananibe 
\q2 weye Po marova apinde to, 
\q2 muno ukiny manayanambe no arono unaki. 
\q1  
\v 6 Koveamo wenao ukangkamambe Amisye Ai rave manamoto manakoeve rai, 
\q2 umba wo anaiyu nsansinao raijaro maneme rai. 
\q1  
\v 7 Indamu wo marova rasakinavo susyo wanave Amisye Ai jewene mansai, 
\q2 muno mangke raugaje irati susye kotaro wanave Ai jewene mansai. 
\q1  
\v 8 Indamu wo poor besi raasaro awa akarijo titi mai, 
\q2 muno waijo besi veano awa akarijo wo nuge raijanande maokaisy. 
\q1  
\v 9 Maisyare omaisy, wo mangke raugaje susyo mine so mai, 
\q2 mamaisyo Amisye Apa dapatimuge rai. 
\q1 Omirati kovo manakoe Amisye Po raugaje Apa kawasae matawandi utavondi Ai mansai mijem. 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\c 150  
\s1 AMISY ararimbe 
\q1  
\v 1 AMISY ararimbe! 
\q2 Amisy ararimbe no Apa tuna ri ndandinit rai! 
\q2 Apa vambunine rararimbe no naumo ntiti ntindimu rai! 
\q1  
\v 2 AMISY ararimbe weye Apa ana dave makokoive, 
\q2 AMISY ararimbe weye Apa kovo ntiti manakoe rave! 
\q1  
\v 3 Tavuna\f + \fr 150:3 \ft Tavuna Israel wo rave mamo korodowai kambino anya.\f* ramawisy veano AMISY ararimbe, 
\q2 Itari anakoe muno itari mamaun\f + \fr 150:3 \fq Itari anakoe \ft muno \fq itari mamaun \ft ranigwano ‘‘gambus’’ muno ‘‘kecapi’’ rai.\f* raeyan veano AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 4 Airap\f + \fr 150:4 \fq Airap \ft ranigwano ‘‘rebana’’ rai. Rebana ranepat maisyare airape ranepat wemaisy.\f* ranepat wasarer indamu AMISY ararimbe, 
\q2 Itari raeyan muno suline ramawisy indamu veano AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 5 Ceracap\f + \fr 150:5 \fq Ceracap \ft omamo maisyare potami vasye jirum yamaisy umba yapapoambe.\f* mamaun yapapoambe veano AMISY ararimbe, 
\q2 Ceracap anakoe yapapoambe indamu veano AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1  
\v 6 Koveamo anakotaro njayaisy tenambe wo AMISY ararimbe! 
\q1 AMISY ararimbe! 